local a={"Riichi","Double Riichi","Chii","Pon (Call for Triplet)","Kan (Call for Quad)","{10}Kita","Ron! !!","Tsumo! !!","Hello! My name is Ichihime. Glad to meet you-nya!","Come on, let\'s play, nyaa! In this room, time is points, nyaa!","I’m Invincible nyaa!","Victory, nyaa!","Nyaaaaa!","Master, welcome back-nyaa!","Master, I have been a good girl today-nyaa.","Master, where is my lunch?","Declare Riichi as soon as possible. Fast attack for the win!","What’s Yaku? I only play by feel-nyaa.","Wow, that smells good. You’ve got some goodies in your pocket? Let me see! ...Hmm? Why are you blushing, Master?","Nyaa~...Snacks always taste better when they are given to me by someone else. I want more!","My favorite foods are chestnut and baked sweet potatoes. Have you remembered? See what they are selling over there? That’s it-nyaa.","Cat ears are very sensitive and fragile. They can’t be touched by random, ordinary people! Speaking of them, master, would you like to touch them-nyaa?","My favorite toys are - Mahjong and master!","Nyaa? Is this for me? You are so kind!","A gift? Is it something yummy?","Master, you have been very active today. I will make sure I become better to repay your favor-nyaa.","Defensive Mahjong? That’s so boring, master. Mahjong is all about attacking. Come, let’s go forward together!","Master, let\'s always play Mahjong together! Today, tomorrow, and forever hereafter-nyaa!","I am very rebellious, so make sure you keep a close eye on me. Otherwise, I may run away from you anytime-nyaa.","Master, is Ichihime sick-nyaa? Recently, whenever master is not around, Ichihime would become very restless and want to scratch all the cardboards into pieces. But as soon as master appears, all the problems seem to go away. Hey, master, do you know the reason? Otherwise, Ichihime would have to make a doll of master and carry it like Chiori does, nyaa!","Miki said once we made a bonding promise, master would buy unlimited snacks for Ichihime-nyaa! But wasn\'t master already Ichihime\'s master long ago? If that\'s the case, what does this bonding promise really do, nyaa?","Happy New Year, master! Quick, where is the loaded red envelope for Ichihime? Nyaa nyaa? My new year\'s red envelope needs to be the biggest nyaa, bigger than those of the others nyaa! Or else, you won\'t be able to touch my ears in the new year nyaa!","Valentine\'s Day? Nyaa? What\'s that? Something eatable? Well, I\'m only interested in festivals when I can keep eating...Nyaa? What\'s this? Master, why do you have so many chocolates? Mind giving me some?! Awesome nyaa! ...Master, why do you look helpless? Don\'t tell me they can\'t be eaten...Nyaa! So they are eatable! My master is the best nyaa!","{5}Robbing a Kan","After a Kan","Under the Sea","{5}under the river","East","South","West","North","Red","White","Green","East Repeat","{5}south repeat","West Repeat","North Repeat","All Simples","Pure Double Sequence","Pinfu","{5}half outside hand","Pure Straight","Mixed Triple Sequence","Triple Triplets","Three Quads","All Triplets","{5}three concealed triplets","Little Three Dragons","All Terminals and Honors","Seven Pairs","{5}fully outside hand","Half Flush","{5}twice pure double sequence","Full Flush","Riichi","Double Riichi","Tsumo","Ippatsu","Dora","Dora 2","Dora 3","Dora 4","Dora 5","Dora 6","Dora 7","Dora 8","Dora 9","Dora 10","Dora 11","Dora 12","Lots of Dora","{5}blessing of heaven","{5}blessing of earth","Big Three Dragons","Four Concealed Triplets","{5}single-wait four concealed triplets","All Honors","All Green","All Terminals","Thirteen Orphans","Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans","Four Big Winds","Four Little Winds","Four Quads","Nine Gates","True Nine Gates","Mangan at Draw","Counted Yakuman","Mangan","Haneman","Baiman","Sanbaiman","Yakuman","Double Yakuman","Triple Yakuman","Quadruple Yakuman","Quintuple Yakuman","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Four-Player Riichi, nyaa.","{5}nine different terminals and honors","Dealing into Win after Kan","Root","Terminals in All Sets","Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Pure Triplets","2/5/8 Triplets","Seven Pairs with One Duplicate","Pure Seven Pairs","All Terminals","Pure Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Pure Seven Pairs with One Duplicate","Four Quads","Pure Four Quads","Ichihime wants to take the tile back, nyaa...","Nyaa! Ichihime\'s Dora!","1, 2, 3, 4... Nyaa? Only 10 tiles left?","Woah—Ichihime\'s mega victory, nyaa!","Ichihime must tell master, nyaa!","I won\'t go easy on you today, nyaa!","Hurry up and sit down, nyaa!","Riichi","Double Riichi","Chii","Pon (Call for Triplet)","Kan (Call for Quad)","{10}Kita","Ron, hehehe~","Tsumo. Oops, sorry~","[0]I am Miki Nikaido. [2000]Glad to meet you~","Make your move with caution.","It\'s my victory.","Well well, how enthusiastic... For some reason, my body is heating up...","This feeling of release... so intoxicating!","[0]Welcome back~ [1600]What are you going to do today?","[0]Ah, [600]here you are. [2200]I was thinking of you~","[0]Riichi! [800]Ippatsu! [2300]Haha~ just kidding~","[0]If you can win me over on the Mahjong table, [2500] I will give you a little surprise.","[0]Mahjong is fun. [2000]But...[2900]If I can play with someone I like...[4500]That’s even better~","[0]That’s it? So soon? [2500]I haven’t had enough yet...[6100]Hmm~? [7600]I mean the Mahjong game [10500]just now.","[0]Hmm~? [1100]Did you say you don’t know where to look? [3500](laughter)[3700]What shall I say. [6500]You can look at anywhere~ [8500]that~ [9000]you~ [9600]like~ [10200]to~","[0]Make sure you train hard today~ [2100]I\'m waiting for you to beat me.","[0]Ah...[700]You look a little sleepy. [3900]Do you want to lie on my knees...? [7500]Oops? [8900]Why are you suddenly so awake?","[0]The Moon [500]looks...[2400]so beautiful...","[0]Thank you! [900]I will take good care of it~","[0]As long as it’s from you, [1900]I love it.","[0](Smiles)[1500]Do you really want to get close to me so badly? [4800]No - way. [6300]You need to work harder.","[0]Ever since I started playing Mahjong, [1800]I have enjoyed every single day. [4400]Of course, you are also one of the reasons~","[0]Mahjong is amazing. [2200]No matter how good I am, I still may lose; [6300]no matter how bad I play, I may still win. [12000]This mixed feeling of both uncertainty and anticipation, [17200]is exactly like what I see from you when you stand in front of me~","[0]I have become more fabulous. [3200](Smiles)[4800]Don\'t worry, [6800]my beauty will belong to you only [9900]from now onward.","Sometimes I feel like you are really an interesting one. What, are you surprised? Hehe, that\'s quite interesting too! I will make sure to find out more interesting facts about you in the days to come!","A bond isn\'t a childish joke, but something you must hold onto for a lifetime! Well, since we have made a bonding promise together, I will hold you responsible for it! As for how to do that, hehe, I have a long time to teach- you- slowly!","Happy New Year, my little cutie pie! Wait, you don\'t like your new name? Hey, I had been thinking for so long before I came up with this special name for you. From this year onward, I\'ll come up with a new nickname for you every year, hehe!","Surprised to receive my chocolates, aren\'t you? Well, it\'s written on your face. You keep throwing your tantrum the entire day just because you haven\'t received my chocolates, am I right? I\'m giving it out late on purpose. You know, I can only see such cute expression of yours by pulling a prank on you.","{5}Robbing a Kan","After a Kan","Under the Sea","{5}under the river","South","{5}south repeat","West Repeat","North Repeat","All Simples","Pinfu","{5}half outside hand","Mixed Triple Sequence","Triple Triplets","Three Quads","{5}three concealed triplets","Little Three Dragons","All Terminals and Honors","{5}fully outside hand","Half Flush","{5}twice pure double sequence","Riichi","Dora","Dora 2","Dora 3","Dora 4","Dora 5","Dora 6","Dora 7","Dora 8","Dora 9","Dora 10","Dora 11","Dora 12","Lots of Dora","Big Three Dragons","Four Concealed Triplets","{5}single-wait four concealed triplets","Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans","Nine Gates","True Nine Gates","Mangan at Draw","Counted Yakuman","Mangan","Haneman","Baiman","Sanbaiman","Yakuman","Double Yakuman","Triple Yakuman","Quadruple Yakuman","Quintuple Yakuman","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","It\'s a Four-Player Riichi.","{5}nine different terminals and honors","Oops, this tile just keeps coming!","You will be punished for eating my Dora!","This is getting exciting!","Winning is so enjoyable!","Wow, a pleasant surprise. Jyanshi, did you bring me good luck? Hehe!","How could I possibly miss a party like this, hehe.","We\'ve been waiting just for you...","Riichi","Double Riichi","Chii","Pon (Call for Triplet)","Kan (Call for Quad)","{10}Kita","Ron!","Tsumo!","Thank you for choosing me. I will keep working hard in future!","SHOW TIME!","Yay! Kana-chan here. I’m the TOP1 idol!","Nice win!","There\'s only room for one star on this stage, and that\'s me!","HELLO! Everyone! Please continue supporting me!","Ah, you are finally here. What shall we play today?","Hmm...The “efficiency” you mentioned sounds so troublesome...I just want to play All Simples, that’s enough.","What a beautiful day! It’s a perfect day to stay at home...Oops...to work!","(Sighs)Is today’s event over yet? I really want to go home...","What’s the trouble of being an idol? Work has taken too much game time away from me, I guess!","Hey, if you want my signed photo, please wait for the next signing session!","Sometimes, I want to have a break too. Let’s sing Karaoke together!","I didn\'t expect you to be so charming when you’re playing Mahjong~ For a second there I was attracted to you! But it was just for a moment only! Haha~","Here’s a special sleep therapy voice for you. One sheep, two sheep, three sheep, four... ZZZZZ...","Thank you for your support!","Wow! ~~~~~~~This is great!!!!!! Thank you!","I will work twice as hard today!","You are always cheering for me whenever I feel tired. I will work hard, for you!","Hey, if I’m no longer an idol, will you still support me as you always? ...Haha, just kidding!","From now on, I will be a fan of yours. You must also shine for me~","You should continue to come to Kana\'s concert. For some reason, when I see you in the audience, I feel like I can give my best performance! Haha, are you surprised at how attractive you are? If you become an idol, maybe you will be unexpectedly popular!","\"What if Kana is no longer an idol?\" That will never happen. Even if Kana stops being an idol for everyone, I will still be the idol for you, so your eyes will always be on Kana and Kana only.","Shh...Kana actually sneaked out from the backstage! Cough...Happy New Year!! That\'s it. Since I\'ve conveyed my wishes to you, Kana is about to continue the New Year show. How about visiting the shrine after the show?","Sorry, we can\'t go anywhere crowded because of Kana\'s identity! But Kana\'s enjoying the atmosphere with just you and me, because...shh...it\'s the secret only between us. Isn\'t it romantic? Hehe...","Lots of Dora","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","So Kana\'s not the only one...","{5}nine different terminals and honors","Ahhh... This makes me a bit upset...","Kana may have discarded a wrong tile...","Hmm, it\'s almost the end. I must take it seriously.","Kana\'s luck is not to be underestimated!","Ahehe! No one can stop me when I\'m on fire!","Yoohoo! I\'m joining the fun as well!","That seat over there is waiting for you!","Chii","Pon (Call for Triplet)","Kan (Call for Quad)","{10}Kita","Ron","Hohoho, Tsumo!","Huh? Are you the new Mahjong player? You look terrible. Don’t hold Chiori back.","Now – who\'s – gonna – be – last – place?","It’s such a pleasure to play Mahjong with everyone!","Oops, looks like I just won!","No one in this world can defeat me!","Why are you here again?","Why are you so late? Hmpf! You must be doing something bad.","Do you think this tile is safe? What a simple-minded fool.","Why are you looking at Chiori like that? Are you thinking of something dirty?","Idiot! Pervert! Fool! ...Um, aren’t you mad at all? What a strange person.","Those who play Mahjong better than Chiori aren’t as cute. Those who are cuter than Chiori... Tsk, they don’t exist!","Hey, check this out! This dress and that dress, which one suits Chiori better?","You don’t look too annoying. Well, Chiori is very kind, she can let you win this one.","Wow, this cafe is quite unique, let’s go... You look pretty familiar with this kind of place. You are allowed to bring Chiori there, just for today only. Let’s go, hurry up~","Why do you keep looking at Chiori\'s pudding? Do you want to eat it? Really? What a pervert. Fine, open your mouth... You can have a small bite~","What is it? Is this for Chiori? Thanks!","You have a good taste in gifts. But that doesn’t mean Chiori will like you.","Hmph, only an arrogant fool would want to challenge Chiori with this \"game theory\" thing... Huh!? Scared? No way! No matter what challenges you propose, Chiori will accept all of them! It\'s too late to regret now! Hmph... Speaking of it, what does \"game theory\" mean anyway?","Has anyone ever told you how bad your skills are? How pathetic. They must think you are hopeless... All right, let \"ME\" give you a special lesson~","It bothers that you are trying to appeal to Chiori everyday. Anyway, I can accept your kindness for now.","Hmpf... Your Mahjong skills are improving quickly. It is not surprised, since you have been with Chiori for a long time. Still, you are nowhere near Chiori\'s level, so keep working on it~","You picked Chiori such a beautiful new dress. That’s very bold. Well, but as a mature girl, Chiori doesn\'t mind it at all, you know?","D-don\'t look! Even if you won, you are not allowed to look! Idiot! Pervert! Fool! Who, who told you it would be fine to just praise Chiori\'s dress!? Chiori\'s cuteness is unquestioned! Your approval is not needed at all... What did you say? \"I will never see any girl more adorable than Chiori, so I want to admire as much as possible\"...? ...Hmph! Fine, C-Chiori is very kind, you can appreciate me just a little longer.","Happy New Year! Surprised? How about jumping around to show how exciting you are? It\'s an utmost honor for you to receive a New Year wish from me, Lady Chiori herself! Since you\'ve got the wish, stay loyal and treat your dearest Lady Chiori wholeheartedly in the new year. Hmph!","Here\'s the chocolate for you...Huh? What\'s with your expression? You must have misunderstood! I\'ve prepared this for everyone, you\'re not the special someone. It\'s just that...I will disgust everyone if my gift goes to a pervert like you. That\'s why your chocolate is slightly different from the others. So...you\'d better be grateful and take it, or else my hard work is wasted!","Lots of Dora","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-Player Riichi","{5}nine different terminals and honors","Ouch!! I\'m so angry!","Tsk... What a pity.","Hoho, even if it\'s late game, Chiori will still go all out! That\'s Chiori\'s style!","Hohoho, I wonder who will be the lucky one?","Chiori\'s the best!","I\'m here!","Let\'s get started!","Double Riichi","Chii","Kan (Call for Quad)","{10}Kita","Ron","Oops, Tsumo...","Nice...to...meet you.","The great deity is watching over me...","I couldn’t win without you all.","Eh? I made a winning hand before I knew it!","Thank the great deity for their blessings!","Master...have you come to accept my cleansing again today?","I am very happy to see you here again today...","Oh... sorry! I didn’t mean to win from you...","Magic Mahjong? I have only heard of spiritual Mahjong... If you would like to replenish your spirits... Maybe I can help...","Ah, that one! Don’t touch it! ...","Oops... I just scored another Ippatsu on you...","Spirits have their ups and downs, just like the luck of Mahjong. So, if you are too tired, don’t force yourself to play.","Ah, master... Please don’t stare at me, I am shy...","You don’t look very well today, master. Are you feeling sick? Having a bad mood? If you need to let yourself out, feel free to come to me.","Please hold my hands while you’re praying this time... Hmm... (expresses happiness)... (suddenly snaps out of it) Oops, sorry, I forgot my lines!","Thank you very much!","Thanks for taking your time to pick me a gift. I love it.","Ah—! Master, you cannot read that b-book! I-it\'s only an ordinary gardening book, I don\'t think you will be interested... No-no, please don\'t, I can\'t show you the book, no way... U-unless you promise Mai that you will never hate Mai for it.","Master, you are different from others. Each time I see you, I feel very happy.","Master, I have prayed for you to God again today.","I heard that taking a priestess’ personal accessories can increase your chance to get Ura Dora... Please, accept mine...","Master, can I call your name directly in future? Just occasionally...","These two pieces of ceremonial attire are called maetengan (crown) and chihaya (robe). Apart from rituals, t-they are only worn at wedding ceremonies... Um... Master, you really don\'t get it. *Sobbing* ...Eh? Do you think Mai looks beautiful tonight? Master... you always do this to me. That\'s why Mai... Ahehe...","Happy New Year, master! Since the issues at the shrine have been finished, perhaps master could spare some time now...to stay with me? S...sorry! Master must be surprised...But I have mustered up great courage to send this invitation. I would like to welcome New Year while listening to master\'s wishes by your side. As a priestess, it\'s my mission to pray and help master\'s wishes come true.","I am not very familiar with western festivals. It\'s said that it\'s a festival when people give their homemade dishes to the ones they miss...Oh? It is not about homemade dishes? Sorry...for my ignorance. Please do not mind this...master? ...Master would receive any gift as long as it\'s a gift that comes with sincerity. If that\'s the case...every bit of me makes up your gift, master! ...Please take me as your gift!","Lots of Dora","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Ah, Four-Player Riichi.","{5}nine different terminals and honors","Hmm...","Aw! That\'s a Dora!","Mai will keep fighting till the end!","The God has blessed me!","I feel really sorry to you all if I win this hand...","Hello, everyone.","Thank you for waiting. I look forward to playing with you all.","Riichi","Chii","Pon (Call for Triplet)","Kan (Call for Quad)","{10}Kita","Ron","Tsumo","Nadeshiko here. Glad to meet you!","My turn to shine!","Let me taste the fruit of victory!","I was just warming up!","Now this is how you dominate!","Hello, we have met again.","You are looking good. Ready for a big win?","The spirits of a person can influence his luck. Those without confidence will never be blessed by the God of Mahjong.","Huh? Are you talking to me? Sorry... You are not impressive enough. I have not noticed you at all.","Instead of being upset about one loss, how about revising the log and scoring a handsome win in your next match?","Those who don’t even know the rules well do not deserve to be my opponents. Even if they force themselves to play with me, I will destroy them.","Want some beer? ...A life without alcohol is just too dull and boring.","I didn’t expect you to beat me today. Well, you better keep it up in the next match, because I hate to admit losing.","My wish is that one day I will be able to travel the world and leave my footprints...and yours on foreign land...","Playing Mahjong in person is much more fun than online, since you can see your opponent\'s movements and expressions. ...Don\'t be so nervous! You\'re much cuter when you\'re relaxed!","Thanks.","Hmm? You have a good taste!","I’m a little impressed. I shouldn’t have judged you by your looks... Pfff (laughing) just joking.","Well, in return, let me give you a one-on-one Mahjong class!","It’s the first time that someone cared about me so much since my mother passed away... Thank you.","From today on, the back seat of my motorbike will be reserved for you. Wanna join me for a trip around the world, Darling?","Wanna join me for a ride? There\'s nothing special about it, I just suddenly feel like riding with you. Even if you ask me why, I myself don\'t have a reason yet. You just happened to appear in my mind at that moment. How about we try to figure it out while riding?","I have added your name in all my future plans seriously. From now on, you will have half of my bike, my wine, my Mahjong, as well as my life. Darling.","Happy New Year! Let\'s talk about the future. Life, dreams, you name it. Or...tell me what your ideal new year is like. Am I included in your new year? Hehe","Reach out your hand, dear! Some girls gave me these chocolates for unknown reasons. Please eat them for me. Well, among these chocolates, there is one that I prepared specially for you, guess which one is it!","Lots of Dora","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Four-Player Riichi","{5}nine different terminals and honors","I don\'t need this tile, no matter how many of it.","Even if it\'s a Dora, sometimes I just need to give it up.","Oh! It\'s coming to an end.","A piece of cake.","Instead of luck, I say the game was won with skill.","Up for a game?","Let\'s have a blast!","Riichi. Looking forward...","Double Riichi. Super excited...","Ah, Pon.","{10}Kita","Ron, give it to me.","Tsumo, all of you, give me points.","...Yui Yagi here. Who are you? ...","Senpai, let\'s do this.","...Should I smile in such a situation?","Yes...","Yes, I did it.","Hello...","...Welcome back, senpai. If you don’t mind, let’s play Mahjong together.","...What’s up?...","Why does everyone have so many facial expression? I don’t understand...","Why did I purposely deal into others’ hands? I just wanted to see the expressions of the other players... Nothing special.","Senpai, senpai~, senpai, senpai... Senpai is an interesting word. Simply changing my tone can imply many different meanings.","Um, you are getting too close. This is weird, senpai, others may get us wrong...","Senpai, why do you keep poking me? I also want to know how it feels to poke others.","...Here you are... It’s a combo I recently discovered, celery, mayonnaise and chips... I have never seen such a pale face of yours, senpai. Let me take a photo.","Senpai, if you don’t mind, how about a Mahjong game? With me.","...Yeah...","...I want it, thanks.","...not really that touched...","...I think I was a little touched. Can you do it again?","...If I stay with you, I think I can change over time.","Senpai, don’t stare at me like this... I’m shy...","Senpai, May I hold your hand?","Stop staring me like that. This new dress... feels so strange...","Happy New Year, senpai. Let\'s go watch the fireworks together.","Senpai, please take these chocolates I made for you. I took account of your preference and made them chili. Have a try.","{5}fully outside hand","Lots of Dora","True Nine Gates","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Four-Player... Riichi.","{5}nine different terminals and honors","...Bad luck...","...Hmm, I don\'t want it anymore...","...It\'s almost over...","...Hehehehe, interesting...","...I smell a large one...","Excuse me.","I\'m ready.","My name is Riu Kujou. As you can see, I’m a maid... Please don’t keep looking at me.","Pardon me. Now, let\'s begin.","Phew, that was a good match!","Not bad.","Mahjong\'s actually pretty fun.","Oh hi, grab yourself a seat.","Oh here you are. The black tea is ready.","This goes here, that goes there. Come on, I swear I will beat you if you mess things up again next time.","You look so free everyday. How about spending a little more time to improve your Mahjong skills?","Hey... Sometimes, even you can put on a serious face. What a surprise.","Tsk, why is your room so messy? Get up now! I will clean the floor, you go clean the table. Move, now!","Abs? How, can, I, have, that?","Hmm... Oh! That was a good move. Looks like you are getting a lot better. Play with me later! I\'ll test your skill level!","Hah... I have never worn such a soft maid costume. But it actually feels good moving in it.","Are you tired? Come sit down for a rest. I’ve got tea and snacks prepared for you. You want a massage? Hohoho, sure, let me give you a GOOD one... Wait, why are you running away?","Is this for me? Anyway, thanks.","Oh! This is pretty good! Thanks!","Don\'t step closer. What are you planning to do to a delicate girl like me?!","...It’s been some time, but I still want to ask. Did you wash your hands before giving me this gift?","...We just happen to know each other for a while. What sort of changes are you expecting?","Being a maid is never easy. I still have a lot of things to learn!","Hey, you look a lot more capable than before. Now I can say you have barely passed my standards, barely.","Black tea, freshly brewed. Would you like a cup, mas~ter~? ...hehehe, did that make you lose a heartbeat? So, how do you feel about my new dress? I\'m all ears~","Happy New Year! Please continue to give me advice this year.","It\'s Valentine\'s Day again...In fact, yesterday, I tried to make some chocolates...Can you please taste them for me? As a maid, it\'s a must to learn how to make desserts...","Lots of Dora","Tenpai","Unfortunately, no-ten.","That is a Four-Player Riichi.","{5}nine different terminals and honors","This happens sometimes...","A decision must be made.","Not many chances left.","One more step!","Time to get serious!","Excuse me, I\'m here for mahjong. Is this the right place?","Then I\'ll begin.","Riichi","Double Riichi","Pon","Kan","{10}Kita","Ron! You have my apology.","Tsumo! Just like I expected.","Xenia. It\'s a lucky name in Oriental languages. Nice to meet you.","Let us play a clean game, and make it a brilliant one.","Good game. If you don\'t mind, would you like to go another round?","Apologies, but I won.","Just as predicted, a flawless strike!","Huh? You’re here. It\'s a little boring. Would you like to go out with me?","Today’s a good day. Would you like some afternoon tea?","Sigh... our school vacation is coming. By then, I’ll be taken to that boring house again and I’ll be trapped in it for days and days... so sad...","Whenever I go traveling, I get to see all kinds of different villages and interact with different people. I get to truly feel the vastness of this beautiful world in front of me.","Someone said that the reason I won was because of my name. Honestly... It\'s really inappropriate to make excuses for failure!","This compass is very helpful. No matter where I go throughout my life journey, this compass will always give me a sense of peace. Or so I was told by the adventurer who gifted me this compass.","It’s quite interesting to attend exhibitions on cultural relics and artifacts. Looking at these relics, I feel as if I can reach out and touch the unknown past.","Let\'s go hike a mountain. Let’s watch the sunrise together and enjoy it between us!","In their recent letter, my parents told me that they started to play mahjong from time to time, and it seem they are enjoying the game. My parents wouldn’t have changed so much had you not come along with me last time. Thank you.","You want to spend time at home instead of going out? Haha, that’s good from time to time, a quiet world between the two of us... How about doing something special together?","Ha... This gift really suits the taste of of the people.","Ah! You have a good taste, I like it!","I\'m not interested in boring stuff or boring people, but you haven’t disappointed me so far.","It truly is better to be accompanied with someone than to be alone.","You are the first person who has brought me so much happiness. I wish to continue to be happy with you.","Those days when I stayed behind those high walls would certainly have been more colorful if I met you earlier.","I wanna see things, all the beautiful and wonderful things in this world. And I wanna see them all with you. Because you can show me such a would. Would you like to go on a journey with me?","What do you think? Do I look good in this dress? Stunned?","Happy New Year! My parents and I are visiting our friends and family these days...Those inevitable small talks might be boring, but I\'d better behave myself during this important period, or else I am disrespecting the gods.","Oh? Surprised to receive my handmade chocolates? That\'s nothing. For a lady like me, cooking is a basic skill. What? You are surprised at the fact that I actually gave you chocolates? I...I don\'t think it\'s a big deal, considering our relationship...","Tanyao","Mixed Triple Sequence","Triple Triplets","Dora 2","Dora 3","Dora 4","Dora 5","Dora 6","Dora 7","Dora 8","Dora 9","Dora 10","Dora 11","Dora 12","Lots of Dora","{5}Single-wait Four Concealed Triplets","All Honor Tiles","Thirteen Orphans (Thirteen Waits)","Big Four Winds","Little Four Winds","True Nine Gates","Counted Yakuman","Mangan","Haneman","Baiman","Sanbaiman","Yakuman","Double Yakuman","Triple Yakuman","Quadruple Yakuman","Quintuple Yakuman","Sextuple Yakuman","Ahahaha, that was a little regrettable.","Sigh... what an immature mistake.","Tut, Four-Wind Discarded.","Tut, Four-kan Abortion.","My, a Four-Player Riichi?","Tut, {5}nine different terminals and honors.","Emmm... what a surprise, but this is the fun of playing mahjong.","Give up my Dora? No, I think you misunderstood. This is a declaration of war!","There\'s not many tiles left. It’s getting close to match point.","Here we go!","This will be a perfect victory!","Good day, everyone.","Ready to start any time!","Riichi","Double Riichi","Pon","Kan","{10}Kita","Ron","Kaavi, I am an unknown fortune teller. Your face, it tells me that you are having issues with women. I can help you solve it with my fortune telling. You’ll need to pay 50,000 coppers, though.","The wheels of fate have begun to turn...","Fate is inevitable.","Such is fate.","I\'ve seen through everything.","Ah, it\'s you again. The one with women issues.","You really like to come to me for fortune telling.","Telling your fortune in love is probably the most meaningless thing to do. Because no matter what the result is, my client will still go to confess. Humans are so predictable this way, why should I bother to tell fortunes.","Ah, I just played a wrong tile... Forget what you just saw, or you will be doubly cursed by both the Tower and the Devil!","By the power of the divine, tell me my fortune for today...","It\'s really strange that I can\'t see through people\'s mahjong fortune including myself. Why,,,","It\'s really strange that I can\'t see through people\'s mahjong fortune, including my own. Why... speaking of mahjong fun... Maybe this is the ugly state of people struggling meaninglessly to avoid their absolute fates... Huh? Do you think that\'s a bad taste? Haha... a bad taste is still a funny taste, isn\'t it?","My mentor? She is a confusing individual who thinks that fate can be altered and can be changed through people’s sheer will. I never agreed with that. Fate is absolute.","Umm... You may have bad luck recently. Do you need my exorcism service? 100,000 coppers will do.","Want to have a match against my mentor? I advise you to give up such ideas. She is much worse than me to some extent, for instance... she will do whatever it takes to show you all the possibilities.","Thank you. I’ll give you a discount on your next fortune telling.","That’s such a nice gift. You are an angel!","Change? Maybe. But fate is never so trivial.","