 contrast, what I am after is to turn the tables with an awful hand.","I\'m feeling good today. How about a few Mahjong games? Don\'t worry, I won\'t win too much from you!","Do you like drinking? I\'m quite good at making cocktails. I can make you one if you don\'t mind. Would you like something sweet, sour or bitter?","Don\'t worry, as long as I\'m here, it is impossible to lose.","Why did I create \"White Night\" in the beginning? It was probably my most genuine wish. If I could be a thief that was capable of everything, maybe I could even steal someone`s heart... Just kidding. I only wanted to steal the original works of a cartoonist.","Would you like to go to the event next week with me? I\'ve already thought about it, nobody fits the assistant of \"White Night\" better than you!","Thank you.","Wow! This, this is it! I\'ve wanted it for a long time!","Looks like you are also interested in cocktails. Would you like to learn with me?","I\'ve tried to make a new cocktail recently. It is a blend of Golden Dream and Margarita. Would you like to try some?","No, that photo is definitely not me. You must have mistaken me for someone else. Absolutely!","How\'s it going? Let\'s play game together when there\'s a chance. I heard this new game, where multiple players could cook together was launched recently. It\'s quite fun.","I don\'t have many friends, and I\'m happy to be with you. If there\'s a chance, I can tell you another secret of mine, how about that?","Sorry that I have kept it from you all along, but this is who I really am. It\'s the truest form of myself that I have always suppressed. So... Hahahaha! You should feel honored! You\'re the only person who knows the true identity of \"White Night\"!","Happy New Year. This chance comes once in a blue moon. Let\'s get some drinks!","What should I do...It was not easy to own this limited figure, and now it\'s yours! ...Don\'t worry, I can manage to get another.","Robbing a Kan","Under the River","Double East","Double South","Double West","Double North","Half Outside Hand","Three Concealed Triplets","Fully Outside Hand","Twice Pure Double Sequence","Four Concealed Triplets (Single Wait)","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","Alas, no-ten.","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","I see... Four-Player Riichi.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Never thought this could happen to me...","It\'s all for the final victory.","This is not the time to relax yet.","Behold, my gorgeous formation!","Sa, let\'s do it!","Hey. So um... I\'m here to play.","Go easy on me, guys.","Riichi!","Double Riichi, woof!","Chii","Pon","Kan","Ron. I\'ve got this!","Tsumo. Luck is on my side!","Yo, my friend, if you like Mahjong, then take me with you. I\'m sure you will benefit a lot. The name\'s Wanjirou. What\'s yours?","Time for my grand entrance, woof.","Oops, I was only getting slightly serious. I am the best.","Piece of cake!","When I go all out, even I\'m afraid of what I can do.","I\'ve been waiting for a long time. Let\'s get started!","Yo, AIBO. How would you like to start the day? Pray first, or play mahjong?","Humans always let their emotions influence play style. How weak... Oui oui oui! If you keep interrupting with small wins, I will bite you-woof!","Before winning, one must prepare for a thousand losses. Those weaklings who start to complain after a few games lost will never beat me!","I guess my greatest weakness is that I am unable to suppress my luck. Sometimes, this will easily hurt others, which makes me sad...","What? You want to challenge me? You gotta treat me to ramen if you lose!","I never wanted to play mahjong with humans, but my brothers knew nothing other than playing fetch.","The so-called \"luck\" is actually a type of belief. If you believe in it, your faith will bring you luck-woof.","Hmm, I shall allow you to pet my head for a little bit... To the left... A bit further down... (Sounds very comfortable) ...Woof-woof","Ouch, why is that cat here? AIBO, don\'t tell anyone that you 