I\'ve been waiting for you. How am I feeling? Not too bad. Wanna play together?","Mathematics is the foundation of this world. There\'s no such thing as \"luck\", only \"probability\" exists. Based on data from your previous games, your chance to win against me is only about 39.8%.","Oops?! The priestess of that temple, isn\'t she weird? A human with cat ears is supposed to be a huge discovery for science!","Mahjong is nothing but a game of probability. I will not lose when it comes to calculating.","I am... very good at Rubik\'s Cube... But nobody wants to play with me... Do you want to play together?","I don\'t often go to school. While I am fine on my own, I still want to play with others...","*Crying*... I am not crying. I only lost a game, I am not crying! I just had dirt in my eyes... Let\'s have one more game, I will definitely winning this time!","Rubik\'s Cube? I played it in front of everyone when I was little, and they all came to me saying \"wow you are great\". So I thought, since they liked me playing Rubik\'s Cube, it must be something that could bring me friends. That\'s why I keep playing it until now...","Hmm... Why do you play this tile? Apparently, the other tile is more efficient! Although you are older than me, you don\'t seem to be smarter. Well, I guess it\'s time for me to teach you how to play with efficiency in mind.","Thank you.","Wow, what\'s this... I will take good care of it!","We may not have known each other for a long time, but you surely don\'t look like the kind of bad guys they talked about... Thank you for coming to see me.","My sister made this dish, steamed eggs with tomato, for me... She said vegetables and protein would be good for my body. Would you like to have some together?","Sometimes, I also want to go to PE classes like everyone else... I want to know what it feels like to run freely on grass... Doctor never allowed me to participate in vigorous exercise ever since I was hospitalized when I was little... Oops, I have talked too much. Anyway, thanks for coming to see me.","Would you like to play Rubik\'s Cube? I can teach you! See, one, two, three! Done! What? Was I too fast? That\'s okay. Let me show you one more time, but make sure you pay attention this time!","Recently, I am feeling better, maybe because you have been coming over a lot. Doctor has said if I keep improving like this, I can go back to school soon! ...Hmm, \"maybe\" is really not a word that I would normally use. I must have been influenced by you.","Apart from my family, you are the first person that I can talk with. I know this sounds weird, but I feel we are already friends. There are billions of people on the planet. The probability of two strangers becoming friends is probably only one in millions, just like winning a jackpot! Are we going to be friends like this all the time? ...That\'s great, I\'m so happy.","Happy New Year! I don\'t usually participate in activities like New Year\'s First Visit. I believe it must be fun.","I present to you my favorite 7x7x7 cube! It may be just a toy, but it is my precious...So you should try your best to solve it!","South","Tenpai (Ready Hand)","No-ten (No Ready Hand)","Four-Player Riichi","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Bad luck in a row.","It is necessary to discard this one for the sake of winning.","Hmm... There are not many draws left, but I still have a chance.","Exactly as I calculated.","Here comes my chance.","Count me in!","Just so you know, I won\'t be holding back.","Double Riichi. Watch out.","Kita","Ron. Thanks","I\'m sorry, but here comes Tsumo.","Hi there, I am Hideki Akechi, the captain of Mahjong club and the president of student union. Do you also like to play Mahjong?","Let us begin.","I won.","It was just good luck this time.","Sorry, this hand might be a little too big.","Oh, do you have anything to discuss with me?","Good work today. Would you like to have a relaxing moment together? Mahjong, or anything.","Victory matters a lot, but the process is equally as important.","Thanks for helping out in the student union. Let me treat you to a meal as a reward.","I only became the president of student union because I wanted to be the captain of Mahjong club. I\'ll be in big trouble if you don\'t join us.","National champion? Definitely not me. You probably have mistaken me for someone else. Many people have similar looks in this world. After all, my style is completely different from that so-called \"Lucifer of Mahjong\"!","Mahjong Soul Shrine is such a great place, just like my grandma\'s house. The comforting sceneries and interesting people make me feel very free and relaxed. If I had come to this place earlier, I might not have to... Hmm? Nothing, it\'s just that some old memories had come to me. Don\'t worry!","What\'s my wish? ...I hope one day I can break away from the shackle of my family and enjoy a carefree life, just like the time I spend with you.","Grandma taught me that, \"the most important thing about Mahjong is to enjoy the game process\". Thinking back now, I really should have visited her more often instead of trying all unscrupulous means to bring her victory. I did win, but grandma left... \"Lucifer of Mahjong\", what an ironic name.","Are you interested in the ancient Yaku? Let me teach you. Grandma showed them to me when I was little, so I often make ancient Yaku without realizing. Many of them are quite interesting, actually. It\'s a shame that they are no longer used.","Thanks. This looks like something you will give to me.","Wow... So you do remember what I like. I will take good care of it.","Is the work at student union too hard? Feel free to let me know if you have any questions at all.","You must tell me if you are tired. You are working very hard already, so it\'s completely okay if you want to take a break. I will help you.","Would you like to go horse riding with me next time? It\'s okay if you don\'t know how to. I will teach you with patience. I may not look like that, but I\'m actually a very good rider.","I used to only care about winning and missed out on a lot of things. Now, I only want to enjoy the process with you, in each Mahjong game.","Winning is not everything. That was the lesson I learned from national competition. So, could you please keep the secret that I am the \"Lucifer of Mahjong\" just between two of us?","As I spend more time with you, I start to cherish these days more and more. I hope we can keep going like this forever. Not just for Mahjong, of course...","Happy New Year! Let\'s make more pleasant memories in the new year.","This is for you, it\'s something you mentioned before. I wonder if you like it?","Alas, no-ten.","This happens often.","One man\'s trash is another man\'s treasure.","One must not relax in late game.","Sometimes, I want to give it a try.","Everybody, be careful.","Here I am. Hope I didn\'t keep you waiting.","I\'m ready now.","Riichi","Double Riichi!","Pon","Kan","Kita","Ron!","Tsumo!","My goal is to become the Lifetime Queen! Hmm? What? Are you saying that\'s a title of Japanese Shogi?","I\'ll prove I\'m not just some airhead!","Wait, what? How did I become the first?","Got it now? I also give it my all when it counts!","See? This is what I\'m capable of!","Are you here to see me again? I\'m so happy!","Here\'s a novel that I would recommended. You should take a read!","What a refreshing morning. Let\'s keep up the hard work today!","What\'s my hobby? Reading novels is my favorite, probably.","I think I have played too much Mahjong recently... I wonder what everyone is doing at the club?","You want me to introduce my sister to you? Why?","What food do I dislike? Nothing particular... I\'m not very good at eating bitter stuff.","Come, let\'s go on a trip. I need inspirations to prepare for my novel!","I feel like a different person with my hat removed? What are you talking about?","What am I reading? \"How to Maintain Hats\", that\'s the title of this book.","Is this for me? Thank you!","