e is over. It\'s my private time now. But... If you can win a Mahjong game that really surprises me, I don\'t really mind some little extra service... Hehe...","Dear guest, if you don\'t mind, could you go to the shrine with me? Recently, Ichihime\'s been a little scared of me... Am I too passionate toward her?","A Mahjong game? ...Sorry, I have not been at my best recently. My intuition isn\'t as good as it was, you will probably laugh at me.","Ah... I have been dancing the whole day, my feet are so sore. Dear guest, could you help me to relax a little? ...Just sit down and have a Mahjong game with me, hehe.","I\'m getting a bit tired... Sorry to make you see me like this. But... you are the only one who will see this side of me.","Dear guest, could you just sit next to me and watch me? You only have to watch. As long as I can feel you around, my senses seem to be sharper than usual.","I have always been living on my own feet. Sometimes, I too want to rely on someone else. Dear guest, what do you think?","Thank you. While my group doesn\'t allow members to take private gifts, I don\'t want to waste your goodwill either.","Wow, this gift is really... I can\'t thank you enough... Looks like a performance in return is a must, hehe...","I don\'t often see a guest like you. You never missed any of my performances. If my dance can bring you happiness, that will be great.","Dear guest, I see you are buying every single merchandise item... I really appreciate your support, but please don\'t push yourself too hard. I want to bring joy to you, not become your burden.","Your advice really helped me a lot, thank you. Perhaps you have great talent in dancing that you do not know.","You haven\'t visited recently... Hmm? Feeling lonely? Perhaps. Before I realize, I am already used to the days with you watching me. But I do hope that you can put your own matters at priority.","What have I been busy with? Hoho... It\'s a secret... You will know when the time comes...","Dear guest, 