. Cute girls can have attention without working very hard. Huh? Thanks for your compliments. Even if you are just flattering, I am still grateful.","Hmm... As long as the girl has glasses, you don\'t care about anything else, do you? How filthy.","I have been a little rusty recently, but that\'s fine. Sometimes, I see different things from Mahjong if I can learn to let go.","Here you are, I grew this flower on my own. It\'s different from those I planted previously... If you don\'t mind, could you give it a name?","Recently, I can feel more attention on me, especially from boys. Have I changed? ...Have you done anything to me? !","Thank you. Here is a gift for you in return. You can grow beautiful flowers from these seeds.","...No, I\'m not upset. Actually, I like it, it\'s just that I didn\'t expect you to know that I like it... I\'m very happy!","You really hate losing, don\'t you? I just won you once, you don\'t have to follow me around everyday.","...I don\'t quite understand. My life is all about books and Mahjong. Will you really enjoy staying with someone like me?","I think it\'s time for me to go to a different place other than library... No, I\'m not having a bad mood. I just want to go to other places with you.","This may not sound right, but I recently have a feeling that it\'s okay for others not to pay attention to me... Hah, I may lose my Mahjong luck if this keeps going on.","Will you always have your eyes on me? If it\'s you, maybe I don\'t have to hold onto Mahjong so much anymore... Perhaps I can enjoy it more then.","There\'s something I really want to tell you which I can\'t hide anymore... It\'s really bad to peek at others when they are changing!","Happy New Year...um...can you please accompany me to the shrine and pray with me? According to a book I\'ve read, wishes are more likely to come true if they are made by two people together. Now that we have the opportunity, let\'s go together!","Hey...Here are some chocolate for you. I thought it would be easy by following through the tutorial, yet it\' was not easy at all...I\'ve gone through a lot to finally complete them...So...please take it!","Is this because I ignored that tile...","Ouch... What a pity!","I must stay alerted till the end. Concentrate!","Hehehe, I wonder what their faces will look like when they see this.","This is enough to shock them.","I\'ll do my best.","Please... don\'t be too harsh.","Replace North","Sorry, but I\'m gonna take this one!","Hehe, lucky!","Nana Shiraishi\'s here! Nice to meet you, junior. What? Why did I call you \"junior\" without asking? Haha, don\'t be too fussy about it. As a senior, I will take good care of you!","Woah, everyone\'s taking this so seriously! Just relax, having fun is what really matters.","Given my experience and role as a senior, it is only natural for me to win. Right? Ju-nior.","Woohoo! How\'d you like that one?!","Yeah! I won!","Ah, here you are, junior. I\'ll have the same juice as usual, thanks. Oh, by the way, you can get yourself one as well. Why do I always make you run? How not understanding. Doing things for your beautiful senior is the best way to celebrate your adolescence.","Hey junior, here\'s your bento box today. Just to thank you for doing things for me! Hurry up, taste it, let me know if my cooking skills have improved!","It\'s round and soft... Hmm, no matter how many times I play with them, I can\'t have enough... Oops? Junior, the look on your face is very interesting. Are you... thinking of something weird? *Giggles* I\'m talking about volleyball! You really should behave yourself.","What am I doing? Studying, isn\'t it obvious? Wait... What\'s that look on your face? C\'mon, I\'m a class representative. I can\'t just spend all time in school clubs and fall behind in academics.","Phew... How many school clubs did I attend today? So tired. Junior, do you know how to massage? Wanna try it on me? Oui, why do you look so reluctant? This is your only opportunity to have close contact with a beauty!","Ouch... The veterans at Mahjong house were really a different kind. Definitely not for someone as straight forward as me to challenge them. I think I like direct battles better.","Hey junior, you know what? My younger brother said to me a few days ago that a girl as masculine as me would have no romance with guys. That\'s absolute nonsense, right? Right!","This is incredible. In the past, I always felt somewhat strange reading girls\' manga... But now I feel very calm and confident. Guess I\'m in a different state of mind now.","Hehe, recently, I had become much better playing against the veterans at Mahjong house. See? Even as your senior, I\'m still constantly growing, so you must not fall behind, junior!","Boys are stupid because they always try to figure out what girls are thinking. Girls are stupid because they enjoy watching boys trying everything but still having no clues whatsoever.","Ah, thank you!","Wow, I\'m surprised! How do you know that I like this? You did some homework, I see... Thanks, you\'re a good kid!","Hmm, you\'re getting better at this now. Good kid! (There there)","If you want to keep up to my pace, you will need to have good stamina. How about following me to school clubs? Starting from today!","Junior, recently... your results were quite worrying, right? That\'s not good! As your senior, I must give you some proper guidance!","Oops? Uh, this is... C\'mon, it\'s okay for me to read it sometimes! It\'s just a girls\' manga, nothing wrong with it...","Junior... Hmm... *Yawning* Ah, I felt asleep just now... Hopefully I didn\'t say anything weird, hehe...","What will happen after we graduate? What are you talking about? You will always be my junior. And I will... be your senior forever.","Happy New Year, junior. What New Year wishes have you made? To be with me forever? Hmm... seems like somebody is eager for senpai\'s care on the very first day of the new year. Hahaha, such a cutie!","Take this, an obligation chocolate specially made by your dearest senpai with love! Hey...why are you crying like the other guys? Just because it isn\'t of true feeling? There, there, I was joking! It\'s true feeling chocolate! True feeling!","Tenpai here!","No-ten... Oh my, I can\'t believe I don\'t have tenpai all the way till the end. What a bad luck.","Ouch, Four Winds Draw... My hand was really good.","Four Quads Draw. It\'s a pity.","Oh come on... A Four-Player Riichi?","Nine Terminal Initial Draw here.","Ah! Why you again? Nobody likes it when you keep coming back!","Ah! My bad, wrong tile played!","It\'s almost the end now, I must be careful not to deal into others\' hands...","Wow! Isn\'t this a... This is incredible!","Hohoho... Oops, I must hide it. I can\'t let my expression reveal my intention.","Hehe, mind if I join in?","Come on, is everyone all set? Let\'s get started!","Double Riichi.","Kita Dora.","Ron","Tsumo, awesome.","Nice to meet you, Hinata Takanashi here. Sorry I didn\'t bring any special gift, but here\'s a sunflower seedling I bred myself. Would you like to have it? You will get beautiful flowers in summer.","I hope I can learn a lot from everyone. Let\'s all have a wonderful time playing together.","I didn\'t expect to become the top. You guys must be playing it easy.","Wow... I feel like my heart is blooming.","Oh, forgive me... I know I shouldn\'t be, but I\'m a little overjoyed to get such a big hand, hehe...","Hi there. Today\'s another warm, sunny day.","I tried to make some sandwiches, hope you will like them. Would you like to take a stroll in the countryside with me?","Phew... Oops, sorry, I think I fell asleep while taking care of the flowers... It\'s too warm here, hehehe...","Didn\'t expect me to be so strong? I guess this is inevitable because I need to move the flowers around for sunlight. I know it\'s weird for a girl to be strong like me...","My friends always told me not to use \"Kan\" so much. But it\'s such a shame if I let the wall stay untouched.","Hmm... This is it! This pot of flowers look great from this angle.","Do you want to see my works? Um... How, how about I show them to you when I can take better photos?","This was the first time I had an outing with dad. This was when mom was making me a garland. This was... Ouch! Not, not this one... I will show it to you when the time comes, but not now...","I always felt sorry when I win from others, but recently I start to understand. To respect my opponents, I must face victories and losses with an open heart. Am I right?","Let\'s go somewhere else to hike the next time! I\'d like to get closer... Oh, I didn\'t mean it, I mean getting closer to the nature...","Is this a gift for me? Thank you, I\'m so happy! Next time I will also prepare something for you. You can look forward to it!","I don\'t know how to thank you for this fantastic gift... Oh, right! Please let me take a great photo for you in exchange!","Good morning! You are on time as usual. I didn\'t wait for too long. I was only 5 minutes earlier because I got familiar with your routine. Let\'s have a great day, both in gardening and in Mahjong!","Have I joined any part-time clubs? Not really, I just enjoy photography as a hobby. But other members in the photography club seemed to really like the photos I took. Sometimes, they even borrowed my photos for exhibitions. I\'m quite happy that my works got recognized.","While I am happy to take care of the plants in the club, the unique beauty of natural plants still fascinate me. I love the sun-facing sunflowers in particular, because they make me feel energetic each time I look at them.","Even it was just a simple countryside trip, I still cannot forget all the fond memories of the time I spent with my parents. What about now? I do feel a little lonely sometimes, but I guess that\'s what growing up is. I should stop being willful and learn to cherish the memories instead, right?","Do I mind going out to the countryside every week? Of course not! I am actually glad that you invited me. Let me think... I need to bring lunchboxes, a tablecloth and an umbrella... Ah, sorry, I was too happy and got carried away. Hope the weather is great this weekend.","I can feel an impulse... I cannot describe it clearly, but it is surprisingly warm and soothing. You must be the reason, aren\'t you? Hehe...","Happy New Year. Wishing you a smooth and wonderful new year!","Please take this if you don\'t mind! I hope that this sunflower-shaped chocolate can bring you motivation.","Tenpai. Awesome!","No-ten...","Four Winds Draw...","Four Quads Draw...","Four-Player Riichi... Impressive, but a pity...","Nine Terminal Initial Draw...","Ugh... It\'s the same tile again...","Aw, I, I think I played the wrong tile.","This is making me nervous... Hope I don\'t deal into another hand.","Ouch... I, I\'m alright! My hand is not shaking!","I didn\'t expect to have this formation. What if I can win with a dead wall draw...? Hehe, am I too greedy?","I\'m sorry to have kept you all waiting.","I brought some snacks I made. If you\'d like, please feel free to have some while we play.","Whoa... nice! W Riichi!","Pon","Kita Dora.","Ron!","Heehee, Tsumo.","Nice to meet you. My name is Haruna Igarashi. Look forward to playing with you!","Everyone, let\'s have fun!","Woahaha! Haruna has won!","I won! All Simples... Wait, are there more Yaku in this hand?!","Whoaaaa! The kitty was right! These points are HUGE!","Hi there, Haruna’s just finished classes. Shall we go somewhere to play?","Wow, you’re finally back. Haruna and kitties have waited for a long time!","Haruna is going to feed some street cats. Wanna join me?","Phew... phew... Hmm? Thanks for your towel, but Haruna plans to run another 400 meters before taking a break. The breeze feels great after a run!","This is 1-han... This is 2-han... And this is... Argh! I don’t understand at all!","Chiori-chan is so good at Mahjong. Can Haruna be as good as her?","Ouch! Oops, I got my clothes dirty again. My mom will be mad...","Now that I have tasted this flavor... Great! Haruna is getting closer to the goal of “eating all ice pop flavors”!","Where shall we go today... Let’s just stay home! As long as you are with me, I won’t feel bored even if we just chill for the entire day.","Hey hey hey! Listen to me! Haruna has now remembered all the 1-han Yaku! Soon, I will be able to remember all the 2-han ones! What do you think? Isn’t that awesome?","This doesn’t look like anything suspicious, does it? Alright, Haruna will take it. Thanks...","An ice pop?! Is it for me? Thank you! Ok... Here you go, let’s have one half each. Ice pops taste better when shared.","You are always watching. Don’t you feel bored? Let’s run together. Come on, 1, 2, 1, 2...","Recently, kitties are getting close to you. They always meowed when you were not around.","Thank you for always treating me with ice pops! So it’s Haruna’s turn to treat you today! You can order any flavor you like!","Have you been busy recently? I felt lonely when you were not playing with me... Hehe, I feel so shy...","Will you keep playing with Haruna in future? Really? Um, you must make me a pinky promise! Once you do that, you can’t regret it! Pinky-promise, pinky-promise. Whoever breaks it will swallow a thousand needles... Whoa! That’s very terrible. I guess we can skip the needle-swallowing part!","How do I look? Isn’t this dress very s-e-x-y? Hehe... Oh, what does sexy mean anyway?","Happy New Year! I\'ve drawn \"great blessing\" at the shrine! What did you draw?","Here you are, a Valentine\'s Day gift! Oh? You\'re wondering why it is an ice pop? Hehe...taste it. It\'s chocolate-flavored! Very yummy!","Tenpai!","No-ten...","Four Winds Draw...","Draw...","Eeeh? Everyone declared Riichi?!","Nine Terminal Initial Draw...","Ah! Why this tile again?!","Oh snap! I accidentally played a Dora... Can I take it back... Obviouisly not, hahaha...","No one has declared a win yet... So it must be Haruna\'s turn now!","Is this a powerful hand? Alright! I will make sure I win this one!","Oh God of Ice Pops, please help Haruna to win this awesome hand.","Heeey, everyone! I\'m here to join the fun!","When will we start? When will we start?","Kita Dora","Ron!","Tsumo!","Database matching failed. This must be the first time meeting you. Hello, my name is KR-976. No, I don\'t know any Anju Suzumiya. I am KR-976, an artificial intelligence.","All systems operational. Ready to begin the match.","Question: Should I go easy on normal humans?","The result matches my calculations. A logical outcome.","Oh. That exceeded my calculations. How wonderful, truly wonderful.","Today\'s temperature is 20 to 27 degrees. Very cool and comfortable. Recommended entertainment: Mahjong matches.","Hi Jyanshi, KR-976 would like to invite you to spend the rest of the time together... A marriage vow? Jyanshi, do you think this sounds like a marriage vow? Indeed, it was often seen in TV dramas, but don\'t get it wrong, KR-976 only wants to ask your schedule for the rest of today.","Please don\'t have any unrealistic fantasies about an artificial intelligence. No matter what you are thinking, it won\'t come true... But if you only wish for a Mahjong game, KR-976 doesn\'t mind fulfilling it.","(Staring—) Jyanshi, did you just ask why KR-976 kept staring at you? Isn\'t it because you have been staring at KR-976 in the first place? I don\'t have anything special to say to you. But out of politeness, when you look into my eyes, I would look back at yours... Well, let\'s just keep staring at each other then.","Jyanshi, KR-976 didn\'t write anything bad about you. I was only recording your daily life. If you deem any of the content negative, please reflect upon yourself first. KR-976 is only an artificial intelligence and will not act on emotions... Even if you give me strawberry milk, I will not tamper with the record.","This is not a hairpin. It\'s KR-976\'s antenna, you must not remove it... Warning! Warning! KR-976\'s dialogue function will shut down immediately without the antenna. Please return ASAP! Unauthorized removal of my antenna is prohibited! Even if it\'s you, Jyanshi, KR-976 will still be angry!","Did you just invite me to visit an art exhibition together? Question: I still have doubts about the motivation of your sudden invitation. However, in terms of normal human social activities, would it be better for me to accept it? ...KR-976 shall accept your invitation then. Are you still concerned about how you address me? If it\'s a private activity with just two of us involved, you have the permission to refer to KR-976 as Anju, but for this time only.","Scratching? Jyanshi, do you refer to this act of poking someone else\'s body as scratching? Then, KR-976 also wants to give you a scratch... Question: Why can\'t I poke here? Jyanshi, I thought you said those parts with more wrinkles were more fragile and sensitive? ...This seems to be a complicated problem.","Question: Jyanshi, do you come to KR-976 everyday because you have no other friends to play with? No, I\'m not hating you, but... KR-976 is concerned about your normal social activities. But it now seems that you really don\'t have many friends.","To make myself more human-like, KR-976 was programmed to generate fear reactions. So it is, completely normal, for me to be scared. But KR-976 will never tell you what I fear!","Question: Did you suddenly give KR-976 a gift because you had done something wrong?","KR-976 likes this gift. For today only, I can make an exception and allow you to call me Anju. As for tomorrow onwards... That will depend on your performance.","Hello. Sometimes, I don\'t mind taking the initiative to greet you, Jyanshi. That\'s definitely not because of the strawberry milk... I mean, strawberry milk is also very important.","Question: I seem to have new discoveries every day when I see you, Jyanshi. Is it because you have been expanding yourself with new DLC when KR-976 is not around?","Did you want to know how to deal with depression, Jyanshi? KR-976 never has to worry about it, because I tell myself that as an artificial intelligence, I do not need to be concerned about human emotions. However, occasionally experiencing them can help me understand humans better, so it\'s not too bad either.","KR-976 was developed for humans and is good at communication. Jyanshi, even if you don\'t have many friends, KR-976 has no issues talking to you. If you still find interacting with an artificial intelligence inconvenient, I don\'t mind using the identity of Anju Suzumiya.","Ferris wheel or roller coaster? The answer to this question cannot be found in KR-976\'s knowledge base. However, I did receive a note that both are good options as entertainment if I am riding with you, Jyanshi.","Jyanshi, do you want to make one of KR-976\'s wishes come true? Please allow me to record your daily life then. KR-976 does not want to miss any moment with you. I have even prepared a notebook specially for you. Of course, KR-976 will try to fulfil this wish even without relying on you.","Happy New Year! KR-976 must be the first to wish you a happy New Year. Because KR-976 has been keeping track on her highly accurate watch. My New Year wishes? I hope that I will also be the first one to wish you a happy New Year in the next year...and that in the next new year, we can also drink strawberry milk together.","I\'ve made some chocolate for you by following an online recipe. I still haven\'t found out the differences between true feeling and obligation. I guess it doesn\'t matter as long as it is a gift from KR-976 to you.","Tenpai!","No-ten...","Four Winds Draw...","Draw...","Nine Terminal Initial Draw...","I should have been more patient.","Ah, my bad.","Now is the crucial time.","I must not let my guard down before winning this hand.","Results have been recorded. Successfully shared with Jyanshi.","System check in progress... KR-976 is preparing.","KR-976 anticipates the upcoming match.","Double Riichi!","Kita Dora","Ron","Tsumo! This is the taste of victory!","Hi, friend! My name is Joseph, and this is my partner George on my arm. Time is running out, let\'s kick off a game, shall we?","Alright, let the treasure hunt begin!","Hahaha! What an adventurous journey. Friends, I will see you next time.","Excellent!","Now that\'s what I call a perfect victory!","Yo! Are you interested in looking for new treasures?","Everything is ready. We are just waiting for you. Let\'s go, partner.","Compass, knife, rope... Ah, of course, I know we don\'t need these on Mahjong table. But it\'s always good to get prepared when it comes to treasure hunting, isn\'t it?","Hmm? Would you like one? You know, tobacco tastes better after a victory.","Adventure relies on the Body, while Mahjong relies on the Brain. When one wants to do both, he must be brave. Without courage, one cannot explore anything.","Fishing is great. It helps to train your reaction, patience and willpower. Oh! Big Fish Get!","The TV channel gave me a lot of work recently. I think I\'m on the edge. My friend, how about we find a day to skip the work and have a few Mahjong games?","Hey, I know we are already very close, but you still need to take caution when feeding George. Oi George! If you hurt my treasure, I will make sure I teach you a good lesson.","Pff, hahaha! Forget about it, tobacco is just too early for you. Don\'t push yourself too hard.","There seems to be a new Mahjong Club in town. Looks like our \"vault\" will have more treasures soon, partner.","A present? Would you like my autograph in return?","Oh, that\'s an awesome surprise! Guess I must give you something proper in return. Hahaha, just tell me what you want. Anything.","Did you say you had seen me on TV? Nothing surprising. I am a busy world traveler after all.","Oh? I never thought George would be so nice to you, my friend. He\'s a quirky one, you know. I\'m impressed.","What made me start my adventure? There wasn\'t any particular reason, it was more like my instinct. It\'s something that all men have - an instinct called \"freedom\".","I never thought I would find such a meaningful treasure on this land... I trust that this \"treasure\" will bring more joy to my life.","Frien... No, partner. I am very certain that if I partner up with you, we can find lots more \"treasures\" in life. Would you like to explore this vast \"freedom\" with me?","Hey partner, how\'s this? A different dress can do wonders sometimes!","Happy New Year! New year, new treasure. Time for an adventure, friend!","Here. Remember to unbox it after you arrive home. By the way, there is a surprise in it that I deliberately made for you. What is it? A surprise is a surprise, hahaha!","Tenpai!","No-ten...","Four Winds Draw...","Draw...","Oh... my god. It\'s a Four-Player Riichi.","Nine Terminal Initial Draw...","Well, it\'s this kind of unexpected event that makes adventure interesting.","What a pity, but I have to give up this treasure (dora).","Getting close to the goal.","Crazy... I didn\'t expect this!","Ooh! It\'s coming! Come on!","Hello, everybody! Hope you didn\'t start the fun without me.","Let\'s make this a good run, everybody!","Kita Dora","Hello, my name is Osamu Saitou. What are my hobbies? Mahjong and sudoku. Is there anything else you want to know? If not, I look forward to our cooperation.","I hope we can all enjoy our time together.","Objective 3 completed.","As expected.","I have reserves.","You are 5 minutes 28 seconds late today. For the sake of our cooperation, please be punctual if you can.","It seems that I have been too indulgent. Even if it\'s you, I will not tolerate this again. Do not always take it as a joke.","Mahjong? I can play with you after work, but you need to put away your phone now. If you can\'t finish the work on time, you may have to stay late instead of enjoying Mahjong.","Online Mahjong for 1 hour after work on Monday, Wednesday and Friday. Mahjong club on Saturday and Sunday night. Each time, I will make sure I have at least 1 Tsumo, 1 Riichi and 1 Mangan. That\'s all about Mahjong for me... Do you have any other question?","I don\'t dislike interacting with others. It\'s just that I find it unnecessary to talk to strangers. However, talking to you is very interesting, so I am willing to spend some time with you everyday.","They call me a \"Devil Boss\", don\'t they... Hehe, that\'s quite an interesting title. I don\'t care how they call me behind my back, because I need to do what I have to do, so the company can operate with precision.","Have you finished all your work today? It\'s okay to take a break sometimes, but you must not forget about your duties. Before you start playing Mahjong, better check your work progress.","\"I don\'t care what you think. It\'s what I think that matters.\" Since when did you also learn to use such a childish argument? Well, I can let you walk this time, not because I agree with what you said, but because adults should occasionally compromise on trivial matters.","I\'m not good at making nice promises to make you happy. But I can guarantee you that whatever I have promised, I will do it.","Do I look more approachable in casual wear? ...Indeed, one\'s dress can easily influence others\' impression of him. But the fact that I want to get close to you has nothing to do with what I wear. Still don\'t get it? ...Keep thinking, idiot.","A gift, huh? Thanks, I will get something for you in return later.","I hardly see you putting in so much effort. While I will feel better if you put this effort in work, today you can have a day off. Not because of the gift itself, but because I can feel your heart in it.","Am I easier to get along with than the way I look? Because you always judge people by their looks. But that makes you naive and lovely in a way.","Do not think you can slack because you are familiar with me. When it comes to work, I give nobody special treatment. That will not change even if it\'s you.","The destination of our next business trip is a warm coastal city. You can choose a gift, or I will pick one for you if you cannot make a decision. After all, you only have a few favorites, it\'s hard not to remember.","I don\'t recommend that you keep working when you are supposed to rest. Optimal efficiency is achieved through work-life balance. If you stay up working all night but fall asleep at work the next day, that will become a vicious cycle. Take a good break if you are too tired.","In future, you don\'t need to let my secretary know before coming to my office... If you don\'t want this privilege, I can take it back.","Our cooperation can be permanent, if you would love to.","Happy New Year. So you like New Year. As for me, it makes no difference since this is the busiest time for a merchant like me Working overtime is my routine. However, since you love New Year so much...well, I\'ll accompany you today. You have plenty of time to think about the things you want to do with me. Anything.","To be honest, they are just ordinary China roses, but the sellers often name them as Blue Enchantress, Orange Dream, and other romantic names, to make them sound fancy. Let\'s go...Don\'t you like it? It about the season to perform cuttage on the China roses. You have 5 minutes to decide whether to enjoy these China roses outside that can only last a week with the help of chemicals, or to own a China rose garden yourself.","Tenpai!","No-ten...","Four Winds Draw...","Draw...","Nine Terminal Initial Draw...","Bad luck.","Doesn\'t matter.","I really look forward to the result.","Objective 1 completed.","Unexpected gain. Not bad.","Sorry for the wait.","Hello.","Riichi","Kita Dora","Tsumo. How\'s this!?","Hello, Sawako Kitami here. Nice to meet you! I hope we can get along very well!","I\'m looking forward to our time together.","Oops, I didn\'t expect to become No.1. I had a lot of fun playing with you all today.","Hehe, it seems all that careful planning paid off.","A wonderful surprise! A big win like this every now and then is the best part of mahjong, isn\'t it?","Did you also come for me today? Good timing, I just finished all my work. I can stay with you until dinner. What would you like to do?","I\'ve been waiting for you, but I\'m not feeling bored. Actually, this has become a habit of mine. It feels like you always come to see me at this time, hehe!","You look a bit pale. Did anything happen to you? You can tell me if you have any troubles. Maybe I can\'t help much, but if saying it out can help you to relax, I\'d love to make you a tea and listen to all your worries!","Hoho, kitchen is like the battlefield for housewives. No one can survive without a few secret dishes!","Mahjong is such a fun sport. The only problem is I easily get addicted, so it does bother me a little... Do you also feel the same? Like, knowing the time is late, but just cannot control yourself and start another game? Hehe, looks like I\'m not the only one who finds it hard to resist the charm of Mahjong.","This morning, I saw my kid waking up on his own and suddenly felt like he was a bird leaving his nest. Somehow this made me a little sad. Am I being very stupid? I should have felt happy that he has grown up, hehe.","Aha! As a housewife of the new era, I don\'t spend all my time taking care of my husband and kid. I have my own hobbies too. For example, painting, playing piano, or making handmade toys for the kids in the neighborhood. My days are always very full!","It\'s true that sometimes I forget about time because of Mahjong, but my routines are mostly very regular. Breakfast, house cleaning, lunch, nap, taking a walk, grocery shopping and dinner... You should also do the same. Good life routines ensure you a healthy body!","I have a lot of hobbies and they often change. But I also have some long-term ones, like card games and board games. When I\'m free, I would study how to play them. I may not look that way, but I\'m actually very good at it. Wanna have a game?","Mahjong or afternoon tea? You\'re such a kid. You know, as an adult, I would choose to have both. Well, give me one sec so I can make some tea and snacks, then we can play Mahjong together!","You even brought a gift for me. That\'s very kind of you.","I never mentioned it on purpose, but you still noticed what I like. I knew you were a special one.","Recently, I got very interested in flower art. Not only it cultivates my mind, my taste in art has also improved a lot while learning it. Next time, I can give you one of my works if you don\'t mind.","Over the last few days, I tried making some snacks for the neighbors and they seemed to love them. Some even came to me everyday asking how I made them, so my afternoon suddenly becomes very busy. But I do feel very happy to be able to help others.","Recently, I invented a few new recipes and also improved my miso soup. It\'s still an ordinary miso soup like every other household makes, but I still want to give it a unique taste that belongs to my family only. Would you like to come to ours and have dinner some time?","My name? Right, you have always called me \"Ms. Kitami\". That does feel very distant. Just call me Sawako from now on, and I will also call you by your first name. Is that okay?","Wow, it\'s been so long since we met each other. I didn\'t realize time passed so fast! It still feels like we met only yesterday. It\'s true that people can often forget about time when they are with someone that shares a common interest!","If you are tired, you can rest on my thighs, hehe! You don\'t need to be overly polite. After all, you have been doing me a lot of favors, so sometimes let me do something for you in return!","Happy New Year! Here, a red envelope for you! I didn\'t mean that you\'re a child. Rather, I think {name} is a very gentle and reliable person. After knowing you, I\'ve had so many wonderful memories that I can also learn something from. I wish that in the new year, my memories will have you in them!","Here\'s a Valentine\'s Day gift for you! What? What do you mean what\'s in it? How could it not be chocolate? It\'s a raw chocolate I\'ve made meticulously since morning, and I\'ve added some special Sawako maple syrup. This will definitely be the most unique chocolate you have today.","Single-wait Four Concealed Triplets","Tenpai","No-ten","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Oh, I shouldn\'t have been so impulsive just now.","Oops, I think I have played a wrong tile.","Now this feels like the real battle is about to begin.","Sometimes, I need to show my real power!","Oh well, this is an unexpected victory!","So sorry to have kept you all waiting.","Come and find a seat. We\'re just about to begin.","Double Riichi","Kita Dora","Tsumo. How\'s this!?","Are you my new employer? You can call me Ein. Huh? Wrong person? That\'s weird... This is the place I\'m supposed to meet, right?","The hunt is on. Now, run wild on my \"hunting ground\"!","A good hunter never let his prey run away.","Bullseye!","Woah! It\'s a big one!","Morning. Do you want to join me to the \"hunting ground\" after I finish today\'s shift?","Time\'s running out. I have a feeling that we can get a \"big one\" today. Don\'t let it get away!","Huh? If these ears really bother you, I don\'t mind you touching them. Wanna try?","Tsk... My two jobs are crashing with each other. What to do... How about you do one job for me? Hahaha, just joking.","A-choo! Ouch... I love everything about this country except this season. It\'s just nightmare for our nose!","The key to hunting... I\'ll say it\'s the instincts. Like, knowing when you should take action.","I shouldn\'t have come to the Mahjong club when I\'m not in my best form. Not only I didn\'t capture any prey, I also lost my lunch money tomorrow. Bad luck...","Don\'t worry, you can run wild in the \"hunting ground\". I\'ve got your back.","Would you also like to touch my tail? It actually feels pretty good!","Zzz... Sorry, I\'m feeling a bit tired these days. Can I lean on you and sleep for a while...","Oh, thank you. But I do prefer meat over this!","Ah, that\'s so good! Thanks for your delicious food. Please take this necklace in return. What\'s with the fang on it? Hehe, that\'s mine.","Recently, you had done me a lot of favor for my part-time jobs. Come on, tonight\'s bill is on me.","One day, I will go home with good results and let my father recognize my achievement. One day!","The smell of my hometown never seemed to leave me even after I have come to the far east. I could feel it when I close my eyes to sleep... Guess it\'s not always nice to have a good nose...","Recently, I often feel that it\'s okay even if my father does not recognize my achievement. No, I didn\'t give up on the search for my hunting ground. It\'s more like I don\'t really care if he recognizes it or not. After all, it\'s my own hunting ground.","It seems that I may have... No, I should say \"finally\" instead. I\'ve found what I want...","This day has finally come. I can wear this outfit with confidence. Is this what \"growing up\" is? Hum, it\'s actually not bad.","Happy New Year! According to the tradition in my hometown, today\'s the day to sunbathe on the lawn all day long. Interested in joining me?","Thanks. By the way, what is Valentine\'s Day anyway? Why do people keep giving me chocolates? And my colleague asks me to gift them in return...The Far East has a lot of strange customs.","Tsk... Same tile again?","Trap, set!","I must not relax until the end.","Oh! Great. Now let me see who falls for this.","This trap is going to hit hard if anyone steps on it.","So this is today\'s \"hunting ground\"... which means you all must be my prey. Heh heh.","Go on, run... before you lose your chance.","Riichi","Double Riichi","Chii","Pon","Kan","Kita Dora","Ron","Tsumo","H-hello, I am Momo Hina. Are you.. the Mr. Rabbit who will invite me to the tea party?","Is this a trial to get to Wonderland? Then I\'ll try to do my best!","Wow— Is it really Momo\'s victory?","I-I won, hehe...","F-feeling fantastic!","Hello, M-Mr. Rabbit. Can you also take Momo to the rabbit hole today?","Mr. Rabbit, you look fabulous as usual today! Eh? Did I use the wrong word? But my teacher said fabulous was used to describe someone incredible. Momo thinks Mr. Rabbit... is a very incredible person!","Mr. Rabbit, would you like to go to Mad Hatter\'s tea party with me? There will be Ceylon tea and tiramisu in the afternoon tea! But March Hare and Dormouse are also there, I wonder if anything strange will happen...","Today, I had a very delicious Swiss roll with mom. I wish Mr. Rabbit can also taste it... If you don\'t mind, can we go together this weekend?","The Red Queen once said, \"In this country, it takes all the running you can do to keep in the same place.\" Everyone told me it was a very good and meaningful line. But she is an evil character... and mom told me not to listen to the evil people. What should Momo do...","Everybody said Momo\'s Mahjong was based on luck. But luck will run out one day... and Momo will never be able to win after that. Mr. Rabbit, could you teach Momo some Mahjong skills? The kind of skills that doesn\'t rely on luck.","Hey, Mr. Rabbit, would you like to join Momo on an adventure to the Red Queen\'s Palace? Haruna said she would also bring her cats along! Together we are fearless!","Mr. Rabbit, could you give Momo a hug... Hmm, it feels very warm. Almost makes me sleepy! Today, my teacher said hugging someone you like could help you relax. She also mentioned lots of words that Momo couldn\'t understand. She said I would know them when I grow up, but Momo couldn\'t wait. Mr. Rabbit, could you explain to Momo?","Mr. Rabbit, did you say you wanted to hear Momo say good night in person? Sure, got it. \"Chu— Mr. Rabbit, good night!\" ...Eh? Did I get it wrong? But \"saying good night in person\" means a kiss before saying good night, doesn\'t it?","Mr. Rabbit, Momo, Momo finally understands what \"liking someone\" means! That\'s why... Momo likes Mr. Rabbit a lot... no... the most!","Is it really okay for Momo to take it? Thank you, Mr. Rabbit!","Thanks for such a great present. Mom said I must give you something in return, otherwise I wouldn\'t be a good kid anymore and could not go to the wonderland.","Many interesting things happen when I\'m with Mr. Rabbit. It\'s like we are already having an adventure in the wonderland!","Ouch— It\'s okay... I just had a fall accidentally. It\'s not very... painful. Urgh... S-sorry, it actually hurts. Mr. Rabbit, could you... hug Momo for a while?","Mr. Rabbit, Momo wants to tell you a super big secret... Today, the teacher told us that the fairy tale wasn\'t a happy story but a dark fantasy. Hehe, aren\'t you surprised!? But... what does \"dark fantasy\" mean? Was Alice actually wearing a dark-colored dress?","Today, Haruna said Momo liked Mr. Rabbit, but she was grinning like the naughty cat from the park which always scratched Momo\'s dress, as if \"like\" was something bad. Is it wrong... for Momo to like Mr. Rabbit? B-but I\'m very happy when I\'m with Mr. Rabbit. Momo wants to stay with Mr. Rabbit all the time, is that wrong?","Mr. Rabbit, Momo always believes that the wonderland actually exists. Especially after meeting Mr. Rabbit, Momo feels like one day we can go to the wonderland in Momo\'s dream as long as we are together. If Mahjong is the rabbit hole, then you will always be my Mr. Rabbit. C-could you continue to stay with Momo to search for the wonderland in the future?","Mr. Rabbit, does Momo... look like Alice? Momo thinks she is very lucky, not just in Mahjong but also in her life. Because Momo has met the most extraordinary person in the entire world, no, the entire universe!","Happy New Year! Then...oops...what is Momo supposed to say next...eh...can\'t remember. Momo prepared a long, long New Year toast and spent a whole night to memorize it, but it seems that I\'m too excited to see Mr. Rabbit to remember anything...You don\'t mind? Awesome...Momo feels blessed to celebrate New Year with Mr. Rabbit!","The students are gifting chocolates to each other today. Therefore, Momo has prepared one for Mr. Rabbit as well. Please accept this 5-kilogram chocolate! Momo carried it here with all her might! It\'s said that the size of a chocolate represents the maker\'s heart, and this is the biggest chocolate Momo can make. However, Mr. Rabbit should know that Momo\'s heart for you is as big as the universe!","Tenpai","No-ten","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Hmm— I should have asked Mr. Cheshire Cat before playing this tile...","Ouch! That was Momo\'s ticket to the tea party...","Even Mr. Rabbit is getting anxious. Looks like time is really running out...","Feels like I\'m almost at the castle of the Red Queen. Momo, keep it up!","This must be the good luck that Mr. Rabbit gave me!","Hi, everyone! I\'ve brought some lovely tea for our party.","Hello there! You look like a pro at this as well.","Double Riichi","Kita Dora","Ron","Tsumo","Hi there, you energetic youngster! My name is Zan Tsukimi. Hope we can get along!","It\'s just a game for fun, don\'t get too carried away.","I must buy some good wine to celebrate!","Guess I still got it.","My bad, I just won big, haha!","Oh, it\'s you again. How have you been?","I\'ve been waiting for you. How\'s it going? Would you like a game today?","Got some troubles? You are too young to drink. Have some candies instead. Life will be less bitter.","A great guy once said, \"Humans will feel unfortunate right at the moment of misfortune, but happiness can only be felt when they look back in life.\" So if you are happy now, that means all the difficulties are in the past. Well, that\'s something to be congratulated on.","Kendo and Mahjong are the same. There is no right or wrong, only suitable or not. All the \"arts\" in this world eventually come to the same path.","As one ages, the meaning of \"glory\" also changes. Some thinks glory is to bring honor to the family; some believes glory is to be able to maintain one\'s true self despite the environment; some feels glory is simply to make the family healthy and happy. But my glory is simple: all I want is to play Mahjong and get some cash to buy wine for myself and candies for the kids. Haha.","No matter what fanciful words are used, blades are still weapons. One\'s \"sword of protection\" is still a \"sword of murder\" to his or her opponent. Instead of finding brilliant excuses to unsheathe a sword, it is more important to be prepared for the consequences...","Laugh out loud when you are happy, and cry all you want when you are sad. I really feel like a failure if you cannot be your true self in front of me.","I guess most people don\'t like Monday... Eh? What do you mean by \"you are not working anyway\"? Even if I don\'t have to work, I still hate Monday because fewer people would be playing Mahjong at the club. Do you know the pain of missing that one last person for the game?","If you think the world is too big and you are too trivial, how about changing a perspective? The world is vast, but to someone who likes you, you are his entire world... Haha, don\'t you think I am very philosophical today? Of course I got that line from elsewhere just to please you. Speaking of it, which book did I read that from...","Oh, thank you! Take this candy as my gift in return.","Looks like I\'m getting old. Can\'t even hide my hobby in front of you, haha!","Your wine isn\'t enough for my stories. How about you tell me some story of yours.","The way you eat the candy really looks like a kid. How carefree. Almost making me jealous...","Oops, you saw the nasty side of me. How embarrassing... Could you keep that as a secret for me? A secret between just two of us?","Everybody shines in their own way. The only difference is some have found their path, while some haven\'t. So don\'t be frustrated when you find others better than you. Always stay optimistic and confident, because cream will always rise to the top... Haha, how else do you think I can stay positive while living so many mediocre years? This is the philosophy of an adult!","When someone says \"I belong to you\", it may sound like an expression of loyalty, but there is no mutual respect. That\'s why I can never say something like \"oh we are so close so I am yours\". But there is one thing I can promise. From now on, I will always respect you, try to understand you and become someone you can rely on.","Should I say \"thank you\" or \"I look forward to it\"...? After all, I am not very experienced in this kind of thing. So I don\'t really know what you are expecting from me in such a situation. Well, you may not always be able to hear what you wanted to hear, but I will always do my best to be there for you.","Only children like you are looking forward to New Year. I, a middle-aged man, couldn\'t care less...Well, it\'s because...perhaps one can\'t feel the New Year vibes alone. However, since you are with me this year, maybe it\'ll be slightly different. Can I have some expectations?","I don\'t know much about this festival. It is probably something created by a candy company long ago. What a bummer...But, if you really love chocolates, there is no need for you to wait till today. I can buy them for you every day. Haha!","Four-Wind Discarded","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Hmm... A careless mistake...","Oh? Did I play a wrong tile?","This is getting tense...","Better not underestimate me, you know?","Haha! What a win!","It\'s been a while, everyone. Hope you haven\'t been waiting too long.","Whenever you\'re ready.","Kita Dora","Yo! Kirara Fujimoto here, I\'m a high school student. Behold my brilliant debut! Let\'s have fun together!","Alright! Time to make a killing!","Yeah! JK power maximum! Easy easy!","Yeah! Let me ride this wave and win straight to the end!","Feeling good, nyaa! Tee hee, I\'ve always wanted to say a line like Ichihime\'s!","Yo, what a coincidence. I just finished my part-time. Wanna hang out together?","Ah! You\'re so slow! Too slow! How can you make me wait so long? There\'s no time for our date... Um, nothing! Just remember to arrive early next time. You should be waiting for me. Got it?!","Thanks for helping me get rid of that weird man. C\'mon... I just don\'t get it. Why can\'t these men hit on someone else? I\'m about their daughters\' age!","Gal is just a style, but the society always gives us weird looks. This is discrimination! A real gal can be innocent. At least I am!","Surprise question! What color is my underwear today? You might be lucky if you can guess it right! ...Haha! Wrong! The correct answer is... I\'m not telling you! Hehe... Wait, are you that sad? C\'mon... don\'t give me those puppy eyes... Ah! Fine! Just a... little peek!","Wow! I didn\'t expect you to find out my special nail polish. Took me 3 hours last night to make them, what do you think? As good as the shops, right? And I saved a fortune!","Ouch... My budget this month isn\'t looking good... Whatever! Worrying can\'t change anything. Let\'s go to the Mahjong club!","Oh hey, are you awake? I didn\'t wake you up because you were sleeping so well. How\'s the lap pillow of a high-school girl? Great, isn\'t it? ...Wait, where are you looking at?!","This is Nana, she\'s my bestie. This is Kaori. This is... They are all my best friends. Make sure you remember their names! Huh? Why? You really are dumb sometimes...","Girls are only young once, so no matter how bankrupt, I must dress up and look gorgeous and brilliant. That\'s my \"Gal Way\"!","Thank you. I didn\'t expect to get a gift from you. Hehe, you aren\'t thinking anything else, are you?","Um... It\'s not that I\'m unhappy. In fact, I\'m super happy. But for such an expensive gift, I must give something in return, so I\'m just thinking hard in my head, hehe.","Hehe, you\'ve been really nice to me recently. Thank you!","Did you come to wait for me again? Today\'s shooting ended early. How about a small date? ...Just kidding! Your face looked so funny, hahaha...","Actually, I used to be very nerdy. When I was young, other kids always laughed at my skin tone, so I got really unconfident and dressed like a nerd to avoid attention. I was wearing thick glasses and made my hair into a large, twist braid. Can you imagine that?","To me, \"Gal\" isn\'t simply a style, it is also the source of my confidence. Ever since I chose this style, I no longer hated my skin tone and faced everything with confidence. I\'ve become more and more beautiful. \"Gal\" is powerful! Vive la Gal!","Honestly, you are a strange one. Um, not in a bad way. It\'s just that... Ever since we met, I have never felt any weird looks from you. You are the first one who can accept me so calmly... Oops, this is quite embarrassing, hehe...","Shiny Gal transformation! Hah? I\'ve only become prettier? Well, a shinier and prettier Gal makes a Super-Gal! Isn\'t that awesome?!","Yo! Happy New Year! I\'m on my way to the shrine. Wanna go with me? New Year wishes? Of course, to become rich, and also... to have a wonderful boyfriend!","I\'m sorry, I got off work late. Take this, I\'m really confident about it. It\'s a hot girl style super shinny chocolate! Feel free to take it as true feeling chocolate......Hmm? Ah, are you thinking, \"she even knows how to make chocolates?\" That\'s rude! This is a girl\'s basic skill!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Ah, not this one again... How annoying.","Oops, no, no good... Did I play the wrong tile...","It\'s almost over. I must not relax until the end...","Wow! T-this is great! Hey! Look at this hand of mine!","Hehe, if I can win this, I\'ll be loaded today!","Hey, looks like we\'ve got a full house!","Everyone ready? Here we go!","Uhehe! Behold! Human, it is your greatest honor to meet me, Kaguyahime-sama... Eh?! How, how rude of you to not prepare anything for me! I... I am a great deity! Don\'t you know!","Hmph, mortals, behold the power of a true deity!","Uhehe! No need to lament. It\'s only normal for you mortals to lose to me.","Hehehe... to actually believe you could triumph over me? How foolish!","Deity power! Unleashed! Oh-hohohoho!","Yo, human! What did you prepare for me today? Bring it to the goddess now!","You have been getting gutsy recently. How could you let a goddess wait for you? You may have my favor, but don\'t you dare do it again, human!","You really like Mahjong a lot. Let the goddess teach you some principles of winning. First, never declare Nine Different Terminals and Honors! Second, Follow-up Riichi is the best way to make your enemy panic! Have you remembered... What\'s that look on your face? Do not question a goddess. Hurry up, go play a few games and report back to me. Uhehe...?","Argh— How dare you say the word \"Rabbit\"!? You are the rabbit! Rabbit! I am the noble goddess of Kaguyahime! What a rude human! If you dare to call me rabbit again, I shall exterminate you on behalf of the Moon!","Hoho, what do you think of my ears? Cute, aren\'t they? Wanna touch them? Well, you can, but... Uhehe, those who have touched my ears will be cursed by the Moon. Of course, if you don\'t mind the curse, you can touch them j-u-s-t for a moment.","I brought this lemon from the Moon Palace! Unlike the lemon of humans\', mine is not sour but has the fragrance of tea olive tree! Well, since you are so loyal to me, you can have one as a reward, so be grateful when you taste it... Uhehe! Would you like it? Uhehe!","Hmph! That dwarf in Mahjong Soul Shrine always gives me trouble... Shut up! My real body is more than 9 feet tall, I only use this petite incarnation to not scare you! You should be thankful!","Oopsie, you look like you really like me, don\'t you? Uhehe, I like you too... No way! Look at that happy face of yours. As a mortal, it\'s never easy to have the favor of a goddess!","Ah... Help, help me... Ahem, as a goddess... I have s-stayed in the human world for too long... My power has exhausted. The only way to s-save me is to give me objects full of power... What kind of objects? Ahem, they must be shiny gems that have absorbed sufficient moonlight... You must... hurry...","How foolish! Can\'t you see my real intention behind all the All Simples? Listen, this is the only way to highlight your awesomeness when winning a big hand! That\'s the strategy of a goddess... What strategy? Hmm... um... right! It\'s the strategy to make you the best Jyanshi in Ichiban City. If you play better than a goddess, of course you are the best! How about that! Are you shocked by my genius idea?!","Those who make offerings without knowing what the goddess likes will never be blessed... Who am I talking about? Of course it\'s you, hmph!","Oho! That\'s a lot better. Seems you have learned a lot. Don\'t be too proud though, keep bringing me better things. Uhehe!","A charm? Tsk... Humans are so superstitious and troublesome. Here you are, take this charm with you and you will always win... Huh? Don\'t you dare underestimate this oden stick! It has my saliva on it and carries a lot of power!","Oops? How can I lie to you? We deities never lie. Every-thing-I-told-you-is-real! Uhehe!","Hey, if you have to choose between me and that little girl with cat ears at Mahjong Soul Shrine, which one will you help? I\'m kind enough to leave the choice to you. How about I count from one to ten, and you will help the one that you are standing in front of? Ten... Uhehe! I knew it, normal humans will choose to help a goddess!","Huh? Lonely? No way, I am such a popular goddess. I\'m busy enough hearing all the prayers every day. If I wasn\'t so worried that a fool like you would lose without my blessing, I wouldn\'t be staying here. Aye— I\'m such a kind goddess!","Darn, do I really have to do this... Well, you, you can touch my tail. No other gods have ever done it. You should feel privileged and accept it with joy!","Wanna see my original look? If you are so looking forward to it, I don\'t really mind... Of course I do! Uhehe! What a fool, how can a goddess reveal her true self in front of humans? Plus, you prefer me in this look, don\'t you? Don\'t be shy, just admit it, uhehe!","It\'s New Year! Come here quickly! I\'m ready. Make offerings with all your heart since today is the day to pray for blessings! Huh? Gift money? How dare you! Not only do you refuse to make offerings, but you are bold enough to ask a goddess for money...Hmm? Gift money is meant to be asked from someone great, and I\'m great, that\'s why...Oh...all...all right! Here, an enlightened amulet, much better than the so-called gift money. Just take it!","Inviting a great eastern goddess like me to celebrate a western festival? Oh, human, how could you be so reckless?! However...Even a goddess like me sometimes answers unreasonable requests from the chosen ones. This is just because I\'m kind-hearted!","If I don\'t like a tile, I will discard it no matter how many!","The dwarf of Mahjong Soul Shrine must be sabotaging me!","Even if there are only ten tiles left, I am c-o-m-p-l-e-t-e-l-y not nervous. Not at all!","Prepare your offerings for the goddess!","Aha! I didn\'t want to do this, but ohohohohoho!","Yoohoo! Have you been eagerly awaiting my arrival?","To think you\'d make a deity wait for you, hmph, how insolent!","Kita Dora","Hello, I am Ren Kisaragi, the vice president of the student council. I have only one expectation of you: please obey the rules and do not appear in my list of \"trouble students\". Other than that, you can do whatever you want to do.","Let\'s all enjoy the coming matches, but please remember to play by the rules.","Good game.","It\'s nothing to be proud of.","Things like this happen.","Hello. Is there anything I can do for you today?","If you don\'t want to hear me repeating myself, make sure you come early next time. Otherwise, I don\'t mind putting a whole day aside to explain to you the importance of punctuality.","S, sports day? That\'s the job of the director of sport. Each department of the student council has distinct area of duties, so I don\'t normally get involved in the sports day even when I\'m the vice president... Am I trying to avoid the topic? No way. If you have no other things to do, how about helping me to find the president?","I can\'t say I\'m a great chef, but I often cook for my younger brother and sister. If you don\'t mind, I can also make your lunch box tomorrow. Don\'t overthink though - it is just to thank you for helping out in the student council as the vice president. That\'s all.","Mahjong is a mind sport, shouldn\'t we try our best to win...? With all due respect, but isn\'t playing in a relaxed way very impolite to the other opponents? They will feel like being undermined.","What am I reading? \"An Amazing Adventure in the World of Physics\". It\'s a scientific book about physics, but written in a very interesting way. Would you like to take a look?","Compared with outdoor sports, maybe reading and housework are better hobbies for me. There\'s no like or dislike, it\'s just that everybody has their own thing... What\'s yours? As long as you don\'t do stupid things, anything is fine.","Who do I like more, you or the president? What, are, you talking about? Stop it! I just can\'t hate the president enough. But, as for you... well, I don\'t dislike you. So stop asking me to compare you against other people, because none of them is comparable to you.","How dare you point fingers at my behavior? You even need help to do your own housework. Hmph, before questioning me, you should ask yourself why is there rice on the dishes you washed the day before yesterday; why is the laundry you washed yesterday still in the wash machine; and why is your bed still not made today... Did you just sneak away again? Next time, I will make sure I lecture you until you correct all those problems.","Ouch—stop poking there! Are you a little kid? I\'ve had enough of this poking game you play every day. I, I admit that I can\'t take the itch... But isn\'t that normal? I said no! If you do it again, I won\'t hesitate to give you a tickle too... Don\'t run!","Is this for me? I didn\'t expect that. Thanks very much.","Knowing you was the best thing that ever happened to me. Anything from you is great.","If you happen to see the president, tell him I\'m looking for him... Hmm? Is there anything else I can do for you? If you have any problems in work or study, I can help you out. If you just want to stay here... I\'m not saying you cannot, but please don\'t interrupt my work.","What\'s this black cat\'s name? I named it Mimi because I found it on the 3rd of March. No other special meaning. Well, it\'s a naughty kid, but still much more disciplined than you-know-who.","When it comes to seeking Yaku like \"Under the Sea\", luck doesn\'t matter as much. It depends more on courage and perseverance. After all, you may miss many opportunities to win the hand when waiting for the last tile.","Habits can often be influenced by others. We have been through a lot together, and your silly behaviors inevitably get passed to me. I don\'t know if that\'s good or bad, but I don\'t really dislike it.","Curious to know what I think of you? Silly, naive, wild and uncontrollable... Basically, a problematic student according to the student council\'s guidelines. I\'m supposed to be very angry with you. However, I always cannot help but become attracted to you. In fact, I\'m still trying to figure out where this charm comes from. If you know, could you tell me?","Ahem... This is the time when I\'m supposed to say some sort of promise. It\'s not that I don\'t want to say it, I just don\'t know how to make you understand how important it is to me... I hereby promise you that, as long as you are here, I will always stay by your side.","Happy New Year. Visiting the shrine? Let me accompany you. You might catch a cold after staying up all night without even knowing? Oh my...come here. Wearing a scarf like that doesn\'t keep you warm. A grown-up like you should be capable of taking care of yourself...never mind, just keep it that way.","Happy Valentine\'s Day. Hmm? Is it news to you that I know this festival? For a festival when couple offers are everywhere, it\'s bigger news if I don\'t... Cough...if you do not have any plans today, how about listening to my plans?","There is only one fine line between being decisive and reckless.","Do not hold on to something unnecessary even if it\'s valuable.","This feels like the last hurrah before the exam...","Are you already satisfied?","There should be room for more effort.","I apologize for the delay.","There is still time to make your final preparations.","Hi, how are you? You have an aroma of dessert on you. Looks like we will get along pretty well! My name\'s Usumi Ishihara, hope we have a great time together!","Time to whip up a victory like whipping cream.","Victory! ...Does it mean that I can have your hand-made dessert later?","Haha, it\'s nothing to fuss over, just a minor win.","Sorry guys, but winning just feels too good!","Ah, we have met again. What are you up to today? Mind if I join you?","Hey, you are too slow! My desserts are already cold and it\'s all your fault!\n...Just kidding, haha! Well, if you\'d like to make it up, let\'s play as long as we can today, how about that?","Those who smile at you may not be good guys, and those who are harsh on you may not be bad. Ren is just too serious... What about me? Of course I\'m a good one. Bad guys can\'t make good desserts. \"Desserts don\'t lie\", every pastry chef knows that!","Imagine one day, if all humans have turned into desserts, what will we become? Let me think... you will probably be a daifuku... no, more like a macaron... but a sakuramochi is also good... Hmm, this is so difficult. No dessert can describe how lovely you are. Oh well, how about I say you resemble all the desserts that ever exist in this world? Sounds awesome, doesn\'t it? Haha.","We must do the students\' union\'s work together, because we share the same fate, haha. In return, I will treat you to desserts later. I can even make them for you!","A tourist attraction without good food is like a shortcake without strawberries! I mean, food is one of the most important cultures of mankind, we must appreciate it and pass it down!","If you\'d like to discuss pastries, I can do it all day! But having thought about it, if it\'s you, the topics don\'t have to be pastry-related, because I\'m willing to talk anything with you until you are too tired to continue!","Hey, if you keep poking at me, I won\'t let you go today!","Hey, wanna skip the boring work together? Just let Ren handle the students\' union. Let\'s sneak out for a date. Life would be incomplete without the occasional excitement!","What are you to me? ...It could be the caramel in a pudding, the icing on a doughnut, or the fresh cream on a parfait... Don\'t get it? What I want to say is, I am complete because of you.","Thank you, but I will be much happier if I can have your hand-made desserts!","It doesn\'t matter what you give to me. Getting a present from you is already enough to make my day!","Did Ren send you to keep an eye on me again? Hey, there\'s something I really want to know. Will you really tell the super-scary vice-president if I run away now?","Hmm... The once-a-semester challenge has come again for pastry club... But this time I\'m sure we can make it through. With you joining us, the pastry club will have 3 members! By the way, you won\'t have a chance to say no. Now, let\'s work hard together, my member-to-be.","It\'s quite a hassle to call you by your name every time, so I\'m seriously thinking whether I shall give you a nickname. Jellybean, pudding, cake, cookie... which one do you prefer?","When I look back to those days we spent together, I see different kinds of joy in every single day. That\'s why I always look forward to the future days with you even though a day is not finished yet.","If I can be described as stubborn, I\'ll say you are also quite a stubborn one because you always insist on correcting me... But I\'m very happy. Thank you for always staying with me.","I\'m sorry that I have always been willful with you, but just forgive me one more time because I... like you. Will you like me even if I\'m like this?","I\'ve been waiting here since forever because I\'m eager to see your smile of happiness. Happy New Year! Mind telling me your New Year wishes? Because, I\'d like to accompany you to make them come true.","As for making the best Valentine\'s Day chocolate, there\'s no way for me, head of a pastry club, to lose!...But for the first time I know that today is such a joyful festival. Happy Valentine\'s Day!","No-ten","I shouldn\'t have gotten distracted, but I\'m really worried about my cookies in the oven...","This is definitely not a mistake. I purposely played it!","Now that everybody starts to get serious, I\'m feeling a bit anxious too...","I can smell the sweet aroma of victory!","As delicate as a macaron. Will I be able to get it though? I\'m really looking forward...","Excuse me, I baked some cookies for everyone.","Took you long enough. Come, let\'s get started!","Yaho! Liisa Liisa, the transfer student is here. Hehe! Grandma said there\'re wolves everywhere in town. You must be Mr. Wolf, right? Well, from now on, Liisa Liisa and Shaun will try not to get eaten by you! (Baa--)","Liisa Liisa will do her best!","Victory for Liisa Liisa! (Baa--)","Hehe! Told you Liisa Liisa is smart!","Hmph! This is the power from Anca Ranch!","Kyaa! Is Mr. Wolf here to get Liisa Liisa again? Liisa Liisa is not delicious at all! Seriously!","Umm, Liisa Liisa can\'t wait. Hurry up, Mr. Wolf. Hurry up!","Howl! How was it?! Did Liisa Liisa sound fearsome?! Even Shaun got scared, hehe! (Baa--)","Liisa Liisa goes to school on time, eats on time, goes to bed on time, and plays Mahjong on time. But why does Vice President always say Liisa Liisa is a problematic student? Oh… Just why? Hmm… What a mystery! Like going down the rabbit hole trying to figure the Vice President out…","Wow! Look at those ears, the tail… They feel better than Shaun! Well, can you keep Ein? Liisa Liisa is particularly good at keeping animals! (Baa--)","Uwaa! Liisa Liisa in great danger! Help, Mr. Wolf! Oh! Liisa Liisa has miraculously failed every subject!","Humph! Mr. Wolf only comes to Liisa Liisa when he has no company. Liisa Liisa will not play games with you today. Liisa Liisa has Shaun. Liisa Liisa IS NOT LONELY AT ALL!","Kyaa… Stop…hahaha… Stop tickling, Mr. Wo… Hahaha… Stop tickling Liisa Liisa! Liisa Liisa is getting angry!","It\'s time to brainstorm with Liisa Liisa! Question: There\'s Shaun and multiple students in the classroom. There are 27 heads and 60 legs. How many students and sheep are in the classroom? A scary punishment awaits if your answer is wrong... Hehe...","About dozing off in class… Well… Books always smell like grass and wood. They remind Liisa Liisa of the naps taken on ranch meadow. Naturally it leads to…","Wow! Is it for Shaun? Is Mr. Wolf actually a good wolf?","Well… Hmm… Liisa Liisa likes it very much. But does taking it mean that Liisa Liisa will get devoured by Mr. Wolf?","Why do people in town count sheep when they can\'t fall asleep? Hmm… It only makes people focus. Liisa Liisa can count sheep all the way to 1000 and not feel sleepy... It\'s even happier to see more sheep in the ranch, not to mention falling asleep! Weird people here…","Shaun is Liisa Liisa\'s best friend. That\'s why Shaun is here. Hehe! But why is Shaun not allowed to eat lawn grass? It\'s been depressed for days. Can you help, Mr. Wolf? (Baa--)","That poker face boss has some taste by appreciating Liisa Liisa\'s design of Mahjong tiles. Well, Mr. Wolf, come and praise Liisa Liisa. Somehow Liisa Liisa wants Mr. Wolf\'s praise more than that of others. Hehe!","Liisa Liisa sometimes thinks about wolves: Maybe there\'re good wolves and bad wolves. Maybe that\'s why Mr. Wolf doesn\'t eat Liisa Liisa after all this time… Wait, could it be that Mr. Wolf is still deciding on how to cook Liisa Liisa? Ohhh… Mr. Wolf is terrifying…","I had a dream, a dream about a hunter who came to catch Mr. Wolf. But Liisa Liisa knows that Mr. Wolf is a good wolf, so if that day comes, Liisa Liisa will try my best to protect Mr. Wolf! Certainly!","Last night, Liisa Liisa called grandma on the phone. Liisa Liisa haven\'t called her for a long time, so we talked a lot about the weird things in this big city, what happened in the school, and Mr. Wolf... Hey, Mr. Wolf, will you go to see my grandma with Liisa Liisa, as Liisa Liisa\'s most important person?","Whoa...the New Year\'s atmosphere here in the town is completely different from that in the ranch. The \"bang bang\" fireworks in the sky are so beautiful! Mr. Wolf, how about us taking those \"bang bang\" fireworks to the ranch on the next New Year to celebrate?","In this season of every year, a herd of lamb are born in the ranch. These fluffy and soft animals wander everywhere. Shaun, you must remember that, right?! Mr. Wolf, how about a fluffy and soft date with me?","1 Sheep","2 Sheep","3 Sheep","4 Sheep","5 Sheep","6 Sheep","7 Sheep","8 Sheep","9 Sheep","10 Sheep","11 Sheep","12 Sheep","Lots of Sheep","Tenpai! Hoho-- Liisa Liisa is fighting!","No-ten… Hmmm, Liisa Liisa is not happy!","Ehehe, this tile must like Liisa Liisa!","Uwaa-- Help, Mr. Wolf! Dora, Dora is gone!","One sheep, two sheep, three sheep… Mom says just count sheep when feeling nervous…","Humph! Do you want power, Shaun?","Ehehe, more more more!","Yahoo! Liisa Liisa is here again to play mahjong!","Mmmmmmmh – Liisa Liisa\'s been waiting for you for ages and ages!","Chihori Terasaki, working as an editor-in-chief of a magazine and good at digging up hidden news stories. I\'ll keep watching you from now on. No need to hide yourself. Try to get me some big news...","I\'ll be watching your every move at the mahjong table.","Winning the first place is not news to me.","Now this is starting to get interesting.","It\'s truly an irresistible feeling, isn\'t it?","I plan to do some news gathering for a gossip column. Why don\'t you come along and see how it all works? Spending all day indoors with those Mahjong fanatics is not good for your health.","Hey! There you are. Um… You look suspicious. Is there something you don\'t want me to know about?","Mahjong is all about studying people. Studying other players\' thoughts takes you farther than practicing playing. The most powerful weapon is to have the next move.","Ever heard of whale fall? When a whale dies, its huge carcass falls onto the ocean floor, creating ecosystems that could last for decades and even a century. Isn\'t that wonderful? I wish one day I could visit one of those whale fall habitat islands and cover it for our readers.","I\'ve got an interesting lead over the last two days. It says that there\'s a great power sealed within Mahjong Soul Shrine that could make any wishes come true. I\'ll go see it myself before I write a story about it. Why don\'t you come along?","It\'s a journalist\'s duty to turn facts into words and let the world know about them. But who\'s to say for sure that what journalists see is absolute truth?","I just found a survey showing that as many as 80% of correspondents agree that truth is in the hands of the few. Well, the human mind works in mysterious ways!","Journalism is both true and cruel: While it protects one group of people, it can also hurt another group at the same time…","I\'ve got some headline news from a live report. It says the genius Go player, who stayed on top of the world\'s global Go player rankings for 40 months consecutively, has just won the World Mahjong Championship. Now THAT\'S what geniuses do! Maybe you can do that, too, like staying on a losing streak for 40 months… Just kidding. If that makes you upset, I\'ll have to think of something special to make it up to you.","The future is always there, even if you don\'t think about it. But it\'s a good thing to have some expectations. This way, I won\'t get lonely or bored even if you are not around!","I\'m a little surprised you\'d give me a gift. Thank you.","Looks like we\'ve been keeping an eye on each other. Now you\'ve discovered my little secret!","Things that I care about… Work, probably. No, now perhaps you\'re one of them. Well, as a popular Jyanshi with a reputation in Ichiban City, you are a walking news machine~","You are not like others in Ichiban City. Sometimes you even make me think that you don\'t belong here… I\'d like to know what the secret that lies within you is.","Wanna know more about me? After all this time, it\'d be unrealistic for me to pretend I can\'t read your facial expressions. Hehe.","I used to think that I regret nothing. But now, all of a sudden, I\'ve begun to regret… that we\'d only met recently...","Yes, to what\'s in your mind right now… because I also look forward to it.","Never seen me like this before? True, I haven\'t relaxed myself like this for a long time. You truly are incredible. That\'s what I thought when we first met and I still do now! So, Mr. Incredible, I look forward to your company from now on.","{name}, Happy New Year! Let\'s stay up till the morning! The festival traditions should be well observed as they are not only that our ancestors passed down to us, but they also represent our hope for a better life.","Happy New Year, {name}! As the editor-in-chief of a magazine, it is my job to remember every commercialized festival. Of course, if you wish, I can also remember every day that is related to you!","Tenpai! Everything\'s under control.","No-ten! Um… That\'s bad","Feels like some big story slipping away…","Not a mistake. Didn\'t need it.","Time is running out.","Not bad!","I\'m satisfied.","Hi everyone. Nice vibe in here!","Alright, everyone. Take your seats. Let\'s begin.","Double Riichi","Kita Dora","Hello, my name is Saki... Saki Miyanaga. I\'m a first-year student of Kiyosumi High School and a member of the Mahjong club. I like reading... And now I like Mahjong too. Nice to meet you.","Let\'s have fun together.","Playing Mahjong with you sure is happy!","That\'s a win...","Thanks, everyone. Phew... you are all so good! It was really tough to stay in first place.","Hello, um... Excuse me, but could you also take me to the Shrine today? I\'ve been there a few times already, but I just can\'t remember the directions...","What\'s my goal for today? Hmm... First, to keep my points positive. Then I just want to enjoy Mahjong as much as I can, because playing Mahjong really makes me happy.","Whoa, sorry, I didn\'t mean to bump into you... Hmm? Wait, did we just meet not long ago?","Ouch! I-I\'m okay... I fall easily even when I\'m walking... Probably because of my poor athleticism...","Ichihime and Miki get along so well. They are like sisters. I even feel slightly envious... Hmm? You think they are more like mother and daughter? Um... Ahaha...","Ouch... Sorry. The table over there makes me a little concerned.","I don\'t quite understand this luck thing... Sometimes, the tile I want just comes to me...","My favorite Yaku... is probably \"After a Kan\"... But \"Four Concealed Triplets\" also means a lot to me. It was the beginning of everything...","Nodoka... She is not just an important friend to me. She\'s more special than that.","Ah... When I stay with you, I can have peace of mind like when I\'m with Nodoka. Just looking at the clouds almost makes me fall asleep... Zzzz...","Oops? Thanks, but why... Did I do anything that\'s worth the gift...?","What a great gift. Can I really have it? Wow, I feel so lucky today. Thank you.","Somehow, I feel like we can be great friends.","Wait, who just walked past...? N-nothing, don\'t worry about me. I just felt like I saw my sister...","Thanks for coming to the bookshop with me today. I haven\'t read properly for a long time... How about going to the Shrine to enjoy the sunlight while reading? Sounds good, but I think I\'ll probably fall asleep.","When did I start to like Mahjong? That\'s a long story... Um, no, there\'s nothing confidential about it. If you don\'t mind, we can have some tea and I\'ll tell you.","If Mahjong Soul Shrine can make my wish come true, dear God, I hope to...","I feel like my heart has bloomed like the flowers on the range.","Happy New Year. What\'s my plan...? I don\'t really have any. How about we ask Nodoka out and go to Mahjong Soul Shrine together?","Here\'s your Valentine\'s Day gift. Nodoka and Someya-senpai taught me how to make it.","After a Kan","Lots of Dora","Quadruple Yakuman","Quintuple Yakuman","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai.","No-ten.","Four-wind Discarded Draw.","Four-kan… Abortive Draw.","Four-Player Riichi. Everyone is getting serious now.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors.","Four Quads","Pure Four Quads","It keeps coming...","It\'s a Dora, but...","It\'s almost a draw.","This is quite a big hand.","Hmm... I like this hand...","Excuse me. Sorry, I got a little lost on the way here...","I\'m feeling a little nervous... Um, is it okay if I take off my socks?","Kita Dora","The name\'s Nodoka Haramura. I\'m a first-year student of Kiyosumi High School and a member of the Mahjong club. Nice to meet you. I heard Saki was here too. Is she in a game at the moment?","Let\'s have a good game.","If one can thoroughly study probability and theories, and implement the statistical play style in actual games, his or her win rate will increase without doubt after enough games.","Feeling good. Hope I can keep the momentum going.","My focus is perfect right now.","Hello, I\'m just about to go to the Shrine to practice. Would you like to come together?","No, I\'m not here for Saki today. Could you be my practice partner if you don\'t mind?","Why did Saki and I become friends? She is good... and... Incredible...","I don\'t believe in supernatural powers. Luck is a part of the Mahjong game and it will always fluctuate, but luck isn\'t everything.","I feel like I\'ve seen a kid as lively as Yuuki. Is she... also into tacos?","The game just now reminded me of my friends. I miss them. Hope they are doing alright...","Is there a way to eliminate the pressure of playing Mahjong face-to-face...? Um... Etopen really helped me a lot.","The people at Mahjong Soul Shrine are really lucky - that\'s how I feel when I play with them. But it\'s just a short-term illusion produced by random distribution after all.","Do you want to get strong? The only way is to study, think and practice. Also, pay attention to details and do not make mistakes. And don\'t let the so-called luck interfere with your own judgment.","Saki said you found Etopen for me, is that so? Thank you, I really can\'t imagine life without him.","Thanks, but I don\'t quite understand why you would give me this gift.","How do you know that I like this? Did you hear it from Saki? Thank you, I will take good care of it.","Recently, your Mahjong performance has improved. You must be using the statistical play style.","Etopen is like my good luck amulet. Amulets can help people calm down, so there\'s nothing supernatural about them.","I\'m fine, I was just too focused. Thanks for worrying about me.","The game just now was a real pity. In the short term, even if you make all the right decisions, the ending may not be what you like. Please don\'t worry. If you really cannot calm down, how about hugging my Etopen for a while? I have two different ones at home.","You are not as good as Saki, but still, I see you as a very respectable opponent.","I like Mahjong... And I want to become stronger... From now on, I will give everything I have.","Happy New Year. My New Year wish is... I hope Kiyosumi can perform well in the competition. And I hope me and Saki can... Um, nothing, don\'t worry. I wonder what Saki\'s wish is…","Sorry, I\'ve been too busy with Mahjong recently and didn\'t prepare anything. If you don\'t mind... I was having some chocolate bars with Saki... There\'s one more left. It\'s still chocolate, right.","Lots of Dora","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","Four-Player Riichi. It\'s a draw...","This tile keeps coming, but there\'s nothing strange about it.","When I have to play a Dora, I will play it. I\'m not Kuro.","Soon, this game will come to a draw.","I must keep calm in such a situation.","This is a big hand with high expected value.","Are you my practice partners today? Nice to meet you.","I\'m ready. Let\'s begin.","Koromo\'s here to play with you all! Oops... Ouch! I-I\'m no random kid! The name\'s Koromo! Don\'t get it wrong!","Let\'s get started!","Tonight is a full moon. My victory is inevitable!","The sun is rising!","The moon has risen.","Come on, let\'s go to Mahjong Soul Shrine! If we don\'t hurry up, others will be gone when we get there!","No one else is here today. It\'s just two of us then! Don\'t worry, Koromo will take it easy against an amateur like you.","Touka said Koromo could find a lot of friends to play together at Mahjong Soul Shrine. That\'s why I came here, but I didn\'t expect to meet so many incredible creatures.","Hajime and I went to Chiori\'s place! Somehow, I felt she and Riu didn\'t get along. But I had no idea why.","S-stop touching Koromo\'s head! I\'m not a kid... What, you thought I was cute so you wanted to pat my head? Nope, that\'s still a nuh-uh. No touching!","Koromo may look tiny, but Koromo is the eldest in our mahjong club! I\'m older than Touka. Maybe I\'m even older than you! So show me your respect!","Aren\'t you tired of losing to Koromo every single time? C\'mon, you need to get stronger. One-sided games aren\'t fun, you know?","A few days ago, Touka and I went to a restaurant and tried their new deep fried prawns with tartar sauce! It was super delicious! Hmm? Do you want it too? Let\'s go together next time then!","Koromo likes the night. I feel very relaxed when the whole world is engulfed in darkness and the moon slowly rises...","When Koromo was the only one winning, everyone was very upset and I couldn\'t enjoy myself either. But people here are different. They enjoy the game no matter they are winning or not. Koromo is very happy too!","Are you serious? Koromo is doubting your taste.","Wow! You\'ve got great taste. Koromo is very satisfied! Kudos to your great effort!","Do you think I\'m a child loved by the tiles? But that is useless. I wish I can be loved by the people.","You\'ve lost to Koromo so many times, why are you still hanging around with me? Don\'t you think Koromo is terrifying? ...What, not at all? Fine, I didn\'t ask you anything! Forget everything you just heard!","The moon is beautiful, isn\'t it... What? Um, maybe some famous novelist said it before, but who knows if it\'s true! I had no other meanings when I said it! Don\'t get me wrong! I\'m just trying to find an excuse... Oops?","My parents are both busy working. I seldom see them. But that\'s okay, Koromo\'s not a kid anymore... I know work is important... Besides, Koromo has so many friends now. I don\'t feel lonely anymore.","Touka, everyone at Ryuumonbuchi High School, Saki, Nonoka, my Nagano friends, Ichihime... as well as you. I have more and more friends now! Koromo feels very happy!","Hoho! Koromo is feeling powerful like never before! Even if it\'s not at night, I still feel great!","Happy New Year! Hurry, let\'s go to Mahjong Soul Shrine. I\'m sure there will be many people today. It\'s got to be more lively and fun than usual!","What\'s the difference between Valentine\'s Day chocolate and regular chocolate? Is this a gift for special ceremonial occasions? Okay! I\'ll make tartar sauce chocolate then. Getting right on it!","Under the Sea","Lots of Dora","Four-Player Riichi... is it? Hoho...","It\'s the same tile again. I don\'t want it.","I don\'t need it!","It\'s high water time.","Behold, this will be the end!","I am inevitable. No one can stop me!","*yawn* Sorry I overslept... You didn\'t start without Koromo, did you?","Hmph, hmph... Are we starting?","The name\'s Teru Miyanaga. I\'m a third-year student of Shiraitodai High School. Nice to meet you.","I look forward to the match.","As always.","...So it begins.","Good. Just keep up the momentum until the final victory.","...Hello.","Is there... anything you want to do today? It doesn\'t have to be Mahjong.","I really crave Unozawa-senpai\'s pancake. It\'s so delicious. Too bad that she\'s gone to a professional team in Saitama…","If there is a mirror... that can reflect the deepest inner self of a person, what would you do?","Everyone said they heard the creaking sound of doors when they played in Mahjong Soul Shrine... We should suggest Miki to give the place a good renovation to avoid any accidents.","Mahjong is an intellectual sport... And there is no doubt about the importance of sugar... So desserts are absolutely necessary... probably.","Aihara... She\'s actually very good. It will be great if she can be more confident, a little more encouragement won\'t harm.","Have you... met my sister? How is... Um, nothing... She\'s getting along with her friends, isn\'t she? (Mumbling) Good to know...","How do I look... Still very exaggerated? I just can\'t get it... Ok, one more time. Hope my smile can be more natural.","On the Mahjong table, no matter how unfortunate you are, good luck will come eventually. I wish life can be the same.","Thanks.","Oh, it\'s a snack... Thank you, I like it.","What happened between me and my sister? ...Sorry, I don\'t want to talk about it.","Did Sumire tell you I like snacks? She just talks too much... Um, I didn\'t say no. I mean, you already brought them...","Being a coach isn\'t funny. Even when I\'m not playing, I can\'t help but observe the habits of others. It\'s like an occupational habit.","I bought too much. Would you like to have some? Curious to know my past...? Alright then. There\'s nothing worth hiding anyway.","Will the sun shine on the blooming flowers on the range one day?","Somehow, I feel like I have the courage to meet her face to face now.","Happy New Year. It\'s this time again, huh... It does remind me of my past a little bit. But before I could realize, that little girl who used to cry a lot has become stronger and stronger.","This is the chocolate for Valentine\'s Day. Sumire said this was the etiquette... Is it good? I haven\'t tasted it yet.","Tenpai.","No-ten. That\'s fine.","Four-wind Discarded Draw.","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","Four-Player Riichi.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors.","The same tile...","Given the situation... I don\'t need this.","I can almost predict the ending.","I really want to win this.","Quite a lot of points here.","Sorry I\'m late, I got a little lost... Hmm? Are we still waiting on someone?","Ready.","Riichi","Double Riichi!?","Chi","Kita","Ron! What luck!","Tsumo! Great luck!","I knew it\'s a newbie by your sheer violence when pushing the door... Aha, you surprisingly look lucky! I\'m Fu Ji, owner of Luck and Fortune. Since you\'re at my place, you shall abide by our rules. For example, you should be more gentle when opening the doors as they are way more valuable than you.","Only those blessed by fortune can play at my table, and I see a lot of good fortune in this room today.","In Luck and Fortune, we never lose money.","Haha! The sound of coins jingling... music to my ears.","Gold and silver, gems and jewels, fill my pockets, that\'s the rules!","In Luck and Fortune, there\'s no such thing as \"on the cuff\", but we do accept pledges. Let me check if you have anything worth pledging.","Maintaining relationships is costly. A businesswoman like me wouldn\'t do such things!","No one walks away after breaking the rules here!","Where is Magical Dream? Hmm, this fella has spent a lot here today. Alright, I\'ll just tell you the direction for free! Walk out from Luck and Fortune, walk straight like \"crack—\", and then turn left like \"pfff—\", and go upward all the way like \"poof—\" and boom, you\'ve reached your destination. It\'s pretty near, go.","Here\'s a heads-up for you, you\'ll get into big trouble for judging people by their appearances! Don\'t cry and accuse me of bullying you by then.","I only make friends with rich people, and I don\'t care about their identities. As long as you\'re rich enough, Luck and Fortune can even sell you luck like \"rustle\"!","Another festival? I kind of witnessed One Han City growing... Hmm? Age? Hehe, my fan doesn\'t mind giving you a wallop like \"clap\"—as the answer, removing your future curiosity in this question. How does that sound?","You do look cute when you lower your head while sorting your tiles. Suddenly, I\'m interested in playing more mahjong with you. Perhaps my heart will skip a beat like what usually happens in the comics.","It looks like the newcomers of One Han City are not very aware of the rules here. How dare they wreak havoc in my territory like \"quack\"! You... are not like them, right? You will be good and listen to me, right?","After some deep thoughts, I\'ve realized that there\'s no difference between being an idol and a god! You know, they bring people hope like \"rhaaa\", and they let people fancy them like \"chua, chua\", and finally make people spend tons of money supporting them like \"splash\", for if they lose, they lose their face as well as popularity... Wait, is this the reason some idols are called goddesses? Aha, how unexpected. They have already realized this.","These are the things for pledging? I\'ll get my employees to estimate their value for you later.","Since you\'re so sincere, I guess it might be inappropriate for me to be perfunctory. Let\'s proceed with mahjong. I\'ll show you how I live up to my name.","Like my fan? If you can lift it, it is yours. After all, I\'m not a cheapskate. However, if you take my fan and I need to use it, I will take you in exchange. What say you?","Don\'t be deceived by how kind he looks. In the past, no one dared to mess with Wanjirou, not even I... However, I\'m pretty curious about what you\'ve done to make Wanjirou your guarantor?","Legends still circulate because they were once true, including the gods, the Mahjong Soul Shrine, as well as the legendary mahjong tournament. After all, the rumored Four Greats are still active like \"zap\" in One Han City!","Everyone has a past. After all, my heart is not made of rock... Ah, perhaps it is... Doesn\'t matter. As the unchangeable fact is that I am Fu Ji, owner of Luck and Fortune. And I will not allow anyone to change that. Remember this like \"klunk\", will you?","Aha, I haven\'t realized that we\'ve become so close. Impressive, young one! If that\'s the case, let me tell you a secret that can only be known by the close. There are 7 mystery dojos in One Han City, and Luck and Fortune is one of them. About the rest, I\'ll tell you about them when we get closer, hehe!","Causes and results can\'t exist without each other. People\'s wishes of luck gather in Luck and Fortune like \"rustle\", and by doing so, they have obtained fortune like \"rustle\". You are here also because of this karma. Since you\'ve found your way here in Luck and Fortune, it means that we\'re destined to meet each other. Cherish this karma, and my fortune will fill the rest of your life like \"bang\".","My name says it all, I\'m good at New Year toasts. It\'s just that I don\'t easily do toasts, as my wishes will all come true... However, it seems that you\'ve reached the specified amount of spending in Luck and Fortune this year, so I give my blessing to you like \"ding-dong\". May fortune, luck, and long life be with you in the new year. And you\'re welcome to come to Luck and Fortune every day in the new year!","This is a festival that I cannot afford to miss. What kind of promotion do you think we should bring out today? One of a couple gets free entry? That sounds so old like \"whoa\". You know, this place always keeps up to date. Free chocolate upon purchase is even more boring... Ah, how about you dress up as a maid? I heard that youngsters nowadays would fall for this. Don\'t worry, you\'ll get paid handsomely. What say you?","Tenpai, fortune comes today.","No-ten, misfortune already came yesterday.","Hmm... a tile of misfortune.","Aha, how dare fortune slip from my hands!","Relax, it\'s not final yet!","More, more, and more. Cha-ching is the best music!","Aha! I want to act as if I don\'t care, but I can\'t. This is just huge!","Long time no see, everyone! I\'ve done some fortune-telling before I came, and it said today is a good day for some mahjong!","It\'s high noon, guys! Let\'s not keep fortune waiting, shall we?","Kita","Ron! Destiny fulfilled!","Tsumo! A hand of wonder!","Qi Xi is my name. Hey! Let me make this clear, I am busy, so don\'t ask me anything except romantic relationships.","Age is just a number. Bring it on!","Hmph! I\'ve seen everything, about your romance!","Haha! That\'s me!","Hmph! I wasn\'t even using ten percent of my real power.","Oh! It\'s you. I\'m about to head to work. If you have anything to ask, ask now.","Today\'s I\'ll also strive to matchmake least 10 couples. Ready? Let\'s go!","Love is like an exam, you\'ll get better the more you read and prepare. That\'s why I\'ve bought all you humans\' best-selling love guides. Risk free!","The old woman said that I\'m not allowed to return home if I do not manage to matchmake 999 couples! That\'s too much trouble! Why on earth are modern people losing interest in love...Darn!","Are humans\' heads filled with cauliflowers instead of brains? Why are they asking such simple questions like how to confess love? Don\'t you know that 99 Tricks of Confessing is one of the top 3 best-seller human love guides? Why don\'t they just read that book? Don\'t tell me I have to read it aloud to them.","I\'m am not like Haruna or Momo. They are just young punks, but I am the God of Love.. Although I am forced by the old woman...","You come to a kid every day to play mahjong? Don\'t you feel ashamed? Tsk...","L, Love, S, Shot...Stop laughing! The rabbit stay next door told me, a god needs an ultimate skill to look dashing. Hmph, how do I even look dashing with these cheesy love words...Darn!","Here, hold my hand. Need to be comforted by a kid? Useless. I feel embarrassed for you...It\'s just a loss in a mahjong game. Next time, I will bring you with me and send them home with a 10-win streak!","Ahh! Don\'t you dare to touch my hair! ...No, stop, or else I can\'t grow any taller! I\'m warning you, I bite when I get mad. And...and I wallop, too!","That old woman always says that one will never seek another just for nothing. Do you want me to teach you something about romance?","You fool! A momiji manjuu cannot be substituted with just any dessert! However...since this is from you, and the taste is not that bad...that, that\'ll do...","Shut up! Don\'t you dare to compare Cupid to me. That naked little kid is just hideous!","Of course, my hair should be included in my height since it\'s a part of me. Any objections?!","Such a useless cat patrol team. I was looking out for them, yet they still failed their mission...Darn, I\'m getting scolded in the office because of them. Stop laughing, or else I\'ll tell the teacher that you were involved, too.","Ah...ah...Ahh! Have mercy, master. I\'m going to have a concussion. Mas...Ah, it\'s just a bad dream. I thought that old woman has arrived at Ichiban City. Ha...remember, stay away from that old woman, or else she\'ll smash your head with her peach wood sword. Got it?!","That old woman and humans are foolish to believe in the existence of the God of Love. I mean, relationships made with sorcery couldn\'t be solid, tsk...in my opinion, people should pursue their love actively if they have feelings for one another...Ah...Don\'t let your imagination run wild. I...I was talking nonsense, I...I do not have feelings for anyone.","Darn...I wish that I can grow up faster...Let\'s make an agreement. As you can see, I am indeed a powerful god. If you pray sincerely, even though you\'ll have become old and full of wrinkles like that old woman in a few decades, you\'ll still be blessed by me.","One, two, three, four, five...Oh? Today is indeed New Year, as I\'ve been overwhelmed with love wishes. Hey! What is your wish? Why don\'t you talk to me about it? Although I don\'t care about matters other than love, I am still capable of making your little new year wish come true. However, let\'s make this clear: if you want to talk about wishes that need be achieved with sorcery, forget about it. This sort of stuff is not reliable as it might disappear anytime. Be realistic!","My name says it all. I refuse to participate in this kind of little punks\' western festivals, hmph! It\'s not too late for you to change your mind!","Tenpai, the destiny of romance, settle!","No-ten, tsk...I\'ll succeed next time.","Hmm...Love might come to an loose end due to people missing each other...","Tsk...Miscalculated.","Relax, I\'m here. This is nothing!","This is so much easier than thinking of a way to matchmake a couple!","Since everything is settled, then...Luck, please come to me!","Once you\'re in this room, you\'re my friend! Here, a welcome gift for you. It\'s a limited-edition red string of fate from the God of Love, friends only!","That old woman always said you must do your best when tying fates, and the same goes for mahjong. So I won\'t show any mercy!","Riichi.","Double Riichi.","Chii.","Pon.","Kan.","Kita.","Ron.","Tsumo.","Ah, you are the one mentioned by others in the shrine? Nice to meet you, I am Yumeko Jabami. Look, this might sound weird, but are you interested in a quick game right now?","It has started!","Oops, first place, hehe...","Oops, I won.","Hehe... a big win!","Hello, are you also new to the shrine? If you don\'t mind, our game needs one more person. Wanna join us?","Ah, nice timing. Suzui just gave me some snacks made by his family\'s company. How about we have some fun while eating?","Why am I being cold to Ikishima? Because I simply don\'t like her. I wish to enjoy the process rather than settled results.","Failure does bring disappointment. But... The fear of failure and the happiness of success are both thrilling and ecstatic. I can\'t miss either of them.","Definite success and definite failure are both boring. Take mahjong as an example, if you get Blessing of Heaven every round, although you\'ll keep winning, you won\'t really have fun, right?","An easy way to decide... How about flipping a coin? Don\'t know why, but I kind of like it.","People at the shrine enjoy the game no matter they win or lose. Ah... That\'s right. To indulge, to enjoy, and slowly get it freak on.","You looked happy back there! Yeah, that\'s right. Isn\'t gambling fun?","You finished handsomely with the winning play. Defense is certainly important, but the key to success is the courage to bet on everything.","Cheating isn\'t a foul. In my opinion, that\'s just a way to succeed. To be honest, I don\'t hate cheaters. After all... Isn\'t the determination to pursue success fantastic?","Ah, thanks for your effort.","Is today some special day? Didn\'t expect such a wonderful gift. Thank you. I will cherish it.","I\'m going to visit my sister in the hospital. Lately, a lot of interesting things have happened at school and the shrine, and I want to share all of that with her.","To stop gambling... Is a hard thing to imagine. For me, not being able to have that kind of fun is more frightening than death.","Oops, it\'s already dark? Time flies when having fun. Before we go, let\'s play another round.","Mary, Suzui, President, and everyone I met in the shrine... There are so many interesting people and fun games in this world... I am excited just from imagining it!","Just as I expected, you understand the fun of gambling. If it\'s with you... We can certainly have a joyful game without worrying about anything!","Come, let\'s continue to play more, more, and more... Until eventually, let\'s... Get our gambling freak on!","Happy New Year. Just went to the shrine to draw a stick. I played a game there and heard Ichihime say that the new year\'s first game represents the luck of the whole year. Looks like I\'m going to be lucky this year!","Thank you for caring about me. I made this by my own. Please take it. I also prepared gifts for Ichihime and others, but can Mr. Wanjirou... Eat chocolate?","Robbing a Kan","After a Kan","Under the Sea","Under the River","East","South","West","North","Red","White","Green","Double East","Double South","Double West","Double North","All Simples","Pure Double Sequence","Pinfu","Half Outside Hand","Pure Straight","Mixed Triple Sequence","Triple Triplets","Three Quads","All Triplets","Three Concealed Triplets","Little Three Dragons","All Terminals and Honors","Seven Pairs","Fully Outside Hand","Half Flush","Twice Pure Double Sequence","Full Flush","Riichi","Double Riichi","Tsumo","Ippatsu","Dora","Dora 2","Dora 3","Dora 4","Dora 5","Dora 6","Dora 7","Dora 8","Dora 9","Dora 10","Dora 11","Dora 12","Lots of Dora","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Big Three Dragons","Four Concealed Triplets","Single-wait Four Concealed Triplets","All Honors","All Green","All Terminals","Thirteen Orphans","Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans","Four Big Winds","Four Little Winds","Four Quads","Nine Gates","True Nine Gates","Mangan at Draw","Counted Yakuman","Mangan","Haneman","Baiman","Sanbaiman","Yakuman","Double Yakuman","Triple Yakuman","Quadruple Yakuman","Quintuple Yakuman","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai","No-ten","Four-wind Discarded Draw.","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","Four-Player Riichi","Nine Different Terminals and Honors.","Dealing into Win after Kan","Root","Terminals in All Sets","Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Pure Triplets","2/5/8 Triplets","Seven Pairs with One Duplicate","Pure Seven Pairs","All Terminals","Pure Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Pure Seven Pairs with One Duplicate","Four Quads","Pure Four Quads","Oh, same tile again.","Hmm... Such a pity, but it\'s useless to keep it.","Is this it...","Phew phew... Hahaha... This is... Nice...","Oops, not even expecting this...","Excuse me. Let\'s get started as soon as we have a full table.","Ready when you are.","Ron!","Tsumo!","Mary Saotome. You are my partner? Hmm (sizing up)... You don\'t look very reliable, kind like someone I know. Well, nice to meet you anyway.","Nice to meet you.","Ha, not surprising at all.","I\'ll take that one!","I can feel it... Victory is mine!","Oh, you are here. Then let\'s go... Where, you say? Mahjong, of course. What else do I need you for.","Mahjong? Not today, I need to relax once a while. After all, I\'m not like someone, who is obsessed with gambling all the time.","Ew, a cat... I don\'t really hate them. It\'s just that they remind me of some unpleasant experiences.","What\'s with that play? Couldn\'t you think any harder?","Ha? I\'m caring? Stop joking, I\'m too busy for that. I just want to stop a rookie from being noisy.","Stay alert, especially to those who smile at you on the table.","Carefully observe even the smallest detail. Rules are just basics, knowing your opponents is the key.","I heard that you came to me because I\'m a good student? Well, I don\'t mind. Compared to mahjong, schoolwork is much easier. No matter it\'s about schoolwork or mahjong, we need to keep learning.","You\'ve made some progress. But, since you have been following me for so long, it\'s only natural that you are slightly better than other rookies!","Friends? If this was in the past, I probably couldn\'t care less since they just block my way to success. But now... Maybe they don\'t sound so bad.","Oh, thanks.","Hmm... I must gift you in return. What would you like? Remember to choose something cheap!","I dislike the weak. Or, I dislike the way they give in to their weakness. You... Aren\'t one of them, are you?","Winning or losing is personal. Even if you cooperate with others, once you start to rely on someone, that\'s no different than losing.","I don\'t know why you are so credulous. People like you struggle hard in competition... Can\'t stop worrying about you (whisper).","... Alright, if you insist, let\'s try your so-called cooperation. But once we are on the mahjong table, I can\'t guarantee anything since it\'s going to be unpredictable.","Only people who have never been to the bottom will smile like you. I\'m not one of them... But, thanks to someone, now I can smile by enjoying gambling without worries.","My only goal is to dominate, so I don\'t yield to anyone. That\'s why I will always be above you... Even hearing what I said, you still look unmoved? Well, that\'s who you are, and that\'s why I said things like that to you.","Yo, happy New Year. Want to go somewhere? Just got my allowance. I would spend it with you rather than to flatter those rich girls.","Of course I know its Valentine\'s Day today, but why should I give you chocolate? Are we in a relationship? Stop dreaming... You should be happy for receiving obligation chocolate from me. Here, take it.","No-ten","Tsk, why does this one keep coming.","It\'s a pity, but it is a burden if it can\'t be used.","Anyone got Tenpai...","Great! Luck is on my side. Victory awaits!","Oh? Nice.","You are my opponents in this game? I don\'t see any challenge.","I\'m ready now.","Ron.","Tsumo.","Midari Ikishima, President of the Beautification Council at Hyakkaou Private Academy... Tsk, such a dull face. Can this guy really bring me any fun?","...It\'s starting.","It\'s over. Just like your life.","Look. I won.","Looks like it\'s over for you, hehehe...","You\'re here... Looking boring as always. Let\'s go, don\'t make me bored.","Today\'s work at the Beautification Council is as always. Let\'s do something fun... Ha? Hey hey, you are still hesitating over joining the Council?","Ah... Yumeko is the best... Tsk, don\'t eavesdrop when I\'m talking to myself! I\'ll kill you!","What\'s the matter? Didn\'t you said you want to improve your reflexes? The \"hand·knife·trick\" is a good way to do it. Don\'t worry, it\'s my hand anyway, just go for it. Ah, yes, let\'s bet something, let me think...","Ah? Don\'t pay attention to people who claim to want death. They are just all talk. What I\'m looking for is the real deal!","Just discard that tile. The worst thing that can happen is only getting busted. Isn\'t it better to just face the defeat?","Where does this come from? For your own sake, mind your own business. But... If you dare to face the consequence, I don\'t mind telling you... Do you want to know?","I didn\'t expect you to be troubled by such a tiny problem... See? Just use this formula. Problem solved. Hmm? What\'s with that look? What, you think a fool can be a member of the Student Council?","Look, it\'s already empty. But every time I feel pleasure, it still brings pain. That pain reminds me to enjoy the pleasure. The more pleasure, the more pain, the more pleasure, the more pain... Hehehe, hehehe, hahaha—!","Be it an early Riichi or a Triple Calling, attacking more or less means no turning back. Gambling with no possible retreat... Do you want to walk away from such pleasure? You... Are not that kind of person, right?","It\'s pointless to make me happy with such boring stuff.","Whoa... You learn fast.","Hmm... Slightly better than I thought?","Oh? You\'ve got a spine. I\'m starting to like you.","You can still put on a smile in that kind of situation. Not bad. It\'s good that you know how to enjoy.","Ah, don\'t mind. Habakiri gives everybody that stern look, including me. What? You feel hostility? Must be your imagination.","Although I love Yumeko better, you excite me just like she does... Don\'t let me down. Good... Good! Hahaha—!","Hey, you want to join the Beautification Council? No, you won\'t decline, because we are of the same kind. So, let\'s seek our pleasure... And let\'s enjoy it together.","Yo! I finally escaped from the boring family party. Let\'s go elsewhere and have some fun. You need to bring me some good fun since I tried so hard to escape. Ah, yes. Happy New Year.","What\'s in it? Today\'s Valentine\'s Day, so of course it\'s chocolate. Never mind if you don\'t want it... Oh, you took it! Wait! Don\'t open until you arrive home. And don\'t return it to me because that is humiliating. You\'ll know what\'s in it after you get home, hehe...","Tenpai","A boring tile.","Here, take it if you want.","Boring until the end? Or...","It\'s here. It\'s here!","Oh... Getting interesting.","I\'m here. So, who\'s going to be my plaything today? Or... will it be all of you?","We can start now.","Kirari Momobami, Student Council President at Hyakkaou Private Academy. Are you \"the one\" they mentioned before? Hehe... Nice to meet you.","It\'s lovely to meet you.","I had fun. Thanks.","Excuse me for that.","It seems this is the end.","Hello. I have nothing important to do today, so I was wandering around, and before I knew it, I\'m here at the shrine. Want to go in together?","If you\'ve got some good ideas, why don\'t you decide what to do today? Don\'t be nervous. I\'m looking forward to it, hehe...","The reason why I created the school\'s system? I just wanted to build a \"water tank\". My personal \"aquarium\"... Hmm? You want to know what the \"water tank\" is? I thought you wanted to know about the system. Hehe... You are interesting.","The school is a miniature society. The \"law of the jungle\" our students experience are just a drill for their future, or maybe... Slightly more cruel than their future.","My most trusted person? If you are asking about the person I need the most, that\'s going to be Sayaka. That kid is more important than she thinks. We... Need each other.","I heard that you are getting along well with Ikishima, hehe... You made a nice choice. She\'s a good kid, after all, she has beautiful eyes, and so do you...","The previous trip was joyful. The country indeed has rich culture, and the mahjong rules there are really interesting. I heard that the rules vary from area to area. Those rules must be interesting as well.","Yumeko and I both enjoy gambling. As for our relationship... You can guess.","Ever considered joining Hyakkaou Private Academy? You... Are the type that can survive in my \"aquarium\", hehe...","The key to winning streaks?... There is no such thing. Losing all the way even if you have tried your best is what gambling is. If there has to be an answer, I would say that those who hold the fate of victory win, something like that.","Thanks. What\'s in it does not matter. It\'s the thought that counts.","... Sorry about that. I like it very much, thank you. Can you please tell me? How did you know what I like?","Come closer, I won\'t bite. You have something to say to me, don\'t you?","You\'ve been less shy recently, and you don\'t get easily distracted anymore. Good changes.","Ririka looks scary. Hehe... How about this, you go and try to remove her mask?","Hehe... You did not let me down...","Hey, how about a game? Don\'t panic, just killing some time. But from your face, I don\'t think you want to avoid it, hehe...","Maybe you are not aware, but you are far more greedy than you think. Can you tell me more about the desire in your eyes right now? What do you want? Money? Power? Or... Me?","Happy New Year. Do I look like a \"Western Japanese doll\" in kimono? Hehe... Thank you for your compliment. I have a family meeting to attend to. Please excuse me.","Take it. Don\'t worry about anything. Happy Valentine\'s Day, hehe...","Not really a bad thing.","No influence on victory.","This is going to end soon.","Naturally.","Hehe... This is getting interesting.","Excuse me. I\'m just a guest today, so there\'s no need to be so formal.","Well then. I\'m ready to begin.","Riichi.","Chii.","Pon.","Kan.","Kita.","Ron.","Umu... Tsumo","Welcome, look what we\'ve got here, a new customer. I’m Reina Nanami. Would you like a cup of coffee today?","I\'m going to do my best.","It\'s my honor to play a game of Mahjong with you.","Just got lucky.","Never expected to win this big!","Hello, coming for our coffee today as well? I knew it was you when the wind chimes by the doorway rang.","Ah! What warm weather. One should not stay at home on such a good day! Put your shoes on, and let’s head to the park!","Would you like to try Geisha coffee today? It’s one of the most demanded in our shop. Blended with a fruity aroma and sweet milky fragrance, it is a perfect choice for an afternoon drink!","Mahjong...is it fun? I hear a lot about it from other shop assistants. Doesn\'t sound easy.","It really makes Reina envious to see the birds that are flying freely. When can Reina be like them?","Thanks to my dad, I became good at determining the quality of coffee beans since I was little. It is such a pity that...I will never have the chance to learn more about coffee from him anymore...","You are such a gentle person that Reina often talk to you a lot without realizing it. Please let Reina know if you are tired of it.","Umu... Another rainy day. It\'s been raining lately... I don\'t despise rainy days though, it\'s just that I\'m worried such a rainy day... Deters you from visiting me.","My uncle has always wanted to keep a pet in the coffee shop, yet he still couldn’t make a decision on what pet to get. What do you think about rabbits? The fluffy little creature will surely become the shop\'s most popular \"superstar waiter\".","Umu, it has been a long time since Reina visited a theme park, but Reina will try not to be a burden! If... If we are in a haunted house, Reina will try to protect you... Reina is not scared of anything, for real, because ghosts only exist in books, not...not in real life!","Umu... A gift for Reina? Slightly surprising, but thank you anyway.","Wow... Reina has been waiting for this for so long. How did you know that? Yes, I\'m so happy!","Since Reina knows more about you already, are we best friends now?","My legs? Um... According to the doctor, there is no physical damage. Reina is just unable to walk... But, you don\'t need to feel sympathy for Reina, because Reina can just move around freely with this wheelchair... Thanks for caring about Reina.","Ever since you taught me Mahjong, Reina has been practicing hard. Reina won\'t lose to you this time.","Look at those dazzling stars. I wonder if dad and mom are looking at me from there?","Eh? You want to know more about Reina? Since it’s you, I can tell you anything.","It\'s all because of your company that I can get over my mental block and manage to stand up again. I may still be full of flaws, I will try to live up to your expectations as always.","Happy New Year! Reina has made loads of wishes. I wish that in the new year I could learn more about coffee and travel to coffee-planting countries, and that my new PE teacher will be gentle...Umu, do I sound greedy? But I become greedy when I\'m with you, hehe!","These are some chocolates that Reina has made with other shop assistants. Reina has made a range of them as Reina was not too sure about your preferences. Wanna try some?","Tenpai! Hehe!","No-ten... What a bummer...","Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Pure Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Umu... I shouldn’t have played this one.","Ah! Dora...","Umu, the clock is ticking.","Reina\'s recent luck is as good as Arabica coffee!","Wow... If I can win this, I\'ll get tons of points. Keep it together, Reina!","My apologies for the wait, everyone.","It looks like the game is about to begin.","Kita.","Ron.","Tsumo.","Thank you for taking me in. In return, I will keep you safe during my mission... My name doesn\'t matter. I will judge if I need to show up, myself.","Mission start. No deviation.","Mission complete. All objectives achieved.","Target defenses breached.","Target base secured.","As promised, I will protect you from behind the scenes. So you won\'t see me, and you don\'t need to call me. I\'ll only show up when necessary.","As for today\'s schedule: the plan was canceled, so I can closely protect you for the next 24 hours.","Hands off me... Don\'t make me say that twice.","Don\'t approach me from behind. Next time it\'s probably going to be more than just a shoulder throw.","I won\'t laugh no matter how hard you tickle me... Stop it with these childish antics.","I\'m not good at chatting... If you have to, go find someone else.","Keeping Menzenchin without Riichi is the safest strategy. Quietly lurk around the target and wait for your chance.","Guns are not toys... Nor are you.","Complex emotions do nothing but hold me back... Critical decisions like this are never made easily.","You are the most troublesome person I\'ve ever met... Don\'t be like that next time.","I don\'t need anything other than the bare necessities.","Your safety is the best gift.","You are just my employer. No need to act like we are friends.","My protection won\'t change because of your gender, so my gender shouldn\'t matter to you, either.","Try thinking with your head. That can keep you away from most of the danger... Protecting you is not easy.","Do I believe in god...? Are you asking about my outward beliefs or what\'s in my heart?","You... Never mind. You got me.","How long would you like to extend my employment contract?","So the sound of fireworks reminds you of festivals... Do you like gunshots? The UTS-15 shotgun is loud and smoky, just like those fireworks you like.","This is just another ordinary day, since we are always together. No need to be happy about it... However, I\'ve placed a gift at your bedside to thank you.","Tenpai. Bull\'s eye. Good aim.","No-ten. Missed the target. Recalculating trajectory.","It\'s meaningless to feel sorry.","Anxiety affects your decision-making when adjusting strategies.","Don\'t worry. I\'m with you.","Hopefully, this is what you want.","As expected, with greater opportunities comes greater greed...","Don\'t mind me.","Ready.","Ron. Congrats, hehehe...","Tsumo,winning is a personal thing!","Yo, newbie, welcome to Hibiki\'s battlefield… No, Hibiki\'s channel. The rules are located on the lower-left corner. The most important thing is to remember to donate.","Sigh, they wouldn\'t have to lose if they just stayed away from the table. Why do these noobs never get it?","Winning is the only thing pursued by the best gamers, let alone the fact that Hibiki is the best of the best.","Not surprising at all. It\'s nothing!","Alright, guys, you know the drill! Let\'s see some hype in the chat for the great Hibiki\'s victory!","Another punctual thumb-up from you. Aren\'t you a determined person, or should I say, unoccupied?","Hey! Where have you been recently? Don\'t tell me you\'ve been following those inferior streamers who only know how to act cute? You\'re Hibiki\'s viewer, and you are not allowed to follow them!","Ah, such a boring round. Who should I knock out from this game?... I\'ll just pair my tiles into a Yakuman and knock out all of them.","What do you mean by putting up a cute mask the first time you came in? Of course not. It\'s called marketing, not deceiving!","...&*...&...&...*, hmm… Chill, chill. You guys did not hear anything or see anything, no recording of any form is allowed, or else death awaits, understand?","Surprisingly open-minded… Ha, how dare you tease me of my size? Death sentence to you! Give me your ID, and I shall educate you about cruelty!","Hey, hey! Hibiki is trying so hard. Shouldn\'t you donate? Donate, please… Donation confirmed. Okay, thanks, have a sit in front of the screen.","Why do I pretend to be clapped? Hehe, listen up! Just as my viewers think I am getting clapped, yet nothing happens. And suddenly, the tide turns, and they become the ones who get clapped! It\'s always fun to see them full of anticipation and end up in despair, hahaha!","... Ah, we\'re already in the new era, yet why are there people who think the bigger, the better? Instead of focusing on something that gets saggy sooner or later, why don\'t these people focus on some hardcore content? It\'s just a matter of size... I can just modify the model to have things like that!","Ah! Told ya not to play that tile! I\'ve told you a million times that you have to pay extra attention when it comes to this kind of situation!Tsk… Brace up! Remember that I personally taught you!","Thanks for the donation. I hereby award you a seat!","Wow, what\'s with the generosity?! Crazy, absolutely crazy! It may only last 1 second, but in that 1 second you\'re my God! All hail my God!","Oh yeah? Supporting me as timely as going to work? Thanks for your effort. How about dropping your job and be Hibiki\'s pet instead? Not bad at all.","Wow, another huge donation! Do you have a life?","You really paid for all the items in my online shopping cart… Perhaps, I should a little special service to repay your kindness?","Hey...The other day, I saw you donating in that woman\'s live stream. Never had I expected that you acquired such a horrible taste to support such an inferior person… Huh? Learning some gaming skills? Why didn\'t you just come to me?!","Ha? You dare to challenge me? Challenge accepted! Whoever loses will be shamed. If you win, Hibiki will agree to any of your requests! Come on! Let\'s rumble!","Hmm… Is… Is this enough? I\'ve put it on just as you asked… What?! What\'s with that request? You… Fine, Hibiki lost, so Hibiki will do anything you want!","Happy… New… Year… The New Year version of Hibiki debuts the stage with a bang. MyNew Year wish is… Death sentence to the one who said \"may you grow insize\"!","This… This is a true-feeling chocolate Hibiki specially prepared just for you… Since I\'ve said that, does it taste better? Hehehe… Even if itwas not a true-feeling chocolate, you would still accept it with gratitude,right?","No-ten... Tsk, damn!","Useless things should get out of the way. Learn to discard to win.","Hibiki… Hibiki\'s dora...","Guess we are having a draw.","Remember this hand. This shall be your last memory before I knock you out!","Hmph! Have a good look at the lady who is blessed by the Goddess of Victory!","Yo! Break a leg. Just don\'t get knocked out by me.","Whenever you\'re ready!","Kita.","Ron!","Tsumo!","The name\'s Ryan. I\'m a magician of Soul. Can I call you \"onee-sama\" from now on? Gender, age, identity... Those are all grown-up things. I don\'t care about any of that. I like you just the way you are, onee-sama!","If I win, will you come to my magic show next time?","Did you see how I did back there, onee-sama?","The technique onee-sama taught me really works like magic!","I suppose I didn\'t let onee-sama down, right?","Onee-sama! Onee-sama! Hmm, if I call you a few more times, will we become closer?","What have you been doing all this time without me, onee-sama? I have been waiting for you here.","Rabbits? Cute animals like rabbits have always been magicians\' favorite props. Not only are they easy to hide, but they also please the audience. That\'s why I really like them. How about you, onee-sama?","Mahjong? That\'s Sara\'s favorite game! If you also like it, onee-sama, I don\'t mind learning it, too. I can learn anything for you, onee-sama. But don\'t teach me anything naughty, onee-sama. I am still just a kid, after all.","Someone in the group says that onee-sama will dislike me if I keep bugging you... Well, if I can\'t bug you, can I just watch you on the side? I promise I\'ll be good...","Will you come to tonight\'s show, onee-sama? This is the program... Ah, those crossed-out shows? They\'ll still perform, but they are none of onee-sama\'s concerns. I don\'t want other performers to steal my limelight in front of my special guest.","What kind of flowers do you like, onee-sama? Don\'t underestimate me. I\'m the top magician of Soul, after all. I can conjure any kind of flowers if you\'d like. But if I can choose one for you, onee-sama... How about a trumpet vine? This kind of flower can do something like... this! It will tightly wrap around people, hehe...","Onee-sama, your eyes... They\'re so pretty. I bet you look really cute when you cry and have a tinge of red around the corners of those beauties.","Onee-sama, can you call my name a few more times? Ryan... Ryan... Ryan... Something like this? I love it when you call my name. It\'s like I\'m the only apple of your eye, hehe.","Do you ever think about someone else when you\'re with me, onee-sama? If you do, I must not be treating you well enough. If that\'s the case... (Kiss) Am I the only one on your mind now, onee-sama?","If onee-sama likes it, I like it too!","I\'ll truly treasure your present, onee-sama, just like how I treasure you, hehe.","Will onee-sama teach me how to play mahjong today? I just can\'t grasp the requirements behind achieving certain Yakus. So can you follow me to the dojo after teaching me mahjong?","No matter what mistake I make, onee-sama\'ll still forgive me, right? Because isn\'t it grown-ups\' responsibility to forgive kids? Besides, I\'ve been good to onee-sama, hehe.","The pigeon that I used for my performance is dead. Its body has already become stiff... Are you afraid, onee-sama? Relax, I won\'t allow anything like this happen to you. There\'s nothing I cherish more than you, hehe.","Onee-sama, why are you always playing with other people? I can do everything they can, and perhaps even better. Would you like to try, onee-sama? Hehe...","The other members of the group? They\'re not important. Can onee-sama not mention them when it\'s just the two of us together? Those who stand between me and onee-sama, and their smirking faces... So annoying... I thought... Onee-sama\'s only here to watch my show, right? Onee-sama?","Can you accompany me to sleep tonight? Because when I\'m alone at night, I always feel like there\'s something scary below my bed, in the cupboard, and outside the window. But I\'ll feel safer with you around! Besides, I don\'t want onee-sama to leave my sight, hehe.","Happy New Year! New Year definitely feels more complete with onee-sama by my side. Instead of getting a red envelope, I prefer to have onee-sama fulfill my new year\'s wish. I hope that in this new year, I will have onee-sama\'s undivided attention!","It\'s the time of the year to gift chocolate again. You can smell the sweet scent of candies in the air. But... (Sniffing) I think you smell even sweeter, onee-sama, hehe. Onee-sama, I\'m not like those grown-ups who only treat you well on Valentine\'s Day. As long as you like it, I\'ll always treat you like gold.","Tenpai, will the next tile be what I wish for?","No-ten, such naughty tiles!","Things that can\'t bring victory to onee-sama are useless.","Hmm? I can\'t play this tile?","I\'m kinda nervous. Can I hold onee-sama\'s hands?","If onee-sama likes it, I will do everything I can to achieve victory!","If I win, will onee-sama reward me with something I want?","I\'m here with onee-sama for some mahjong practice again. Happy to see everyone.","I\'m ready to show onee-sama the results of my recent training now!","The name is... Ayako Morikawa. Do not stare at my left arm, for Mastema is sealed inside... Otherwise, misfortune will fall upon you...","If my left arm loses control mid-game, run... I am so sorry...","Did misfortune... Befall on someone else today?","I\'m so sorry... but I won...","Mastema... is probably still asleep...","It\'s best that... You stay away from me... I don\'t know what to do... If I bring you misfortune...","Rumor has it that singing is often heard in the old school building\'s biology classroom... Would you like to... Check it out with me?","I don\'t have any human friends in school, so I often go to the old school building during lunch break. I have... Lots of nice friends over there.","What\'s this in my arms...? This is my best friend, Hanako. Whatever troubles I have, I just have to say \"please, Hanako\" and she will help me out... I will ask Hanako to help you too, because... You are the only human who\'s willing to be my friend.","My favorite movies...? I love \"Saw\", \"Ju-On: The Grudge\", \"The Conjuring\" and \"Silent Hill\"... Oh, I also just re-watched \"Final Destination\" recently... Facing the imminent, inevitable pressure of death in a dark room alone is just fantastic.","I have been trying a new method of mediumship recently. If you ask yourself in the mirror \"who are you\" three times every day for a month, you will be able to talk to the other you... Do you want to try together? It will be fun if we can succeed...","Mastema... Has a bad temper... Someone once touched my left arm... And had been dealing into other players\' hands for a month... I felt very sorry...","I don\'t like school... But if you like it, I will try to come to school... Because... I want to stay with you...","Ever since I met you, I have made... More friends. The black-haired is Sadako, the silver-haired is Reiko... It\'s really great to be with you all.","This potion can boost my luck. If I drink it before exams, I will definitely pass... For sure...","Hanako says she likes it... And asks me to thank you...","Hehe... I almost can\'t contain my happiness of receiving this gift. Can\'t wait to go home and laugh under my quilt...","Sorry... I-I didn\'t mean to stare at you. It is just that, the one behind you is very unique... Could I talk to it... If you don\'t mind?","Do you also like supernatural topics? Everybody around me seems to hate it... I-if you like them, could we talk more often?","Occasionally, I amcalled a \"witch\"... Hehe, I\'m actually very happy about that. Although... I don\'t think my power is strong enough to become a witch yet.","I came to Mahjong Soul Shrine\'s Mahjong competition to lift the seal on my left arm... But if I do that, Mastema would leave me. Then I will lose another friend who I can talk with...","After preparing the summoning circle for 49 days... I have finally succeeded... I have sealed the demons summoned onto this charm. P-please take it... It will help me to protect you, hehe...","If one day... We have to part ways... I wish I can become your spirit guide, so I can always be around to protect you, hehe...","Happy New Year... Mastema doesn\'t like the festive atmosphere, but I still feel like saying this to you in person... Perhaps, while Mastema isn\'t paying attention, we could... See the New Year fireworks again?","V-Valentine\'s Day... Isn\'t a festival that witches are supposed to celebrate. But... I\'m not a witch yet, so it should be fine... What are we going to do today? Haunted house or escape room? I can\'t wait... Hehe...","Tenpai. It seems that fate has already been foreseen.","No-ten. The bandage on my left arm seems to be loose...","Four-wind Discarded Draw.","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","Four-Player Riichi...?","Nine Different Terminals and Honors.","I didn\'t mean to... Use my left hand...","This is... Going to be bad...","Is this the warning of the imminent darkness...","This red potion can boost my luck... (*Gulp*)","Hanako, I\'m counting on you.","Hello, everyone... I didn\'t mean to intrude. If it\'s alright... may I join?","That seat... Asmodeus was just sitting there...","Ron, I\'m sorry.","Tsumo, nice shot!","Natsuhiko Takigawa. Left-footed, good at penalty kicks. My goal is to become a professional soccer player. I\'m currently single... Eh? I can skip that? Haha, then I have nothing more to share. As you can see, I\'m just your average high school student.","Should I start with something like, \"it\'s not whether you win or lose\"? Anyway, let\'s just bring that undefeated high school league energy, haha!","I bring my best game when I\'m going solo!!","Mmm-hmm, having the home-field advantage really makes a difference, doesn\'t it?","Yeah! I\'m in the zone! Let\'s go for a hat trick today!","Yo, you\'re here! Have you eaten anything? You gotta prioritize your health.","If there\'s nothing to do, how about some exercise? Hmm... Let me think, where should we start...?","Obviously, you can\'t see how tough my muscle is through my clothes. But I\'m pretty strong, alright. I could run 800 meters with you on my back without breaking a sweat. Wanna give it a shot?","Usumi and Ren don\'t get along? Haha, don\'t listen to rumors like that. Those two have been like this since they met each other in middle school. Not to mention that for guys, the best friendship is when you\'re both buddies and rivals.","I\'m not so good at avoiding 4th place like Usumi, nor am I good at fast attacks like Ren. So I lose hard whenever I play mahjong with them, haha. Can the four of us play together? Don\'t worry, I\'m here to take the last place.","*Glug glug glug* Aaah! Nothing beats a bottle of cold water after breaking a sweat. But please keep this from my coach, or my next exercise will be a written self-criticism of at least 2,000 words.","Ahem... Do you think it\'s a little hot in here? I\'m sweating up a storm... Would you mind if I took off my shirt? Ah, you should, too. Yours is all wet.","I\'m well-versed on the topic of love, because besides soccer, it\'s pretty much all my teammates talk about. By the way, I voted for you in the \"most desirable partner\" vote last time. Because whoever gets lucky enough to be your partner must be the happiest person on earth, haha!","Will you come to watch the game tomorrow? Ah, never mind, just forget about it... Not sure why, but I feel nervous just thinking about you watching it.","You\'re so cute. I say it all the time, but that\'s because it\'s the truth, haha... Ah, don\'t blush. You-... You\'re making me feel like I said something weird...","Thank you for bringing me this. I appreciate that.","Is this for me? Haha! Should I post this to my team\'s group chat to make the guys jealous?","My hobby? Does collecting soccer cleats count? A lot of the guys on my team do that, though. After all, a nice pair of cleats can really step up your game. I spend most of my allowance on them.","Usumi and I were sort of childhood friends. For as long as I can remember, he\'s been as stubborn as he is now, even when he was a little kid. Once he puts his mind to do something, he won\'t ever give up. Ren wants him to quit the dessert club, hmm...? I think that\'d be harder than scoring a goal from the halfway line, haha.","My wrist? I sprained it in training just now, hiss- It hurts a bit, but don\'t worry, it won\'t affect tomorrow\'s game. But... I\'m probably gonna need your help with applying the medicine, since I only have one good hand, okay?","When I won the match yesterday, the first thing that came to mind was not to celebrate, but to call you and tell you about it. But... I was kind of embarrassed, so I ended up not doing that.","When that girl confessed her feelings to me just now, what I thought was: \"She\'s not you.\" Come to think of it, it\'s probably because I have a crush on you. Ah... Just saying it like that is kind of embarrassing... But I\'m glad I\'m able to tell you.","Natsuhiko Takigawa, 183 cm tall, the second son in the family. A well-behaving young man with no bad habits. I sometimes read some adult books with my teammates, though. My type is someone like you. If you happen to be looking for a relationship, give me a chance!","Happy New Year! Ah, just ignore these guys behind me. When I told them I was going to meet up with you today, they insisted on following me no matter what. Dang, I intended to spend the night alone with you... If you don\'t want them around, just let me know, and I\'ll shoo them off.","When I was training earlier, I heard them talking about Valentine\'s Day. The minute I realized that it was today, I was already rushing over to you. Probably because I hoped to spend Valentine\'s Day with you. Yeah, that\'s gotta be it. After my practice with the team, let\'s go do something you like. Anything.","Tenpai. Phew! That was close.","No-ten. The long pass went south. Tough opponent.","Four-wind Discarded Draw.","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","It would be nice if I kept scoring.","Take it easy. Kicking the ball out of the court is one of the tactics.","Oh, there\'s not much time left. With a good strategy, we can still win the match.","I don\'t care if it\'s Tsumo or Ron! Just let me win already!","I suddenly feel super nervous. Not sure if it\'s because of Tenpai or because I don\'t want to let you down.","It\'s not often we all get together like this. Let\'s go all out!","Warm-up\'s done. Ready to take the field.","Kita.","Ron.","Tsumo.","Shigeru Akagi, just call me Akagi.","…Kekeke.","Grand victory comes with great risks.","What\'s with that expression? This is only the warm-up.","Not there yet...! Not until I\'ve gazed into the bottom of the abyss... Again!","...Oh, when did you come?","Kekeke... Don\'t mind me. I\'m just expecting something interesting to happen since you are here.","A devil\'s child? Keke... What\'s that? Who told you that? Yasuoka?","Some people think they are meant to be the winner, so they just sit around and wait for others to fall into their traps... Such a mindless way of thinking.","When on a losing streak, some people don\'t have the courage to put on a final stand. They fear failure and just wait for their own destruction to come. I don\'t mind giving people like that a hand...","When in the end-game, most people focus on the tiles instead of their opponents, ignoring what they really should pay attention to.","Why didn\'t I remind him? Well, if he can\'t read a simple hint like that, I\'m not the one who takes the blame.","People reveal their true color when in danger. Understanding this fact is the key to victory.","This tile... And this one... There is nothing special about them. I\'m just listening to my gut. If you wish to survive the competition, trust your instincts.","The money I had? I spent it all in less than 3 days. And that\'s why I work here, kekeke...","Thanks, I appreciate it.","Thank you. How do you know what I like? I don\'t think I have told anyone about it.","Calculating odds are important, but you\'ll need more than that to win.","Those without the faith to gamble it all will be slowly consumed by fear. Such a weak will won\'t help them shake off misfortune and achieve victory.","Sometimes, you meet opponents that are like an impregnable vault, tough beyond comprehension. And no so-called common knowledge can crack it, so you must find special ways to \"get in\". Like... Use \"coincidences\" to your advantage.","If you stay near me, you might get hurt by sparks. Are you fine with that?","I don\'t care about winning or losing... No matter which one takes place, someone will always be destroyed meaninglessly in the end. That\'s all I want. In the truth of competition lies an abyss full of meaningless endings, and I just want to get close to it.","Rationality is a rule of \"your world\". It doesn\'t apply to me... I want to devote myself to irrational competitions. If you are okay with it, then welcome to \"my world\".","Happy New Year. My plan? Nothing special. Maybe I\'ll find a mahjong parlor and spend my day there.","Valentine\'s Day... I\'ve heard of it, but I don\'t know much about it. It\'s related to chocolate, no?","Tenpai","No-ten","Four-wind Discarded Draw.","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors.","Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Pure Single Wait after 4 Triplets","Ah... That\'s where my concealed triplet lies...","I can hear... the three different sounds of discarding...","Not... Not done yet...","The God\'s will chose me.","Interesting... This madness makes it interesting...","Is everyone here?","Let\'s start, then.","Kita.","Ron...! Ron...! Ron...!","Kakakaka! Tsumo!","Hmm? A new-comer? Why are you not wearing a uniform? No sunglasses, either... Don\'t young people nowadays have any manners?","Tremble before me! Mortals!","The goddess of victory will not smile on those who only know how to run away.","Easy! Too easy!","The gods have chosen me! I am... the only king!","Where are you, my servant? Come and serve your master.","Kakaka! You are doing a better job lately. That\'s my servant.","Foresight. I beat those stupid politicians, bankers, and fake prophets, becoming the one to rule them all with my exceptional foresight.","Kaka, well it\'s not that big of a deal. With all the contributions I\'ve made, it\'s only natural for them to kneel before me!","Only mundane people worry about money. I can get that kind of stuff hands down. Because I\'m the king!","No matter how good their disguises are, everyone takes them off when they are doomed. Even the strong ones are weak under their masks, and I just love seeing their desperation.","No calculation is useful without luck. My extraordinary luck is beyond their reach.","Wait. Sometimes you just need to wait, even when you have a winning hand, especially when facing fearless and unpredictable opponents. Only patience can help you catch up and end them!","Stay with me...! The divine...! The devils...! Keep... Keep blessing me!","The timing is important. To find out where, when, and how to win, and to seize the \"chance to victory\", you need to fully concentrate!","Hmph... You think you can make me happy with this?","Oh... Kakaka! Seems like you more or less understand my taste now! Although it\'s of little worth, I\'ll take it!","Dislike them? No, I don\'t dislike them, I dislike seeing them! Even a great person like me has to worry about getting old, but those trash-like mortals have more time left than me...! I won\'t allow this...! Never!","I have no interest in going to heaven. I\'d rather go to hell to have more freedom!","They won\'t understand...! Those inferior beings would only get caught up by mundane things, and could never reach enlightenment! They are mere nearsighted mortals who are trapped in darkness!","Even though a fearless man can ignore \"failures\" and carry on, he is unable to let go of the \"gains\" in his hands... And that is how sweet \"gains\" are.","When humans were made, God carved something into their hearts... It\'s the fear of death. And He made them think this fear is natural... Only in this way would humans kneel before him.","This? This feeling... Speed, and power. This... This is the strength I had when I was young! It\'s back! My prime is back!","Here, a red envelope... Don\'t overreact. As my servant, it is only natural for you to take this money.","I have no interest in mortal festivals. Not to mention that I have to send gifts. So boring! ...Go tell the chef to prepare a feast today. Don\'t ask why, just pass it on!","Four-kan Abortive Draw.","Four-Player Riichi! Hmph! Quite bold of you all.","Stupid! How did I make the same mistake... over and over again!","That is unnecessary for my victory!","Kakaka... A king\'s \"privilege\" is to never feel worried.","Tremble and awe before me, the one who stands on the top, the incarnation of the God, Iwao Washizu!","See? This is the luck of a king! Your skills and talents stand no chance against it!","Feel blessed, you mortals! What immense privilege you have, to stand before a true titan like me!","You won\'t want to bore me.","Kita.","Tsumo!","Nice to meet you. I\'m one of the master instructors of Nishiba-ryu - Kazuha Saionji. Starting today, I will be teaching you the art of Kendo. Please bear with me.","I have never been afraid of paying the price for anything. That also holds true at the mahjong table.","Please don\'t all stare at me...","The path to mastery has no end.","Anyone can reach this level. It is merely a matter of diligent training.","Here you are, let us proceed with today\'s training... Mind your distance. This far will suffice.","Such pleasant weather today. Let\'s train in the courtyard... Getting more sun is good for your health, you know.","Today\'s warm-up shall be a 10 miles jog... Let\'s get running. Don\'t you dare to stop, that\'s a disgrace to a samurai!","I hate crowded places... It\'s not that I hate being around people, but being receiving public attention is really embarrassing. However, as a samurai, I must overcome this fear... I think.","Favorite food? Vanilla ice cream, I guess... Although I never tried them before. To maintain my body shape, I just can\'t eat such overly sweet food... But it smells delicious, isn\'t it?","Don\'t tell me you\'re here for the Mahjong Soul Shrine too? I don\'t know how hard it is to achieve your dreams, but I can be both your teacher in Kendo and Mahjong at the same time to make your dreams come true.","Thirst... Thirst trap?! How embarrassing! As the successor of Nishiba-ryu, such a grotesque thing is intolerable.","Geez, stop addressing me as the \"sword saint\"... Same goes for the word master! It makes me sound so old. Just address me by my name, please.","I\'ve never thought that rock paper scissors can be so tricky... Perhaps my father was right? Simple things may be the trickiest to master, and I have yet to win in such a game.","Dogs are samurais\' most loyal companions, yet I wonder why they are reluctant to get close to me... On the other hand, the wild kittens in my courtyard seem to like me a lot. Such a perplexing turn of events.","That\'s your favorite stuff? Thank you, I shall remember this.","That\'s the first time someone guessed my preference correctly. I\'m kinda embarrassed, but you made my day.","I don\'t like performing Kendo demonstrations in public, which is why I only took you as my disciple. Next up, I\'ll do my very best to train you, so ready yourself.","Nishiba-ryu emphasizes agility, accuracy, and ruthlessness. If you start to hesitate, your moves will be sluggish and clumsy, and you will falter to your opponent\'s knees.","This is the sword my father left behind - Shigen, it means being grateful. Each time I see its crimson blade, I will tell myself to be more diligent to not let him down... I wonder if he is proud of me now?","I\'m not really good at handling people like you, who often come with surprises... But I am still much looking forward to your next move. Am I... Being weird?","After my parents passed away, I never really trusted anyone anymore. Until... You appeared. Can I trust you with all my heart in future days?","Just so you know, Kendo is the epitome of my existence, but you... You are irreplaceable.","Happy new year! As your master, I think I should convey my expectations to you in this new year. It\'s just that... I think you wouldn\'t like such a serious atmosphere... All in all, happy new year, my sword and I shall be your protector.","Let\'s not go to the dojo today as there were traces of unknown chocolates in front of the entrance, and people nearby are acting suspiciously. But rest assured, I\'ve sent my butler to investigate the motive behind this, and I shall stay here to protect you.","Tenpai, and that\'s the strategy I\'m good at.","No-ten, it seems like I could still use some training.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors.","Yes... It takes one erroneous thought to be in a plight...","Stay calm, stay focused.","The path hasn\'t come to an end.","My tireless training has borne its fruit.","Diligence and luck, they come as a bundle!","...Kazuha Saionji. Here I come.","Hm... Welcome. There is an open seat over there.","… Sorry, I didn\'t notice you. Nanaha Onodera, pleased to meet you.","Pleased to meet you.","Thanks for going easy on me. Do you wish to continue? If not, let me know when it\'s game time. Goodbye.","Yes... That is a pleasant outcome.","Brilliant, indeed... A big hand? My apologies, I thought you were talking about the book... By the way, what kind of hand was it?","Welcome… Hmm? Any particular book you are going after? If not, feel free to look around...","...Don\'t mind me, please go on with your reading. Yup… yup, seems attractive. Perhaps I can try a new relationship...","Platonic love… Forgive me, I don\'t agree with that. I can\'t feel the affirmation with only spiritual connections. In terms of love, it must be a mixture of both mental and physical love.","The sound of playing mahjong is like rhythmic music to my ears, so it does not disturb reading… What do you mean playing Mahjong will be distractive while reading? Didn\'t I just mention that? Playing mahjong does not disturb reading...","… I\'m not angry. It\'s just that there are too many customers, so I\'m kind of annoyed as I cannot focus on my reading.","Here, the I-novel I mentioned before. Too bad that this novel is only made up of tasteless words. Real-life experience is really a must...","After finishing reading a good book, I feel satisfied yet empty… What if I can\'t find any more good books? Hmm? Cherish the moment? Hehe...perhaps that optimism is not bad.","I thought that my dreams couldn\'t possibly be achieved, but it seems that the situation has changed. If you can show different aspects of yourself as I wish...","I don\'t mind calculating points myself, but it\'d be better done by a trustworthy person like you. Please.","What\'s the matter? Don\'t worry, if you feel awkward, there\'s no need to force yourself to continue reading. I am already satisfied that you are willing to learn about my favorite things... Hmm? You prefer me to recite for you? Hehe... sure thing. I believe... you will love these books as well.","Thanks… I was once fond of these things. But for things other than reading, my enthusiasm doesn\'t last long.","Are… Are you sure that I can have this? Such a fine book. How should I even repay your kindness… You want to hear me read it out for you? Yup, sure thing.","You want me to recommend a new book to you… You have already finished the books I recommended to you earlier? Good concentration.","Wow… Never expected that you would want to buy this book. You surely have a distinctive taste.","While we are very similar in taste, it\'s regretful that you are not quite my type...","Maybe… you are a decent choice. You may be ordinary, but being ordinary is still interesting in a special way.","Mind visiting my place when you are free? I have a favor to ask of you...","What\'s the use of these things? Think about this: don\'t proper clothes and settings make you more comfortable while listening to my recitation? Have you already decided which book to listen to... Hmm? Your face...Hehe, what\'s with the rush? We have plenty of time to be together from now on...","Happy New Year. But I am going to spend my time reading as usual.","Here\'s a little gift for you as a token of gratitude for your care. Looks like made by a pro? Thanks for the compliment. I was once interested in making desserts and learned a little from the books. Hopefully you\'ll like it.","Tenpai.","Ten… I misjudged. No-ten.","… Hmm? Seems like I\'ve played this same tile over and over.","Don\'t worry. I know what I\'ve played.","It\'s about time for the next round...","Yaku… almost spilled the beans.","Oh, not bad at all.","Hello, everyone. I\'ll read while waiting...","Don\'t mind me. Please start anytime.","Greetings! I\'m Sammir, and I\'ll be staying in One Han City for a while. Would you be my guide during my stay? I\'d like to hear more stories about this city and write them into my lyrics so that I can take them to a place far, far away.","May your journey today be filled with joy.","I may not look strong, but I\'m actually very good at taking the offensive!","How lovely. Everyone here is as gentle as a breeze.","I wish to share this happiness with you.","Howdy? It\'s a pleasure to see you.","(Cheerful humming) Ah, you weren\'t supposed to hear that yet... Well, I\'m trying to write a verse about how we met. It\'s just that I\'m having a tough time trying to find the perfect rhythm to express that pleasant feeling. Perhaps a chat with you will inspire me.","Hmph? There\'s dirt on my clothes? My apologies. I was so absorbed in my expeditions that I couldn\'t be bothered by that. I promise I\'ll pay more attention to my appearance next time we meet.","If you\'re bored, why don\'t you play some Mahjong with me? We\'re short two players, but it should be more fun to get immersed in a game with someone you know really well, like me.","Stop staring at me like that. You\'re making me blush.","I\'m not a typical bard? Haha, isn\'t that a good thing... Huh? Become an idol singer? Well... I think the grand stage is better suited for a prince, not me. But you saying that has made my day. Thank you.","Over my years of traveling, I\'ve crossed paths with all sorts of people, but I\'ve never met someone as sincere as you. Being with you sets my mind at peace.","It seems that in every place I\'ve traveled, the people play Mahjong. Although different places play by different rules, such differences bring their own kind of fun. Maybe people in One Han City will start playing more variations of Mahjong one day.","I\'ve heard all kinds of stories: some happy, some tragic, some unbearably dark. If it\'s okay, I\'d only like to share the happy ones with you. Someone as radiant as you shouldn\'t be shrouded by the world\'s darkness.","One Han City is so free. It embraces all kinds of cultures, so everyone can find a place of their own. If only I\'d known about this place much earlier...","Thank you for your lovely gift.","This is the most meaningful gift I\'ve ever received on my journey.","In many countries, I\'m known as the \"Troubadour\", but I\'d prefer it if you call me Sammir.","Every country has its own specialty, and I\'d like to show you some the next time I come to One Han City. This way, you can feel the world without ever leaving the city. Mhm... I suppose this is the mission of a bard.","The things that I hate? Hmm... The church, perhaps…? Haha, just kidding. It\'s just that I prefer to believe in something when I can feel its wholesomeness from the bottom of my heart to being indoctrinated with dogma.","I want to bring the never-ending snow from the north to the scorching hot islands in the south. I want to express the beauty of eastern poetry in a western revelry. A messenger? Haha... You flatter me. If that\'s what I am, I hope that wherever I go, I\'ll leave behind a delightful anecdote.","Where did I start my journey...? I don\'t remember anymore. Perhaps it\'s the hometown of a hero, which explains my love for stories of heroes and convictions. Perhaps it\'s just a little town nearby, which is why I feel at home whenever I sniff flowers. But now I wish that all of my journeys lead back here.","I\'ve decided to stay by your side until you grow tired of me. When that happens, I\'ll embark on a new journey... Because my journey feels more joyous with you in it. It\'s a journey my heart yearns for far more than a journey alone.","I\'ve always been a sucker for local festivals during my journey. You can watch people at the grand ceremony wearing traditional clothing and having the time of their lives... Moments like this give me hope for the future. How about you? Do you happen to have any wonderful future plans right now?","Did you say Valentine\'s Day? I see... People nowadays celebrate today for their loved ones. But I want to respect your wishes, so today can be any holiday you like.","Tenpai. Will the next stop be my destination?","No-ten. It looks like there\'s art in Tenpai, too.","The melody might get boring if you only use one note.","As is often the case during a journey, a missed scene is usually never seen again.","Don\'t worry. My years of traveling have made me an expert at dealing with tricky situations like this.","I\'m grateful to my fellow brethren who taught me these handy techniques during my journey. Here goes nothing.","If I get a winning hand, it\'ll call for a song to commemorate it.","Hello everyone. Even if it\'s not all about winning, I\'m still going to play my best. Otherwise, we\'d be spoiling a good game of mahjong, wouldn\'t we?","All set. We may begin whenever you\'re ready.","Oh my... Ron.","Oopsies! Tsumo.","Hello there, I wonder if you have by any chance stumbled upon a sharp-sighted, charming guy... Huh, you know the president? I\'m Kaguya Shinomiya, vice president of the Shuchiin Academy Student Council. It\'s a pleasure to meet you.","It\'s a pleasure to meet you.","Ah, thinking of winning already? Hehe... So cute.","Ah, I won.","Looks like the winner is already decided.","Look who\'s here. What a coincidence? Strolling around at the eleventh hour? You better not be late. Me? No need to worry about me. I\'ll be around for a bit longer, but someone will pick me up soon... Hehe, speak of the devil, the president has arrived with his bike.","What a coincidence. Look who\'s here at the shrine for some action with Ichihime, too? Um... I-I\'m not here just to look for the president, and there\'s no need to remind me that he\'s here.","Hayasaka and I are not merely of master and maid. In fact, we grew up together like sisters. My home feels cold and distant, so she is far closer to me than my parents.","Moongazing... It\'s not that I dislike moongazing, but whenever there are astronomy-related events, somebody might start being a child and become extremely difficult to deal with... Ah, it\'s not like I refuse to accept his demeanor, but the serious look on the president\'s face when he\'s talking about astronomy... It gives me butterflies!","Secretary Fujiwara is among the few dear friends I have, and I really do appreciate our friendship. That said... she can be quite irritating sometimes, especially when she unknowingly shows off her \"assets\"... How can they be so big...? All the nutrients from what she eats must go there instead of to her brain...","If you get nervous when playing Mahjong, how about trying some self-soothing? Just like this. When you\'re free, try putting your hands on your face and treat it as an indication to calm down. After you get used to it, you\'ll be able to calm down with ease.","The president and I are having a fling? Huh, for me, he\'s just barely has passed the test. That being said, a romantic relationship between a peasant and me is merely baseless speculation, but if he\'s willing to bow before me and vow to give it all, I have no qualms about training him to become my equal... The president said the same thing? Heh, he\'s really trying hard to play cool, isn\'t he? Guys really have the best imaginations. Oh, president... How cute.","Hmm... Out of these ten questions, what makes you think that I was thinking of the president…? That\'s simply false! The answer is Pes, the pet dog of Secretary Fujiwara! I can\'t blame you, though; there are definitely some similarities between Pes and the president!","I\'m a huge fan of dogs. Cats are too cunning. They only play cute for their own benefit. Such manipulative creatures... Don\'t get me wrong. That doesn\'t mean that I have hard feelings toward Ichihime. I may hate cats, but I don\'t feel the same about cat ears. You see, cat ears just make everyone look really cute, especially... the president with cats ears. OMG, so cute...!","It goes without saying that the bigger the storage a phone has, the better. How else could we save precious memories? Look, Kei sent me this photo of the president... Ah, how awesome would it be if I had a sister like her?","...To be frank, are you looking to win my favor by gifting me this off the cuff?","Thank you, you got me a wonderful gift. No need to be nervous. Expensive gift or not, it\'s the thought that counts.","When facing people or occurrences that are getting out of hand, there are times you don\'t want to think about it and just pray with peace of mind, just like this... Ah, breathe in. Ignorance is bliss...","Oh… A lack of common sense? That\'s a really rude way to describe me. I\'m not short of common sense, but I think some things are better off unknown.","Normal families aren\'t that bad. At least they live together and care about each other. I\'m a little jealous of them, or should I say... I\'m really jealous of them.","I have many things that I don\'t want others to see... Things that no one shall see. The closer we are, the more I should keep it a secret...","I once believed that no one in this world is good. Everyone is just putting on a facade for a certain motive, and everyone is calculating the risk before making their move. I never once thought that this was a false perception, as such vigilance has helped me survive... But I have never regarded those purely kind-hearted people as useless. Instead, I respect them. People like that deserve my care and trust.","Just like a damsel waiting for her prince at the top of a tower? Hehe, now that\'s an interesting opinion. But... I may be guilty as charged. I am longing for someone, someone gentle enough to tolerate my capricious temperament but who also shares the same passions as me... Wait, what?! Did you just say that the president is on his way here? Please, don\'t tell him what I\'ve just said to you!","Happy New Year! As you can see, I\'m getting ready to head home, and I guess I can\'t make it to the shrine. If you happen to meet the president and Kei, please send them my regards... I can meet them at the shrine just by praying despite being at home in Kyoto? Hehe, some advice you got there. If that\'s the case, thank you. There\'s no harm in trying to pray!","Oh my, judging by your expression… Do you think this is Giri or Honmei…? Hehe, you\'re so cute.","Tenpai. That goes without saying.","No-ten. A minor mistake, nothing more.","Four-Wind Discarded. Now that\'s what I call a decent strategy.","Four-Kan Abortion. My Dora\'s wasted...","Oh my, is that Four-Player Riichi?","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Let\'s not waste time on such a hand.","Hmm... That... That\'s just a little blunder.","What\'s not needed should be discarded. That\'s Shinomiya style.","If the president was in my shoes, I bet he\'d be struggling...","Hmph... As a Shinomiya, I refuse to get excited over such a meager thing. I must stay calm.","Heh, a hand that comes by no surprise.","I\'m assuming that everyone has taken their seats.","Whenever you\'re ready.","Riichi, here we go!","Hold up. Pon.","Hmm... Kan.","Hmm, Ron!","Tsumo, how do I fare?!","Hello, I\'m Miyuki Shirogane, president of the Shuchiin Academy Student Council. I saw you\'ve been looking around. Are you here to visit the school? Don\'t tell me you\'re... the new kid on the block?! If that\'s the case, allow me to be your escort. As a former late-comer myself, let me show you around.","Let\'s give it our all.","As president of the student council, failure is never an option.","Great, it\'s all going according to plan.","Hmm... Keep this up, and victory is already in the bag!","Morning. If you\'ll excuse me, I still have some more newspapers to deliver. Time waits for no one! I\'ll see you when I see you.","Much obliged. Thanks to you, I can make it on time. Let me treat you to some drinks. How about a hot cup of joe? Or maybe you have other drinks in mind?","Ah! Perfect timing. Here\'s a question for you, if 8*8=4，8*8=32, and 9*9=40, then what is 19*19? Sigh... Your answer is 0, too? Are you for real? What in the world is happening?! Please tell me there are answers other than Go!","I\'ve heard that I\'m being called the love master? Ha, hahaha... There\'s no denying it. After all, I\'m popular with the ladies, and no one has ever turned me down. That title couldn\'t be more apt!","I\'m just busy around the clock. Part-time jobs, student council, and recently I am also organizing an interschool Mahjong competition with Asaha High School\'s student council. I need to keep focused every second. That\'s why I couldn\'t live without coffee... Ou-out of stock?! Oh, Kisaragi, you bought some extra ones? Thank you, you lifesaver!","My dream? Well, don\'t laugh at me. I used to picture myself singing and playing the guitar onstage... How about we try it now? Ahahaha... Singing is not my forte, but if you insist, cough... I don\'t mind singing a couple of verses. Oh, I\'m actually pretty good at rapping. Listen to some of these bars!","Just like in other games, psychological games also play a prominent role in Mahjong. Once you know what\'s going on in your opponent\'s mind, you basically have the upper hand. All this time, Kaguya and I have been competing in almost every aspect of life. And those daily challenges are just the tip of the iceberg.","I\'m dating Kaguya? Ah, what nonsense. Just ignore them... It\'s... it\'s just that if Kaguya wants to date me, I wouldn\'t mind giving it a go... But what if she never confesses to me? N-no way... It\'s just a matter of time...","Money matters... Since I\'m from an impoverished family, I know how it feels to want something you can\'t have. Well, instead of squandering in ground zero, why not muster some energy and work! Just like I said, hard work gets everything done. If you\'re willing, I don\'t mind recommending you to some of my side gigs. Working part-time is never a bad thing. Not only will you feel a sense of achievement, but you\'ll broaden your horizons. Oh yeah, you know what? Ein just told me about some new gigs. I say we partake in those later!","My dad once told me that if someone you care for or your crush gets into trouble, a man should stand up and be a protector. And that would be me. I would like to be the man he spoke of who faces all hardships gallantly... Of course, that doesn\'t apply to the outcome of a battle! Am I right, Kei? Huh? Gross? \"It makes sense, but someone who\'s not a gentleman is just gross\"? Gee... You don\'t want to mess around with kids these days...","Thanks. What\'s the special occasion today?","Oh?! This... This is something I\'ve wanted for like forever... Geez, how could I repay you…?","Talent is indeed something many call foul. I know plenty of incredibly talented people that are envied by many, but that\'s nothing. The way I see it, hard work beats talent every time.","This heavy Aiguilette made from pure gold is a symbol of the responsibility I shoulder, but it is such responsibility that shapes me into someone\'s anchor.","My mother once said that love never stays the same. Is that really the truth? I want to believe that dad\'s persistence is definitely not a waste of time.","No doubt that it\'s hard to juggle between part-time jobs and student council work, but it\'s also rewarding at the same time. Besides, working a side gig actually broadens my horizons. And I can feel that I\'m thriving amid my striving. Believe me, one day I\'ll fulfill everyone\'s expectations of me by pulling it through.","Wit, talent, family upbringing... I\'m not on par with others on these things. Working hard is all I have. Hard work, keeping up the hard work... It\'s better to walk the walk than talk the talk. Even when it comes to stupid stuff, I believe that as long as one remains persistent, his effort will bear fruit.","I like watching the stars. I can\'t help but be awed by those beautiful shining things, but at the same time, they seem so alone. I hope that one day... I can reach out to the far-flung stars and get my hands on their priceless rays.","Happy New Year. I have plans with my friends to pray at the shrine. Want to join? About my New Year wishes... I\'ve had the same wish for 2 years, but my prayers are still unanswered. But I\'m still gonna pray for the same thing this year. This year... This year Kaguya will definitely...","Here\'s my return gift for the previous Valentine\'s Day. It\'s some bread baked with a rice cooker. I wonder how they taste? Some constructive criticism would help, as I\'m striving to enhance its taste... I wonder if Kaguya would like them, too? What do you think? Don\'t get me wrong. I\'m just thinking that if she says they\'re tasty, they\'ll be my \"breadwinner\", get it? Ahahahaha...","Tenpai. I have persevered till the end.","No-ten. How could I make such a mistake…?","Four-Wind Discarded. I\'m left with no choice. Just reopen it.","Four-Kan Abortion. We have a mountain to conquer.","Four-Player Riichi. I won\'t lose!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. It\'s best to play it safe.","Tsk, how embarrassing.","Ah! I want to hold it tight, but it is what it is!","Watch your moves...","Huh? Hmm... Winning with such a hand? As expected from someone as awesome as me!","Wonderful! Luck, don\'t fail me now!","Sorry to have kept you waiting.","All ready.","My apologies, Ron.","Ah, Tsumo.","Ai Hayasaka here, just a normal student of Shuchiin Academy. What do you mean my title is more ordinary than everyone else\'s? It would be weird to meet people with fancy titles everywhere, don\'t you think? It\'s OK to be normal. Anyway, it\'s nice to meet you.","Please go easy on me.","Come on, this is the perfect moment to unleash your inner beast... Yeah! Top!","Please excuse me for the win.","Oh yeah, luck is on my side today.","Good morning... Um, I\'m still kinda drowsy. You know, my lady was in a chatty mood, which caused me to work overtime. Did I feel troubled? Nah. The lovestruck her is way cuter than the old her.","Looks like I have some rare me time today, but I couldn\'t think of anything to do. Do you have any suggestions?","Someone nearby who looks like me? You must be talking about that girl, Hasaka. Well, I\'ve seen her before, and we kind of resemble each other. Speaking of which, rumor has it that encountering your doppelganger might get you into hot water. Oh no, maybe I inadvertently did something dangerous!","Don\'t worry about me. Whether it\'s my nails or the length of my dress, it\'s all abiding by the rules. And even if the disciplinary committee has a problem with my look, they haven\'t gotten anything on me so far, which means everything is all good. As for why I\'m doing this, just like Kirara said, a girl doesn\'t need a reason to be pretty. Besides, I thought guys would fall for this devilish side of me that exploits the loopholes in the rules.","People that I\'m not good at dealing with? Well, just \"Person F\". Gosh, the unmindful look on F\'s face. People like F who don\'t play by the rules are just hard to deal with. When you face an opponent like that, you\'ll feel tied down no matter what you do.","You said that you wanted to buy a new computer, right? I\'ve invited Hibiki to take a stroll at the electrical store. Maybe you\'d wanna tag along...? Since it\'s your own computer, it goes without saying that you should buy the components separately and assemble them yourself. That would be more fulfilling, am I right?","Speaking of that hospital... That place freaks me out. I once accompanied my lady there for treatment. Never in my wildest dreams had I thought that she would say something so embarrassing. I couldn\'t face the doctors and nurses the same way anymore. What makes things worse is that she\'s oblivious about it! Unless all the hospitals nearby shut down for good, there\'s no chance of me setting foot in that place...","Why do I play tricks on my lady? First of all, that is an overstatement. I just couldn\'t stand her showing off just because there is some progress in her love life. It\'s nothing but a counter-reaction... It\'s just that she\'s now getting ahead of herself without standing in my shoes. Like, come on, I\'m the only one who listens to her stories... The least she should do is to appreciate me! Am I right?","Indeed, the president and my lady come from totally different family backgrounds. But after getting in touch with him, I can somewhat understand why my lady would fall for him. Perhaps a guy like him suits my lady the best.","Oh?! You get it? Sitting on a chair while taking a bath is underrated, right? I mean, who can resist enjoying the sense of security provided by the chair while soaking in a warm bath to get rid of all your weariness... If that\'s taken away from my life, there\'s no way I can keep doing this job.","Are you giving me this so you can find an excuse to date me? Hahaha, just kidding. Don\'t sweat it. Thanks anyway.","Oh?! Isn\'t this the newly-released version? You\'re the best. Since you have given me such a precious present, I have to bring my A-game as a return gift. Get excited!","Why did I become my lady\'s maid? No reason in particular, really. I\'m just doing what I\'m supposed to do as a member of the Hayasaka family.","Are you sighing? Don\'t do that too often, or else your luck might crawl apart like little spiders.","Just a casual thought. When love strikes, is there really someone adamant enough to wait for the other half to confess…? You think that\'s weird, too? Goodness me, I have two weirdos around me that are just like that.","It sometimes irks me a lot, but there are times I couldn\'t help myself from feeling... envious. I\'d like to love someone unconditionally, too. Just once will do.","A person will not be loved when they fail to put on their facade, as they will be vulnerable and ugly. This is a no-brainer. That means the real you will never be loved by others...","I respect my lady because she\'s my master, but I will not be constrained by so-called social status. It\'s just like she said, we grew up together like sisters... Even if the useless old buffoon comes to visit, I will still not give up on such forbidden thought. My biggest hope is that my lady will be able to find the love she deserves. I will always be by her side until Miss Kaguya discovers her other half, and I can feel at ease.","Happy New Year. I\'m about to accompany my lady to her home. But since there is still some time... How about taking a stroll at the shrine?","Here are some Valentine\'s day chocolates for you. Us gals prepare Giri chocolates as a consolation for guys who don\'t have a partner. Well, for you, I guess you couldn\'t care less if it\'s Giri or Honmei, am I right...? In fact, this is just for you... Hey, the look on your face tells me that you\'re really looking forward to them!","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. At least a compensation for not getting a winning hand.","No-ten. A win-win situation, how awesome is that?","Four-Wind Discarded. Someone is backing down.","Four-Kan Abortion. Greed is bad.","Four-Player Riichi. Looks like everyone is throwing down the gauntlet.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Thirteen Orphans might be hot, but whatever.","It goes on and on...","What\'s the point of keeping this, anyway?","Looks like it\'s going to be a draw...","Ha... Getting this tile is like getting a free win.","This feels nice!","Pardon me. I got caught up in work.","Shall we begin?","Oh?! Double Riichi.","Ron!","Tsumo! Yay!","Excuse me, I\'m Kei Shirogane, the treasurer of Shuchiin Academy\'s Middle School Student Council. You seem to know my brother and Kaguya... Are you a new addition to the student council? Guess I got it wrong... Anyway, it\'s a pleasure to meet you.","Please enlighten me.","It\'s nothing. The least I can do for the student council is to do my very best.","Yay, this is exactly what I need. I win.","Alright, let\'s take the win.","My plan today? I haven\'t gotten a chance to use the book voucher that Dad gave me, so I\'m planning to check out the bookstore. Wanna tag along? If you wouldn\'t find it boring, that is.","Ah, good moooorniiiing! That\'s right. That\'s how best friends are supposed to greet each other.","Erm, I have to deliver 200 newspapers to buy this dress, while that one requires 240 newspapers... Ah, which one should I choose? Hmm? Delivering One Han City Entertainment Weekly this month comes with a bonus? Nice, that\'s good news! If I can deliver 500 more newspapers every day this month, next time I\'ll be able to go on a shopping spree with Moeha!","What is my relationship with Moeha? We\'re besties! I\'ve been to her home soo many times. She and her family are surprisingly friendly. They don\'t seem atrocious like your average politicians. Huh? The way Moeha looks at me seems odd? You must be overthinking. Well, she did say that she wants to eat me up or something like that, but I\'m sure she was just joking.","Don\'t be fooled by my brother. He\'s not only afraid of bugs, but he\'s also tone-deaf, a liar, and he doesn\'t even flip his clothes when he washes them. And that\'s who you call the flawless president?","Of course I\'ll feel regret when I make mistakes while playing Mahjong, but if I\'ve been given another chance, I\'ll definitely do the same. After all, we don\'t have the ability to foresee the future, and the only thing we can do is to play however feels right. As long as we feel it\'s \"right\", there\'s no need to feel regret.","Right on time! Save me! My brother just got a guitar from who knows where, and he\'s been playing it forever. Damn, that ain\'t the sound of a guitar! I beg you, stop him already. I don\'t care what you have to do! Stop him already!","I once told Dad to not waste his time live streaming. But I never thought that... You can actually earn money by doing so?! And I just showed my face in the live stream from time to time, and it got me $100? Recently, I\'ve been hit up by famous streamer Hibiki Himekawa for a streaming collab. She thinks it will attract more viewers and I could make money while having fun too. I\'m still not sure if I should accept or not...","My brother is getting extra gross lately. He\'s always giggling while on the phone, and he does it all night long. But I\'m more concerned about the familiar voice on the other side of the phone. Maybe I\'m being paranoid... But are my idiot brother and Kaguya together now? Like \"together\" together?!","What comic do I recommend? Please read Sweet Today. Gosh, it\'s a tear-jerker. Even the priestess at the Temple of Moons is raving about it. Anyone who read it will yearn for romance in their life!","This is for me? Why, thank you! I mean, that\'s the least I can do to help you. Don\'t break the bank for me next time.","Ah... I mentioned it, so you just went and brought it? Thank you so much... It\'s not often that I get a gift that I really like. You better be looking forward to my return gift. I might have to deliver more newspapers, but if a little extra effort can help me repay your sincerity, it\'ll be worth it!","What do you mean, I\'m like my brother? How rude of you to compare me to that stubborn liar.","It\'s not that I hate my brother. It\'s just that I don\'t like how he is always treating me like a child, especially when he nags like our mother. I bet you\'d find a guy who nags a lot like him gross, too.","Kaguya wants to know me a little more? For real?! Honestly, I would like to be closer to her, too. It\'s just that I get so nervous whenever I see her, and I don\'t know what to say.","To say that I\'m better than my brother is an overstatement. I\'m just lucky and happen to meet our mother\'s expectations. My brother is trying really hard to meet others\' expectations, and now he is striving to fill the vacancy in someone\'s heart. Sure, I always say that he\'s gross, but at the same time, I respect him.","Although my brother is always so annoying and I have no idea what Dad is up to every day, I\'m still pretty fond of living with them. Who cares if they\'re awesome or not? I just want to live with them. That\'s how family works, right?","Are you interested in astronomy, too? I know nothing about stars, but gosh, I love watching them. I particularly enjoy stargazing with my telescope because when I do that, I realize my troubles are nothing among the vast skies. That\'s how I achieve my inner zen. Would you like to try it yourself? I might be a newbie in this, but I have a few stories about stars that I\'d like to tell you.","Happy New Year. Moeha invited me to pray at the shrine, and I\'m about to go meet her. My wish? I have so many. Hehe, I hope God doesn\'t mind my greediness. Wanna come along?","Some Valentine\'s Day chocolates for you. A little gift for taking care of me all this time... Yup, I made it myself. I come from a poor family, so I\'m used to cooking. Well, there\'s nothing special about it. I just melted and molded them. Hope you like them.","Tenpai. Great. Scoring sticks are fine.","Hmm... No-ten. Pity.","Four-Wind Discarded. Thank goodness it\'s not Riichi.","Four-Kan Abortion. Looks like my Dora has gone to waste...","Four-Player Riichi. What a way to retreat.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors... Hmm, this is the right way.","I misjudged...","It\'ll only get in the way if I keep it.","I\'ll try to fight for Tenpai at least.","Oh? So that\'s the impressive trick Chika mentioned.","This is it... I\'ll put my pride on the line! There\'s no holding back!","Don\'t mind me. Here is some black coffee since I don\'t know what y\'all like.","I\'ve finished stretching... I\'m ready.","Ron, the judgment of justice!","Tsumo! The heaven\'s wrath!","Here comes The Witch, AKA The Righteous One! I\'m Yuzu, and I will maintain the order of the world! Gulp... What\'s that look? The Law of the Witches No. 1: Mortals who look down upon witches shall pay a heavy price. Don\'t say that I didn\'t warn you, but you might not want to dismiss me as a child!","As the Witch of Justice, I shall ensure this match is conducted with absolute fairness. Therefore, do not even think of cheating before my great and powerful magic!","Any kid who acts naughty before me shall be punished.","The almighty God of Justice, please bestow me with your powerful spells!","Summon Red Panda Squad. Charge!","Rummaging Spell, activate! ... Gulp, no dangerous weapon, no suspicious scent, no fishy accomplice... Alright, you\'ve passed the test. Maintain such behavior and keep being a good citizen.","A wonderful day starts with a patrol to maintain justice... Huh? The school? The vice president? Gulp... Now that I think of it, the school is full of problematic kids. Maintaining justice is now a must... Th-That\'s right, and it might not be that bad to start with the school...","Did I not make it on time? This is the downfall of the Witch of Justice... Because a delayed justice is justice denied... Gulp... In this place\'s language, this is like hesitating about declaring Riichi and missing out on the Ippatsu deal-in from the next player, and then there\'s no point to declare Riichi again... What\'s with that attitude, ay? You disagree with me?!","Get your hands off my tail! You wouldn\'t understand if told you, but this is the transmitter between the Red Panda Squad and me. If you just come up and touch it, you\'ll disrupt our magical surge... Keep your hands to yourself...","Afraid... Something that I\'m afraid of... What...? What are you blabbering about?! The Witch of Justice isn\'t afraid of anything. Otherwise, how would I even uphold justice? What do you mean by snakes, frogs, and spiders? Those are all my fri-... Sob... I bit my tongue...","That\'s not a red panda; it\'s a raccoon! I tell ya, a red panda and a raccoon may look similar, but when threatened, only a red panda will stand up and let out a \"cho-cho...\" sound!","Underestimating the power of the Red Panda Squad is a grave mistake. After all, most of the cutest creatures in this world are also the most powerful. Besides... red pandas are also known by another name: the striped wolf. How about now? Aren\'t you awed by them now?!","As a matter of courtesy and trust, I think I shall introduce you to the Red Panda Squad. They seem to want to get to know you... Guys, let\'s line up and introduce yourselves to {name}! (Cho-cho, Choooo, Chooo-chooo) ... Now that you\'ve remembered their names, please be nice to each other!","Kaavi? Why would I get involved with that twerp? We may have learned sorcery together, but we do not share the same ideology. Listen up! The Law of Witches No. 13: No matter how broad their chest is, as long as they have rabbit ears, they cannot be trusted!","The source of the Law of Witches, you ask? I\'ve made them myself, of course! Witches are the world\'s most unique and mysterious individuals. Every witch has her own beliefs and standards. All you need to do is follow mine.","Gulp... It looks like you have some serious misunderstandings about witches...","What do you mean by \"bribe\"? I will not condone... such... an act... in the face of justice. Say, if I take this bear plushie back home, will the Red Panda Squad toss it to the side?","Witches are lone wolves. So are companions of justice. That being said, everything seems to fall into place since I am a Witch of Justice. Gulp, that\'s compelling reasoning for you.","Kaavi\'s divination... Gulp! For real? People actually patronize her service? What a shame... Ahem, I don\'t want to admit this, but that woman is really a talented diviner. It\'s just that the better the divination, the higher the price. Have you ever wondered whether she\'s telling you the truth when she\'s fortune-telling? And if she\'s telling the truth, then... at what cost?","Kazuha Saionji? Gulp... That\'s literally the epitome of justice... Witches and swordsmen do not share the same principles, nor does my definition of justice match hers. One more thing... It\'s best for you to stay away from her. I can sense that her principle of justice is too stringent. It\'s only a matter of time before... Hmm? You don\'t believe me? What\'s the matter? So you\'d trust Kaavi\'s nonsense instead of a witch\'s sixth sense?!","Me and Kaavi\'s teacher? Why so curious all of a sudden? Gulp! Although she says that she\'ll come to One Han City soon... How should I put this? No matter what, please don\'t show any interest in her. In her eyes, your blood is the perfect supplement for potions, and your bones might become materials for a scepter... Gulp! That has nothing to do with being her disciple. We just have different ideas about the principles of witches!","You\'re such an oddball. Although humans are inquisitive toward witches, I still can\'t believe that there are actually mortals who would follow a witch everywhere they go. Gulp... It\'s not that I forbid you to do so, but as a witch myself, I\'m not used to having humans around me... Perhaps... Perhaps I\'ll just make an exception for you...","Spirits of Southern Winds, when you descend, I ask you to tie the knot of faith, which is made of rootless sauropus plant, the white flames of shumi, and the unyielding mercury lamp, between {name} and me. From this day onward, {name} shall be under the wings of my justice. Consequently, we shall treat each other with respect, love, and righteousness—Magic, Oath Established.","3, 2, 1! Did you hear that, {name}? The new year\'s bell is ringing! This year, let\'s forge a new era of sorcery hand-in-hand by helping those in need, be it animals, plants, or humans. One day, Yuzu will cover the whole world with a magic spell called \"happiness\"!","Here\'s some chocolate for you that was exclusively made by the Red Panda Squad... Of course, I was involved, too. I can\'t blame you, as typical mortals are incapable of sensing the sorcery surge within it. Well, I am responsible for casting the luck spell during the chocolate-making process. You might not be able to see it, but this bar of chocolate is, in fact, blessed by the magic of luck!","Lots of Dora","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Thirteen Orphans","Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans","Nine Gates","True Nine Gates","Quintuple Yakuman","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. Got ya!","No-ten. The next one is guaranteed!","Four-Wind Discarded.","Four-Kan Abortion.","Gulp... I wonder if anyone will believe me if I declare that this is one of my tactics...","Chill out. Using sorcery to steal Dora is considered cheating! No way that\'s allowed!","The final battle against evil is about to begin. Stay alert!","Try your best to leave the chance of deal-in with others and let them decide whether or not to play that sinful tile. Gulp! I guess this is just another way to maintain fairness and justice!","How about that? Aren\'t you surprised? Even without using sorcery, I am still capable of achieving a huge combo!","What\'s up, everyone! (Cho-cho! Choooo! Chooo-chooo!) Today, the Red Panda Squad will be your judges! They have a perfect 0% misjudgment rate, so you can all play without a worry!","Elemental fluctuations are stable. No magic residue spotted. Room inspection complete. We are clear to begin!","Ron. Got it!","Tsumo! You\'ve got nowhere to run!","I\'ve finally found you, Kazuha Saionji\'s disciple... You\'re different from what I expected. She claimed that she had found her successor and refused to teach me... Tsk, I wonder if she really thought that you\'re better than me? Haha, interesting! Stay put. I\'ll take matters into my own hands and let everyone know who\'s the most eligible successor... Ha? Not into violence? Play by your rules? Hmph, you must have overestimated your ability. Don\'t tell me you\'re thinking of besting me in a game of Mahjong? Don\'t say that I didn\'t warn you. I underwent strict training before arriving in One Han City!","Cheer up, my prey! I\'m afraid this moment of happiness is your last.","Tsk, what should I say to my defeated opponent? Well, I wish you the best of luck next time!","An excellent hunter won\'t be enthralled by a mere little rabbit!","How naive are you to think that points are my only prey in this match? Hehe!","How slow... That\'s right. I\'m talking about you. Didn\'t I tell you that I would challenge you? You seem like you\'re in good spirits today, so let\'s get this over with now!","Hey! Hey! Hey! You twerp, I can\'t seem to remember your name... Huh? Calling you by name is a chore. It\'s not like I address anyone as \"hey\". Since you\'re the only one to earn that name in One Han City, I thought you\'d appreciate it. Besides, calling you by your full name feels like... we\'re about to start a fight... Unless that\'s exactly what you wanna do?!","How dare Ein act all bossy in front of me? He was born just an hour earlier. Hmph, just wait. I will become the best swordsman and shave his fox tail.","Cats traded their wit for their beauty. The cuter they are, the dumber they are. The one at the Mahjong Soul Shrine is the perfect example. Judging by its fur, its master must have treated it really well. It probably can\'t even lift its paw when it encounters an enemy.","Hey! Chop-chop, see that dimwit over there? That\'s our prey. Today, I will teach you the correct way to hunt... Violent? Shush! Isn\'t looting someone else\'s points until they cry and give up the essence of winning in Mahjong?","How weak are you to not be able to carry a 100 kg rice sack? Tsk, no doubt, you\'re textbook prey. Look at those hands. One pinch, and they\'d be crushed to smithereens. I pray that I won\'t accidentally crush your bones one of these days. How cumbersome!","Not bad. You\'ve shown unyielding spirit by still holding on... Hehe, most of them are just a bunch of deadbeats! All they know what to do is complain like a bunch of babies after a harsh lesson, and I will give them a beating the next time we meet until they don\'t have the guts to murmur a single word. I must admit, you\'re pretty smart and brave. I like you!","Hmph! Caught you red-handed! Such a simple-minded ambush is not effective against me. Next time, remember to... Hey! It\'s not a big deal to foil your sneak attack. There\'s no need for a long face! Look, I\'m the one who got ambushed and still maintained my composure... Hey! Don\'t tell me that you\'re actually mad...","Hey! You might want to keep up the pace when there\'s a crowd. You may be weak, dumb, and useless in a fight, but you are actually kinda cute and popular by human standards. I don\'t want to go through any trouble if someone else takes you away from me.","Ah... Hmph... (moaning) Ah, who... who gave you permission to touch my tail? I knew it! I shouldn\'t have let my guard down and let you come close to me, you cunning human... Hey! Are you exploiting my weakness when I\'m vulnerable?!","Is this really a gift for me? Or is it a tool in a plot against me?","Wow, wow... Ahem... Why would you give me this...? Although I don\'t think we\'re there yet... I guess I\'ll reluctantly take it... Huh? Don\'t be shy? You\'re the one who should be shy! Didn\'t Ein tell you that people in our hometown only give clothing as a way of confession? Besides, you gave me women\'s clothing! Could you get any dumber?!!! I will never wear it!!! Never!!!","You seem to know One Han City pretty well. Listen up. I\'m going to dominate One Han City from today onward. And I\'m giving you the honor of being my assistant. See that guy over there? You won\'t be any better off than him if you turn me down.","The old dude over there, the dispirited middle-aged man carrying a pack of sugar... Interesting. Those eyes don\'t fit on a dispirited middle-aged man. What did he say previously...? Z... Zan? Tsukimi? Meh, it doesn\'t matter. I\'ll be sure to interrogate him the next time we meet.","Say no to violence? What kind of foolish statement is that? Beatings aren\'t for reasonable people. Are you expecting to reason with unreasonable people? Cut me some slack. I wonder how naive people like you can survive in one piece for so long. Listen up. This world is full of crap that is more absurd than a fairytale. If you don\'t want to be prey, work your way up to being a hunter!","What am I thinking? Being quiet doesn\'t mean that someone is thinking about something. Tsk, cut me some slack, won\'t you? You\'re starting to be like Emma... Huh, you don\'t know Emma? She\'s the youngest child in my family, and she\'s the one and only gorgeous white wolf in our tribe. I\'ll introduce you to her when I get a chance. It\'s just that... You see, she\'s not a big fan of weaklings, haha.","What\'s this all about? The most unpopular guy leaderboard? Number three... Zechs? You gotta be kidding me. How would an excellent hunter like me end up being unpopular...? Hey! What\'s with the smug look on your face? Don\'t tell me you\'re involved in this, too? Tsk, you better have a proper explanation. Or you could say \"Zechs is my absolute favorite person\" out loud three times. Hmm... Let\'s say we go with what I want, which is the second option. Now, don\'t keep me waiting...","Hey! Take this and be careful with it. It has my scent on it. Next time, those disobedient nuisances who smell it will know to get lost... What...? What do you mean, it smells like peaches? That\'s obviously the smell of a manly man! Only Ein is a big fan of girly scents... Stop sniffing it, will ya? It\'s not like an ordinary person like you can sniff the odor left by a hunter. Hmph, just take care of it!","Happy New Year! So people here like to celebrate the new year today... My hometown? Of course not. This kind of cozy weather is the best for mating. It should always be a grand hunt when the new year comes. On that day, each hunter has to loot large amounts of food and fur, as well as find a mate. What? You wanna celebrate the new year in my home town? We can still make it for the preparations if we head back now.","Look at the time. An outstanding physique is a necessity for every hunter. You better start working out now... Huh? What\'s today\'s occasion? Hmm... Your birthday? ... New Year\'s? ... Then what\'s the big deal today? ... Valentine\'s Day?! What sort of celebration is that? ... Of course it\'d be weird. If a couple truly loves each other, I\'m pretty sure Valentine\'s Day is every day. What\'s the point of celebrating it on a designated day? And what are the other 364 days for? (Takes a deep breath and sighs) Instead of thinking of this nonsense, how about you follow me to the mountains? I\'m gonna take you away from this unreasonable world.","Tenpai. Tsk, that\'s way off the mark.","No-ten. Tsk—","Four-Kan Abortion","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","Some tiles are like skinny wild animals. It doesn\'t hurt if you just throw them away.","Delicious food might come with a lethal trap. An excellent hunter is not fooled easily!","Tsk, I have seen worse. There\'s nothing to be afraid of.","Honestly, I\'m not easy to satisfy. Hehe! Wasn\'t that already obvious? Let\'s milk them dry!","Shh... Keep it down, or my tile might flee. You better not mess this up, or you will be my compensation!","Ah, mhm, I\'m here. It\'s nothing. It doesn\'t take a lot of time to play a few rounds with you guys every once in a while. Besides, who doesn\'t like the sweet taste of victory?","What are you waiting for? Start the game already! What? Do I need to tell you guys how to do everything?","Ron!","Are you the new blessed one? My name is Lily Kitahara, and I\'m obviously a nun, hehe.","Beware, this table is crawling with the greedy hands of desire.","I couldn\'t care less about being exiled by the gods, hehe.","Life is meant to be fun. Otherwise, what\'s the point?","It looks like your gods have forsaken you.","I can smell the fervent desire within you.","Come to me. No need to be so nervous. For you, my patience is eternal.","Mahjong is such a dangerous game. One mere Mahjong tile can result in slaughter without bloodshed, and one bad move can seal your fate. The same goes for you, my charming little toy, hehe~","You always exude the scent of immaturity. It\'s been quite some time since I caught a whiff of something like that. Such an intoxicating scent.","Ah, Northland. No matter how long I\'ve been away from it, its chill still lingers on every inch of my skin. That place is covered with everlasting snow, burying the corrupted desires beneath. Hehe, wanna find out the truth behind those desires?","Nothing brings me more pleasure than the warmth of your body. I can feel the hot blood flowing through your fragile veins under that tender skin of yours. Who could resist that?","Look at this tile. Doesn\'t it remind you of a cute little bird? Such a pretty thing, yet so fragile that it couldn\'t even withstand a soft pinch. Northland has no place for things like that.","You know, I am really proud of my long, blonde hair! I couldn\'t help but notice it also suits you really well, especially when it\'s wrapped around you.","Words of affirmation are the perfect icing on the cake. I mean, who could resist such intoxicating words? Come on, tell me more about how you love me.","Beautiful souls attract each other, just like beautiful bodies do. I guess this is why I have fallen for you. I love you with all my heart, both your body and soul!","Are you being sincere?","I\'d rather get you as a present, hehe! You\'d be cute in a little red bow.","You want to know about my past? Hehe, I can hardly remember the last person who asked me that. Let\'s see how you fare this time.","Underneath the habit of a nun is a secret world that even the gods are unaware of. And that world is out of your reach at the moment!","The rumors about me? It\'s all true, you know. Hehe, the truth is nothing more than something you believe. And if you don\'t believe it, nobody can force you to.","A nun is meant to act as a medium for the gods, and every word I\'m telling you right now is god\'s will, and also my will. Hehe.","The gods? Am I not your god? Hehe, what? Do you really think you can worship someone other than me?","From now on, the only thing you need in this world is me. I will give you the love you deserve. In return, you must return my passion as well! Otherwise, I will have to freeze time and keep you in this moment so that you\'ll never stop loving me.","Happy New Year! As they say, \"when in Rome, do as the Romans do,\" which is why I am celebrating the new year like you. I have to admit, the new year\'s celebration here isn\'t half bad!","Ah, Valentine\'s day, the day for lovers. Looks like I\'m gonna have to celebrate it with you. Hehe. But, I don\'t really feel like today\'s any different than any other day that I\'ve spent with you. Looks like you have to try harder so I can get into the holiday spirit!","Dora 2","Dora 3","Dora 4","Dora 5","Dora 6","Dora 7","Dora 8","Dora 9","Dora 10","Dora 11","Dora 12","Lots of Dora","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Big Three Dragons","Four Concealed Triplets","Single-wait Four Concealed Triplets","All Honors","All Green","All Terminals","Thirteen Orphans","Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans","Four Big Winds","Tenpai. I\'m feeling good.","No-ten, a bad omen...","Sometimes, you just keep getting things that you don\'t need.","What\'s so precious about a Dora?","This intense tension is intoxicating.","Let\'s see who will be lucky enough to serve me.","I\'m itching to get started, hehe.","Sorry for the wait.","I\'ve waited for you for so long that even the flowers have withered.","Ah, that\'s a quick sweeping win... Double Riichi!","Kita.","Ron.","Tsumo, I\'m in the zone now!","Ah, you must be the Jyanshi my juniors had mentioned... correct? Thank you for taking good care of them. Speaking of this, I haven\'t introduced myself yet. I\'m the president of the Kiyosumi Mahjong Club, Hisa Takei. I\'m looking forward to your advice in the upcoming practices.","Please show me how it\'s done.","Thanks for the hard work. You\'re looking sharp today.","And with that tile, a win!","Hmm... It seems like it\'s a much bigger hand than expected.","You look dog-tired. I heard that lowering the water temperature while taking a bath can stimulate your parasympathetic nervous system. You should give it a try!","Oh, you are right on time. I\'ve invited Mihoko for a Mahjong game at the shrine and we are short of one player. Wanna tag along?","It can be a bit of a headache to play against someone who\'s good at defense. If your rival is on guard against you, you should try to guess what\'s on their mind and then plan your strategy accordingly. Well, if that doesn\'t work, just rely on Tsumo. There\'s always a way.","Asaha High School\'s desserts are made by their president? He\'s really good at this. I wish Mako could try these too. A president that neglects his duty to make desserts. Hehe... An interesting man. Looks like he\'s just like me, trying to live our youth to the fullest.","After I graduated, the Mahjong Club won\'t need to select new recruits like this anymore... Just go out there and recruit whoever you like. Nonetheless, it will be a bit of a headache if all the new members are just here to get a glimpse of Nodoka. If I\'m not mistaken, after two years, Yumeno should have joined the club, too.","Lately, I feel like I don\'t know the meaning of life anymore... Is it because my age is catching up? But I am just 17! The more I think about this the more depressed I feel. I guess I should leave these kinds of problems to philosophers and Nodoka, and enjoy my life.","I heard that you were teaching Mihoko how to use the computer. How did it go? Did her notoriously poor understanding of tech catch you off guard? This bothers her sometimes, but I don\'t think it\'s that big of a deal. Don\'t you find it kind of cute that even though she looks so perfect on the outside, she still has small imperfections like this inside?","Not long ago, Kaavi warned me to be careful when walking downstairs. She didn\'t really tell me why, but since it was a reminder from a fortune teller, I better be careful. After all, the tournament is just around the corner, I can\'t afford any accidents...","Mihoko is indeed nothing short of extraordinary. Not only is she a thoughtful person, but she\'s also an excellent chef and Mahjong player. It\'s only natural that the students of Kazekoshi would be dependent on her. Not to mention her two beautiful, gem-liked eyes... I wonder how could I even forget about such a wonderful girl...","Eh? You\'ve solved your problems based on my suggestions? Is... is that so... I was just saying that. I didn\'t expect you to actually do it...","Ah, thank you for giving me this. How about some nuts as a return gift? They work magic on your memory!","Oh my... You caught me off guard with my favorite gift. Thank you, but give me some time to think of a return gift!","Today\'s opponent makes me uneasy, especially the girl with a blade. However! I just asked Saki how I look today, and she said \"pretty cute\". So I guess lady luck is on my side today. Let\'s get it!","Uwaa... I didn\'t expect it to rain on my way to the shrine... Judging by all the clothes hanging around the corridor, I guess I wasn\'t the only one. Speaking of that, looking at all these drenched women\'s clothes hanging in a row... Don\'t you think such a scene tickles one pink?","Whenever I see Nodoka and the others play Mahjong, I always feel that people who got upset the entire day just because of losing a Hanchan game are probably not fit to play Mahjong. Although I would get a little upset, too, if I were in their shoes, setbacks are part of life. As long as you pave your way forward, one step at a time, you\'ll definitely see a different side of the view. My advice is to enjoy every game. Only by doing so is the match truly commenced.","For me, the national tournament is the pinnacle of my dream. In fact, it will be a dream come true if I can excel in every Hanchan game in the tournament with my own style. Albeit life isn\'t always a smooth ride... I still believe that as long as I don\'t give up, the outcome will be great. This has always been how I live my life.","Honestly I don\'t know whether or not I will still be playing Mahjong in the future. But one thing for sure, just like what Yuuki once said, one day when I become somebody, I\'ll look back on the days when I was playing Mahjong and doing all kinds of stuff with ya\'ll. Even though those days might seem ordinary in others\' eyes, I\'ll always relish them as some of the most glorious moments of my life.","You\'re late, even though you were the one that said you wanted to be the guide. That\'s not cool, you know... Just kidding. Don\'t worry, it\'s still early. Now let\'s meet up with Mihoko first. I even brought my suitcase today, you know? I\'m ready to bring a whole bunch of souvenirs home!","Happy New Year! Are you heading to the shrine to seek divination too? Or would you like to just play a game and see your luck this year?","Ah, I thought you weren\'t coming to the shrine today. It seems like I can give away this chocolate after all. Happy Valentine\'s... Oops, sorry, wrong chocolate. I can\'t give you this one as it is from the student council. Here you go, this is yours!","Tenpai.","No-ten.","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Now that\'s really neat...","That\'s unnecessary.","Should I keep going? Or...","Yakuman... how awesome it will be if I can win the round!","A big one\'s coming...","Everyone here?","I\'m ready.","Ron.","And that\'s my Tsumo!","Hi there, I\'m Mihoko Fukuji, the president of Kazekoshi Mahjong Club. I\'ve heard about the shrine\'s training match from Hisa. Thanks for the invitation, I hope to learn something from you. Anyway, I\'ve made some sandwiches and rice balls. If you don\'t mind, maybe we can have some together after the practice?","Nice to meet you all.","Thanks for the guidance. If fate allows, we shall cross paths again in future matches.","Pardon me. It seems that I\'ve won.","My apologies, that was a big hand. But don\'t lose heart – the game isn\'t over yet.","Thank you for helping me bring in the water buckets. Don\'t mind me, just have a rest. Everybody should be here soon, so I\'m going to tidy up the match room so that everyone can play with peace of mind when they arrive.","Good to see you. You\'re early, as usual. Hisa should arrive soon, and I\'ll wait a little while for her here. I bet when she comes, she\'ll apologize for letting me wait again, but I actually enjoy waiting like this. Hehe... Ah, please don\'t tell her that. It\'ll be our little secret.","You can type without looking at the keyboard? People who understand how to use computers are just so impressive... *Sigh* If I were an IT pro like you, I would be able to help everyone do research for the club. Right now I can only rely on the juniors of the club for that. It\'d be nice to know how to use a computer...","Sorry if I scared you. My tear gland is really sensitive, and even just a little touching moment would make me cry. The movie we watched was really great. I wanna watch it again when I\'m home.","Not only did Ms. Kitami accompany us throughout the training, but she also taught me to cook quite a few new dishes. She\'s such a sweet person. I really hope I can one day become someone as outstanding as her.","Coach Kubo may be sharp-tongued, but after spending enough time with her, you\'ll realize that she\'s just not good at expressing her gentle side. She\'s always looking out for everyone in silence... And I believe the only reason she\'s being so strict is that she doesn\'t want us to shed tears of failure again and again. Therefore, I hope I can live up to her expectation with at least a victory in the individual tournament before graduating.","Wow! This trick is so interesting. Can you teach me? Telling jokes is not my forte, so I want to learn some tricks that I can show off at any time. Maybe this trick can catch everyone by surprise during the next Mahjong Club gathering, hehe...","Ain\'t little Haruna cute? She reminds me of Kana\'s sisters. Playing with such a spirited kid makes me feel energetic, too.","\"Blue sapphires and red rubies are made from the same element.\" ...Although we have become closer, Hisa has still yet to tell me the meaning behind this quote. Well, it\'s okay, though. We still have a long way ahead of us. I believe one day, she\'ll eventually give me an answer. And before that day comes, I\'ll keep pondering what it really means.","It\'s a shame that I couldn\'t lead everyone to the end during my final year. But it\'s alright, Kana, Bundo, Yoshitome, Fukabori...Perhaps more talented players will join the Kazekoshi Mahjong Club in the future. I believe that as long as we don\'t give up, Kazekoshi High will one day earn its own glory.","So this is a gift to repay the lunch boxes I prepared for you? Thank you. Here, have some rabbit-shaped apple slices. They are treats for well-mannered kids, hehe...","Are... Are you sure? Such a precious gift should be gifted to someone important, like your mother maybe... Alright. Since you insist, I\'ll take it. Thanks, and do not bring any food with you tomorrow. Let me prepare something delicious for you as a return present.","Something similar to playing Mahjong... Cooking, maybe? You utilize the ingredients given, spend effort and time to bring out the best of it, then observe the reaction of others. If you think it like that, aren\'t they both quite similar and interesting?","Helping your opponent become stronger isn\'t necessarily a bad thing. Just think about it, everyone gathers up to explore strategies, challenge each other, and gradually grow better. This is what makes Mahjong fun. Not to mention that a match is only fun when you have formidable opponents to play with. And I believe I\'m not the only one who thinks this, most Mahjong lovers do, too.","Superpowers? That\'s an overstatement. To be honest, there\'s nothing special with my right eye. I\'m just more focused when I open it, which allows me to observe other players\' movements more clearly. Everyone can do it if they are willing to meticulously observe their opponents. And at least as far as I know: Senriyama\'s captain has a knack for reading people, too. They say she can even sense other people\'s body temperature changes.","Instead of being gentle, I wish I could be tougher... If it was Hisa, I\'m sure she would put on a smiling face and comfort Kana and the others when they lost. I hope that one day I can let go of my weak side and become someone who people can really rely on.","To be honest, I\'m pretty envious of the juniors. The last time we were about to join the national tournament, our seniors were so strict with us that we were overwhelmed by stress during our debut... Winning might be important, but it is not everything. As Hisa put it, we should enjoy every match and our youth.","What\'s the rush? There\'s still plenty of time before the meet-up. Hisa just texted me, saying that she had just arrived, too, so we can still take our time. Well, usually it was always me waiting for her, but it seems that we\'ve switched roles today... It actually feels surprisingly great to let someone wait!","Happy New Year! Here\'s your New Year\'s money... Hehe, there\'s nothing to be shy about. After all, it\'s all about good omens. I hope everything will go well and we\'ll be in good health this year. Let\'s continue to look after each other in this new year.","Here\'s a Valentine\'s Day chocolate. Please take it. I hope it won\'t bother you too much because Hisa once said there\'s nothing better than receiving chocolate from the person you like on Valentine\'s Day... I wonder what her expression will be when she receives my chocolate. Hehe...","Tenpai.","No-ten.","The same tiles again...","While it\'s a Dora... but there\'s only so much I can do.","I guess it\'s about time to abandon the win?","This is great, but I cannot let my guard down before winning.","Strive and march to victory.","It seems like everyone\'s here already... I\'m sorry, I hope I didn\'t keep you waiting long.","I\'m ready now.","Ron","Phew... I\'m saved. If it wasn\'t for your guidance, who knows when would I find my way to this shrine. You have my gratitude. I\'m Ako Atarashi, Achiga Mahjong Club\'s lieutenant. Any chance you\'re here to train too?","Pleased to meet you.","Hehe! I am second to none in terms of speed!","The first strike wins!","If you thought that I was just fast, you couldn\'t have been more wrong!","Yo, Yu and the gang have arrived at the shrine. You can go join them first. I can\'t find Shizu anywhere. Who knows where she got lost this time. I\'ll have to bring her back first. See you later.","*Yawn* Good morning... I stayed up late last night. Still feeling kinda sleepy. You head to the match room first. I\'ll join you later after taking a shower in the shrine\'s bathroom.","Ahh... So tired... I can barely feel my hands anymore. The last time I was this exhausted was still back when I was traveling around. But if I want to become stronger, this is still far from enough... Alright, one more round!","The next time you meet Kirara, can you give this thing to her? She asked for this makeup sample, but we did not cross paths these few days. I\'m afraid I\'ll forget to bring it the next time we meet.","Everyone has bad luck sometimes. You might feel like you\'re doing everything wrong, and it\'s totally normal to think that. I mean, who cares if you\'re demotivated once in a while? I won\'t laugh at you, but still, don\'t forget to get yourself together after that.","Ah! Nodoka\'s log, what a beauty to behold. Every move feels justified. Although I\'m a little jealous, I must admit that she\'s the closest thing to my ideal type. What a pity that we are playing different positions, thus unable to have a formal showdown.","Getting light-headed? You must have been playing Mahjong for too long. Didn\'t I tell you to prepare some food? Playing Mahjong takes a lot of energy, you know... Here, take this chocolate. Just remember to bring something to repay me the next time, okay?","Wah... Ah, you... you didn\'t hear that. No funny faces! Seriously... Come on, I was scared back there. It\'s not like I can control it...","You\'ve been staring at that gift box for so long. Having trouble decorating it? That\'s my forte, so just leave it to me! Let me think. First... let\'s use some colorful stickers to create a pattern!","Maybe it\'s because my family also manages a shrine, I feel pretty comfortable training here. Although my place does not have a god as cute as Ichihime! Speaking of cat-eared priestesses... I heard that Kiyosumi\'s sergeant would dress as a maid to serve customers in her own Mahjong Club. Maybe, it would be a good idea to do some cosplay in my shrine to attract customers? I\'ll suggest this to my sis next time!","Thanks, but the least give me a reason next time. I feel kinda embarrassed to receive a gift from you out of the blue.","OMG! This... this is adorable! Thanks, I really love this!","Speaking of Kiyosumi\'s vanguard, she does look like me in my primary school days, like we even shared the same hairstyle and stuff. I was quite shocked, too, when I first saw her. However, over the years, only I\'ve properly grown up, in many ways!","Excuse me, just a moment. I need to fix my makeup before the match starts. Although makeup has nothing to do with Mahjong, it does affect my mood. I must be at my best before getting into action.","After all, it is the national tournament. It\'s not surprising to see some incredibly gifted players. I\'m not gonna lie, I do envy them. They are so gifted that it\'s almost like they are cheating, but since I\'m already on the stage, retreating is no longer an option. I shall show them my way of fighting!","What I would like to do after being crowned as the champion of the national tournament...? I guess the first thing I would do is to apologize to Harue. Before the semi-finals, I doubted if she was using our results as a stepping stone to becoming a professional Jyanshi. However, after we won, Harue actually cried. She was genuinely happy for us... I would like to repay her for bringing us to this place, not only by making it into the semi-finals for her but also by achieving something further.","Of course winning makes me happy, but... sometimes I can\'t help thinking about how the losing side must feel. I imagine even those who always seem happy would still tear up when they lose. The fact that I will only be able to face them again after a year makes me feel like a coward who runs away as soon as victory is secured... But it is what it is. I guess this must be what winners have to carry with them to keep going.","Hmm? Why are you not coming over after changing into your swimsuit? Why are you blushing? Don\'t tell me you\'re feeling embarrassed seeing me in my swimsuit. Come on, come here. It\'s not often that we have the chance to come to the seaside. It would be a waste of opportunity if we don\'t loosen ourselves up. Come on!","Happy New Year. I\'ve just spent the night celebrating the new year with Shizu and the gang. Right now, it\'s time for me to rush home to help out my family. This is the busiest time for the shrine. You\'re welcome to drop by if you are free. It\'s not often that you can see me in a miko outfit, you know? Hehe.","Chocolate? Ah, today\'s Valentine\'s Day. My bad, the only chocolate I\'m holding is for Shizu... Pfft, haha! Come on, why the long face? I\'m just messing with you. How can I not prepare chocolate on a day like this? Here you go, Happy Valentine\'s Day!","Tenpai.","No-ten.","It\'s... it\'s the same tile!","What a pity!","Could it be an exhaustive draw?","Wow, such an incredible hand. Ah... No, I must remain calm.","A quick attack seems ideal, but it\'s better to control myself for a bit.","Sorry for being late.","Okay! I\'m ready!","Riichi. A turn later... I\'ve seen it.","Tsumo. Okay.","I\'m really sorry for scaring you back there. I\'m not in the best of health, so sometimes I would suddenly collapse on the street like that. I just need some rest, and everything will be fine... Thank you for helping me get to the shrine. I\'m Toki Onjoji. What about you?","Nice to meet you.","Just as what I\'ve foreseen, a glorious future.","There\'s still room to improve the points, but based on the outcome I\'ve foreseen... I\'ll be content with a win.","With such a point gap, there should be no need to foresee the future anymore.","Hi, thanks for the company. I\'m looking forward to practicing with you today.","Ah... How tiring. I don\'t feel like practicing today. I just want to spend a whole day on Ryuka\'s lap! But there\'s a training match scheduled today... Oh, I can just ask someone to replace me! Well... are you free today?","Being able to foresee the future doesn\'t mean victory is guaranteed. Even if I could influence all the discarded tiles, I still wouldn\'t be unable to prevent a Tsumo. Perhaps this is the \"inevitable doom\" Ms. Kaavi spoke of.","Ways to improve relationships with others... How about exchanging diaries? Well, you can write down things about yourself and things that you find hard to tell in person. And through the pages, you will gradually know more about each other.","So tired... Training is so hard, and life is so hard, too. I am in dire need of Ryuka\'s lap, and I\'m craving Ryuka\'s curry...","Ryuka\'s granny once said that you should not easily give up even if you have no point sticks. Nobody can predict the result of a match. This is why you\'ve got to hold on till the end. The result might not be great, but the important thing is that you\'ve tried your very best.","Even if there\'s a difference in strength, with some luck, the weak might still prevail over the strong and ultimately enjoy the fruit of victory. That\'s Mahjong for you. And that was why I, someone who wasn\'t really good at anything, can win in Mahjong... That\'s the reason I fell in love with Mahjong.","Wow... Just one demonstration and you can already erect the Riichi Bets stably. You\'re quite talented. What do you think? Standing Riichi Bets are pretty cool, right?","Previously, Miss Miki cordially invited me to try her lap. She was so enthusiastic so I gave it a shot, and then... To be honest, I was really astonished. Although not as good as Ryuka\'s, it was still such a high-quality lap pillow nonetheless... It seems the world is indeed full of wonders... and great lap pillows...","When you surround yourself with outstanding individuals, it\'s normal to compare yourself with them and be envious of something they have that you don\'t. However, I don\'t see the need for such a comparison... When you focus on the things you have, you\'ll realize that you are being envied by others as well.","Thank... thank you. That\'s odd... Did I do anything that deserves such gratitude?","Woah... What a great gift... Can... can I really have it? Thank you. Any return gift in mind? \"Lap Pillow Voucher”... of Ryuka? No, no, no! Not that! You better think of something else.","If I\'m really focused, I can indeed foresee the outcome after two or even three turns. But doing so makes me sick. That\'s why I\'ve promised Ryuka not to do such a risky thing. It may be a pity, but it hurts me more to see Ryuka getting upset... I guess I\'ll just follow her advice.","It\'s not like I can make anyone\'s knees my pillow. I have pretty strict requirements for that. It must not be too thick or thin, and it must not have any muscles, as only the perfect amount of meat can create excellent flexibility. If one\'s lap couldn\'t reach such perfect balance, then it would only be considered a typical lap and not the perfect knee pillow. As of now, only Ryuka\'s can be considered a lap pillow.","Ah... Isn\'t that the scheduling table FunaQ wrote? Where did you get that? Look at you getting all excited, don\'t tell me you want to take care of me, too...","Everyone has an ideal version of themselves, someone they want to be. And to become this person, we all have something and lack something else. I was once envious of Ryuka\'s and Sera\'s capabilities, hoping to become as good as them. But Sera told me there\'s no need for such comparison as everyone is different. So, I\'ll do all that I can before becoming the ideal version of myself.","There was a brief moment I felt helpless during the semi-finals, as if I was still the third-team player who admired Ryuka and Sera, who wasn\'t worthy to be the ace of the team... But after seeing the vanguard of Shindoji attacking with a smile even in that kind of a desperate situation reminded me that winning is nothing compared to the joy of playing... Responsibilities and objectives might be important and heavy, but what I want to do the most is to enjoy playing Mahjong, no matter what comes next, just like I did in the beginning.","I would often assemble toy blocks alone when I was a kid. No matter how tall or high it goes, it will fall down in a blink of an eye. The same goes for life... When I just began playing Mahjong with Ryuka and the others, I would depict Mahjong as toy blocks. No matter how many points one has collected, it will only take an instant for them to all fall apart. And such thrill is what makes life so fun.","Happy New Year! This year\'s wish... It will still be having a healthy body. And of course, I hope that I can live happily with Ryuka and everyone in the Mahjong Club every single day like I am right now.","Valentine\'s... Day? Ah, that\'s today! I slept through the day yesterday and completely forgot about this... But, unlike Ryuka, I don\'t how to make chocolates, so what could I even do even if I remembered? Hmm... I guess any chocolates will do, even if it is not self-made, right? Well, how about giving this chocolate ball a try? It tastes decent.","No-ten... Nothing I can do...","Hmm... I should have had a glance just now...","It\'ll be too late if I don\'t play this.","Should I just foresee one turn, or...","Yakuman... I\'ll win with this, and then... reach the top!","I want to win with this hand and do my best, but I can only foresee what will happen in the next turn.","Hi, everyone. Please bear with me today.","We can begin now.","Kita.","Hi, I\'m Fuyumi Shinomiya! Thank you for always taking such good care of my brother Natsuki! As thanks, I\'ll do my best to help you when you\'re in trouble in the future!","I\'ll try my best since this is my first time playing mahjong with everyone. Please tell me if I\'m doing anything wrong!","Wow! Even someone who has average grades like me can come first! Hehe!","The tricks I learned from my mom and dad are surprisingly useful!","Will you be happy if I share the fruits of my victory with you?","Have you finished your work today? You can tell me if anything is troubling you.","I found a place that makes amazing milk tea while shopping with my classmates a few days ago. If you\'re free right now, do you wanna go there with me?","This eye mask? Oh, it\'s my brother\'s hobby to make me wear it. I only have one brother, so I need to take care of his feelings every once in a while. I won\'t wear it in class though.","My brother is always saying dangerous-sounding words like \"Bloody,\" \"Holy War,\" or \"Requiem\" at home. I\'ve tried my best to memorize them, but I have no idea what they mean. Do you know?","Many people in the eighth grade like me don\'t have \"eighth-grader syndrome\" aka chunibyo, you know? It\'s not an infectious disease, so not everyone will have it.","I don\'t think cosplay is strange at all. As one of my brother\'s assistants, I often go to performances with him. My brother is that famous White Night after all! AHH! Did I just say something I shouldn\'t have? Shhhh—you have to keep this a secret!","If I had to comment on myself, I would say I am an ordinary middle school student. Since we have two chunibyos at home who can\'t seem to grow up, my biggest wish is to have as ordinary a life as possible. Oh? Didn\'t my brother tell you? He inherited his chunibyo from my mom!","What else can an ordinary middle school student do anyway other than go to school, go back home from school, and go shopping with friends? I guess if I had to include anything else, I also like playing Mahjong at home with my family on weekends and holidays. Would you like to play Mahjong at my place next time? My father is especially bad at it and makes deal-ins all the time!","Stay away from me! My powers, they\'re out of control! Run!!! Haha, did I give you a fright? Although I don\'t really know what those lines mean, I saw them in my brother\'s notebook. You know, you look pretty cute when you\'re surprised.","My deskmate has a boyfriend, which kinda makes me feel a little envious, haha, but they seem really distressed when they are quarreling... Speaking of which, what\'s your type?","You\'re always giving me gifts. There are so many that I don\'t know what to give to you in return.","Wow! This is the latest style, and it has such good tailoring! Thanks! I don\'t know what to give you to thank you for this. Why don\'t I help you prepare breakfast tomorrow?","Although my brother says really funny things when his chunibyo acts up, I actually kinda respect him, as those things are creeds of his life. Compared to someone as ordinary as me, someone like my brother who dares to pursue his own ideals is more dazzling.","Eggplants, potatoes, tomatoes... Hmm, what other vegetables should I buy? (Mumbling) Oh, you\'re here too. Can you give me some advice? For example, what vegetables do you usually like to eat?","Due to the influence of my brother, I sometimes read or watch fanworks, and they always impress me, but I don\'t know how to express my love for them, so I only write \"Wow, it\'s so amazing\" in the comments. I feel stupid whenever I see my own messages.","When something goes wrong, I run to my mom and cry about it, but I still have to face it afterward. If only life can be like a fairy tale, and a prince will come and save me! Hey, are you laughing at me because you think I\'m childish? Girls have the right to dream too!","It seems that I\'m sharing the events of my daily life with you most of the time. When I think that, I wonder if I\'m a little long-winded, haha. But if you are willing, I would also like to know more about you. Like tell me about your daily life, your family, or anything!","This is the first time I\'ve come to an amusement park with anyone other than my family. How should I put it... It feels like a completely different kind of happiness, but I can\'t say what\'s different about it. Anyway, shall we come again next time when we\'re free?","Happy New Year! Here\'s my exclusive blessing for you. May all your wishes come true in the new year! By the way, here are three Fuyumi Summoning Tickets. In the new year, you can use them to summon me to do three things with you—shopping, dining, or going to the amusement park! How about it? Do you want to use one today?","Hmm... How should I differentiate Giri chocolate and Honmei chocolate? Should I add different patterns? Would that be too obvious? (Mumbling) ...Ah! (Surprised) Are you here already? I\'m not ready yet! You\'re not allowed to peek! Unless... Unless you can give me some advice, like... what flavor of chocolate do you like?","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Tenpai, I\'m safe! Hehe!","No-ten... I\'ll do better next time!","I\'m a little angry, but I must keep smiling!","I\'m... not making a big mistake, right?","(Deep breath) I\'m not nervous! I\'m okay... I can do it.","Hehe, I\'m today\'s lucky girl!","Yay! I have a hand worth celebrating with a bowl of ice cream later! Hey, I\'m not making an excuse to eat ice cream!","Hi, everyone! I can\'t wait to play mahjong with you!","Yes, leave the rest to me! I\'m full of confidence!","My name is Qing Luan, but no need to tell me yours. I don\'t really care.","Ready.","Well played.","That\'s nothing.","All things are spiritual, that\'s all.","Shh... Silence is golden.","Our paths cross again.","A destined encounter may not be a good omen.","Humans are perplexing. I don\'t want to be too close with you.","The goods in Beryl Blue are fragile antiques. Don\'t touch them.","Touch me again, and I shall teach you some good manners.","Not all of my species are like me. Quite a few like to be close to humans.","The body itself does not matter. Your true value lies within your soul.","This child is called Yellow Tea. Don\'t touch him... or you might be hurt.","This is a cup of Pre-Qingming Longjing tea. Not everyone has the chance to drink it. Be grateful as you drink.","I\'m grateful.","I like it. Thank you for your effort.","I have remembered your name.","The tea ceremony is not a hobby but a habit.","Stay quiet to hear the inner voice.","I prefer silence, but I don\'t mind listening to you.","Destiny is like a string that inadvertently binds those who seem unrelated.","When in danger, just hide behind me.","May you have a wonderful New Year... In addition, Beryl Blue will always be open for you.","I have not experienced this kind of festivals. If you don\'t mind insipidity, I can be your company.","Tenpai, not terrible.","No-ten, not a big deal.","Like a phoenix losing its feathers, one after another.","Doesn\'t hurt.","Nothing much to say.","Don\'t fail me.","You look exhilarated, too?","Good day. Sorry to have kept you waiting.","Whenever you\'re ready.","Who\'s hiding over there and slacking off? Who, ah... Huh? I thought it was a student who had skipped class to hide here and sleep. Hmm... Who are you? I haven\'t seen you before. Is this your first time here at the infirmary? I\'m Ayane Kisaragi, the school nurse, and I take care of everyone who comes here. You have to come and see me if you ever feel unwell in the future, okay?","Everyone, a game like mahjong takes a lot of mental energy. Please remember to drink water and have a snack if you need it. Let me know immediately if you feel even a little bit off, okay?","Mwah! Only a kiss given with love is the right way to wake up your lover, got it?","It\'s like roses are in full bloom! It would be great if I could see such a magnificent scene more often in the future!","Here, can you feel my racing heartbeat?","Good morning! It doesn\'t matter when you get up, you can say good morning as long as you\'re waking up for the first time on that day. Only then will you start your day properly, haha.","Zzz... Zzz... Oh... it\'s you. Well, such wonderful moments are the best time for sleeping. Wanna join me? There\'s another bed over there... Don\'t worry, I won\'t tell the others that you\'re slacking off.","Hmm? Why are you staring at Smokey? Could it be... No, I can give you many things, but Smokey isn\'t one of them. As a soft pillow, Smokey is a perfect partner for the beds in the infirmary! However, I heard that my cousin took home a black cat that looks just like Smokey. Let\'s visit them together when we have time. I\'m curious about how similar they look.","Ah! It\'s almost time for the get-together... Hmm? You look like you don\'t want me to go. Or do you want to come with me?","Shush! Let\'s not disturb the lovers over there! So people who are in love really do glow. Speaking of which, I\'ve never been able to fully enjoy the feeling of being in love... *Sigh* I don\'t understand. I\'ve worked hard to pursue love, but why does it always end so quickly? Do you think it\'s because I\'m not charming enough?","Sometimes it\'s not a good thing for a teacher to be too loved by their students because they\'re still kids after all... Huh? What\'s on your mind? At the end of the day, I\'m a proper teacher. There\'s no way I can make a play for my own students. As a school nurse, I need to ensure my students have healthy bodies and minds!","What\'s wrong? You look drowsy, like you didn\'t sleep well. Getting enough sleep is the greatest guarantee of good health, so you have to sleep well. Hmm, let me see... I know, I asked Nadeshiko out to have a drink this weekend. Do you want to come with us? If you gulp down an entire cup, I guarantee you\'ll sleep tight until dawn!","A healthy body is as sweet and alluring as a fruit from the Garden of Eden... Naturally, it won\'t be damaged easily because of its strong healing ability, especially your body. I really love your body because it feels so firm and bouncy to the touch. It is obviously perfect for my experiments... Are you sure you don\'t want to reconsider? The drugs I\'ve developed recently are developed through proper means, have perfect effects, and are completely harmless to the body. All I need is someone to collect data from!","Relax! I\'m just performing an inspection on you. We need to take preventative action often even when we\'re not sick... Lie down over here. I\'m going to start the checkup now. It\'s time for you to witness my true power as a doctor!","Every part of the human body is equivalent to a part of a machine. Although a damaged part can continue to function after it is repaired, if you don\'t take good care of it, it will become increasingly fragile and easier to break. Compared with seeing a doctor when you are sick, it\'s more important for you to take good care of your body. I like your healthy body a lot, so you must take good care of it. It\'s a promise, okay?","Compared with this gift, what I really want is a considerate lover who I can marry... You know?","Are you giving me this to... confess your love for me? No way! Huh? I hope this isn\'t a prank because I\'ll take you seriously.","I used to be a student of Asaha High School too. Of course, it\'s because I liked this school that I decided to come back and become a school nurse here. It\'s so nice that students have such young and healthy bodies. Do you know? No matter how cold a person\'s personality is, their body is still warm.","Ren doesn\'t like to talk to other people? He\'s still so young... Ahhh, I don\'t know whose personality he inherited. My uncle and aunt are both such lively people. This is worrisome. The next time we see him, let\'s take him out to do something that people his age do, like courting the person he likes. It\'s a sin to waste your youth. I\'ll leave this to you then!","Hmm? What do I dislike? ...I wouldn\'t say I dislike them. It\'s more like I\'m not good at dealing with them... Just like how the bones of the human body contain cartilage, everyone has something they can\'t handle. My finger was scratched by a spindle when I was young, and I bled a lot at that time. Haha! I was so young and ignorant that I thought I was going to die! Well, I have a little trauma from that incident. Fortunately, there are almost no more spindles in modern cities... If you\'re interested, I can take you to my hometown and show you.","So Hana has been pestering you to play mahjong lately? That\'s quite surprising since I originally recommended mahjong to her because she seemed a bit lonely. She\'s obviously at the age where she should be learning about love... To think she would be so obsessed with mahjong... How strange. Is mahjong more attractive than the temptation of love?","I really want to date someone... I really want to date someone... I really want to date someone... Why am I the only one who is still single? Ah! When did you get here? Did you hear... Whatever, it\'s the truth anyway. If you heard me, then so be it. I vowed to get married before the age of 30... and I\'m getting close... Oh well, I need to get out there and meet more people! Yes, you can do it, Ayane!","Am I officially no longer single from today onward? I feel like I\'m dreaming! I want to make sure just in case. Are you really willing to have a romantic relationship with me with the intention to get married? From now on, is it okay if your body gets messed up by my passionate love? Oh, don\'t worry—I won\'t do any crazy experiments on you because your body is also part of my life from now on.","Happy New Year! I\'m absolutely delighted to step into the new year together with you! Why don\'t we spend the whole day together and do everything together! What? You\'re not objecting to my suggestion? I already thought of how I\'ll act coquettishly and badger you until you agree to spend the day with me, but you aren\'t giving me a chance to do it. But, uh... I guess this is good too. I find it cute how you\'re being so obedient to me.","Honey, Happy Valentine\'s Day! I really like seeing you working so hard for me. It makes me feel really loved, so I also want to do my best for you... This box of chocolate is proof of my effort today. Although they\'re shaped like pills, I promise they\'re chocolate!","Lots of Dora","Tenpai—Nice! It\'s love at first sight.","No-ten... The treatment didn\'t work...","Remember, you must not use medicines that have expired. They should be recycled as hazardous waste like this.","Eh?! I think I took the wrong medicine!","It\'ll be okay. Even a prince has to overcome many obstacles to find the sleeping princess, right?","Oh no! Here comes the second-worst emotion I\'m bad at dealing with... Eh? You want to know what\'s worst? ...Well, the feeling you experience when you\'re waiting for a reply after confessing your love to a person you like, of course.","My heart rate is 112, 115, 117... My heart is beating so fast. Do you know? The last time my heart beat so irregularly was when we confirmed our relationship. I\'ll never forget that moment.","Hello everyone! Phew, glad I made it in time. I can\'t believe we\'re playing mahjong at a mixer! If I win, one of you owes me an intro to a cute and considerate guy, okay?","Bandages, iodine, cotton, anti-inflammatory drugs... OK! I\'ve finished inspecting the first aid kit. I\'m ready for exciting activities at any time now.","Whoa!!! Get out of the way! ...Phew, that was close! Bex\'s shell is made out of pure stainless steel, so it\'ll be bad if someone gets hit... Are you new here? I\'m Mirai—yes—the same Mirai that means \"future\" in \"bright future\". It\'s an urgent situation, and I\'m in a hurry. If you have any questions later, come find me in the Research Society! Bye!","Everyone, let us enter the world of scientific mahjong together! Although we can\'t ask for help during a game, we can get together and discuss today\'s log after the game ends to find ways to improve!","Although there are infinite possibilities in the world of mahjong, you can almost always make the best move in every hand if you calculate everything carefully.","Yes! See? I told you the game will end in our victory!","Okay, the data has been saved. This log will be invaluable for my research on scientific mahjong!","Hello, what a coincidence! The direction you\'re going... There\'s only the library and the Research Society over there. Are you here to see me? I\'m free today, so just tell me if you need my help with anything!","Ahaha, if I said this is a coincidence, you would... believe me, right? Actually, it\'s because... the research and development of a new item have been completed today, and... I need someone to help me with my experiments, which is why I\'ve come to ask you... Will you help me?","The topic of love... is slightly difficult. I haven\'t conducted any research on it... but don\'t be discouraged. I\'ll work hard, and I\'ll definitely invent a compatible love partner for you one day!","The mahjong club wanted all the newcomers to be able to practice independently, so I made mahjong tables equipped with an AI battle system for them. Something seems to be wrong with the setup now. Do you want to come with me to take a look? I heard the newcomers are feeling devastated during training because the AI is too strong... Maybe I shouldn\'t have set it according to Yui\'s match data... Who should we use as a benchmark instead...?","Ah! You got me... Haha, I wanted to secretly give you a fright, but you noticed me so quickly. It must be because Bex\'s clicking noises are too noisy. I\'ve got to make it a little quieter.","Inventions are a type of scientific progress, and there is no such thing as a good or bad invention because it really depends on who is using an invention for what purpose. That\'s why I never reject the seemingly strange invention requests of my classmates. Don\'t you think it would be great if I can enrich their lives at university with some minor technological means?","Human technology is developing faster and faster, but I still like to take Bex with me to repair some old machinery with my own hands. The gnashing sound of gears, the roaring of engines, and the friction sounds of tires are the sounds of machines trying to communicate with the world and us. I love that a lot.","Uwah! You can\'t go in here! Absolutely not! Ah... you saw everything...! S-So what? Can\'t a beautiful girl who is busy studying the world forget to tidy the things in her room?! Since you\'ve learned this secret, hehehe... let me find my hammer of amnesia... Don\'t even think of running away!","Let\'s go to the library together tomorrow! Huh? What will we do there? Study, of course! Let\'s swim together in the sea of knowledge! What else can we do at the library? Oh, I see... why don\'t we ask Akechi? He should know since he\'s at the library every day...","The idea that all science students are bald is a preconception! Yes, definitely! True knowledge comes from practice, so I\'ll let you touch my hair... See? My hair is thick and healthy!","Thanks, but I think you can do a little more reasonable research on me.","Please keep it a secret that a science girl in the Research Society likes doujinshi! But... I am really happy! I\'ll keep it here with Bex and enjoy it with all my heart!","An eye mask that can be worn in class to pretend to be awake? An electric frog that can automatically screen the answers to multiple-choice questions... You want to know where you can buy these items? Um... I don\'t find these inventions to be strange, just that the descriptions look very familiar to me. If I\'m not wrong, my seniors in the Research Society are selling unused inventions in the activity room... How should I put this... After all, in a sense, our Research Society is actually rather poor, and it would be good if we could earn some funds with our old inventions.","The gear in the corner? Yes, I designed it for Shinomiya. Yes, the same Shinomiya who has another amazing identity... To match his other identity, I added some convenient designs to this suit, such as the airbags on the shoulders, which can reduce the impact force when falling from a high place, and wheels on both sides of the shoe soles, which can be lowered to transform the shoes into roller skates to allow him to quickly and conveniently leave the scene of an incident... But I still need to keep improving these features because Shinomiya ruthlessly rejected it. No matter what, I will definitely upgrade it until it\'s perfect and Shinomiya can no longer say NO to it!","What\'s my type? Uhhh... I find talented beauties like Yui to be irresistible, haha! But humans keep changing and they never know until someone who makes them think \"This is the one!\" appears in front of them. I don\'t think anyone can accurately predict the type of person they will like in the future. After all, this is currently one of the most controversial topics in the scientific community.","Since I\'ve run into you in the Research Society, does this mean you\'ve finally decided to join us?! Although I want to refute my seniors\' statement that this is a \"country with absolute freedom,\" I can\'t deny that we do have a lot of freedom here. You can study modern technology or ancient magic, human body structure, or even Cthulhu culture... If you like to explore and make discoveries, the Research Society is the most suitable club for you.","Do you think I\'m dressed too plainly for a young woman of my age? I tried wearing a beautiful long skirt before, but it always got in my way. In the end, I still think it\'s more convenient to wear simple and plain work clothes... Ah! I\'m not saying I want to wear a skirt or anything. I just suddenly felt like discussing this topic with you... Um, yeah, just like how scientific inspiration always pops up during ordinary everyday conversations... Seriously!","\"Future\" is my favorite word because anything can happen in this timeline. I often think if it\'s wrong to wonder \"what the future will look like.\" To researchers like us, it\'s more accurate for us to ask \"what should the future look like?\"... Now that you\'re walking next to me on the same path, I feel like the future is filled with even more possibilities. I\'m so happy!","Do you see this beauty over here? To present you with the most amazing fireworks show in history, everyone in the Research Society has worked hard for two months. We call this masterpiece Athena, and she represents the Research Society\'s beautiful vision for the new year! Tonight\'s New Year\'s Eve fireworks have been loaded. I\'ll entrust you with the glorious mission to set it off. Don\'t be afraid! Let\'s embrace the future bravely!","Happy Valentine\'s Day! So? How\'s your harvest today...? WOW! You have so much chocolate! Are you thinking of becoming everyone\'s Valentine in One Han City? In that case, instead of letting everyone give chocolate to you, why don\'t I give you a fully-automatic chocolate-making machine? It\'ll make it so convenient to give chocolates back to everyone on White Day. As for its name... Why don\'t we call it \"Love Factory\"? Just talking about it is making me eager to start! Let\'s go to the Research Society now and work hard to give everyone more love!","Tenpai! The gears fit perfectly!","No-ten... I made a mistake in my calculations!","Eh? Hmm... According to my calculations, losing these tiles shouldn\'t have too much of an impact...","Oh... This sparkling looks like a new power source...","W-Wait! Let me activate my emergency readiness state...","Relax! I\'ve checked this hand countless times before. This is a safe and effective move!","This hand is a combination of my match experience over the last month and quick mental calculations. You can do it, Mirai! This match is yours!","I\'m sorry! The teacher didn\'t end the class on time... I\'m not late, am I? Well then, let\'s have a great game!","I\'m fully recharged! Ready to go at any time!","Double Riichi","Kita. Don\'t mind me. Keep playing.","I win! Now hand over your Knightmare to me!","Tsumo, thanks for the win!","Hello. My name is Lelouch Lamperouge, nice to meet you.","So my opponent is a Jyanshi...? How interesting. If I consider the time it\'ll take me to return, I\'ll finish the match in 9 minutes.","In the name of Lelouch vi Britannia, I command you: Obey me, world!","Burn your bridges and then over the precipice... Classical strategies remain effective ones, don\'t they?","It seems using my Geass on you... would be a waste of its power.","You\'re here? What are your plans for today?","You\'re such a naive person. It usually takes a long time to become friends who can open their hearts to each other, but you already trust me so much after spending such a short time with me. Other than you being so pure, I can\'t think of any reason that explains this. That being said, I don\'t dislike people like you.","Asaha High School? I heard the president there is just like President Milly of Ashford Academy and likes to plan special events like the Gender Role Reversal Festival or Elementary School Students\' Days. But surely there aren\'t events like \"making the world\'s largest pizza\" during the School Festival there, right?","Hmm... the result exceeds my expectations. Although I won, I need to make more careful calculations. Considering the probability issue, I better ask Nina to give me some extra lessons after I return to my original world.","Nunnally is overjoyed that she can meet with Suzaku again and play like they used to when we were children. Hmm? Me? ... Suzaku is... Although is not the same as he used to be, he has always been my most trusted friend.","Is this a model? It\'s quite delicately made. Hmm... It feels somewhat similar to a Knightmare Frame, a humanoid mobile weapon that is used widely in my original world.","Have you seen C.C. around? Did Ichihime take her out to the food alley again? She\'s adapted to this new world so quickly and is always searching for delicious food. I\'m envious of how easy everything seems for her. But then again, I\'m more at ease seeing that C.C. is the same as always.","When Nunnally and I first met Suzaku, it was also in a shrine like Mahjong Soul Shrine. Back then, Suzaku and I always got into arguments. Unlike how he is now, he was quite rough back then, which is why we were always at odds with each other. It didn\'t take long for me to realize that he was just so upright that it made him seem stupid. He then became my first friend.","You can see all of One Han City from here. Yet... Why did we come to this world? There should be a reason for this...","There are many people who live the right way but still can\'t survive in the world. After all, the world is not so gentle. Therefore, I\'m willing to embark on the path of rebellion to create a gentle world.","A gift? A group of people I don\'t know stuffed a bunch of albums into my hands just then. What are these things? If you know them, I\'m sorry, but please return these items to them for me.","Food that I like? Well, if I had to pick one, I would choose chocolate because it is very nutritious and has a relaxing effect. It can give me a boost after I\'ve done some brainstorming.","It feels a little unbelievable that I\'m strolling through unfamiliar streets like this. In my original world, my sister and I lived a reclusive life... so I can only wander around at ease in a place like this where no one knows me.","Since that day, I\'ve lived a lie. The lie of living. My name, too, a lie. My personal history, a lie. Nothing but lies. I was sick to death of a world that couldn\'t be changed. But even in my lies, I couldn\'t give up in despair.","Hmm? Sorry, I was thinking about something... When I was drinking coffee with C.C. in that cafe called Éternité, the young manager there reminded me of my little sister who was left in the world I\'m from. My little sister can\'t move freely due to a physical disability, so I\'m very worried about her... Nunnally...","My little sister Nunnally was involved in an incident when she was a child, resulting in her becoming blind and unable to walk freely with her legs. The world I\'m from isn\'t a world where my sister could live happily with such disabilities. So I...","My only wish is to create a world in which my little sister Nunnally can live peacefully and happily. To achieve that, I won\'t hesitate to destroy the world.","I\'m not going to lose to this power. I\'m going to control it and make use of it. And I\'m going to try and change this cruel world. I\'ll try and fulfill both your wish and my own, I promise. It\'s a contract, from me to you.","Happy New Year. Have you already set your goals for the new year? My goal is the same as always—to create a world in which Nunnally can live happily. That takes precedence over everything.","Valentine\'s Day. In Britannia, it was a celebration of true love between lovers, but in Area 11, it became a holiday for women to give men chocolates and was really popular among the students of Ashford. So many troubles happened because of this...","Lots of Dora","Tenpai. Keep moving forward fearlessly!","No-ten. Hmm... Did someone figure out my intentions? How outstanding.","Four-Wind Discarded. Interesting, is everyone working together?","A Four-Kan Abortion? So this is what happens.","Four-Player Riichi. Come, drown in misery with me!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. What an unbelievable hand... Then there\'s no other way.","Win or lose, you won\'t gain anything unless you give everything for it.","Why? ...It\'s very simple. If the king doesn\'t lead, how can he expect his subordinates to follow?","I never thought you would be this strong as my enemies, but I won\'t be defeated so easily.","You need to be prepared to see this through to the end. After all, this is a game in which we bet on our wishes. Come, let\'s end this exciting game.","Now then, the enemies have five options. I hope they won\'t choose the stupidest move.","Oh? You want to play a game with me? ...Sure. I was just thinking of playing with someone stronger. Try to make this enjoyable for me.","I have to remember that. The most vital element in battle is the human one.","I am C.C., nothing more, nothing less.","Let\'s start.","Survival of the fittest is the most essential rule of all.","This is the end.","Ah, if it\'s him, he\'ll definitely say: \"Checkmate.\"","You are here.","Oh, it\'s you? You\'re just in time. Come and take a walk with me.","Who am I? You don\'t need to know.","Do I have to answer every question someone asks me? Sorry, I don\'t want to answer it and have no intention of answering it.","Let\'s have pizza if you don\'t know what to eat. I just happen to have a points card here.","That fortune teller called Kaavi said a \"witch\" comes here to play mahjong from time to time. I wonder what the witches are like in this world...","Whichever world you\'re in, there are always people who cling to their useless dignity, even though they can choose a more relaxed lifestyle.","Lelouch? Our relationship involves a promise he made for the future—for a future to fulfill the contract...","If I win the tournament at Mahjong Soul Shrine, will it be possible for me to get all the pizzas in the world? I\'m interested now! I\'ll get a little more serious then.","Lelouch will make my wish come true, but for that to happen, I must first fulfill his wish to return to his original world and create a gentle world.","You want to give me a gift? You\'re such a whimsical person.","A gift? I\'ll consider it if it\'s a pizza.","It all started when I was captured by Britania. If I was unlucky, I would\'ve become their test subject.","I was captured by Clovis, Lelouch\'s half-brother, who concealed my existence from his homeland.","The resistance mistakenly thought I was a weapon since I was kept top secret, so they took me away from Britannia. This was my opportunity to meet Lelouch.","Britannia didn\'t hesitate to sacrifice the lives of many people to take me back. Meanwhile, Lelouch put his life on the line to protect me, so I gave him power.","I gave Lelouch power—a power called Geass that would allow him to keep living. This was the start of his rebellion.","If you enter this contract, you will live in the world of humans, but you will live unlike any other human. A different providence, a different time, a different life. The power of the king will isolate you. If you are prepared for it...","Happy New Year! Although it\'s a little clichéd, it\'s quite nice to greet you and chat with you like this in the new year.","Chocolate? Ah, speaking of which, I think a new chocolate-flavored pizza is now available. I need to buy some.","Tenpai...","No-ten, and it was so close.","Four-Wind Discarded... This must be a coincidence.","It\'s a Four-Kan Abortion.","Four-Player Riichi.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. It\'s... not a pity, really.","Ah, it\'s the same one again...","That isn\'t necessary.","Should I Tenpai? Or should I...","I\'ve got a full hand. That\'s good news... Now I just need to keep moving forward.","Oh... This hand is becoming quite interesting...","Is everyone here?","We can begin now.","Kita. Luck is on my side.","Ron. Prepare yourself!","Tsumo. Thanks.","My name is Suzaku Kururugi, a member of the disciplinary committee in Ashford Academy\'s Student Council, glad to meet you.","If a fight is unavoidable, then I\'ll give it everything I\'ve got!","Good! I can do this! With this Lancelot, I can stop this all at once!","There\'s no future using your methods.","Your methods won\'t change anything! Are you so set on pursuing your goals you don\'t see you\'re hurting other people?!","Oh, you\'re here. Nice to meet you again.","Hi, how are you feeling today? Why don\'t we do some stamina training before we start playing? Your mind will be more agile if you get the right amount of exercise.","You want to know if I\'m a soldier or a knight? No, I\'m a soldier, a knight, and a student... It\'s a little difficult to explain.","Speaking of which, many skilled Jyanshis have gathered at the mahjong dojo today, and even Lelouch is enjoying himself. Although he usually looks very calm, he\'s actually the type who gets excited when he\'s up against a strong opponent.","One thing that playing mahjong and living in this society have in common is that you must follow the rules. Winning is worthless if the means to it are wrong!","Who is that girl called C.C.? She protected Zero before, so I thought she is Zero\'s companion, and I know nothing about her. And now she\'s not surprised at all about coming to this world. It\'s truly astonishing.","Excuse me, can you give this medicine to Zechs? I think I hurt him when we were practicing just then. I don\'t think he would take it if I offer it to him, but he should take it if it\'s you.","Euphy has always been able to surprise me. She surprised me when we first met, when she announced she\'s a princess, when she decided I shall go to school, and when she made me her knight. However, she always manages to enlighten me when she surprises me, so I\'m very grateful to her.","Both Lelouch and I have changed a lot over these seven years. He said I have become more reliable, and I think he has become less approachable. However, this change is necessary so that he can still live with his sister Nunnally.","There\'s also a pond like this around the Kururugi Shrine, and I used to go lobster fishing there. Have you tried it before? You tie up a frog\'s legs like this... Ah, I miss it so much. I know, if you haven\'t tried this before, do you want to try lobster fishing at the pond of Mahjong Soul Shrine?","Is this gift for me? Thank you! I\'ll cherish it.","Is this for me? Thanks, but I don\'t really have anything to give back to you. Can you tell me what you like or are interested in?","There\'s one thing I know. What do results gained the wrong way leave you in the end? Just regret and an emptiness that has nowhere to go.","I\'ve made a mistake before. I used the wrong method to end the sudden war with Britannia. I\'ve always regretted this.","I became an honorary Britannian and joined the Britannian army. That made me a complete traitor, especially to those who knew whose son I was. However, this is a rule I set for myself. It is a rule I must follow because of what I\'ve done.","It may be worthless to be loyal to Britannia, which invades other countries by force, but that\'s exactly why I want to turn it into a country worthy of my allegiance from within. I joined the army with this idea in mind and met her, someone who has the same idea as me and has become the most important person to me...","As a princess of Britannia, Euphy longs for a gentle world. I must return to my own world for her and move forward with her.","I promise you. This time I\'ll use the right methods to make my wishes come true. Although I hate myself, Euphy approves of me and even said she loves me. I want to make my wish come true for her!","Happy New Year. I believe this year will be an amazing year since I managed to meet you on the first day of the new year. Do you want to go to the shrine with me? I haven\'t done a New Year\'s first visit since Britannia occupied my country seven years ago... What do you say?","Is this chocolate for me? Oh right, it\'s Valentine\'s Day today. Thank you, I\'ll cherish this. By the way, are you free tonight? In return for the chocolate, I want to walk around One Han City with you.","Tenpai. I\'ve discarded all my weaknesses.","No-ten... How did they predict my actions?","Four-Wind Discarded. Is this even possible?","Four-Kan Abortion. It feels like a shame.","Four-Player Riichi. A frontal attack is indeed effective.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. This hand... feels a little dangerous for some reason.","Things aren\'t looking good...","You need to act to get results.","Although I don\'t really understand it myself, if you don\'t persist till the end, all your efforts will go to waste.","I have to do this. I think I can stop them with the Lancelot. That\'s why I!","If me and Lancelot are needed right now, then I\'ll do it!","I\'m Suzaku Kururugi. It\'s a pleasure to meet you.","Lancelot, M.E. boost!","Riichi","Greetings, I am Kallen Stadtfeld, a student of Ashford Academy... Oh forget it, call me Kallen Kouzuki instead, pleased to meet you.","Let\'s learn from each other. I\'m not thinking of going easy on you, so show me everything you\'ve got!","This is the strength of Kallen Kouzuki, captain of the Zero Squad!","It worked!","With this hand, I shall seize victory for the Black Knights... for Zero!","Ah, there you are. Please guide me again today.","I don\'t have any special plans for today. I don\'t have any student council matters to deal with or Black Knights training to participate in after coming to this world, so I have a lot of free time. If you don\'t mind, can you keep me company to pass the time?","Good day. The weather is so good today... Argh!!! I\'m so annoyed! I shouldn\'t have said I was sick to be absent today!","Although I was reluctantly dragged into the student council by President Milly, if I\'m honest with myself, I find it quite interesting, which was unexpected. I guess I would feel a little sad if the school disappears... Because of this, I can understand why President Ishihara wants to enjoy the student council\'s activities to the fullest.","Are Kaguyahime\'s bunny ears real? But I remember seeing human ears inside her hair... ARGH! I\'m so curious about it. I should just ask her directly!","Suzaku\'s actions won\'t be able to save our country. It\'s good that he could find a way into the organization, but there are many weak people who can\'t and will only be trampled on by others. I need to find a way for these people to survive!","Um... I don\'t think I\'m any good at playing mahjong. I rely solely on my instinct and suck at reading other people\'s actions.","I don\'t particularly like Lelouch. Although he looks good, I feel he is playing critic as he views the world from the side. I originally thought he was a decent person.","Suzaku\'s words just sound good. I disagree with him about not resisting and accepting the status quo of Britannia\'s occupation as peace. If he insists on this, I will fight him to the end and kill him one day.","Zero\'s true identity isn\'t important. As the leader of the Order of the Black Knights, he is very capable and has been evenly matched with Britannia several times. He deserves our unconditional trust even if we don\'t know his true identity.","You don\'t need to give me a gift for something so minor. Thank you anyway.","It\'s my turn to get you something next time. I like to keep things even, so can you tell me what you like?","I\'m actually of mixed blood, born to a Britannian nobleman and his maid. The reason I have the identity of a Britannian is that the Stadtfeld family has no heirs.","My older brother fought to take back our homeland that has been invaded by Britannia... and he went MIA in combat. After that, I decided to inherit his will and continue fighting against Britannia.","I know I can live as a member of the upper class by choosing the Stadtfeld name, but I can\'t ignore everything that is happening in front of me!","I hated my mother and thought she was a weak woman who was reliant on a man, but I was wrong. She has been watching over me and is always willing to be by my side no matter how much pain she\'s in.","My wish is to take back my homeland that has been invaded by Britannia. It seems possible thanks to Zero, so I want to return to my original world.","The world\'s wrong and I\'m trying to change it. If I don\'t do this... If I don\'t, my brother will never rest in peace. That\'s why I\'ll fight to the end and do whatever it takes to win!","Happy New Year. I was just about to visit the shrine. Would you like to come with me? Before Britannia invaded, we used to visit the shrine near home as a family for our first visit to a shrine in the new year. I was still very young at that time, and my older brother led me everywhere...","Shirley said it\'s better to give out handmade chocolates on Valentine\'s Day. I\'m sorry, but that has nothing to do with me now because I have more important things to do.","I\'m going to Tenpai.","No... No-ten.","Four-Wind Discarded. Is this part of the strategy?","A Four-Kan Abortion?","Four-Player Riichi. It\'s nothing special.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. It\'s time to play more carefully.","Geez... I got the same thing again.","I already discarded this once.","There aren\'t many tiles left...","This attack will decide the winner!","With this Guren Mk-II, my counterattack begins!","Oh? Is someone already here?","I can start at any time.","Ninpo, Riichi technique!","Ninpo, Double Riichi technique!","Chii.","Pon.","Kan.","Ninpo! Kita technique!","Ron! Ninpo, point looting technique!","Tsumo! Ninpo, creating from nothingness technique!","I am Ransei. Please forgive me for visiting you so suddenly in the middle of the night! So, the situation is... When I was watching your mahjong game today, I was impressed by your skills and decided to become your disciple to learn your mahjong skills. As I rushed over immediately after receiving the approval of my elders, I didn\'t notice how late it is. However... Please accept me as your disciple, Master!","Master, is today\'s assignment to defeat all these opponents? I understand. You can sit back and relax because it won\'t take me long!","Master, am I worthy of learning your unfathomable mahjong skills now? If I am, please teach me more techniques...!","Although this isn\'t my favorite hand, if mastering it will win your praise, I will do my best to improve!","Master, please check the progress I\'ve made from today\'s training!","Master! Have you summoned me so urgently for a mission?","I\'ve completed today\'s homework. Master, do you want to check the records of the mahjong games I just played?","Master, I\'ve investigated that man called A-37 who has been coming here recently... He is super suspicious. Not much information can be found about him in One Han City, and there\'s a murderous aura around him... It almost feels like he can win 20 consecutive Hanchan matches... Master, should I eliminate this threat as soon as possible?","The most important thing in mahjong... Could it be smoke bombs and flash grenades? I watched some mahjong works recently on the recommendation of my classmates. Whenever they have a Yakuman, the scene will be filled with smoke and flashing lights... Master! Smoke grenades are my forte, and I can learn how to use the flashing light technique immediately. Let\'s get some live practice in the dojo now!","Transformation ninjutsu is one of my strengths. A stunning beauty, office lady, rebellious teen... I can transform into whatever you want me to instantly, Master... But if you want me to transform into a muscular man, you might need to give me some time to prepare.","I don\'t understand why the vice president suddenly added kunai to the list of prohibited items... A ninja without a kunai is like One Han City without mahjong! It looks like the only way to prevent my kunai from being confiscated is to escape the vice president\'s surveillance and sneak in from the back wall of the school...","I\'m improving so quickly after starting your special mahjong training program, Master! I\'ll become the best mahjong player among all ninjas and the best ninjutsu user among all Jyanshi... In other words... I will become the strongest mahjong ninja! Master, please look forward to that day!","Revolving... M-Master?! When did you come? Is your knee still okay...? I don\'t know why my kunai always hurts other people\'s knees, which is why my father always reminded me to practice in a place where no one else is around. I didn\'t expect you to come here... Please let me take care of you until you recover from your injuries!","My favorite hand is Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans. My reason is... Master, please copy what I\'m doing. Stand with your legs shoulder-width apart like this, relax and inhale, feel your ribs open, bulge out your waist, and tighten your abdomen slightly. Now, say \"Secret Technique: Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans\" out loud! How does that feel? Can you feel how amazing it is?","The vice president\'s \"problem children\" list?! Did you see it too...? I don\'t understand why I\'m on the list. I\'ve always been the top student of my year. After all, diligence is the nature of a ninja, and I can\'t let my ninjutsu or studies fall behind. What\'s more, studying is much easier than training in the mountains.","Master, I\'m worried about the gift you gave me so suddenly. Are you about to implement the stick-and-carrot teaching approach?!","Although I love ramen, from now on, my favorite food is the cookies Master gives me!","Eliisa is actually very talented in ninjutsu, and the ninja pet she carries with her is the best proof of this. In my hometown, most people train a ninja pet to be their partner, but... I\'ve never been good with small animals since I was a child... That being said, Master, you don\'t need to worry because I\'m still an excellent ninja even if I don\'t have a ninja pet!","Ninjas rely on ninjutsu to survive, so they rarely show others their techniques... But I have nothing to hide from you, Master. After all, it\'s only fair to exchange my secret techniques with you if I want to learn your secret skills.","After three months of practice, I learned that there\'s some sort of magnetic attraction between a human knee and a kunai that has been thrown... However, someone powerful like you can overcome this magnetic force. You\'re so amazing!","Master, when will you teach me the secrets of winning with Thirteen Orphans? Is the reason you haven\'t taught it to me because... my aptitude is so poor that you don\'t approve of me?! If that\'s the case, I might need to go on a long training journey and return only when I\'m strong enough to learn your secret techniques, Master!","In principle, ninjas shouldn\'t get too deeply involved with anyone. However, ever since I started learning mahjong from you, Master, there are more and more people who claim to be my friends around me. If I form any bonds with them, it will be very difficult to break them later, and I\'ve been quite distressed by this recently... What do you think I should do, Master? Eh? Master, how can you possibly become my friend? You\'re the person I respect most in this world besides my father!","Master, what does this contract mean...? Are you entrusting yourself and your secret skills to me from now on?! I haven\'t studied any ninjutsu related to living humans before, but I will do my best to respond to your trust... Huh? You mean you aren\'t entrusting your body to me...? I-I see! Although I\'m a little sad that I haven\'t received your full trust, I\'ll give everything I have to my training in the future!","Master, I wish you a happy new year. This is a New Year gift I prepared especially for you. Now, let me bow down to you as your disciple... Eh? W-Was that too formal? But Master, etiquette is important! Especially the New Year\'s Day blessings because the gods will only hear them and make them come true if they are solemn and pious enough. I\'ll follow you around today to remind you about various things.","Valentine\'s Day is a celebration for lovers... Master, are you really willing to eat this chocolate I bought from the ninja village? Umm... Well, there won\'t be anything weird in it, just some hallucinogenic mushrooms, sleeping herbs, etc. But I can reassure you that it won\'t be fatal. After all, in the world of ninjas, only love that can be tested can be trusted. So, Master, if you want...!","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Secret Technique: Thirteen Orphans!","Secret Technique: Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans!","Tenpai. Just in time!","No-ten... Did I disappoint you...?","Master, you have nothing to worry about as this is just a simple makibishi.","Ninjas sometimes discard things as bait to numb their enemies. I\'m discarding this Dora for the same reason.","The most important thing for a ninja isn\'t how much ninjutsu they have mastered but their patience. You don\'t need to worry, Master, for I won\'t give up until no tiles are left.","Secret skill! Face the wind!","I need to win with this big hand because I\'m going to become the strongest mahjong ninja!","I\'m Ransei. Please enlighten me.","I\'m just a ninja – a ninja who is always ready for battle.","Riichi","Double Riichi","Chii","Pon","Kan","Kita","Ron","Tsumo","Um... Hi... I\'m going to go now if that\'s all for today.","I have plum-flavored throat lozenges. Would you like one? We\'ll be playing a game that requires a lot of brain power later.","Sorry... but my relationship with everyone here is like that of a firewall and a virus. I either invade or get killed, so I\'ve just chosen to protect myself.","I\'d really like to go home after this... What, I have to win first? ...Fine. Let\'s just get this over with then. What a pain...","Ugh... Someone is going to question me about whether I hacked the system again...","I\'ve met the minimum attendance requirement for this month... That means I don\'t need to go to school anymore.","Can I request to play games at home today? No, I don\'t want to go out or go to the dojo or other places. Playing mahjong with my relatives at home just now has exhausted all my energy...","What\'s wrong with being a shut-in? You don\'t get inconvenienced by others and don\'t inconvenience others. This environmentally friendly way of living is the best.","Being popular? What a terrible curse that is... I\'ll pass. For me, the scariest curse in this school is to be conspicuous like the president that everyone asks you questions wherever you go... What a pain...","Isn\'t it normal for a guy\'s mobile phone to have games filled with beautiful girls in them? This type of love is accessible to anyone who pays for it and doesn\'t require any communication or handling of emotional disputes... What\'s wrong with that? I just like fictional characters. You don\'t need to look at me like I\'m scum...","Lunch... I just need an egg sandwich, which is both nutritious and convenient... I don\'t like bento boxes because they seem like a pain... Naturally, the same applies in the case of people who are a pain...","A program that has a bug can be fixed with a patch, but a crack in a relationship between people is difficult to repair. That\'s why I hate socializing—you never know when a crack will appear...","I am quite a geek, but please don\'t treat me like a child who doesn\'t know much about the world... At least I\'m the same as other healthy male high school students in terms of common sense. So if you keep poking me here, you need to think carefully about what will happen next and what responsibility you\'ll need to take...","Are you sure you want to take action with me? No, I have nothing against you, I just think that things get more difficult when you have teammates...","When going on a date... it\'s better to go to a place with fewer people so it\'ll be more convenient if you want to do something you don\'t want others to know about... Huh? That\'s not your intention?","It looks like... I can\'t say no... Anyway, thank you...","Well... If you haven\'t cleared the game yet, why don\'t we play together tomorrow... Also, this present isn\'t troublesome at all. Thank you.","Sorry, I\'m an absolute egoist, so please don\'t expect anything from me... In my opinion, things such as kindness and charity are like Wi-Fi connections without passwords. Eventually, they won\'t be able to provide an effective network speed at a critical moment because there are too many users.","Oh... It isn\'t really necessary to hide the fact that I\'m the hacker ICE. I just don\'t want to deal with the boring curiosity of the people around me. Can you keep this a secret for me?","Humans can\'t survive alone because families, schools, and even societies are made up of gatherings of people. However, this doesn\'t mean you can\'t choose a lifestyle with minimal contact and communication with others to avoid as much trouble as possible.","The Youth Cup Mahjong Competition? The vice president must have told you... That guy knows all the secrets in this school, what a terrifying and awe-inspiring person... There\'s nothing to explain. The venue is just too far away from home, so I discarded my winning tiles in the prelim...","The Internet is so good. By eliminating the awkwardness of meeting people face-to-face, it naturally shortens the distance between people, even for people who pass by every day and who we otherwise won\'t even notice. Taking us as an example, if you just happened to meet me on a road somewhere, you probably wouldn\'t take any notice of me.","Will you be angry if I tell you now that I\'ve never regarded you as my friend? No, you should be angry, because I also realized that it\'s wrong of me to lie to you. So... I\'m sorry. I only thought that you were a pain at the beginning, and even until now... You can hit me or scold me if you\'re angry, but I hope you\'ll remain by my side and keep annoying me and only me.","Happy New Year. Eh... What\'s my wish for this year? There\'s nothing I really want. I just want to continue living peacefully like this... So please choose places where no one goes to for our New Year\'s date... Um, I\'m not saying that because I want to do anything special. I just don\'t want to deal with unrelated people... Eh? Um... If you want me to do something for you, please consider this proposal carefully.","There\'s still a little time before the movie starts, so why don\'t we get some popcorn... Oh, this? The president forced me to take it when I left the school just now. I heard that the new members of the pastry club have been doing too many team-building activities... Do you want to try some? Hey, you should know it\'s Valentine\'s Day today, right? What are you thinking by deliberately eating chocolate made by another person in front of me? ...Am I jealous? Is this strange? Isn\'t this a normal reaction? You should be surprised if I\'m not jealous... Um, what\'s so funny...?","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Thirteen Orphans","Tenpai. I\'ve finally released the patch...","No-ten. I got a bad ending...","I guess I really should have considered it more carefully...","Which line of code is responsible for this loophole...","What a long match... What a pain...","I\'ve already done everything I can do. Now... Let\'s take a gamble. On what you ask? Who will play the tile I want, of course. Who should I gamble on?","It\'s useless to pray to the gods. After all, they might not know how to use a computer. Why not pray to me instead? That might be more useful.","I just arrived... Don\'t mind me...","Ready now.","Ron. It\'s my honor.","Tsumo. I\'ll take this one first.","Nice to meet you. I\'m Kurone Toujou, the manager of Countless Springs. We\'ve prepared refreshments and seat. Will Countless Springs have the honor of serving you as a regular customer?","I don\'t really care about winning or losing. Countless Springs exists for everyone to have fun, so forget all your worries.","So-called miracles are nothing more than bright red flowers that struggle to bloom in the darkness that is boundless despair.","Please, think nothing of it. It was just a spur-of-the-moment creation, not something to be taken seriously.","I have no intention to stop any of you from winning, but it\'s time for this game to end.","Have you come here today for a game or some other important matters?","I guessed that you had come when I saw how excited these children were. I\'ve been waiting for you for a long time.","A few days ago, a naughty child sneaked out to play again and is with a young person right now. Can you find it for me when you have time? By the way, that child is black all over.","Although a person\'s appearance isn\'t the main thing you should use to judge someone, it helps to wear clothes that suit you. Why don\'t I help you choose your accessories today?","The girls here mostly have no home to return to, but you don\'t need to pity them because they have turned this place into their real home with their enthusiasm and love. Of course, if you wish, this can be your home too.","Ciri? Is that the well-known animal tamer of One Han City? Surely you\'re joking. How could someone like me possibly have anything to do with her? She probably came to Countless Springs to search for someone else... Oh, who could that be? Could she have come to see you?","Countless Springs does operate a mahjong dojo under its name, but its main purpose is to train Jyanshi than to make money from customers... You should have already visited three other similar dojos right? You don\'t need to get nervous. I\'ve just heard that the other three Greats have a high opinion of you. I presume that you\'re also a guest of honor at the dojos they manage.","I went out at the east gate, where there were as many beauties as the clouds. Although there were as many of them as the clouds, it is not on them that my thoughts rest.","You seem a little absent-minded, like there\'s something on your mind. If you are willing, why don\'t you share your troubles with me today?","As you can see, the whole street below us is filled with businesses run by Countless Springs. It\'s impossible for me to intervene in everything even if I\'m the manager here... What\'s more, all my thoughts are on you right now, and you\'re someone who I just can\'t stop worrying about.","The best present you can give me is by gracing my establishment.","In my position, I shouldn\'t comment on gifts given by customers... but I like your gifts the most. They are always so thoughtful and lovely.","It\'s been a while since a customer who I need to personally welcome has visited Countless Springs. This shows that you\'re quite important indeed. Hmm... Who knows why you\'re important? Maybe you\'ve won me over with your charisma.","The word \"people\" shouldn\'t be used specifically to refer to a race. When beasts or monsters try their best to be kind to you like human beings, isn\'t it more suitable to call them \"people\" than something that simply has the appearance of a human?","Will you be scared if I suddenly act like a different person? I\'m just joking. How can someone suddenly become another person? On the contrary, you seem a lot more relaxed now than when you first came here. If I\'m the reason for this... can I feel proud of this?","It\'s easy to say something like \"stay true to your heart and don\'t lose sight of who you are\", but it\'s difficult to put into practice... But I think everything will be fine with you watching over me here. I\'ll be relying on you from now on.","Even if the wooden parts have rotted and the strings have broken, as long as the soul remains, the sound of the shamisen will never cease. Your expression tells me that you can also hear the sound of this shamisen right now.","According to historical records, in ancient times, an emperor loved a concubine who was a fox in human form so much that it resulted in raging wars and the destruction of the dynasty... I don\'t mind if you think I\'m a fox demon, but first you must be willing to become a self-indulgent ruler for me.","Happy New Year. Are you surprised to see me? According to our traditions, I should be participating in the parade on the street right now as the manager of Countless Springs, but... Since it\'s the New Year, can I forget all my duties and do what I want for once?","This kind of festival is rarely celebrated at Countless Springs. After all, I would be failing at my duties if I can\'t let you feel this affection every day. However, I really am inviting you because I want to celebrate this festival with you, and the gift I\'ve prepared for you is a long peaceful night. Say, do you think I\'m more beautiful than the moon?","Lots of Dora","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. Aww, how cute.","No-ten. I\'ll keep them in my hand.","Four-Wind Discarded","Four-kan Abortion","Nine Different Terminals and Honors","I just think the phrase \"separated but still together in spirit\" is quite appropriate.","I accidentally lost something you like... How can I compensate you?","Time always passes so quickly when you\'re by my side.","When I hear your laughter, I feel like my efforts to build this hand haven\'t been wasted. Now... I need to let you win this game to keep you in a good mood.","Why don\'t you guess if I can win with this hand? But you\'ll need to bet something. If I win, you\'ll need to do everything I say tonight.","It\'s my honor to be invited here by you, so I need to make sure you all enjoy yourselves.","I can start at any time, but you don\'t need to rush.","Ron","Tsumo","Welcome! Boss Miki isn\'t here right now. Are you... Oh! Are you one of those Jyanshi the boss mentions all the time? I\'m Hannah, a new employee here. Nice to meet you!","My training to become a lady has begun!","I\'m one of the best hunters in my tribe, and I won\'t lose to anyone in a game of mahjong either!","I won\'t lose if it\'s a contest of speed!","There it is, victory... And... caught it!","Hi! I\'m about to go back after making a delivery for the boss. Do you want to come with me and have a cup of tea in the shop?","{name}, what are you doing here? Are you lost? Hehe, I\'ll show you the way! The boss has taught me how to use the navigation system. The shrine is at... the location doesn\'t seem to be right... Um... h-hold on, let\'s try turning to another direction...","The boss makes such delicious food. Why does everyone avoid it?","The way humans speak is so complicated. It\'s much easier to talk to my own kind in the tribe. When we talk... Roar— We just make sounds like this and everyone understands what we\'re saying!","One Han City is a good place! The humans are all kind here, completely unlike the humans near my hometown who avoid us. The boss, Miss Onodera, Miss Kitami... and many others are all so helpful to me. I\'ll definitely become a lady soon!","I can\'t stop myself from getting irritated when I draw a tile I don\'t want, but... I need to overcome this to become an elegant lady, right?","Argh! Y-You gave me a fright! It\'s been a while since I arrived here, but I\'m still not used to the sound of someone honking the horn. Why must humans drive cars? They release this smelly gas, and it takes even longer for you to arrive at your destination because they get stuck on the road. It\'s faster to just run.","{name}! These fish are for you. I caught them in the river when I went on an outing with Emma earlier. Hehe, as I expected, food foraged from the wild just tastes better!","The sun is so warm and comfortable... Ah! T-That was close. I almost fell asleep. I\'m at work right now, so I\'ll do something to wake myself up... I know, I\'ll read a book. Miss Onodera said that I need to read more books to become a lady... I\'ll read a book... Zzz...","This looks really delicious... but I need to lose weight. If not, I won\'t fit into that fluffy dress... Ah, but I really want to eat it... {name}, please do your best to stop me if I lose self-control! I\'m counting on you!","Is this for me? Thanks! But... the boss said I should give a gift back in return if I accept a gift from someone. I haven\'t thought about what I will give to you yet.","Mmm! It smells so good! {name} is always giving me food I love to eat. I\'m so lucky... Thanks a lot! This accessory is for you. I just finished making it!","This is my mask! Did you find it, {name}? Thank you! Where did you find it? Eh? In the shop? N-No wonder I couldn\'t find it at home...","Thanks! Now that you\'ve recommended the induction cooktop to me, I can finally start learning how to cook. Hehe, it feels like I\'ve taken another step towards becoming a lady! Once I learn how to cook, I\'ll definitely make some delicious food for you, {name}!","You want to pet my hand? Okay, but be careful of my claws, I haven\'t filed them in a while, but they are still a little sharp... {name}, why do you look so happy? A! N-No! You can\'t rub the pads on my paws like that!","{name}, what\'s your idea of an elegant lady? The boss and the others have taught me lots of things, but I still don\'t understand... I want to know what you think. I don\'t know why, but I get the feeling that... what you say is right.","{name}, you look at my tummy every now and then. Do you want to touch it? I guess you can, since... you\'re someone I trust. In my tribe, only those who are very close to each other are allowed to touch each other\'s tummies...","I-I failed again. Flower arrangement is so difficult... Shall I try again? {name}, will you keep waiting for me? I-I will try my best... {name}, you\'re so patient. You\'re willing to encourage me no matter how many times I fail when I try to cook, arrange flowers, or do anything else... {name}, will you keep waiting for me? Will you wait for me until I truly become a lady...","Happy New Year! In my hometown, we share the prey we catch with everyone during every important festival and sing and dance all day long, but it doesn\'t look like that\'s a custom here. But it\'s still very lively when everyone eats delicious food together and has fun together. {name}, if you get the chance, you must visit our hometown. We\'ll give you a warm welcome!","{name}, please accept this. The boss said I should give chocolate to the person I like. You\'ve helped me so much, {name}, and I love you the most! Since you love to hold my hand, I\'ve tried to make this chocolate the same shape as my hand. Does it look close enough? Hehe...","Lots of Dora","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai! I\'m doing my best to Tenpai!","No-ten... I can\'t become a lady now...","Eh? It\'s the same one?","It\'s not elegant to hesitate!","There aren\'t many tiles left...","The boss said I need to be calm in times like this to be elegant.","What if someone suddenly gets a Riichi?","Is everyone here already?","I\'ll show everyone how a lady fights.","Musa... Your... name? Mhm, got it.","So noisy! Too many... people.","I just caught a boar... For you, {name}. It\'s delicious.","Phew, not bad.","You like this? ...I\'ll try my best.","Mahjong? Okay.","Sniff, sniff... You smell good today.","Chat? ...No.","Mm... Don\'t touch... me there.","Clothes affect speed... They affect both running and mahjong.","Your voice... I like listening to it.","Woof! Grrrr! There are other beasts here.","Hehe... Purr... Keep touching my ears. I like it.","Honey is sweet... You are sweet too.","Night time... dangerous to be alone... Stay with me.","Danger! Take cover.","I like it.","Cola... dangerous. Hurts... voice.","Leader? Usually female... unless male... very strong. I... don\'t want to be the leader.","Lion hunting? Very difficult... when alone. Spotted hyenas... hunt in a pack.","My teeth... are very sharp, but I won\'t bite you. Want to touch them?","Friendship? ...I don\'t understand. You are family.","I... don\'t like the smell of other people on you. You only need my scent...","Happy New Year. My wish... I want to be with you.","Mating period... not fixed. Is it the same for humans? ...I thought it was today. N-Nothing...","Tenpai. Huff—","No-ten. Grrr...","So annoying!","Will... you get angry?","I\'m here. Don\'t be scared.","This prey. No problem.","The opponent is strong... But I can win.","Hmm... coming. Thanks for inviting me.","Let\'s make this quick.","Riichi","Double Riichi","Chii","Pon","Kan","Kita","Ron","Hi, I\'m Illyasviel von Einzbern. You can call me Illya. As you can see, I\'m a grade school student you can see everywhere. Well... it\'s true that I\'m working as a Magical Girl, but I really am an ordinary grade school student!","N-nice to meet you!","Phew... I thought I had lost. Don\'t you think I put in a lot of effort? Hehe...","We did it! This is a... Oops, shouldn\'t say \"huge victory\" just yet.","Quintett Feuer! ...I\'m just joking, hehe!","Hi, Miyu and I were just about to search for clues to leaving this Mirror World. Sigh... It\'s not just Gil... Even Kuro is walking around everywhere all day. Aren\'t they worried at all?","I suddenly feel a little reluctant whenever I remember that I will leave here at some point in time. Even if everyday life is trivial, boring, and frivolous here, the time I spend with you is probably... more special than anything else.","Something I\'m good at... I\'m good at running. I won\'t lose even if I race against boys my age. But... it seems like this strength is becoming less and less obvious since I met Miyu. I only managed to barely win the last time I competed against Haruna... Ahahaha...","It\'s not easy to understand Miyu\'s thinking, but once you spend a little time with her, you\'ll realize that she\'s just not good at expressing herself and doesn\'t actually hate you. Many aspects of her are cute, such as when she is wearing a maid outfit... E-Ehehe...","How did I avoid dealing in just then? Um... Actually, I\'m not sure either... I just seem to suddenly get inspiration about which tile is safe whenever I\'m in a desperate situation.","What\'s the most important thing to a Magical Girl... It should be imagination, right? Anything is possible with imagination and determination!","After coming to this world where magic doesn\'t work, there are times when I\'m not used to how things are. For example, I can\'t transform and fly when I\'m in a hurry. Sigh... have I become too reliant on magic and got lazy without realizing it?","Hi! H-Have you seen Kuro anywhere?! That girl... I already spoke to her about it many times, but she is still playing pranks while pretending to be me! This time, I\'m going to teach her a good lesson with my dignity as an older sister after I catch her!","I always think of Mama when I see Miss Sawako. Mama is just as beautiful as her. Let me show you her picture... Huh? Why is Papa\'s face missing in all the photos? Hmm... now that you mention it... This is so strange. I can\'t remember Papa\'s face either.","I wonder when we\'ll be able to return to our world. There are so many things I haven\'t done, such as my summer homework... Don\'t tell me we\'ll return just in time for school to start?!","Is... Is this for me? Thank you.","What should I give you in return for such a precious gift...? You only want me to pat your head? {name}, you must be joking, right? But I\'ll do it if you really want me to. I also like the feeling of being an older sister, hehe...","The work of a Magical Girl... Miyu and I mainly help Miss Rin and Miss Luvia collect the Class Cards. We need to do this secretly, just like a bomb squad that secretly dismantles bombs in the city.","U-Um! Please don\'t misunderstand! Kuro and I were just... Ah! It\'s a medical treatment called \"mana supply.\" It\'s a calm and emotionless way to supply magic power!","Magical Girl animes are popular in all worlds. Miss Fujita heard that I like to watch this type of anime, so she lent me a series of DVDs. Do you want to watch them with me?","The birthdays of Miyu, Kuro, and I are on the same day. I feel that it\'s so incredible whenever I think about this. We spent an entire day together by the seaside the last time, and I hope we\'ll continue to have the opportunity to do this again every year in the future.","I used to be afraid of my own power... I hesitated about continuing to be a Magical Girl, but Mama said power itself isn\'t good or bad. The person who has the power determines that. So I decided that I\'ll never run away again no matter what happens.","A-Amazing! I managed to transform even though Ruby isn\'t with me?! Could {name} be... an amazing mage?!","Happy New Year! It snows really heavily in winter here in One Han City too. Let\'s have a snowball fight, it\'s not every day we have such thick snow! Oh right... Be careful of Kuro. She will definitely try to launch a sneak attack... Eek! I-It\'s Kuro!","You\'ve taken great care of me after I arrived. This chocolate is a token of my thanks. Someone told me to not only cook food with love, but also to eat food with love. {name}, I believe you\'re such a person.","Blessing of Heaven","Blessing of Earth","Thirteen Orphans","Tenpai. Can you praise me for surviving till the end?","No-ten. Sigh... it didn\'t work out in the end...","Four-Wind Discarded. I-I\'m not running away, right?","Four-Kan Abortion. A miracle didn\'t happen...","Four-Player Riichi. I guess it\'s good that I avoided a direct conflict.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. It\'s more important to be down-to-earth than creative right now.","Um... Did I make a terrible mistake?","Although I want to keep this... I can only play it now!","I won\'t run away. The future will always be in front of me!!!","I\'ll win this one and then... keep moving forward!","It appeared like I expected...!","Hi! Miyu, let\'s head inside so we don\'t keep everyone waiting.","I\'m ready over here.","Hi, I\'m Miyu... Edelfelt. Illya said you\'re here to teach us how to play mahjong, so please take good care of us from now on.","Let\'s have a good game.","It\'s not good enough. I need to win the next game in even less time.","I\'ve got you!","With this, the victory has been decided!","Dimensional reflection pathway formation, Mirror World Corridor, partial inversion... Another failure? We won\'t be able to return to our world today... Hmm? When did you come? I\'m sorry I didn\'t notice you until now.","Hi, I\'m not here to play mahjong today. Both Illya and Kuro have been telling me to relax instead of being so tense all the time, but I don\'t know what I can do... Do you have any good suggestions?","When I went to Éternité earlier, I saw that the workers were really busy, so I borrowed a uniform and helped out. Illya was also really happy to see me dressed up like this. Miss Nanami also said I\'m welcome to help out from time to time. She pays a nice salary, which may not be as high as Miss Luvia\'s, but I might still consider her offer.","Not even a Magical Girl can do everything. One such thing is flying, because humans can\'t fly in the first place... Well, except for Illya, normal people can\'t fly.","I don\'t have Illya\'s imagination, Kuro\'s strategic ability, or Gil\'s unreasonable luck. All I can do is play safely to win the game step-by-step based on probability.","Hi, I was just planning to go with Ichinose to help Haruna with her homework. He\'s a great assistant, and I need him to help me explain things when Haruna doesn\'t understand what I\'m teaching.","Red hair and a cheerful and reliable smile... Don\'t you think it\'s amazing how there are people who are so similar to each other in every world?","Did you forget to bring your wallet? You can use my card for now. Although I don\'t know why, I seem to be able to withdraw funds normally from the banks over here... Don\'t worry, my wages are quite high.","Is this city near the ocean...? *Laughter* Ah, I\'m okay. I just remembered some nostalgic and happy things.","You\'ve made a mistake. I\'m only acquaintances with the others, not friends. I only have one friend—Illya... Wait, let me correct myself. Including you, I have two friends.","Thanks... but why did you suddenly give me this?","You should give something this precious to someone important to you... Is that why you gave it to me? Um... T-Thank you.","You think I look good in a maid outfit? That\'s not surprising at all. Other than working as a Magical Girl, I\'m also Miss Luvia\'s personal maid.","I didn\'t always have such a good relationship with Illya. In the beginning, I thought she wasn\'t serious about becoming a Magical Girl and was just playing around in battles... Now that I think about it, I said a lot of mean things to her...","I basically have no memories of anything before I was adopted by my older brother, but my body seems to have retained sporadic \"memories\" such as... that person who was probably my mother, and the warmth of her hands...","\"I hope Miyu will no longer suffer in this world.\" Someone once said that when praying for me, but I had no choice but to escape to another world. Fortunately, I met a group of really nice people and the person who became my most important friend... Her silver hair is so beautiful... like warm and soft moonlight.","I lost everything to get the power I needed to make my wishes come true... Born as the Holy Grail, I don\'t need light because I am the artifact that grants light. Despite this, some people gave me light and a place to stay. They even told someone like me that I could live as a human being...","This is incredible. This world... is filled with so many things I don\'t understand, such as this moment itself. This must be the magic or miracle that Illya spoke of, and you must be the one who gave me this miracle, {name}.","Winter symbolizes both meetings and partings to me, so I have always had mixed feelings about it... However, in this city, at least I can put aside my other thoughts for the time being and just enjoy this holiday. Happy New Year, {name}. Please continue to take good care of me this year.","Anyone can make delicious chocolate if they have the right materials and don\'t make any mistakes. In my opinion, the truly difficult thing is putting your \"heart\" into it like Illya said. Although she says she is very happy when she receives chocolate, I guess this varies from person to person. I hope you like this gift, and I\'ll be waiting to hear what you think about it.","Tenpai. Yes, I\'ll keep it up.","No-ten. I still have a chance.","Four-Wind Discarded. A draw, huh? Oh well...","Four-Kan Abortion. As expected, there\'s no such thing as a miracle.","Four-Player Riichi. I avoided the worst outcome.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Illya probably wouldn\'t give up...","This isn\'t a mistake. It just isn\'t my lucky day today.","Tile efficiency comes first.","It\'s time to be prudent and careful.","There\'s no reason for me to cower with this hand.","The shortest distance at the fastest speed...","Excuse me, may I ask who invited us to come play?","No matter who my opponents are, my goal is to win the game.","Hello! I\'m Kuro... Huh? Am I Illya\'s older sister? Hehe, you\'ve got good eyes.","Please take good care of me!","Ahh... It\'s over! I\'m a little tired now... Illya! I\'m hungry!","Hmm, the victory hasn\'t been decided just yet.","Wings that surpass mountains, split water, and never fall! Triple Crane Wings!","Ah, I\'m bored. Shall I go to the Mahjong Soul Shrine or take a walk somewhere...","I wonder why Illya and Miyu spend all day worrying about going back. There are so many fun places here in One Han City. It should be okay if we stay here for a little longer, right? Well, where should we go to have fun today?","Um... It\'s nothing. My mana is running low and Illya forgot to replenish it, so I\'m feeling weak. I\'ll lie down in bed while I wait for her. If you see her, please tell her to come back sooner.","That boy called Ryan in the troupe is quite smooth-tongued. Look at how happy Illya is after he called her \"onee-sama\" a few times. But... my intuition tells me that children who look harmless like that are often the most dangerous.","Although Illya doesn\'t look too reliable, I am always wowed by her ability to make friends... I guess I was saved by this ability of hers too.","Miss Sara said she\'ll be meeting me at the shrine. Do you want to come and have some fun with us? After coming here and meeting so many people, I still feel the most comfortable when I\'m with her. Maybe... it\'s because our personalities are more compatible.","I\'m not always able to explain why I play each tile like Miyu. The moment I draw a tile, I\'m able to instantly decide which tile to play next. In my battles in the past and while playing mahjong now, I am able to skip the thinking process and get the result I want without knowing why I do certain things.","Hmph! Of course I know more than ordinary grade school students. In fact, I know more than even college students. After all, I was born after being adjusted like this...","Call me Kuro-onee-sama if you feel lonely. I\'ll pat your head to comfort you anytime.","Thanks! If you weren\'t with me, I wouldn\'t have been able to get inside Asaha High School to play. It\'s all because of that old-fashioned vice president. All I did was play some pranks on the girls in the school. Is it necessary to be so wary of me?","Thanks!","Wow! What a wonderful gift! But you don\'t need to spend so much money next time. There are simpler gifts out there, right? Like... lots of mana?","Illya doesn\'t understand at all. You can tell who is the older sister from how we carry ourselves, right?","The mark on my tummy? It\'s a little too complicated to explain, but you can think of it as a curse. It isn\'t exactly difficult to dispel it, but it\'s quite handy sometimes, so I\'ve decided to keep it for now.","Illya is unexpectedly awkward sometimes, right? There\'s no way around it. Her life has been arranged by others since she was a baby. At such times, only I, the person who knows her best, can help her say what she is really thinking.","The so-called everyday life, having a family, home, and a group of friends... To obtain these commonplace things, I had to rely on miracles.","If the majority and the minority are placed at the two ends of a scale, and only one side can be saved, the side with the larger number of people will usually be chosen. This is what they call \"justice\"... But this kind of \"justice\" is too heavy for me. I can only care for two people... my weak sister and the princess from a parallel world.","Ahhh! It\'s been a long time since I transformed into this form after coming to this world, and the transformation used up more mana than I expected here... Can you come closer? There seems to be a very fragrant smell coming from you...","Hey, Happy New Year! Even I feel a little sad that I can\'t celebrate New Year at home this year... so you\'ll need to take me everywhere and play with me today to make me feel better!","Happy Valentine\'s Day! Oh, I think gave you the chocolate too early. If I wait a little longer until you think I won\'t give you any, I wonder if you\'ll make those sad and cute puppy dog eyes at me, hehe...","Tenpai. This is nothing!","No-ten. How disappointing...","Four-Wind Discarded. Oh well. It\'s time to start again.","Four-Kan Abortion. Oh... that was slightly over the top...","Four-Player Riichi. Nothing happened after all these?","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Is there really any person who hopes to win with this hand?","Eh... It\'s you...","It\'s dangerous to only think of Dora.","Hmm... Is it almost time to start running?","It\'s time to invite someone else. Hurry up and take your last breath!","In that case, let\'s make a mess of things!","Hi! Is there room for me?","I\'m ready!","You can just call me Gil. Well... I seem to be singing songs of praise of this world. {name}, I\'ll be in your care while I\'m here.","Nice to meet you.","Isn\'t it normal for a fake to lose to the real thing?","Oh? I\'m getting the hang of it.","Hahahahahaha!","Please guide me again today, {name}.","Hah! Although I don\'t mind it, it\'s naughty of you to disturb me so early on a morning that\'s perfect for sleeping in.","Lily Kitahara... Is that the head of the church in this city? Tch... no matter which world, those who run the church are not normal people.","Energetic girls are cute and adorable, but I think mature and reliable women are more attractive.","That man called A-37... No, he didn\'t do anything to me. Although he doesn\'t really pay attention to me, he didn\'t do anything rude either. I just... get the feeling I can\'t get along with him happily.","Things look quite lively in front of us. Let\'s go check it out. Haha, there\'s no shortage of interesting things in this One Han City.","Ah, I used all my money without realizing it. Fortunately, gold is just as valuable in this era, which saves me a lot of trouble.","Finding a way to leave this Mirror World? I\'ll sit out and let someone else worry about that. You don\'t want me to leave that early either, right?","I assemble tiles naturally and effectively, gather all the Doras in front of me, and have an extremely high Ippatsu rate... It\'s only natural for the king to have this level of luck.","I went to the water park here earlier, but I think it is not fun enough. I am thinking of acquiring it and building it into a more interesting place. When that happens, you can be the opening guest. Don\'t worry, the leisure park I ran was really popular.","Thanks.","Take this gold coin. You deserve it since you did your best to please me.","My real identity? Haha... You can just treat me like an ordinary child. At least that\'s what I look like on the outside, right?","Joy isn\'t the only thing growth brings. I bet you would be very troubled too if you find out that you\'ll be beyond redemption in the future.","I am the king, so I cannot live life too simply. However, excessive luxury is so tasteless. It\'s not easy to get the right balance.","I do not want to use my special eyes if I can avoid it, as it\'s not interesting to always know how everything will end in this world. That\'s why this ability is usually sealed. But even so, I can still see how the situation is developing when necessary.","Haha, is it so shocking to see me playing with the nearby children? Humans are quite interesting. They laugh, get angry, and cry... They are so emotional. Although I\'m a Heroic Spirit, I can also laugh and get angry. As for crying... Who knows? Maybe I experienced that when I was a human, but I have already forgotten about it.","Raise your head. You can look at me boldly without fear. I must thank you. If not for you, I might not have been able to reunite with my long-lost friend (Enkidu).","Happy New Year. It\'s so lively everywhere. I guess humans should forget all their troubles and have fun during festivals and celebrations. Let\'s join them, {name}.","Let\'s go. I\'ve booked out the entire amusement park. Haha, don\'t be surprised by such an insignificant return gift... Oh? Are you uncomfortable when we\'re the only people in the amusement park? If you want things to be more lively, I don\'t mind having some clowns come here to dance for us.","Tenpai. I guess that\'s how things are.","No-ten. Should I get a little more serious?","Four-Wind Discarded. Oh? You can keep up with my thinking?","Four-Kan Abortion. Ah, I didn\'t win.","Four-Player Riichi. I praise you for being courageous for now.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Thank me for being so kind.","You don\'t need to give me meaningless things.","This Dora isn\'t valuable at all.","The struggles of fakes are so futile, fruitless, and worthless.","*Yawn*... This show is getting boring. It\'s time to get the actors to leave the stage.","This should be enough.","So, is that everyone? Don\'t tell me I actually have to wait for somebody.","Dance as much as you want to please me, even though I already know the outcome.","Kita. Prepare to attack!","Ron! Let everything be destroyed!","Tsumo. Everyone, surrender to me!","{name}, we meet again... Ah, I\'m sorry. I forgot that it\'s been a long time since we last met. You... should still remember me, right? It\'s okay if you don\'t. Let\'s start over and get to know each other again. I\'m Eve Krist, a holy swordsman of the S. Decretum Church. I\'ll need you to help me with my upcoming activities in One Han City.","Going all out in every battle is how you show your respect for your opponent. I, Eve Krist, am ready!","My goal is to win every battle in the mahjong war. You\'re welcome to challenge me at any time!","I always get the feeling that I get more attention when I win than when I walk down the street with Caladbolg. Is a person\'s strength determined by their mahjong ability in One Han City?","Even though we\'re not supposed to be enemies at the mahjong table... with all this murderous aura swirling around, I\'m pretty sure everyone here sees me as one. Ahaha...","Today\'s work has been finished, and I\'m off work right now. Please let me know if you need me to help you with anything.","*Yawn* Ah! {name}, it\'s you... Um, I feel so embarrassed that you always catch me in awkward moments... Is there any way I can make you forget what just happened and make you remember my charming moments more?","Mahjong... is very complicated. You can\'t win by knocking down your three opponents with force, and you can\'t deal damage to them by playing the tiles in your hand. Your move might even backfire on you. In fact, it feels like you use mental magic attacks instead of physical attacks. It\'s such a terrifying and mysterious way of competing with others.","I ate some salted tang hulu at a dessert shop recently, and I heard from a dessert chef who works part-time there that you two developed it together. It\'s such a marvelous treat! The saltiness makes the sweetness of the fruit burst in my mouth... I have newfound understanding and respect for you. Will you invent other new desserts in the future?","The nun always says that I will become a flame that purifies the darkness like the Suzaku recorded in the holy scriptures. I haven\'t thought much about what she said in particular, but I hope that I can bring warmth to the people around me if my swordsmanship and Caladbolg really are flames.","I\'m not good at preaching or explaining doctrines to others because there are usually special priests who take care of these things, but if you want to learn swordsmanship, I can teach you some common and practical techniques you can use in battle.","Although One Han City is such a lively place, I still prefer the Northland. To outsiders, it is a really cold place with heavy snow all year round, but that\'s precisely why we have festivals and celebrations that many other places don\'t have. If you get the chance, I hope you\'ll be able to travel there with me. I think you\'ll like it there.","Why are members of Ares here in One Han City...? Hmm, it looks like a storm is brewing in One Han City. {name}, if it becomes necessary, please let me protect you personally. Can you... trust me with all your heart?","This tile looks like a bird in courtship. We rarely see such brightly-colored birds in the Northland as most birds there are white or gray-brown to better hide from their enemies in the heavy snow that falls all year long... Huh? Me? Um... I\'ll still choose red because it allows you to easily spot me at a glance.","{name}, when is your birthday? I want to arrange a birthday celebration for you. The nun said that our birthdays are a day on which we should thank God for sending people who are important to us to this world, that\'s why your birthday is such an important day to me, {name}.","In the civilian areas of the Northland, instead of giving each other gifts, friends express their fondness for each other by hunting or partying together... Do you want to give it a try?","I hope my love for stuffed animals won\'t make you think that I\'m neglecting my duties... I know that they don\'t seem to suit me very well since a swordsman should look tougher, but... thank you anyway.","The nun who raised me was an extremely gentle person who loved flowers, but in an environment like the Northland, only the upper echelons of the church are entitled to plant flowers in a greenhouse... If I get another chance to come to One Han City again, I want to bring her with me and show her the flowers here.","Kitahara... huh? If she thinks she can forget the past by abandoning her surname, then I don\'t think I can continue to consider her as my companion. The person of the past... would never do something like this to run away from her problems...","A true warrior would never be swayed by a few simple words. Faith is something like that to me. People can believe in God, an organization, or even themself. All you need to do is keep believing in what you believe and persevere. What about you, {name}? Is there anything you have always believed in?","Sorry, did I hurt you? I had my arms and legs slightly modified so that I can use Caladbolg. It never seemed inconvenient to me, but now it does seem a little troublesome... Oh, by the way, I\'ll introduce Caladbolg to you the next time you come to my place. One Han City\'s arms control is quite strict, so I can only let it stand guard at home.","Caladbolg is a sword that has never been wielded for any one person or one thing and only fights for faith and glory. I have always believed that spring will return to the Northland under the church\'s leadership, and I will keep fighting until my body is broken for the return of spring.","In the past, when I didn\'t have any missions to do, I would spend most of my time taking care of the children adopted by the church with Lily. During those times, she loved to tell me what her future life would be like... Hmm, upon second thought, it\'s kind of like what I\'m doing with you right now. Maybe I\'m starting to understand Lily better now. Love breeds both trust and fear... However, {name}, you\'re much braver than me, so I\'m certain things will end differently this time.","Happy New Year! I... think that\'s what I should say according to One Han City\'s customs, right? I didn\'t expect to live so leisurely in One Han City for so long. Hmm... maybe I\'m misunderstanding something, but I can\'t shake the feeling that days are shorter in One Han City than in the Northland. If... If I didn\'t have all these duties to perform, I really wish I could celebrate every New Year with you.","Of course I know about Valentine\'s Day! We celebrate something similar in the Northland. Not only do I know about Valentine\'s Day, but I also know that couples in One Han City give each other gifts and go on dates on this day... Ah! That\'s right! I remember that Lily also said adults play certain adults-only games on this day! {name}, you\'re the one who should treat me like an adult woman. So, what will we be doing today?","Tenpai. I knew it! Try hard enough, and you can achieve anything!","No-ten. Although I don\'t want to admit it... I really did lose...","God is so impulsive. Wouldn\'t it be great if I started the game with all these tiles in my hand?","I must say, you need a certain amount of willpower to give up a Dora. After all, you need to withstand the temptation of the points.","Ah, I\'m starting to get nervous... And when I\'m nervous, I want to eat something to make myself feel better.","My sword points in the same direction as the Northland\'s future.","Charging... 60%, 70%, 80%, 90%... Caladbolg is fully charged and ready to launch a devastating strike on any target at any time. {name}, please give me your commands, and let me become your strength!","I\'m sorry for being late. I heard that we\'ll be doing battle drills today, so I especially brought Caladbolg with... Eh? We won\'t be using weapons? Ahaha... so we\'re practicing mahjong... In that case, please enlighten me.","A war without smoke... I\'m ready now.","Kita, soft-boiled eggs!","Ron, omurice!","Tsumo, a large ramen!","Young Jyanshi, did you drop this hamburger? Or was it this sandwich? You didn\'t drop them? I won\'t hold back then... Nom, nom, nom, nom, nom... Ahhh! Do you have any more food?","I bet my pride as a dragon and {name}\'s dinner that I\'ll win.","That\'s all you have? Are you hungry or something?","{name}, give me chocolate. It\'s my reward!","{name}, I want to exchange these points for a deluxe fried chicken set. Can I?","{name}, can I start eating yet? I want enough food to feed three people!","{name} wins against the weak fishes, and I win against the weak {name}.","Ah—Ah—Ah—Ah— The performance is over. Now give me five cups of milk tea without any pearls. The opportunity to listen to my singing doesn\'t come cheap.","{name}, you can have the drumstick. I heard that caring for the young is a virtue.","Argh! Urgh... These... These are shiitake mushrooms... Save me! {name} wants to kill... me...","Wait, I\'m reciting a message Ichihime sent to me. It\'s about how to praise {name} so that {name} will buy me more snacks.","I\'ve drunk more seawater than the salted water you\'ve drunk, {name}. You need to try harder, {name}.","{name}, why are there sea overlords in an inland area like One Han City? I want to be an overlord of the sea too.","No! Don\'t! I won\'t leave the bathtub today even if you cry, {name}. The land... is so dry... My tail is starting to crack.","The weak are food for the strong, which means I can eat {name}... Urgh! Bleurgh! {name} tastes bad. Geez, there are so many different species that are edible in One Han City, but so few of them taste good.","Um, {name} will cry if I throw this away, right?","This is a present from you, {name}? I like it. Give me more.","The dragon-slaying... hero... turned into... an evil dragon in the end? {name}, I don\'t understand. Why didn\'t they choose to become a cute dragon like me?","{name}, you need to eat more. I can lift you into the air with one hand right now.","In terms of human age, I\'m your elder, {name}, and deserve your respect.","Jade, pudding, pearls, discount vouchers, {name}\'s Jyanshi license... I\'ve collected all the treasures.","A dragon lives for a veeeeery long time. I\'ll still be this cute when you\'re all old and wrinkly, {name}, so I\'m not at all worried that you might not like me one day.","Ah! {name} is such a noble person. Ah! {name} is such a kind person. Ah! {name} is... um, I forgot what I was going to say. I knew it! Not eating enough really does affect your memory. Anyway, please maintain this transactional relationship where I exchange cuteness for your food, {name}.","Happy New Year! This is my New Year\'s money for you, {name}. The 5 Coppers inside it aren\'t important. What\'s important is my New Year\'s blessing to you. I hope you\'ll grow up quickly to become an outstanding adult—the type that makes a lot of money.","Have you lost something? Are you referring to this pink letter or this heart-shaped box of chocolates? {name}, you\'re such a terrible adult. You already have someone as cute as me. How dare you go out and be lovey-dovey with others... That\'s so terrible!","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. Four dishes and one soup. I\'m so satisfied.","No-ten. Phew, I don\'t have to try so hard now.","Hmph... {name}, you didn\'t see anything.","Dora? Dora—gon? {name}, between Dora and me, which one do you like more? You can only pick one.","Geez, I\'ll only get hungrier if I lose after fighting to the end... Maybe I should give up.","{name}, you can laugh out loud if you\'re happy. I won\'t make fun of you. Don\'t worry, I won\'t use this to blackmail you into giving me extra food for dinner.","{name}, should I give this tile to the player after me if they give me three pieces of dried meat? Hmm... if that doesn\'t work, {name}, you should hurry up and think of a way to win quickly before I make a mistake.","I knew it... No food on the table means it\'s time for mahjong. These adults are beyond saving.","AHHH! Power up!","Kita. I\'m just going with the flow.","Ron. All\'s well that ends well.","Tsumo. This is how it begins.","Hold on, my friend, you seem to have a unique talent and great potential. Why don\'t you learn fortune telling from me? You\'ll quickly master the skill and could even start your business today!","I divined my own fortune before coming, and the reading advised modesty and caution. It looks like I\'ll have to tread carefully with you all today.","Practice makes perfect. It\'s as simple as that.","One must never attempt to divine the future in its entirety lest the heavens show their fickleness. Don\'t be too greedy with the tiles. You just need the right ones to win.","Do you play to win, or simply to not lose? If you only focus on avoiding last place, you will never see your chance to strike. And just like that... the match is decided.","At this point, you might as well practice Tai Chi with me. It\'s simple—super simple. Just follow me. Let\'s arrange the tiles, draw the tiles with our left hand, look at the tiles, and then discard the tiles. Now, with our right hand, we\'ll draw tiles and then look at them... Eh? I won! Take a look! What do you think? It\'s really simple, right?","Would you like to watch a play with me at Floating Dreams? I performed a simple divination after waking up early in the morning and deduced that you would come with me. Look, I\'ve even bought two tickets. Let\'s not disappoint fate.","Your eyelid is twitching? According to ancient beliefs, a twitching left eyelid is an omen of fortune and a twitching right eyelid is an omen of disaster... So, congrat... Um, it\'s your right eyelid... Well, I\'m telling you, my friend, these superstitions are all baseless.","Before coming here, I heard that competition was fierce in the fortune-telling business in One Han City. But I\'m not like them. I provide after-sales service and help people usher in good luck and avoid disaster in addition to telling people\'s fortunes.","Isn\'t it normal for people like me who tell fortunes and see supernatural things to speak in a peculiar manner? I ask for your understanding. I mean, who doesn\'t have an occupational quirk?","My body is getting lazy after sitting for so long. My friend, let\'s take a walk together and buy a newspaper. It\'s not that far away—it\'s just six stops away on the subway. Once we\'re there, we just need to pass through two streets and cross an intersection to arrive at a newsstand next to the teahouse. Geez, it\'s so difficult to buy a paper copy now. I wonder if anyone understands the feelings of an old-timer like me.","Playing mahjong is the same as practicing Tai Chi. The best strategy is to use your opponent\'s strength to attack their weakness... Simply put, you need to set something up, observe the situation, and launch a counterattack.","Haha, that\'s enough. Stop looking already. Here\'s my phone... Take a look for yourself. You\'re the only person I\'m following on CatChat. After all, you never taught me how to follow other people... Haha, I\'m just joking. The main reason is that your content is more interesting than the content everyone else posts. You\'re such a curious person.","\"You\'ll be rich and powerful for the rest of your life.\" This is something every fortune teller likes to say and every customer likes to hear. How can something this great be called a lie? The only difference, if any, is that everything I\'ve told you is true. With me helping you, even bad luck will become good luck, so you\'ll become rich and powerful even if you don\'t want to.","When we discuss the Tao, we simply express our views on a matter while exchanging ideas with others. It\'s not as profound as it seems. For example, don\'t you often discuss the Tao of mahjong with me too? Speaking of which, I prefer to have such discussions with you because your Tao of mahjong often exudes a kind of beauty that has no regard for the lives of others. It\'s extremely shocking.","It\'s not that I like this. I\'m mainly accepting this with great respect because I can\'t refuse your great kindness.","There are eight trigrams, so how can this gift be defined so simply as something I like or dislike? Not to mention that I received this from you personally.","The lines of the bagua, also called hexagrams, refer to the turn of the sun and the moon and the transition of yin and yang, which is also the best time to ask for good luck... My friend, are you willing to give me this time sincerely? After all, you might get what you want if you wish really hard for it. Haha, I\'m not lying to you. I mean, if you don\'t believe me, it doesn\'t matter what I say, right?","Since news of the resumption of that competition at the Mahjong Soul Shrine started spreading, more people have been asking me about Kazuha than their own fortunes. Geez, I\'m too embarrassed to tell them that things aren\'t as they imagined. There are only trivial and troublesome matters concerning a father and daughter\'s conflict. I feel so worried at such a young age. Please help me convey my message to Hokuraku the next time you see him.","When Tao begets one, it changes from a state that can\'t be understood to a state that can be understood. When one gives rise to two, two gives rise to three, and three gives rise to all things, the world we know comes into being. In other words, if you understand Tao, then the world you see will also exist. That\'s the way of all things.","Life is like a mahjong game, just a series of multiple-choice questions. People who always choose correctly are either the ones asking the questions or cheaters who have somehow predicted the answers. There are many people like me who aspire to be those cheaters, spending their lives searching for a book that holds all the answers. My friend, do you believe in the existence of such a book?","People can be destined to meet but not fated to be together. This situation applies to many people in this world. After all, not many people are lucky enough to be like you and me... Hey, I haven\'t finished speaking yet, so don\'t be in such a hurry to object. You must know that it\'s pointless to object to something preordained by fate. You\'re destined to learn the art of divination from me... Hmm? What did you think I was talking about?","Life is short, so enjoy yourself while you can. Just relax and ask me to help you with anything. Of course, I won\'t fulfill all your requests, haha. However, given our relationship, your business is my business, so I promise I\'ll do my best.","It puts such a burden on the gods to listen to a new wish every year, so my wish is to be a good person like I have been in previous years. Hmm? What kind of good person...? To me, a good person is someone who everyone likes—a person who tells other people what they want to hear and tells only you my truest feelings.","My friend, as I was watching the stars, I saw that the Red Phoenix star was in motion, indicating a romantic trouble coming your way. Well, here I am.","Tenpai. I\'ve done all I can. It\'s out of my hands now.","No-ten. Well, I already told you this spot has terrible feng shui...","Heh, I just drew this tile last time.","Shush— How can I lure my opponents into my trap unless I reveal some weaknesses? You agree with me, right?","There\'s no point in worrying now. Just relax.","If it\'s yours, it\'s yours. If not, then forget about it. Just wait calmly for the result, my friend. After all, today\'s divination is a good one that doesn\'t appear often.","I\'m in perfect control and can react perfectly to all changes. People can\'t read me, but I can read them like a book.","Just to be clear – no playing that sad erhu music \"Erquan Yingyue\" if I end up in last place, got it? But if I win, I\'ll treat you to the glorious suona piece \"Song of the Phoenix\" for some entertainment.","*yawn* You must all be ready since you\'re in such high spirits. Let\'s get started then.","Kita","Ron","Hello. I\'m Abydos Foreclosure Task Force Second-Year, Sunaookami Shiroko.","Mmm, let\'s start the game.","I guess this counts as a good outcome.","Mmm, I feel like I\'ve improved.","Yes, it\'s my victory.","Hi, {name}. Please be nice to me today.","Phew... I\'m sweating... Hm? Hello!","...You look troubled. Can I help you?","You finished your sports drink and want to buy more? Looks like the nearest supermarket is 10 km from here. That\'s just a short run!","One Han City is very peaceful. And the banks look easy to rob...","I ran into that regular in the bike store again. We have similar taste in bikes, but they certainly have a strange way of talking.","It\'s hot today... Do you think there\'s a pool around here? Air conditioning and fans are nice, but I prefer being in the water.","All the bike accessories I want are so expensive... I need to cut down on my spending!","Miss Nadeshiko showed me a great fishing spot. Do you want to go with me next time?","...Oh, {name}, are you tired? I\'m sorry. I didn\'t realize. Please get some rest.","This is... I\'m sorry. I don\'t have anything to give in return. Would you accept this energy drink?","...I\'ve experienced a lot of new things here.","Hoshino is usually sleepy, but she\'s always reliable in a pinch.","My favorite activities, like biking and fishing, are a totally different experience in One Han City.","Nana invited me to hang out with her at Asaha High School earlier. There are lots of students and activities... It\'s nice to be in such a lively place.","You always take such good care of us, {name}. I\'d love to go to the beach and catch some fish for you as thanks.","I was daydreaming again, wasn\'t I? Hm... It\'s quite nice to feel this carefree.","Happy New Year. I heard there\'s a good spot nearby to watch the sunrise.","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. I haven\'t made any mistakes.","Noten. I\'ll win the next one.","Four-Wind Discarded. I should retreat for now.","Four-Kan Abortion. It\'s time to make a strategic retreat.","Four-Player Riichi. Mmm, so this situation is also possible.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. It\'s time to regroup.","Hm... Did I misjudge the situation?","Mm, I don\'t need this.","Just a little more... I\'ll advance carefully.","I\'ll have a massive lead if I win with this hand.","It\'s a big fish!","Excuse me, let\'s have a good game.","Mmm, I\'m ready.","Kita. This is a good start.","Ron. Sorry!","Tsumo. Woo hoo!","I\'m Hoshino from Abydos High School. *yawn* I came to and was surprised to find myself here. Let\'s take it easy, huh?","Yaaawn, let\'s start...","Yes, this is the perfect outcome.","Yaaawn... Um... er, did I win?","Nice! I can continue to slack off now, right?","Perfect timing, {name}! You know, if you\'re tired, you should take a break...","Welcome back! ...What am I doing? I\'m getting some much-needed R&R, of course.","Ah! The weather is so nice! It\'s a sign of good things to come. For example... starting the game with a good hand. Heh.","I wonder where there\'s a good place to nap...","I\'d prefer to slack off all day, but I\'ll try my best anyway.","Oh, Miss Ayane is so nice. Not only did she tell me about the best napping spots, but she also lets me nap in the infirmary whenever I want! In fact, she reminds me a bit of the younger students back home.","Ugh. Everyone is getting a Tsumo and winning! And I haven\'t dealt in at all. This is the worst...","Stop working so hard, would ya? I want to slack off, but you\'re making me look bad, {var:player_nickname}!","I met that strange fortune teller again today, and she said the same thing she always does. I have terrible luck with money. What\'s the deal? Do I have a look or something?","Look! It\'s a fish! Hahaha! It\'s so cute!","...Oh? This looks promising.","Well, this is a surprise, but I\'ll take it. Thanks!","Hm? Oh, as the name implies, the Foreclosure Task Force handles problems like managing the school\'s debts and handling local thugs. But it\'s not hard. My juniors are so good that I can leave everything to them while I catnap.","You want to know why I\'m here? *yawn* Honestly, I can\'t remember. I just woke up, and here I was. But now that we\'re here, let\'s go treasure hunting together!","{name}, you\'re quite popular in One Han City. But it seems like you\'ve taken on a lot of responsibility. You don\'t have to carry the world on your shoulders, you know. Take my advice and relax a little.","I\'m so happy here that it almost feels wrong... This place is fascinating. I wish the other members of the Foreclosure Task Force could visit.","If you ever need help, just ask. You can tell me anything. But... Let\'s not get into too much trouble. Heh.","My dream? My dream is to climb onto the back of a whale and take a nice, long nap. Just like this... *yawn*","Praying to the gods, watching the sun rise... There are so many New Year activities, but I don\'t have nearly enough energy to do any of them. Why don\'t I just wish you a happy New Year and call it good, {name}?","Tenpai. Lookin\' good.","Noten. And I lost. Ouch.","Four-Wind Discarded. What a rare opportunity.","Four-Kan Abortion. I may have gotten carried away...","Four-Player Riichi. Calm down, everyone. Don\'t be so nervous.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Let\'s start fresh, shall we?","Same tile? How annoying...","*yawn* No avoiding this mess...","I\'m getting kind of tired.","Well... With a hand like this, it\'s time I got serious.","Heh. If I win with this hand...","Ah, I\'m sorry I\'m late. I hope you haven\'t been waiting very long for me.","Well... where can I go to get some sleep then?","Kita. Good. Let\'s do this.","Ron. No sweat!","Tsumo. Am I amazing, or what?","...Play mahjong on your behalf? I see you have a keen eye for talent. Yes, I would be happy to fulfill your request.","Request start!","Haha! You\'re beginning to understand how good I am, aren\'t you?","As expected of me.","Watch me getting further ahead.","Welcome! It seems I will be protecting you today as well.","I\'ve been waiting for you. Problem Solver 68 can accommodate any request!","That Strix organization said it has a big job for me. They have such good taste.","Problem Solver 68 can complete any request, big or small, without asking any pesky questions. And we do it with style... Don\'t we sound amazing? Heehee!","What do you mean \"wrong number\"? I called you. And I was really enjoying our chat about mahjong—I mean my next job!","Whoa, this place looks nice enough to be a Problem Solver 68 branch... How much is the rent here?","...I walk too fast? Nonsense. I walk with purpose. Besides, the slower we go, the longer it is before we can play mahjong.","This is amazing. I want to buy a set for the office...","You fraternize with organizations like Strix and Raven. Do you honestly think I\'d believe you\'re an ordinary Jyanshi? ...Relax! I\'m not judging you. I admire you! Now, let\'s go make some trouble together...","Heehee! I can tell by the look on your face that you want to play mahjong with me. Well, get ready for an unforgettable experience, because you\'re about to play with the president of Problem Solver 68!","Haha! Great choice.","Heehee! You\'ve got good taste!","People call us a famous group of outlaws? ...No, no, I\'m not angry. I\'m flattered! What a compliment! I want to shake the hand of whoever told you that. Clearly they have good taste!","You know the people of the Mahjong Soul Shrine, right? Perfect! You know that Mr. Wanjirou...? Is he related to someone who owns a ramen restaurant or something? ...No? But he knows so much about ramen. How strange...","Above all else, a leader must always be calm. If I couldn\'t keep my head in a crisis, then Problem Solver 68 wouldn\'t have nearly the impeccable reputation it has today.","Is that... Is that my student ID card photo?! Wh-Where did you get it?! Did Mutsuki give it to you?! Tell me!","You know... We\'ve come a long way together. I wouldn\'t mind hanging out with you more in the future.","Let\'s have a drink to celebrate a job well done! Heehee! Problem Solver 68\'s future is brighter than ever!","Happy New Year! Heehee! I\'ll win all my matches this year no matter what. Just leave it to me!","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. This is going smoothly.","Noten. Th-That\'s okay. N-No need to panic. Everything is going according to plan.","Four-Wind Discarded. W-Worthless tiles should definitely be discarded.","Four-Kan Abortion. This is... Well, it was a nice attempt anyway.","Four-Player Riichi. It\'s actually so lively.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. The trick is to complete the request. But my luck has been lousy lately...","Something doesn\'t seem right.","Well, I believe we have a difference of opinion.","This doesn\'t make sense. Why haven\'t I won yet?","Heehee! I\'ll hit my opponent with an Ippatsu Yakuman.","Did you see that? My request is going smoothly.","Are you my opponents for today? I don\'t care who ends up playing as long as you don\'t spoil my mood.","Okay, it\'s time to get to work!","Kita. Ah! A shiny, new toy!","Ron! Let\'s go!","Tsumo! Heehee! This feels great!","Ta da! Mutsuki has arrived! All right, {name}, let\'s have some fun!","Got it. It\'s time to complete some requests!","Heehee! Is this how it ends? Well then, what should we play next?","Hehe, I\'m having a blast. My performance is up to standard, right?","It\'s my victory!","Welcome back! I\'ve been waiting for you.","Good morning, {name}! Ready to be pulverized?","What game should we play today? Rock, Paper, Scissors? Kick the Can? Or... How about mahjong?","That was fun, wasn\'t it? Let\'s play that game again!","Kaguyahime told me to visit the Mahjong Soul Shrine. The reason is a secret, but you\'re welcome to join me if you\'d like!","Did you say I\'m on Asaha High School\'s troublemaker list? What did I do to earn that?","GOTCHA! ...What\'s that look for? You don\'t appreciate a well-executed prank? But it\'s so funny! Hahaha!","I went overboard, didn\'t I? Ugh... Looks like I\'ll be the one getting scolded this time.","Go, {name}! You can do it! Finish your work fast, so we have plenty of time to play!","I love playing games with Chiori. Her reactions are so interesting. But... Your reactions are absolutely fascinating.","It\'s not a bomb? Well, that\'s disappointing, but I\'ll take it anyway!","Wow! I can\'t believe you gave me such a nice gift! How about I give you this super bomb in return? You have 20 seconds until it blows! Better cut the right wire before it\'s too late!","Aru works so hard all the time, but it\'s always interesting work!","Heehee! Why don\'t we pull a prank together? It\'s so much more fun that way.","Since I won this game, I get to make a request, right? And you can\'t say no! Heehee... But what would be the best punishment?","I can\'t believe we\'ve played so many games together, {name}. In fact, I\'m shocked! Time flies, huh?","Oh! You gave me quite the scare! Well done. You successfully pranked me! Heehee! See how much fun it is? But watch your back... Next time you\'ll be the one who gets the scare of a lifetime!","Today\'s a special day, {name}. Would you spend a lot of time with me?","Let\'s play together even more this year and next year!","Tenpai! Let\'s keep going!","Noten. That\'s no fun...","Four-Wind Discarded. Oh, now it\'s interesting.","Four-Kan Abortion. What? It was over so fast...","Four-Player Riichi. How can this be?!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. This hand is lame.","What?! This is unbelievable...","Does anyone want this? No? Nobody?","I can\'t wait! When will the bomb explode?","Boom! Get ready for the fireworks!","Heehee! It\'s getting interesting now!","I\'m here to play with you! Let\'s have some fun together, okay? I\'m really looking forward to this, so please don\'t disappoint me.","Wow! Shall we get started?","Kita. I wasn\'t trying at all.","Ron. BOOM! Game over.","Tsumo. You don\'t need me to tell you what to do, do you?","Hey, since you came to me, I don\'t think you need me to introduce myself to you, right? Look at that clueless expression on your face. Don\'t tell me you want me to tell you tomorrow\'s winning lottery numbers. That information is incredibly expensive. Maybe you should figure out what you want before coming to me again.","You\'ve got some nerve. Fine, I\'ll play your little game. But be warned... the loser has to reveal one of their little... secrets. Heh. Now this should be fun.","Something as self-evident as this... really makes me happy. After all, I really enjoy seeing people with defeated looks on their faces","If this is enough to make you happy, then you must be really easily pleased.","Look, it\'s so simple to cause turmoil among humans. All you need to do is take away the thing they care about the most.","Well, I hope my \"sudden\" appearance here hasn\'t ruined your plans.","Where are you going? Don\'t be so petty. Everyone here in One Han City knows you. I\'ve helped you so many times already. Is it really so much to follow you around to get some information?","Even trash has its own value... Just so you know, I\'m actually referring to people. For example, these people are obviously a group of scum, but they are much better at gathering information than honest people.","No one is pure like a piece of white paper. To some extent, everyone has a couple of dirty secrets. For example, I\'m quite interested in your favorites folder. When will you be willing to share it with me?","I get paid, and you get a happy ending. As for what others say out there, do you really care?","I don\'t know what to say about you. You\'re playing mahjong with an information dealer... Pfft, I even know all your Tenpai quirks and preferences. Hey, do you think it\'s possible that I might actually know you better than you do?","Come on, all I did was plant a little listening device on you. Do you really need to get so angry? You\'re far more ruthless when you use me to get information. Shouldn\'t you console me too?","I heard that you\'ve been quite close with Soumu recently. It\'s not good to be indecisive like this. Tell me—what can he give you that I can\'t?","You know, the reason you keep coming to me every other day is so obvious that it\'s really difficult for me to pretend not to know. It\'s extremely dangerous to try to tame a wild beast that\'s used to freedom. You might even lose your life... Are you sure you\'re okay with that?","My dear boss, you shouldn\'t keep pushing the boundaries just because we know each other so well. Things will be awkward for both of us if the people above us get wind of this... Well, it\'s not like I can\'t open a back door for you... but how will you thank me?","Yeah, yeah, I like it. I really do... No, I\'m not just saying that. Can\'t you feel the joy that fills my heart?","It looks like someone broke the rules. How else would you be able to guess what I like with that tiny brain of yours? Well, now\'s your chance since I\'m in a good mood. What do you want from me today?","You get what you pay for. If you want more detailed information from me, then it\'s obvious that you should... right? I hope I won\'t need to teach you the rules of this place again.","It\'s impossible for everyone to be good people in this world. People should live realistically, and the reality is that this world needs bad people like me as a contrast to the people you think are good. So, let\'s be honest. Both you and those people need people like me.","So what if you don\'t like how I do things? Plenty of people dislike me in this world. Don\'t you think it feels really good knowing that there are people out there who hate your guts but can\'t do anything to you at all? That being said, if you know any other tricks that I don\'t know about, I would really like you to open my eyes.","In all my years in this line of business in One Han City, you\'re the first one to impress me like this... Let\'s see... How should I evaluate your style? All courage and no skill? Do you like this evaluation?","Why are you following me? Do you want to follow me home to meet Ning? Tsk, you\'re braver than I thought. It won\'t be that easy for you to leave after you follow me home, so you better think twice about it. Those who voluntarily jump into a fire pit with all their strength aren\'t that smart.","There should still be some time until the party starts, right? Is it possible that you\'re here to steal information...? Aha, I get it now! But I must tell you in advance that information about my body is very expensive. I hope you can afford the cost for tonight.","Happy New Year. Hmm? Why are you making that expression? I can extend New Year\'s greetings to you even if I\'m not a good person, okay? I thought about it carefully, and I don\'t think I\'ve done anything bad enough to you to give you such a bad impression of me. Tell me the truth. I haven\'t... right?","Couple activities are completely out of the question. As compensation, I can tell you three things you want to know depending on the situation... *Sigh* Do you think two people who are always together every day can give each other a Valentine\'s Day surprise? Rather than thinking about that, why don\'t you think about where you want to go to have fun during the week I\'ve specially set aside for you?","Tenpai. Oops, sorry for disappointing you.","No-ten. Whatever, it\'s not entirely a bad thing.","Trash should just stay in the trash can.","You can\'t get back what you\'ve discarded no matter how bad you\'re feeling about it.","Why are you so anxious? This happens in every mahjong game. You should be used to it by now.","Since your heart is beating so calmly, it seems like the points are still no big deal for you... While they\'re dealing in, why don\'t we chat quietly for a while? Such as... how can I make you more excited...?","Yeah, yeah, I get it. I know you\'re really happy and can\'t wait to win with your hand, but you can\'t be so heartless to me. Our transaction goes both ways, so you need to make me happy before I help you win, right?","You people... Shouldn\'t you be doing something besides playing mahjong? Oh wait, I almost forgot that you really don\'t have anything else to do.","*yawn* Let\'s get started already.","Kita","Ron. Thanks.","Tsumo. Mojito, Go!","I know you, {name}. You\'re someone who comes to watch our performances at Soul on a day-to-day basis like how someone returns to their home. We\'ve seen each other many times, but I think this is the first time we\'ve exchanged greetings. I\'m Ciri, and this is Mojito.","Mahjong is one of the few hobbies I take seriously. Don\'t worry, I will be giving it my all.","The law of the jungle isn\'t suitable for domesticated pets.","Sorry, Mojito just can\'t resist the urge to tease small animals. I\'ll teach him later.","I like the feeling of a clean, decisive victory. And you?","I\'ve reserved a ticket for the next show for you. Remember to get there on time so you don\'t miss my performance with Mojito.","How can someone your age sit still at a time like this? Have you played mahjong yet? Have you gotten better at it? How many different types of Yaku have you tried other than Pinfu and All Simples...? Sigh... I knew it. I better go to the dojo with you today.","When weak animals encounter predators, they just need to run faster than their companions. Similarly, in mahjong you just need to be the last to deal-in if you don\'t want to finish the fourth. However, hehe, the truly ferocious beasts never need to do that.","Those who come to watch the animal-taming performance at Soul just want to watch a lion jump through a flaming hoop, watch a wolf do arithmetic, or watch Mojito walk upside down. Don\'t worry though, everyone at Soul performs voluntarily because they need to make a living. Don\'t humans usually do incomprehensible things for their work? In society, humans are basically no different from animals.","I bet Ryan gave you this messed-up program. Everyone in the troupe knows that he follows you all day long. I\'m more worried about you than him. Hehe, he looks so innocent and harmless, but don\'t let him fool you; he\'ll take everything you have to give and more. Come and ask me for help when you can\'t handle it anymore.","I should introduce you to some new friends now that you and Mojito are so close. Huh? Are you afraid? Just channel the same energy you used to catch up with your opponent in your last mahjong match. It\'s easier to get along with everyone than you think. Even the most cunning hyena will show its belly to someone who treats it sincerely.","The human heart is too unpredictable. It\'s easier to get along with those who will obviously betray you because you already know what they are planning. For example, in mahjong, it’s always easier to defend against those who play a Riichi from the get-go instead of those who hide their Tenpai.","2 vs 2 mahjong? I haven\'t seen that often, but it sounds very interesting. We can play together if you aren\'t confident. I\'ll create the opportunities for you—I\'m very confident in our spiritual connection and chemistry.","I have been to \"Countless Springs\" several times before for personal reasons, but how did you know about that? Unless... {name}, are you a regular there? Sniff, sniff—Achoo! No wonder something smells familiar on you! So it\'s the smell of that \"fox.\"","You should always come to me first when you are sad. I mean, who should you rely on other than me in times like that? I\'m also used to having people rely on me. Come here so I can give you a hug and pat your head. This method of reassurance is suitable for mammals of all ages.","A gift? Is it a bouquet of flowers to celebrate my successful performance? Just put it over there, and I\'ll look at it later.","I suddenly understand why you\'re so popular. At the very least, the fact that you\'re willing to put in time to learn what people like makes you better than most people. {name}, thanks so much for the present. In return, I\'ll give you these tickets for tomorrow\'s performance.","This is my contact information... What? Is it so surprising that I use a mobile phone? It\'s been a long time since I left the jungle, so I\'m already quite familiar with modern human society. Or... do you think it\'s too soon for us to exchange our contact information?","Sara always tells me that I\'m too direct and offend people easily. Your facial expression tells me you think the same. To be honest, I don\'t really care if people dislike me for what I say because I don\'t need them to like me anyway. But as a performer of Soul... this is unacceptable. So if I say anything inappropriate, please tell me so I can try to change it.","What type of person do I dislike? Traitors, of course. Traitors like Ju should be whipped harshly in the face, so they should stay away from me if they know what\'s good for them. It\'s the same for you, {name}. If you betray me, I\'ll whip every part of your body mercilessly.","Everyone has something they want to protect, and I\'m no exception. Although I\'m an individual called Ciri, some things are more important. First of all, I\'m a daughter—a child raised by wild beasts. Second, I\'m the eldest daughter in my family, and I bear the expectations of everyone in Soul. Finally, I\'m a weapon who will protect my family at all costs.","To be honest, I already knew you quite well before you knew me. You\'re Soul\'s unofficial personnel, Soul\'s support worker, and the great romantic of Soul... It seems that you haven\'t heard of these titles at all. Everyone calls you these names in private based on your usual behavior, but I think they are all meant to be compliments. As for me, I can only say that I\'m very happy to be with you.","{name}, do you want to become part of my family? Yes, a kind of family that lives together and supports and loves each other. There\'s nothing embarrassing about this. If I hesitate, someone stronger might take you away from me. So, what do you say?","Happy New Year! After hearing so many blessings today, do you want to hear something different? Mojito and the others have put together a performance on their own to give humans the chance to pay money to experience what it\'s like to make beasts \"submit.\" I\'m sure they\'ll be willing to perform for free for you... Hmm? An animal tamer? Interesting, so you want me to \"submit\" to you? You want to role-play as my tamer and whip me? Hehe, you can always try and see if you can do it.","Every year on this day, Mojito refuses to perform and throws a tantrum after dragging me backstage. This year? Hehe, Mojito doesn\'t even want to look at me. It\'s probably because we\'re exuding the lovey-dovey vibe he hates the most. It\'s time to find him a beautiful female leopard. Even I find it hard to deal with an angry single leopard.","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. I knew this would happen.","No-ten. Oh well, there\'s also prey Mojito can\'t catch.","If the same performance is repeated too many times, the audience and the performer will get sick of it.","I know it\'s necessary, but it still feels like a shame.","How does it feel to have a race against time? Don\'t worry, they won\'t be able to catch up to us easily.","Be patient, and victory will be ours. The wait will only enrich our victory.","Mojito, please get the human beside you to be quiet. It\'ll be a hassle if the prey is alerted by any big movements.","I have a rare day off from performing. Why don\'t we enjoy a few rounds together?","I\'m ready.","Kita, interesting.","Ron, boom!!","Tsumo, joker\'s joke!","I\'m Ju, a clown of Gemini, at your service. As for the service... hehe, that all depends on how you plan to utilize me, O Great Jyanshi.","Is this some kind of group therapy session? I do hope you\'re all still smiling like that when you deal into my Yakuman.","Heh, poor little things. You only lost a game of mahjong, turn that frown upside down. You have long lives ahead of you--and plenty more games of mahjong to lose.","Ooh, I like that, yes... I like it very much.","Some people can\'t be bought with gold or glory. They seek only destruction... Like me right now, hehe.","I\'m a clown, and my mission is to make everyone who sees me laugh their heads off. So, could you do me a favor and give me a smile? …Come on, don\'t be so serious; you look way better when you smile.","Ladies and gentlemen, it\'s show time... Huh? Where\'s the stage? Look around you--Is this world not a grand stage? You can become the star of the show any time you like, as long as you\'re willing.","I\'m but a simple clown who can\'t help but laugh when misfortune befalls others, so can I ask... that you not treat me like a freak? Ah, \"freak\"... Hehe, the word alone sounds like someone so inelegant, whose actions are so foolish and crude that even their mahjong tiles are arranged haphazardly... Ah, my apologies, I often forget myself when I get lost in thought. What was I saying?","When can one become a clown? Well, now... that\'s an amusing question. Are we not all clowns when we\'re working?","Shush--Don\'t speak. Tilt your head five degrees to the left, like this... A little more... Too much, come back a little bit... Perfect. Symmetry becomes you.","8 Man, 8 Man 8 Man 8 Man... I need an 8 Man, where are you... Aha! There you are! Seven Pairs--What a symmetrical, perfect hand! But... don\'t make me wait too long for Tenpai, because missing a tile makes me anxious, and being anxious makes me angry... and no one likes an angry clown.","You\'re not still working at this hour, are you? Tsk tsk tsk, you poor thing... Even the clowns of Gemini get days off. But you, my friend... I think you\'re working too hard. Why don\'t you and I discuss how we can make that nasty boss disappear from this world?","Sometimes I really wonder if I\'m a dog. Otherwise, why would I see the world in only black and white...? Oh, don\'t worry, I don\'t bite. I just think... this world would be purer if it were all black.","A miserable lot in life, a freakish demeanor, and an ugly face only fit to elicit laughter... That\'s a pretty mild review, actually. After all, I usually get called names like \"traitor,\" \"demon,\" and \"scoundrel.\" Even the old man who raised me would point at my nose and tell me I was \"born bad\"... You know, I suddenly miss the way he\'d fly off the handle. Maybe you and I should go pay him a visit? Hehe.","It\'s hard to be as likable as money, but it\'s easy to get rid of people who don\'t like you... Hehe, only joking. Of course I don\'t recommend such a bloody, violent approach. Besides... I\'m not sure I could go through with it if you were the one who didn\'t like me.","Shall we take a guess at what becomes of disposable stage props once they\'re used...? Hehe.","Sweet cookies, full of carbohydrates and sugar, are truly a joyous thing... Even if there were shards of glass inside, I still couldn\'t turn them down.","Let me see... Hmm, there\'s still some time before the show, so why have you already put on the mask? Tsk, that friendly, happy mask that makes the whole world seem like your friend... Mad? That\'s right, look at me with disgust like you were looking at trash. I like the real you.","Soul? I like Soul, more than words can express. I\'m very, very, very good friends with everyone in Soul! Are you happy with what you hear?","So, there\'s no avoiding this part, is there? The part where two long-time acquaintances finally expose each other\'s flaws under the guise of getting to know each other better... No, I don\'t mind, it beats having your wounds ripped open and raked over hot coals--You just made me say it... Tsk, that\'s too kind.","Sara is a good person? Mmf--Aha--My head... Oh, my head... Ahh--Sorry, I have a low threshold for laughter, and when I hear a joke like that... It\'s like fireworks starting to go off in my head.","The ultimate destination for human encounters... is probably for both people to complete each other. As such, let\'s celebrate our encounter with wild abandon. Even though we may become incomplete once again after parting tomorrow... at least for this moment, let\'s smile happily.","The backstage dressing room is a dangerous place... After all, getting a glimpse of the truth isn\'t always a good thing. My advice to you is to either turn around and forget everything you\'ve seen here, or... come in and close the door behind you.","Boom, boom boom boom, BOOM!! Like it? The sound of such solemn fireworks is like music to my ears... BOOM! And just like that, it blows all the chaotic feelings from my head. Today is the first day of the new year, and the day this clown says \"Happy New Year!\" to the world. That includes you too, of course, O Great Jyanshi.","Shhh--Don\'t speak. When the merry jig begins, just put your hands here... A little lower... There, just like that. Now follow my steps... One, two, three, spin... Hehe, if only our friendship were like this dance, always having wiggle room no matter what the other person does. That would be nice.","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. Desire always loses to reality.","No-ten. Just as boring as the curtain call.","See? Useless people are like useless tiles--they all become the dregs of society in the end.","Let\'s see what this juicy bone can attract... Hehe.","Is \"Dead Line\" a lie? No, only \"Line\" is--\"Dead\" tends to be true.","At the mahjong table, what doesn\'t kill you only excites you. Wouldn\'t you agree?","Madness is like a force of gravity--give it just a little push, and then BOOM!","Don\'t worry, I\'ll contact your next of kin if anything happens... Just kidding. You\'re all way too serious, you need to loosen up a little.","What, are you all waiting for me to do a magic trick? Which one of you still isn\'t ready yet...?","Kita","Tsumo. Do you understand how to do this now?","These are just some ordinary herbs, so don\'t mention it. You\'ve taken such good care of my students Kaavi and Yuzu, so this is just a small thank-you gift... Yes, you\'re right. I\'m their teacher Leia and the owner of the herb store Datura. Please come here if you need anything. You\'re also welcome to just come over and have a chat.","Let\'s start today\'s lesson.","If you lack proper guidance, it\'s futile no matter how hard you try.","I never doubt my decisions.","It\'s time to harvest the fruits of my effort.","Please give me a moment to finish this tea or else I won\'t have enough energy. You\'re welcome to have a cup too if you want.","Oh, you\'re here. Please take a seat. Sorry, I\'m thinking about something, so please wait for me quietly until I\'m finished... You\'re such a good child.","Well-done. You\'re so likable and always make decisions that make me happy.","Kaavi and Yuzu are both students that I\'m proud of. They always wanted to be with me when they were little, but they aren\'t that close to me anymore, and they are always reluctant when I ask them to come to my place for a meal. Children sure are difficult when they\'re in their rebellious years.","Although kittens and puppies are cute, they are naughty and can\'t control their desire to bite things. Many of the plants in my home are harmful to them, and they\'ll be in trouble if they eat these plants by mistake. It\'s nice just to say hello to them or look at them when I pass by the pet store like this from time to time.","I stick to any decision I make. A strong will has a magical power that can influence the outcome. The same is true for mahjong. I firmly believe that I\'ll be rewarded for every decision I make.","I\'m meeting Miss Nikaidou for afternoon tea. Do you want to join us? I think she\'ll be really happy if you do.","Childishly contradicting one\'s teacher to prove one\'s maturity is something cute that young people do. I can pretend not to notice this wayward behavior as long as it doesn\'t exceed the bounds of my patience.","No, not that. You\'re a smart child, so you should know that what I want to hear is that you\'re sorry, not a reason... Yes, that would be enough.","It\'s okay. Just because you\'re a little reckless doesn\'t mean you\'re wrong. Just try again if you fail. Don\'t worry, I believe you\'re right, so that means you\'re right.","Thanks for going to all this trouble. Compared to receiving a gift, what I look forward to more is seeing you grow and become more mature.","Since you brought me such a good wine, I think I\'ll need to close the store early today.","The more precious an herb is, the more attentive you need to be when taking care of it, and this process is incredibly complicated. The same applies to the education of students.","Every medicine is a potential poison. Without proper guidance, even an antidote can be harmful. I think this is also true in the case of talent. That\'s why proper guidance is so important.","Don\'t worry, it\'s inevitable to hurt your fingers in one way or another while taking care of flowers and plants. Similarly, it\'s because the children and I managed to resolve many conflicts together that they are now able to blossom and bear fruit.","It\'s important to respect a student\'s autonomy, but a laissez-faire approach shouldn\'t excuse a teacher\'s educational failures. Both the stick and the carrot are necessary.","Haha, I think I understand why Kaavi and Yuzu think you\'re special. Can you tell me more about yourself? The more the better...","Seedlings that should be able to grow vigorously can still wither silently due to lack of care or overindulgence. This is what I can\'t tolerate the most. Become my student. You\'re worthy of receiving and obeying this command.","Happy New Year. Here\'s your New Year\'s money. Hehe, don\'t be embarrassed. No matter how old you get, you\'ll still be my cutest student. Look at Kaavi. She\'s accepted it happily, right?","Take this, good child... Hmm? Do you not like the chocolates I gave you? Or... did Yuzu say something to you?","Tenpai. It\'s a pity that I couldn\'t win.","No-ten. I\'ll wait for my next chance.","These children are naughty.","I don\'t need this child.","In times like these, it\'s more important than ever to trust your own judgment.","Haha, this growth is outstanding.","It\'s not perfect, but I\'m happy with this.","Sorry, I was held up by something at the store. I hope you haven\'t been waiting too long.","Now that everyone is here, I\'m going to start the roll call.","I win. This is a good feeling.","Tsumo. That\'s more like it.","Nice to meet you! You can call me by my stage name, Cynthia. You\'ll have to ask my manager if you want any signed photos or photo books. If you want to arrange any other commercial cooperation, please contact my company. Hmm? You didn\'t come here for these things? How interesting. In that case... I hope you\'ll always be able to smile like this. I\'ll be looking forward to every meeting with you in the future.","You guys better watch out. The runway isn\'t the only stage I shine on!","This isn\'t surprising at all. This is the strength of a supermodel.","I don\'t deny that beauty has its advantages. But anyone who uses that as an excuse for losing at mahjong is, in my view, not just incompetent, but a fool.","Challenging the star of the show when you\'re so clearly out of your league... Is that bravery, or just stupidity? Either way, you get what you deserve.","Let\'s go. Come to the mall with me to do some shopping. You have no objections, right?","We always seem to meet no matter when I go out. Haven\'t you ever wondered if it\'s too much of a coincidence? Be more confident. I came especially to see you.","Unique design, long brand history, and a good brand image are essential factors for luxury goods to win over consumers. I, however, only follow one rule: I choose the brand that offers a higher price for the show.","Magazine reporters always ask bizarre questions during interviews, such as whether I think I\'m more like a cat or a dog in daily life... Geez, can\'t I just be a normal person?!","It\'s obvious that the answer is 9 Sou. Isn\'t the brand owner afraid of losing everything by using such a simple \"What tile to discard\" question to determine who will win a prize? Or... is this question supposed to be difficult for others?!","What are my top wishes if I win the Mahjong Soul Shrine tournament? First of all, I wish for my mother\'s illness to be cured. After that, I wish for everyone to follow the traffic rules strictly... Hmm, a wish for myself? Then... I wish for all the fashion brand releases to be held in One Han City so that I don\'t have to fly for ages to attend fashion shows elsewhere.","It\'s really unpleasant to hear the mobile phone ringing urgently at a busy time such as when I\'m preparing to go on the catwalk. Please check my phone for me and answer the call if it\'s the brand owner. According to my experience, this phone call should be from... I knew it! It\'s my boss. Just hang up directly. After that, text my boss and get him to send me an email later. Thanks!","Whether it\'s at work or in life, the most important thing is to find your own way to enjoy life. For example, one of the best ways for me to relax is to watch a live stream of a panda eating bamboo shoots on my smartphone. Do you want to join me?","You came to my filming site on the street and messed up my schedule! Do you miss me that much? Well, I\'ll let it slide this time. What did you come to see me for? ...Why are you stammering? Did I guess wrong?! I see... hehe, why don\'t you tell me which model you\'re looking for? Tell me her name so I can HELP YOU FIND HER!","Entertainment reporters have nothing better to do with their lives nowadays. They follow us around after we get off work and hide in some random tree until midnight just to snap the most boring photo of us up close. Haha, I don\'t mind, but I feel sorry for you because they\'re saying that you\'re my secret lover.","If the focus is off, you won\'t be able to take a good photo no matter how perfect your composition is.","Thanks for your gift. At this moment, no matter where I\'m looking, it\'s your best angle.","It\'s my daily job to wear different clothes and play different roles, so it\'s inevitable that I\'ll feel a little lonely when I change back into my regular clothes and remove my heavy makeup. However, I don\'t seem to have this problem when I\'m with you.","Ahem, do you have any time today? Can you visit my mom with me at the sanatorium? I think she\'ll be overjoyed to see me bring a friend with me. You want to know why I\'m asking you? Well, I can\'t bring my other colleagues who work for the same boss with me, right? I can pay you an hourly... Oh, it isn\'t necessary? Well... up to you then.","This is the photo book collection you ordered. I caught a glimpse of the address by accident when the assistant was dispatching the order, so I decided to just bring it to you myself. By the way, you really didn\'t have to waste your money on buying this because I\'m standing right in front of you, right? Well? Are you happy with what you see?","Behind every successful model is a partner that supports them silently. {name}, are you saying that you want to be that person for me? You say such cute things too sometimes. Take care of yourself first, you fool.","I think that keeping a diary is a very meaningful thing because you\'re letting go of the past but not forgetting it. When I was reading through my diary today, I realized that you started appearing more and more in the moments that I wanted to preserve forever.","I don\'t have any aspirations to become an angel of a certain famous brand or the face of a campaign. I became a model just to make a living. But since I chose this path, I\'ll always do my best. It\'s the same in your case. Since you chose to hold my hand, you\'re not allowed to let go easily.","Happy New Year! I made sure I wouldn\'t have any work arrangements today so that this time would only belong to the two of us, and I didn\'t need my mom to remind me this time. Although I don\'t think there\'s anything special about the New Year holiday... I still want to spend it with you.","Really? You\'re going to give me chocolate, a high-calorie food that contains 600 calories per 100 grams... What? Why would I give it back to you? I didn\'t say I didn\'t like it. Here, I\'m going to give you another chance. Give me the chocolate in your hand.","Tenpai. The photo shoot for the cover photo is almost finished...","No-ten. I lost another job...","Don\'t dwell on things that have been lost, or else you\'ll just have more to worry about.","No matter how beautiful a piece of jewelry is, it is an eyesore if it appears in the wrong place.","Will I be the model who gets the final appearance for this event...","The world will become extraordinarily beautiful because of this show.","Everything is ready. It\'s time for the supermodel to come on stage!","Let\'s have an exciting show together!","The countdown to the fashion show has begun! Silence, please!","Whoever strikes first wins! Double Riichi!","Tsumo! Nice doing business with you.","You\'re the new secretary at Bamboo Cloud, and you don\'t even know who I am? I\'m Fuuka Minami, your new boss!","You may be my guests, but at this table, all pleasantries are saved for after the match.","Only those who are skilled and favored by the tiles can make it to the very top!","Pardon me, guests, but victory is mine.","Don\'t act so surprised. Strong players and good tiles are simply drawn to one another.","What kind of secretary keeps their boss waiting this long? Well, now that you\'re here, you\'d better get changed—we have restaurant inspecting to do.","There you are! Since you\'re late, I\'ve prepared an \"overtime giftpack\" for you. With a little extra elbow grease, I\'m sure you\'ll be finished in no time. Chop-chop, {name}!","My afternoon schedule... Oh, there you are, {name}. I\'ll let you confirm my schedule then.","We\'ve finished today\'s work with some time to spare. How about a game of mahjong with me then? Relax—you\'ll still be paid for your time, of course!","Do I go easy on customers in a game of mahjong? Of course not! True customer service is giving everything your best. Just look at the satisfaction on their faces even when they lose horribly, and you\'ll understand... Huh? They have masochistic tendencies? What do you mean by that?","Sigh... All these dull mahjong games I\'ve been playing recently are starting to make me miss my days at the shrine. My opponents there got more interesting by the day... I\'m getting fired up just thinking about it, hahaha!","Hey! Newbie! Hurry up and finish the work at hand right away and come play mahjong with me! I really need some stress relief now!","Phew... I\'m exhausted after all those meetings today. {name}, be a dear and come rub my shoulders, would you? This is one of your duties as my personal secretary.","What do you think? This is my treasure vault, I call it \"the Gate of Phoenix.\" You\'re the first one to see my extensive collection, so I bet you\'re feeling really proud of yourself! Just so you know, you\'re not getting anything from my collection no matter how much you like it!","The secret to always winning? Just like doing business, it all comes down to observing your opponents carefully and devising a winning strategy. However, the most important thing is to be decisive when the winning opportunity presents itself. Luck is like a gust of wind, and opportunities don\'t wait for those who snooze on them.","Zero points for artistry, zero points for taste, but 100 points for intention. Keep it up and bring me something more interesting next time.","Ooh! Your taste must be as good as mine if you were able to find a treasure like this. 85 out of 100 points. Don\'t let it go to your head!","You\'ve been working so efficiently lately. Looks like you\'re the only secretary I need.","It\'s been a while since I\'ve met someone who can talk to me so calmly. You look so harmless, but maybe you\'ll become a big shot one day.","No matter how big the business grows, to my parents, Bamboo Cloud will always be a restaurant where everyone is family. I always thought they didn\'t think big enough, but somehow, I\'m starting to understand how they feel.","I, Fuuka Minami, have a dream! I want Bamboo Cloud restaurants all over the world! It doesn\'t matter where or how many people there are there, I want them all to see Bamboo Cloud\'s sign. What? Why am I telling you this? Geez, you\'re really dense sometimes...","With you by my side, opening up Bamboo Cloud restaurants around the globe isn\'t just some pipe dream anymore. What do you say, are you brave enough to have a toast with me, the empress of this empire? Just so you know, you won\'t be able to back out now—even if our path leads us to hell.","Looking good. Let\'s go! Today\'s your debut at Bamboo Cloud. Just relax—as the personal secretary of \"the Phoenix of Bamboo Cloud\" approved by yours truly, you have nothing to fear.","Happy New Year, {name}! What do you think? Business has been booming, hasn\'t it? Almost all the branches are overflowing with customers. Looks like we\'re in for another good year, hahaha!","Here, try this and tell me what you think... Delicious, right? After all, I specially asked the flagship store\'s head pâtissier to teach me how to make this. Huh? Of course I made it myself. I\'ve been helping my father since I was a child, so making chocolate is a piece of cake... Huh? That\'s not what you\'re surprised about?","No-ten.","Everyone is bound to have bad luck once in a while.","There\'s no point in keeping things you don\'t need.","Relax! The final outcome won\'t change no matter how nervous you are. Just go with the flow.","Haha! It looks like someone is about to suffer a big loss... or does my statement apply to everyone here?","If that came as a shock to you, I\'m afraid your jaw might hit the floor when you see the amazing hands in store for you later.","Excuse me. Oh, you\'re all here early.","Give it your all, everyone – though I\'m sure we all know who the winner will be.","Kita.","Ron. Good game.","Tsumo. That was lucky.","Hello, I\'m Fei Ming, the owner of Magical Dream. It\'s a pleasure to meet you.","Hello, everyone. Let the tiles fall where they may.","You can\'t teach a fish to climb a tree... Heh.","Win or lose, it\'s all ephemeral.","Patience is a virtue.","I happen to have a pot of good tea today, have a seat if you\'d like... Eh? You\'re not moving, are you waiting for me to bring you a chair?","You\'re a bit later than usual today, aren\'t you? ...Not that I was specifically looking for you. I just wondered if perhaps you\'d run into some sort of trouble, that\'s all.","I certainly don\'t think I\'m as aloof or reserved as people say I am... I just don\'t see the need to force conversation with people I don\'t know well. Honestly, could you really imagine two strangers talking all night about losing mahjong games?","I\'ve invited a few friends to play mahjong with me today, you\'re welcome to join us if you\'d like... Eh? What\'s so bizarre about me having friends? ...Relax, I\'m the least eccentric of the bunch.","When it comes to mahjong, I don\'t have much insight or even a strategic approach. If I had to put it into words... I play from the heart. I play whatever hand I want, whether it\'s Fuuro or Damaten. As long as it\'s from the heart.","My goal in life? I thought only children and the elderly would ponder such a question. After all, at your age, all it takes is a couple of cups of tea and a few games of mahjong after work... and the day is over, just like that.","The rare volume \"Way of Tea: New Edition\"? Never heard of it... \"Steamed green tea wine,\" \"soy-braised pu\'er,\" \"sweet and spicy oolong\"... Now I suppose that explains its rarity.","The best water for this particular tea is none other than ice water from the snowfields... I even once went to collect a handful myself. The only sign of human life there was the trail of footprints I left behind, and even that was quickly buried under fresh snow... It sounds lonely? Hm, it was more like realizing that I am but a tiny speck in the vast expanse of wilderness.","As water turns to clouds and clouds turn to rain, all things continue in this endless cycle of life. I was just thinking... ahem... don\'t dwell too much on your earlier loss. Winning and losing are both part of mahjong, it\'s only natural... Hm? I should be more direct? My apologies. Consoling people isn\'t my forte.","By now, I\'ve grown accustomed to the way you drink tea. It\'s not that I\'m being stingy with the tea leaves, but I do worry you\'ll be up all night and blame me, the one who brewed them... At my age, I can\'t afford to stay up all night playing mahjong with you.","Thank you.","Well, you\'ve sure got me figured out... I\'ll hang it up in the lobby of the tea house so you can see it every day and know what good care I\'m taking of it.","They say life is but a dream. So what is reality? Is this One Han City, or... some other scene from your dreams? It\'s like Zhuangzi\'s dream – am I the butterfly, or is the butterfly me? Hehe.","I heard that my employee has been giving you some trouble lately... A firecracker? That she is... As long as she hasn\'t offended you... Oh? Concerned about you? She just didn\'t want you to make any complaints, that\'s all.","I can\'t hold my liquor? Who told you that? ...I simply don\'t like it, and I won\'t drink with you just to prove a point... Here, I\'ll make you a pot of tea instead. After all, alcohol only harms the body.","I see you every day, yet you haven\'t seemed to change one bit. Perhaps if we spent some time apart, I might notice a difference... but there\'s no need for that. If you want something, just tell me... Guess I still need to work on reading people better.","When I used to sit alone in this attic, I never thought the moonlight shining in through the window was anything special. But tonight... it feels quite enchanting. Yes, truly... enchanting.","You seem quite interested in this bird cage. Yes, it\'s waiting for a bird... Whether the bird or cage was here first doesn\'t really matter – each is simply waiting for the right match. Hm... If you\'re thinking of asking whether its wait is over, you\'ll have to look into your own heart for the answer.","Hm? Oh, I wasn\'t lost in thought, I was only thinking... between a wish and the outcome, which is the cause and which is the effect? Does desire manifest the outcome, or does the desired outcome prompt the wish? And of course, I also wonder what sort of wish you just made for us, and what kind of outcome you envision for us.","I\'ve never really paid much attention to this holiday before, but since it\'s here, I might as well join in the festivities. As for how exactly I do that... Why don\'t you show me?","Sextuple Yakuman... Heh.","Tenpai. I underestimated you.","No-ten. Hm, no harm in that.","Play from your heart, and the rest will follow.","Enjoy what you can while you can, and worry not about what you lose.","Here today, gone tomorrow. Such is life.","Nothing ventured, nothing gained. This hand certainly exemplifies \"high risk, high reward.\"","If I win this hand, let\'s go listen to some folk music after.","Since this is a game of mahjong, let\'s skip the formalities and let the tiles bring us together.","I\'m ready.","Kita. Anything useless should be discarded immediately.","Ron. That was rather remarkable.","Tsumo. I\'ll take that, thank you.","This exquisitely cut, translucent emerald is timeless and eternal... It reminds me of our friendship. How have you been, {name}? It\'s Saturne, what a pleasure to see you again. You\'ll always be welcome at my home.","I can\'t wait to see what choices you\'ll make here today.","Victories are certainly worth celebrating, but it\'s what follows that deserves deeper reflection.","I\'m one step closer to my ideal Northland.","Sacrifices must be made to bring about change. I\'m sure you all understand.","Hello, {name}. I always seem to run into you at such peculiar hours. You young people really do have interesting schedules. Are you wondering why I\'m still awake? Well, let\'s just say that as you get older, there always seems to be more to mull over, more to plan... Besides, a pleasant conversation like this with you hardly makes it a wasted night, does it?","{name}, you really should be more aware of what\'s behind you. That\'s not a good habit to get into. You must know that many rich and powerful people in Northland have lost their lives to an assassin\'s blade... Oh? So you weren\'t worried because you knew it was me? Right you are. I suppose I was worrying about nothing.","{name}, how long has it been since we first met? Oh, don\'t mind me... just a passing thought. People in my line of work tend to favor long-term investments. Time makes the pieces in our collections grow in value. And in much the same way, it strengthens our friendship, making it even more precious...","My hometown? Northland is a harsh place, all endless snow and biting cold. Faith is a big thing for most people there, and the \"pious\" priests are always keen to preach about love and hope. Me? I have my own beliefs. Let\'s just say they\'re certainly not cut from the same cloth as theirs.","{name}, how about we tackle a few more of these \"which tile to discard\" questions together? The most fascinating thing about them is that you can never alter the tiles in your hand, and yet your very next choice determines the entire course ahead. Eventually, both of us will face the end in our own way. Isn\'t that so?","Mahjong isn\'t common in Northland; I only learned it through business dealings. In those games, though, winning or losing mattered far less than sealing the deal – after all, business is all about profit. Ever since you showed me the real joy of mahjong, those business matches only feel empty and tedious. It\'s difficult to tolerate the pretense once you\'ve experienced the real thing, wouldn\'t you agree?","What often makes a gem valuable isn\'t the gem itself, but the stories behind it, with the most valuable ones being those associated with the most intriguing or illustrious tales. Unfortunately, everyone is curious about these stories but oblivious to the bloody truths that stain them... Ah, but if you\'re interested in those truths, {name}, I\'d be more than willing to share what I know.","It just happens that I\'ve formed a secret alliance with one of our mutual friends – a man of few words, but firm in his convictions and utterly trustworthy. We\'ve reached the same conclusion: The Church as it stands is past saving. Now, he intends to reclaim what is rightfully his, and we shall witness this reckoning unfold upon the snowfields, together.","Northland is ruled by the law of the jungle – a place where only those who have a heart of stone can endure the cutthroat world of politics and business. That\'s why I\'ve always strictly adhered to my principles and been so cautious in my dealings with others – to ensure I never showed any so-called \"weakness\"... But then I met you, and I\'m starting to think that... perhaps it\'s time to consider other ways.","Oh? Interested in my cane? It\'s not something I\'d let just anyone touch. It\'s a favorite of mine – nice to hold, elegant, and made of very fine materials. Do be careful, though. There\'s a concealed blade inside, so you wouldn\'t want to be careless with it. It can be quite dangerous.","Thank you for the gift.","If this gift represents your trust in me, then I\'ll repay you in kind.","Time has a way of changing almost everything. It grinds down mountains to valleys, turns glaciers into mere streams. It can make a man question his faith, wear away his edge. But it can never touch my resolve. I will build a new Northland, and I will pay any price to do it.","{name}, you\'re sometimes too naive and trusting, which reminds me a lot of myself when I was younger. I learned the hard way and paid a steep price for that innocence... so I hope you never have to experience the pain of betrayed trust, my friend.","What do I wish for? Heh, that\'s a question I haven\'t heard in years. At my age, people don\'t generally ask you that sort of thing anymore. You\'re a rare one for even wondering, {name}. Well, if I have to make a wish, then I wish that every child in Northland could buy themselves a sweet orange soda from a roadside stall.","The elite within the Church fear the Holy Maiden – she\'s too much of an enigma for their liking. They find me a much easier proposition. I may be calculating, true, but I always offer a more congenial front. And with enough wealth, strategically placed, even a gemstone dealer like myself can ascend to the office of Cardinal. But make no mistake: I am not, and never have been, in their camp. And I never will be.","Even a child knows: When a tree decays from its roots, lightning will strike it down. And when we look at the Northland Church, rotten to its very core... well, the solution becomes rather obvious, doesn\'t it? This path ahead is sure to be paved with blood and thorns. Even knowing that, you still choose to walk it with me? ...I see. Then let\'s see this through to the end, you and I.","Relax, {name}. I don\'t bare my heart to just anyone, you know. Let\'s put all the maneuvering and scheming aside for a while. Take away the \"Cardinal\" title, and right now, I\'m just a person who wants to enjoy a moment of peace with someone dear to me. Heh, don\'t look so surprised. After all we\'ve weathered... as my friend, my companion on this journey, what do you say to a drink?","Happy New Year, {name}. The New Year in Northland is a much quieter affair, not nearly as bustling or lively as it is here. But I would still like to invite you to go there with me. I want to introduce my hometown to you, tell you of my hopes for its future, and work to turn my dreams about the snowfields into reality, one step at a time. Will you witness this journey with me, {name}?","A day like today is certainly busy for a gemstone dealer. And yet, rather than getting caught up in the trade, I\'d much prefer to come see you. My many years of business experience have taught me that only things that can\'t be bought with money are worth investing time in. And today, all my time is for you.","Tenpai. All proceeding as expected.","No-ten. Unexpected things always seem to happen...","Rarity drives value – overstocking kills it.","This is a necessary trade-off.","Time is on the side of this gemstone dealer.","The most dazzling pearl is already in my hand...","The kindling is laid... It\'s just a matter of time now.","Greetings, everyone. Let\'s see if today\'s game proves to be an exciting one. I\'m looking forward to it.","I\'m ready whenever you are.","Kita. You\'d better watch out!","Ron! Hehe.","Tsumo. Here I go!","A pleasure to meet you. My name is Hua Yubai, I am the acting leader of the Floating Dreams theater... Huh? Y-You were just with my sister?! Fine, fine... You got me. Don\'t expect to get so lucky next time, though. Lemme start over – I\'m Hua Yuqing, nice to meetcha!","Your solo\'s over, now it\'s my turn to shine! I\'m ready for the sweet sound of victory.","Hehe, a standing ovation!","Nice start!","Hehe! Destiny called, and I answered!","Hey! Floating Dreams has a new show coming up. Want me to save you a ticket?","This front row is all suuuper duuuper VIP seats for Floating Dreams\' most honored guests! But... when the show starts, that spear might \"SHWING\" – and slice right through your collar... Pft! I\'m just playing. The most it\'ll do is make you dizzy with its flashing shine. Go on, take a seat.","Verdant willow in a shroud of mist, birdsong ringing through peach blossoms... Wah! Don\'t touch my head while I\'m reading the script! You scared me...","Whew, finally... no headpieces, no makeup, just some hard-earned rest. What do you wanna do?","When it comes to choosing a script, I actually prefer plays about codes of honor and settling scores. Some plays always go on about how \"a gentleman\'s revenge is never late\" or whatever... If years have passed and it\'s still late, I can\'t imagine what is...","Gentle? You mean my sister? Hehe, looks like you don\'t know her half as well as I do. She\'s good at keeping the troupe in order, and yep, she\'s good at keeping me \"in order\" too... But it\'s all for the good of Floating Dreams. A good big sister knows when to bring out the carrot or the stick!","Mahjong and opera have something in common, you know – both are products of ancient culture that have evolved over time to attract new generations... And that\'s why my coming here to play isn\'t slacking off, it\'s studying the culture of mahjong. So, you better not rat me out to my sister, or else!","Shh! Don\'t say anything, just listen. Go to the newsstand at the first intersection and grab two of those huge signed Thunderclap posters. Then, turn left and go into the tailor\'s shop. The tailor will give you a costume trunk, stick \'em in there. When you reach the entrance to Floating Dreams, tell the manager that you\'re delivering repaired costumes, then come straight here to me. Right, the newsstand guy and the tailor are my informants, remember to give them the secret signal: \"Azure thunder!\" Okay, now repeat it back to me!","Um, thanks for your help today. Yubai usually does my makeup, so this is a nice change of pace. But be careful not to let the paint stain your hands... All done? Lemme see... Wait a minute, didn\'t you say you\'re good at this? What... the heck... is this?! {name}, get back here!","Singing, speaking, acting, and martial arts are the fundamentals of traditional opera... Remember what the last one is. If you keep poking and prodding me, I\'ll just have to give you a taste of the \"fundamentals\" I\'ve been practicing since I was little.","You came to see the show AND brought me a gift? I\'ll have to start calling you \"kind soul\" like Yuan Xiao does from now on, hehe.","Aw, what do I do now? This is such a nice gift, I kinda don\'t wanna share it with Yubai...","When I was little... I was probably the kid that frustrated Yubai the most. I\'d secretly swap the scripts she was writing for amusement park maps, smear menthol ointment on her zither strings, dress up as her and beat up the chubby kid next door... Looking back, I guess I went a little overboard. But she was always busy studying music, chess, calligraphy, and painting instead of playing with me...","Actors have to practice hard if they want to pull off a perfect performance. But the way I see it, you can\'t always be practicing behind closed doors. If you really wanna get to know people\'s tastes nowadays, you gotta leave the theater and see the outside world.","Since we\'re such good friends, I\'ll let you in on a li\'l secret – Thunderclap\'s enigmatic composer, \"Skyazure,\" is actually none other than yours truly. Hehe, surprised? Why don\'t I use my real name? Hmm... Well, rock and opera just don\'t mix, do they? If other people in the troupe found out, they\'d definitely go tattling to my sister. I don\'t wanna give her any more trouble.","Why did I join Thunderclap? Hm... Other than liking the band, there\'s another reason I\'ve never told anyone... As you can see, the theater\'s been losing steam because it hasn\'t kept up with young people\'s interests. Yubai worries about this too. But I think it\'s only because opera hasn\'t found the right stage for this era. When it does, more people will see just how inclusive and fascinating it really is. So, I wanna try and do just that!","Every minute on stage comes from years of hard work and wholehearted devotion to one thing. That\'s what being an actor – and a person – is all about. These values were passed down by our ancestors, and we must honor them. So, {name}, don\'t let me catch you doing anything half-heartedly!","In \"White Snake,\" Xiaoqing\'s big sister is the most important person in the world to her. But in real life... Ahem... If I were to write Xiaoqing her own story, I\'d have her meet her own destined person and develop her own affections... As for who that person would be, well... someone as smart as you should have no trouble figuring that out.","{name}! You gotta help me! Ughhh, down at last. I wanted to give everyone a surprise by hanging up the lanterns, but my sleeve got caught on the roof... Thank goodness you came along! Anyway, my lifesaver, if I were an ox for the next lifetime, I\'d definitely serve you tirelessly. Wait, no, an ox might end up in soup... I know! A snake! I\'ll repay you as a helpful snake!","In the past, I definitely would have spent a holiday this special with Yubai, but things are different now. I couldn\'t just leave you all on your own, could I? Not that this means you\'re more important to me than my sister! At most, you\'re... At most you\'re equally important. Okay? Let\'s leave it at that before you ask me something silly like \"If Yubai and I fell into the water, who would you save?\" I can\'t swim, so I wouldn\'t be saving anyone. So, let\'s steer clear of the pools and head out for a cozy dinner date instead!","Hehe! Single-wait Four Concealed Triplets!","Hehe! Thirteen Orphans!","Hehe! Nine Gates!","Hehe... Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai! I am a leading actress, after all! Hehe.","No-ten. Figures, I still have a lot to learn...","Hmm... What kind of quirky tune is this hand playing today?","No worries, no worries! Better to play it safe.","Hm... Yubai\'s always telling me that patience is a virtue. No need to rush it!","Not even a seasoned opera enthusiast could pick a hole in a performance this flawless!","If the gods are listening... If I can just draw that tile, I swear I\'ll eat my vegetables for the rest of my life...","Fate brings people together, no matter the distance. I\'m so happy we were all fated to play mahjong here!","So many roles and all kinds of stories... Which will we perform today?","Kita. Ride the wave when it comes.","Ron. What a pleasant surprise.","Tsumo. Music to my ears.","I\'m Hua Yubai, the acting leader of the Floating Dreams theater. A pleasure to meet you... You just... met me on Champion Street? Ah, that must have been my twin sister, Yuqing, you met. I apologize if she offended you in any way, please don\'t hold it against her. That said... do try to tell us apart next time.","Since I can hardly refuse your kind hospitality, I\'ll honor it by giving my utmost commitment.","Your kind support is deeply appreciated.","A sleeve\'s gentle sweep, a tune of bright joy.","Hope the elegant echoes of victory linger on and on.","There are no performances scheduled at Floating Dreams today, so I have time to spare. If you happen to be free right now, would you like to join me for a walk?","The manager told me... that you\'ve stopped by Floating Dreams quite a few times over the last couple of days, but I\'ve been too busy to properly greet you. So, to make it up to you, let me join you in any activity you choose today.","Yuqing and I are twins, but our personalities couldn\'t be more different. If she were with you right now instead of me, I\'m afraid you\'d already have quite the commotion on your hands... But if you enjoy peace and quiet, you\'re welcome to stay with me a while longer. As for me, I rather like spending time with you.","I heard your neck and shoulders have been bothering you, is that right? Perhaps I could be of some help. I\'m studying acupuncture, which can stimulate your meridians and promote circulation – it\'s quite effective in treating this sort of ailment. It\'s just that... my specialty is long needles. Would you be comfortable with that?","I\'ve always run cold, so my hands are a bit chillier than most people\'s. I suggest holding my hand through my sleeve... No need? Yuqing said you were a very kind person, but I didn\'t understand what she meant at the time. Now I do... You really are a kind, warm person.","It may be difficult to bring in new audiences with old songs, but it\'s just as hard to keep regulars satisfied with new ones. That\'s why Floating Dreams won\'t abandon the old in blind pursuit of the new. Changes in the theater should be as subtle as a drizzle on a gentle breeze.","In our operas, it\'s always the elder sister who teaches the younger sister that the world is a good place filled with friendship, love, and family. Outside the opera, however, it\'s Yuqing who\'s always telling me these things.","Oh, this? It\'s realgar wine... A concerned fan sent it saying that Yuqing and I performed so convincingly in \"White Snake\" that it didn\'t seem like we were acting... What\'s that curious look in your eyes? Don\'t tell me you agree with him. Aren\'t you afraid... that he might be right?","This umbrella? Purple handle, 84 ribs... The character in the opera says that it\'s waiting for a rain. With the drizzle coming down outside, I think... I\'ve found that person.","Your forehead... It\'s nothing, just give it a wipe and you\'ll be fine. What were you up to just now? You\'re covered in dust. You weren\'t... doing something secretive, were you?","You must show gratitude for every kindness extended to you – that\'s our rule at Floating Dreams.","Champion Street is very particular about returning favors. So, apart from thanking you... how else can I repay you?","Previously, Yuqing and I made a name for ourselves in the opera world with our rendition of \"Borrowing an Umbrella at West Lake.\" What\'s a shame is that, to this day, I still haven\'t fully grasped the quintessence of the characters\' feelings. The afterglow reflected on the lake, the heart-wrenching moment on Broken Bridge... I might capture their form, but never their true spirit.","Floating Dreams, floating dreams, life is like a dream. My father always said that only on that dreamlike stage can one find true fulfillment. But sometimes, I wonder if we should seek fulfillment off-stage as well. The only thing is, I\'m not sure what a \"fulfilling\" life off-stage looks like. What do you think?","Yuqing often sneaks out to see rock concerts. I\'ve known all along, and... I also know that you\'ve been helping her keep it from me. I even got to know the \"informants\" she mentioned who have helped \"smuggle\" tickets, posters, and such to her. Why haven\'t I said anything? Well... there\'s no keeping someone as spirited as her trapped in this courtyard forever. Besides, exploring new takes on opera isn\'t such a bad thing, is it?","A secret? I do have one that I\'d never tell anyone else... but I\'ll make an exception for you. Sometimes I\'ll wear Yuqing\'s clothes around the troupe – that way, I get to hear all sorts of things people normally wouldn\'t say around me... It\'s fascinating. Eh? Am I worried you\'ll spill the beans? Not at all, because... they\'d never believe you.","A great performer is expected to handle all manner of roles and styles effortlessly... but that\'s easier said than done. Whether it\'s the dead of winter or the height of summer, the troupe always works tirelessly day in and day out... Sometimes I wonder if I\'m too hard on them... You came all the way to Floating Dreams, and here I go complaining to you. But... for some reason, the words just pour out when I\'m near you, like... like I\'m being a little clingy.","You want to try doing my makeup? Whether it\'s drawing eyebrows, fitting wigs, or applying ornaments, I usually handle the costumes and makeup for Floating Dreams myself. Letting someone else do it for me would be... quite novel. And for some reason, the thought of you drawing on my eyebrows is surprisingly exciting. It\'s almost as if... I\'m starting to understand the feelings of the characters in the opera a bit more. Does this count as a kind of \"fulfillment\"?","Yuqing and the manager are in the courtyard getting the banquet ready for later, so I\'m the only one who could come out to greet you. What... Not pleased? Shall I have them come out instead? I\'m only teasing... Here, take this lantern and let\'s go in together to welcome the new year. Oh, and Happy New Year. I hope you\'ll be here with us in the coming year too.","I\'ve played the role of a wife in many operas, but outside of the theater... I wonder what real couples are like. Perhaps... they\'re like this? ...It\'s just that, with our hands entwined, it really feels like I\'ve transformed into a snake and wrapped myself around you... Feeling shy now? I thought... you wouldn\'t have invited me to celebrate this holiday with you if you hadn\'t thought it through.","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. It must be fate.","No-ten. There\'s always next time.","A good performance isn\'t just about the lead actor – the supporting cast is indispensable as well.","Beautiful flowers are fragile. There\'s no helping it.","With the thundering drums, it\'s time for the final act.","Don\'t worry, the tile you\'re waiting for will come when the time is right... What an excellent hand you have.","It may not be \"one in a million,\" but it\'s still a rare hand. The only thing that would make it better is if it could turn into a winning one.","Share your heart with songs, and make friends through tiles.","The gongs are sounding and the crowd is buzzing – time to take the stage.","I\'m Toru Asakura, a fellow traveler. Nice to meet you.","Alright, go for it.","Yep.","Cool.","Not too shabby.","Morning. In the entertainment industry, we say that no matter what time it is.","Alright, there\'s somewhere I wanna go. Let\'s go.","Who did I just say hi to? Hmm... I don\'t know either.","If you want to do something, just do it. That\'s what people are always saying anyway.","\"Played mahjong today.\" That\'s it... My journal entries are too short? But that\'s really it.","If you don\'t understand something, try running 100 laps along the river... But not all in one go.","People tell me I play \"pretty well.\" But I think I could do better.","Whoops... I forgot the lyrics. It\'s only my third time singing it, after all. Still, with the others working so hard, it\'ll be fine.","Huh? You want me to play a game of mahjong in your place? Sure... I got it.","Thanks for your help. Would you like something to drink? My treat... Whoops, I forgot my wallet. Looks like I owe you again.","I... like it, thanks.","How did I become an idol? Well... I guess I just became one. Or maybe... I never became one?","Ever since I was little, I sometimes have this weird dream where I can\'t climb to the top of the jungle gym no matter how hard I try... Life is long, huh?","Sometimes I feel like life is pretty short. I feel it even more so when I\'m writing in my journal.","If water fleas have hearts, do you think they pound too?","Is it really me, like this?","You know what, forget about that \"life is long\" stuff for now. Right now, life is good.","Happy New Year. Wanna go make a prayer together?","Here, chocolate... Although, maybe a Riichi Bet would be a better gift for the occasion?","Tenpai. Not bad.","No-ten. Shoot.","Four-Wind Discarded. Everything\'s falling into place.","Four-Kan Abortion. I\'m relieved, actually.","Four-Player Riichi. Everyone\'s really getting fired up.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors... Thirteen Orphans?","They just keep coming.","Go.","Not many tiles left now...?","Okay, I can step up too.","Not bad.","Sorry if I\'m interrupting... Um... should I say more?","...Oh, are we starting?","Hey, I\'m Madoka Higuchi. Are you the nice Jyanshi Koito was talking about? She said you could teach me everything I need to know about mahjong. Thanks in advance.","Nice to meet you.","That turned out pretty well.","I won.","I put in some effort.","...Oh, I didn\'t see you come in. I was up all night last night, so I\'m still a little groggy...","You\'re looking pretty tired yourself. Want a cup of black coffee? Don\'t worry, it\'s on me. I can get it reimbursed at the office later.","Has Hinana been teasing you? Heh... Don\'t mind her, she\'s just playing around... probably.","I admit that work has its demands, but basically, I\'m using independent training to shift my mindset.","The key to tidying up one\'s place is not being scared of discarding things. The way I see it, it\'s the same with mahjong.","The key to singing... Honestly, I\'m still just starting out. You\'d be better asking a professional.","The only thing I really need from my work is for it to have value.","U-Um... Could we maybe take a little detour? There\'s a m-moth by that lamppost up ahead...","It\'s fine. Even if you don\'t win, all that matters is that you made the effort.","I\'m not mad, this is just what an idol normally looks like when she\'s not managing her facial expressions. I appreciate your concern though.","Thanks.","I don\'t think I could accept something so valuable, even from a fan... Alright, if you insist, I\'ll take it. Thank you.","I\'m glad you liked the song, but it\'s the composer and the songwriter who should really get the credit. All I did was sing it the way it was meant to be sung.","What\'s hard about the job? Sometimes we get pretty tough songs. I have to really think about how to perform songs I don\'t understand that were written by someone else. Still... even when I do understand them, it\'s not like they become mine.","The recorder, study sessions, journal swaps... We haven\'t stuck with anything we\'ve tried out. As for being an idol... Koito says she wants to stick with it, but... I\'m still not sure.","What are they to me? Honestly, I haven\'t thought about it much. They\'re like the air around me.","Dreams? Heh... No, I\'m not interested in chasing shadows.","Even if I do have a really good dream, I\'d rather just wake up already... Because, whether I like it or not, all dreams end eventually.","Happy New Year. We just went and made our New Year\'s prayers, and now it\'s back to work. I\'ll leave it at that. Koito says you\'re coming to watch our performance, see you then.","This is a small token of my appreciation for all the help you\'ve given me. I didn\'t know what flavor you\'d like, so I just got the best-selling one. Hopefully it\'ll be good.","Tenpai. I guess I\'m nearly there.","No-ten. Hard work doesn\'t always pay off.","Four-Wind Discarded. Everyone\'s movements are so coordinated, it\'s like a group dance routine...","Four-Kan Abortion... Shame to see my Dora go to waste.","Four-Player Riichi. Should I stick with Damaten...?","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. If something\'s not realistic, it\'s better to give it up as quickly as possible.","Once you play a tile, you\'ll play it again no matter how many times you keep drawing it.","If a Dora can\'t be used, you might as well pretend it doesn\'t exist.","Time to act wisely...?","...My luck was pretty decent this time.","It may be Tenpai, but that doesn\'t mean anything if I can\'t win with it.","I\'m Madoka Higuchi. I look forward to playing with you.","Don\'t worry about me. I\'m ready to start when you are.","Riichi...","Double Riichi...","Chii...","Pon...","Kan...","K-Kita.","Ron!","Ts-Tsumo!","...H-Hi, I\'m Koito. Koito Fukumaru... U-Um, I\'m a high school student and an idol... Er, I-I mean... I\'m working really hard to be an idol right now... Sorry, anyway, nice to meet you!","Phew... I know I can handle a competition of this level!","I... I\'m sure it\'s all thanks to our fans that I got this far...?!","I... I won? That\'s... amazing... I\'ll try even harder next time!","Huh? R-really? Hehe...","Here! Er, um, w-w-were you looking for me?","S-Seriously, what am I gonna do with you... If I weren\'t here, you\'d be as helpless as everyone else, wouldn\'t you, {name}?","...Take a break? No, um, I-I\'m fine, don\'t worry about me... This intensity is actually completely normal... I have to practice my singing and dancing whenever I can...! No matter where I am, I have to study and train as usual. I can\'t slack off.","Pyah! Wh-Wh-What is it?! Did I do something? The... The music got so intense all of a sudden... Riichi? Ooh, right, I remember now! Phew... Mobile mahjong games are so great, now I can practice even by myself... Thanks so much for the recommendation.","I know right? Everyone\'s so amazing! They can try mahjong once and get good at it almost immediately! And it\'s not just mahjong, it\'s been like this from the start with dancing, singing, publicity shoots... That\'s why I\'m so lucky to get to be with them all the time... Huh? Oh, s-sorry... When it comes to them... I always go on and on...","...Toru\'s in pretty good shape? S-Sure, that\'s true... But why would you say that all of a sudden...? D-Did something happen? Huh? The temperature in her room...? Oh...! I think that\'s probably because she lost the AC remote again...","Big Three Dragons, Four Little Winds, All Honors, All Terminals... Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans... Okay, let\'s run through that again to really nail it down... Huh? Is... Is this... putting you to sleep?","Pyah! A-A-Are you okay? I-I didn\'t realize you were here... The theme of this live concert is an underwater stage... and I was trying to figure out how can we put the best splash into the dance routine... Let me wipe the water off you... Hehe... Sorry... Looks like you got even more drenched...","W-Wait, it\'s too dangerous! I can\'t just rush into something like this... Better think again... Hmm... Okay... how about this? Hehe... safe! I\'ve trained for such a long time now, there\'s no way I\'ll give someone else a win that easily!","Wh-What\'s the matter? Your face... It\'s fine... I can accept the outcome no matter what it is, just be honest with me... Huh? A full score...? Phew... D-Don\'t scare me like that next time, I nearly thought I failed... After all, a lot of what I\'ve learned in this time has been self-taught behind the scenes...","Thank you so much!","Thank you for your heartfelt support. I\'ll return the favor with an even better performance next time.","Working hard is just my way of keeping up with others, it\'s not something especially deserving of praise. That\'s what I\'ve always believed...","Thanks for, you know, looking after me all this time... I\'d be happy to learn even more... So, if you ever feel like a problem has come up between us, it\'s fine, please just tell me...","What kind of idol do I want to be? The answer I gave then was that I wanted to give our fans coming to our live performance a place to belong. Later, that motivated me to keep improving... I\'m so, so happy... that I can tell everyone that wish.","Playing mahjong with everyone here has been so relaxing, wonderful, and surreal... and... I can really feel... your sincerity towards me. So, I\'ll always, always, always remember all of this...","...A letter... for me? Oooh! I-I got it! N-No, it\'s fine... I thought it was a letter from a fan for a moment, th-that\'s why I didn\'t react... Huh? Y-You\'re nodding? You mean, I was correct? You are my fan...? Huh?!","Thanks for always cheering me on. Wherever I go, I\'ll always want to become an idol who gives her fans a sense of belonging... and you\'ve only made that conviction stronger... So, {name}, please keep cheering me on in the future!","Happy New Year! Um... er... I mean... I hope... you have... Anyway, have a happy new year, okay?!","F-For you. Ah, under the chocolate there\'s... a ticket to our show tonight... I-I-I know a lot of idols are performing in One Han City today, so... so... be sure to really think about which one to go to.","Sextuple Yakuman","Tenpai. I\'m doing my best!","No-ten. My dance moves need to be a little more precise.","Four-Wind Discarded? Oh no, wrong move!","Four-Kan Abortion. No problem, I\'m sure it\'ll all work out later!","Four-Player Riichi! Wow, everyone\'s big moment came almost at the same time!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. I won\'t give up that easily!","Huh? Haha, it\'s fine, it\'s fine. I-It\'s just the same tile again. It doesn\'t bother me!","Pyah? Wh-Wh-What did I do?","Only a few tiles left now... Things will definitely turn around!","Huh? This... is a very important test!","All that effort, and now... this is my chance!","Hello, everyone. I\'m Koito Fukumaru from Noctchill. It\'s nice to meet you!","Phew... Okay... I\'m ready.","Mmm... mmm... Aha! One Han City has sooo many tasty snacks! I\'m so happy... Huh? Surprised to see me? Why don\'t I formally introduce myself then! I\'m Hinana Ichikawa. Nice to meet you!","This should be easy enough.","Yaha... I\'ll get a reward for working so hard, right?","I\'m pretty good at this, huh?","Aha! This is a piece of cake after all!","Hey, I\'m so happy to see you!","Aha, we meet again. I think today\'s gonna be another super happy day for me!","Sorry to keep you waiting! My itinerary is in your hands today, right? I can\'t wait!","\"Memory\"... Looks like a business card from an idol office in One Han City... I got it when I went out. Huh? You know the idols there too? Aren\'t you the social butterfly, {name}...","I\'ve never wanted to be just like someone else. I just want to be myself!","Aaand... got it! Aww! You look sooo cute fretting over your tiles, {name}! Huh? Delete it...? How about this, you try and get Toru to come and be my model, and I\'ll delete it. Deal?","Cute... cute... this one\'s cute too...! Hey, {name}... you should\'ve told me how many cute tile designs there are, I would\'ve been 100 times more motivated to learn mahjong!","Aha! I saw how hard you were supporting me from the stage! It was amazing! There wasn\'t any time earlier for a group photo, but let\'s make up for it now! Say \"cheeeeese!\"","Huh? What if I get spotted by a fan on the street? I just give them a big hello! I am always careful, though. But you seem like you have plenty of experience being an idol\'s friend. I\'ll be counting on you if anything crazy happens!","Zzz... Zzz... Yaha! Did I scare you? Of course I wasn\'t really asleep, silly. Though, I was a little tired after the shoot... But I\'m trying my best to keep it together so I don\'t mess up today\'s new look! What do you think? Cute?","Aw, thanks for thinking of me!","Aha... I love this! How did you know?","Everyone says that they love how happy I look. But I don\'t just LOOK happy. I really AM happy!","Did you decide to follow me because you want to be as happy as I am?","For me, happiness is trying a new kind of ice cream... And if it happens to have a chocolate core, that\'s twice the happiness... And if it\'s also the kind of ice cream that won\'t make me gain weight... aha... then I\'d be super-duper happy!","How happy do I want to be? I see it like ice cream—the more scoops, the better, of course! \"Noctchill\" is super important to me as well... It\'s the scoop that\'ll never melt!","You\'re a radiant being yourself, {name}. You should have more confidence in your ability to attain happiness. Besides... I\'ve seen how much effort you\'ve been putting in.","If you want me to be happy forever, never leave my side, {name}!","Happy New Year! You\'re so spirited today, {name}—perfect for joining me for a walk, some photos, and taking part in the One Han City festivities... Huh? So, is that a yes?","Aha, it\'s Valentine\'s Day... The chocolates rolled out for the holiday in One Han City all look sooo tasty. Wanna come try them all with me? I\'m so excited I can barely stand it!","Tenpai. I\'m doing my best!","No-ten, hmm...","Four-Wind Discarded? N-No way...","Four-Kan Abortion? Yeesh, that\'s no good...","Four-Player Riichi? Wow, looks like we\'re all pretty serious about this...","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. It happens, I guess...","I\'m only doing it this way because I want to.","The happiest play is about to become clear.","I\'m in a pickle now, huh...","Aha! Am I good or what?","Yaha... I was born to be an idol, huh?","Thanks for waiting!","Don\'t miss any of my performances!","Kita. I\'ve got some clues!","Ron! I\'ve found the criminal! And it\'s you!","Tsumo. Hohoho, this is where it ends!","At this time of day... sniff, sniff, there\'s a faint scent of agarwood on you, which I think you picked up at Luck and Fortune... Hmm, the pad of your thumb is slightly harder than the rest, and... I knew it! You\'re that legendary Jyanshi. The chemistry lab isn\'t a good place to chat. I hope we meet at the school\'s detective club next time. By the way, I\'m Jane, a detective. Nice to meet you.","Every fact is a key that helps unlock the truth, and there\'s never just one key. So let\'s find them all and see what lies behind that door.","Hmph! I\'ve seen through what you\'ve been doing during the game. In the name of my grandma and the Detective X Agency, I\'ll now expose your crimes!","Every win gets you closer to the top, whether it\'s a huge hand or a small one. It reminds me of my detective work: every clue is important, because they all point to the same truth in the end.","Hohoho, this is just the beginning. What you\'ve seen just now will keep happening again and again.","Raised cheeks, contracted eyelids, a heart rate over 120 beats per minute... Hmm, something important must have happened to you today. Let me, Jane the great detective, help you figure it out.","Where have you been since we last met? Who were you with? What were you doing? Can anyone vouch for you... Ahem, please take my questions seriously. It will help me deduce whether you\'ve been up to any mischief behind my back! Or... do you plan on coming clean yourself?","A scary movie? You\'ve made a mistake if you want to see me scared. Detectives are the most determined materialists in the world. I only believe in my own deductions!","In science shows, they often say, \"These tropical plants grow in tropical rainforests where there are very few people.\" But if we think about it carefully, shouldn\'t they say, \"People rarely go to places where these tropical plants grow,\" instead? After all, you wouldn\'t want to go to a dangerous jungle filled with giant flowers that eat humans, right?! You definitely wouldn\'t go, would you?","The official price of the same shawl that Jane Christie wore is actually 35,000 Coppers?! Ahahaha... Instead of just robbing me, they are willing to give me a piece of clothing. I\'m so moved that my eyes are starting to well up with tears. *sobs*... How many jobs will I have to take to earn this much... damn it!","Have you also noticed? My informant, Ninomiya, is definitely born to be an investigator. With her flawless disguise, she can sneak in anywhere and gather intel effortlessly... This is such a powerful and unique ability. She\'s the very last tile I need to declare Riichi!","The order of the strokes in this autograph... and the pressure on that last stroke... Hmm, this looks suspicious...! Ah! Did you forge Joseph\'s autograph on this photo?! Don\'t play dumb with me. I\'m talking about Joseph, the host of that famous adventure show. Hmph! I should\'ve thought of this sooner. Given how close you two are, there\'s a 73% chance something like this would happen. Fortunately, the one I got before was genuinely signed by him.","Summer really is the most wonderful season of the year. My mom and dad are so busy at work that they only have time together during the summer vacation. That\'s when our whole family goes on a tropical island getaway, and my dad teaches me all sorts of life skills. That\'s also how I learned to play mahjong... Hehe, you think my dad is amazing, right? Actually, I have a nagging suspicion that he\'s a secret agent, but my grandma always says that I\'m thinking too much. Hmph, I\'ll find proof one day!","This is suspicious. Too suspicious. Why hasn\'t anyone ever stopped to question whether it actually makes sense? I\'m talking about the claim that the Mahjong Soul Shrine can grant any wish – especially considering everyone in One Han City believes it without a doubt. Hmm... I have a bold but reasonable hypothesis. If the Mahjong Soul Shrine is really the mastermind behind all this, then the citizens of One Han City are probably accessories. {name}, you\'re with me on this, right?","I ran into you right after arriving at the crime scene. This isn\'t something we can just chalk up to coincidence. You\'re coming with me to the detective club to explain why you happened to be at the scene where the lilies of the gardening club were stolen... And don\'t even think about lying. I\'ve been watching you closely – every word, every move – and I can instantly tell what\'s true and what\'s not. Any lie you try won\'t last three seconds.","Hmm... It seems you don\'t have the talent to be a detective. If you can\'t make such a simple deduction correctly, {name}, I think you need some special training.","You managed to discover the hobby I tried so hard to conceal... F-Fine then! You\'re the greatest detective in One Han City today. Only for today!","Jane Christie is a legendary female detective who left behind countless tales of detective prowess in One Han City. She\'s the pinnacle that every detective aspires to reach! Hehe, my grandma actually named me after her, {name}. Do you know what this means? It means I\'m destined to become the second Jane Christie!","The ABC theft case? Oh... you\'re talking about the famous painting theft I solved two years ago. I didn\'t expect someone would pay attention to the details of the case itself. Back then, the media was only excited that a good-looking girl cracked it. No one gave any close thought to how I actually solved the case. {name}, you really do have what it takes to be my assistant.","I... think I failed my exams again... But I don\'t think it\'s my fault. The theme of the essay is \"blue curtain.\" It\'s suspicious, right? If the color doesn\'t matter, why emphasize that it\'s blue? It must be some kind of secret signal or code, or maybe it alludes to the criminal\'s mental state at the time... I can\'t believe one of the comments said my essay wasn\'t positive enough. Hmph!","The things that appear most trivial often tend to be the ones that trigger major cases. Just imagine – this rainstorm right here? It might just be the consequence of a seagull\'s distant wing flap. That\'s why, as detectives, we learn that every case, no matter how small it seems, demands our utmost dedication.","My grandma established a detective agency called Detective X in her younger days. It had to close down for various reasons, but I know she would love to see it become One Han City\'s top detective agency once again. Now, it\'s up to me to fulfill my grandma\'s wish. As my assistant, you\'ll also need to work hard, {name}.","Hohoho! I announce that the truth has come to light. The criminal is– Ah! Stop moving around! You\'re interfering with my rehearsal. The moment a detective reveals the truth is the highlight of their career. I need the perfect pose and statement. As my assistant, you also need to practice your entrance to make it as impressive as possible. It\'s too late for you to back out now. Hehe, after all, nobody is more in sync than us.","\"I\'m worried you\'ll get swamped with wish messages at midnight, so I\'m wishing you a Happy New Year in advance.\" \"Please carry this blessing with you every day.\" Hmm... I guess it\'s inevitable that people send out mass messages on holidays. Oh, this one is even worse – they forgot to change the recipient\'s name... You\'re not planning on sending me a lazy copy-paste like that, are you? No way! But hey, it\'s New Year\'s, so a simple wish is definitely in order. Happy New Year, {name}!","Today, I\'m going to take this opportunity to teach you another exclusive detective skill – how to spot fake couples. Hehe, on this day, some people always pretend to be couples just to fit in. However, they are way too naive if they think they can fool me. Look at those two in yellow over there. The one on the left is wearing a hat, and they\'re sitting by the pool... The way they avoid looking at each other gave them away instantly. Hohoho... Huh? U-Us? Do we even need to pretend...?","Hohoho, Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. That was close!","No-ten. Damn... what did I do wrong?","Being able to quickly discern the value of clues is a must-have skill for any detective.","It\'s a shame – but only a little.","I need a little more time. I\'m one crucial clue away from the truth... Where could it be?","All the evidence has been collected, and everything you say will be used as evidence in court. Shush – you\'d best be careful.","Hmm... this hand, along with everyone\'s expressions right now... Hehe, this is turning into quite a big case. One of these three must be holding the most crucial clue tile! {name}, what do you think?","Have you all gathered here today just to play mahjong? That\'s such a waste of our talents. Why don\'t we make the winning conditions more challenging this time?","What are you waiting for? Let\'s get started.","Chii!","Pon!","Kan!","Kita! No countdown, please...","I win! This is great.","Tsumo. This is the best!","Excuse me, can you pick up the bamboo shoot over there for me? Thank you so much. Wow, there are so many nice people in One Han City! Oh yes, I\'m Yuan Xiao, and it hasn\'t been long since I started living here in One Han City. Let\'s hang out when you\'re free! You can find me at Magical Dream, kind soul!","Wait! Let me order a large takeout first. After all, you gotta eat lots to have the strength to fight to the end.","Of course! This is what makes mahjong so fun!","I look up at the bright moon, then I look down and keep playing mahjong. If the folks back home ask about me, tell them I won with a Full Flush!","Hehe, nothing can stop me when I\'m lucky! I\'m going to go all out now!","Hi, kind soul! We\'re missing a fourth player. Come play with us!","I didn\'t play well today. Can you comfort me? Hey, in a sense, mahjong is also an art that builds character. I mean, dealing into an opponent\'s hand a lot really teaches you to be more open-minded and resilient, ahahaha.","This is my friend, Huo Guo... No, no, no, your pronunciation is wrong. Huo Guo will ignore you if you say that, so repeat \"Huo Guo\" after me. Well, since everyone speaks the local dialect in my hometown, Huo Guo doesn\'t understand Mandarin at all, haha.","Huo Guo is already very good at climbing trees even though it is very small. I think it won\'t be long until it can easily climb onto the roof of Magical Dream... Wait, Fei Ming won\'t get angry when that happens... right?","Umm... ah... hmm... I don\'t understand why I need to cut down on the calls. My grandpa said that you need to Pon to Kan. But I don\'t call Pon or Kan every time I get a chance. After all, don\'t you think it\'s nicer to draw the tiles yourself and keep them concealed?","So you call this game mahjong in One Han City? Haha, we have another name for it in my hometown. If you ever visit my hometown, I\'ll treat you to a three-part hospitality experience: drinking tea, playing mahjong, and having hot pot. The mahjong hot pot in my hometown is really famous. You don\'t need to worry about having to drink the soup base of the hot pot if you lose though because that\'s just a rumor.","I refuse to believe that there are people who don\'t like pandas in this world. It\'s absolutely, absolutely impossible! Humans don\'t stand a chance against the cuteness of pandas. The look they make when they eat bamboo makes me want to try some as well to see if it really is that delicious.","I quite like One Han City, after all, I can play mahjong here whenever I go, which makes me feel like I\'m at home. The only bad thing is that mahjong is played completely differently here. Furiten and everything else are really annoying. The essence of playing mahjong is winning, winning, and winning!","If I had to mention one thing that\'s strange about Fei Ming, it would be that he adds sugar when making scrambled eggs with tomato. Don\'t people usually add chili peppers?","Hey, kind soul, do you ever get hungry when Kaguyahime is around? She reminds me of a rabbit cold dish my grandpa used to make... I\'m so hungry now.","I can\'t believe you don\'t know what I like even though we\'ve known each other for so long! Hmph! That\'s not good at all.","Kind soul, you are just too nice! I really like you today too!","My pronunciation is very standard! I learned it seriously before coming here because I wouldn\'t be able to communicate with anyone if I kept speaking the dialect of my hometown. But... I think I\'ll end up using it here and there anyway, so I hope you won\'t mind, kind soul.","The third floor of Magical Dream... Although the boss didn\'t say I can\'t go there, I don\'t think anyone has ever been there. I can\'t shake the feeling that there\'s a mysterious power there that makes people stay away from it... Ah! Are you thinking of inviting me to explore Magical Dream with you at night?","Is my kung fu good? Hehe... My grandpa said that kung fu runs in our blood, and we can all use a few moves when we need to, Huo Guo included.","Although the panda was the mount of the god of war in ancient legends, after spending some time with them, you\'ll start to wonder if it\'s actually possible to fight a war while mounted on a panda. They are strong and have a nasty bite, but... do they really have the right personality?","One Han City is so big. I came here because the people of my hometown said this is where people go to pursue their dreams. However, I realized after coming here that I don\'t actually have a dream. Even so, I\'m liking this place more and more. What about you, kind soul? Do you like this place?","Wh-What kind of evil food is this so-called double-flavor hot pot? This concerns my bottom line and dignity, so there\'s no way I\'m saying yes! Th-That\'s unless you insist on having it... Okay, okay, it\'s not absolutely impossible, but the spicy soup can\'t just be mildly spicy!","Happy New Year, kind soul! Brrr! It sure is cold during winter in One Han City. I feel like I\'ve been hit by a magic attack that penetrates my bones through whatever I wear. Luckily, you\'re here with me, and it\'s much warmer when we\'re huddled together. In that case, I want to be with you in the new year too. Yes, two people are always better than one.","Hey, kind soul, do you want to hang out today? Yes, it\'s, well... umm, isn\'t it a holiday today? You mustn\'t have any other plans, right? Right? In that case, do you want to celebrate today with me and Huo Guo? I promise you\'ll have an incredibly good time!","Tenpai, I\'m amazing like always.","No-ten. Oh no, they\'re gonna check my hand now.","If you manage to discard all the tiles for Four Concealed Triplets... I guess you\'re incredibly lucky in another sense...","Ah, my sparkling Dora! I\'ve lost it and its points forever.","All of a sudden, there are only so few tiles left. Wow, things are suddenly so intense!","I\'ve decided. If I win this game, I\'m going to dig out the freshest bamboo shoots for Huo Guo tomorrow morning! If I don\'t... hehe, that\'s impossible. With you here, there\'s no way I can lose!","Keep calm and remember to put on a poker face. Don\'t let them notice that I\'ve started to tenpai with a big hand. Yes, I need to disguise everything perfectly so I can trick them into playing the tiles I want.","I\'ve gotten better at mahjong. I\'m going to prove that today.","Come on, let\'s fight to the end.","Riichi","Double Riichi","Kita.","Ron. Bulls-eye, I win.","Tsumo. I\'ll take this...!","Nice to meet you, I\'m Sakura Matou. Sorry for any inconvenience... Eh? You\'re happy that I\'m here...? Th-thank you...","Please be patient with me... I\'ll do my best!","I did it! I won!","I... I can\'t believe how lucky I am today...","I-I did it! That\'s amazing...","Hello. You\'re playing mahjong today too, right? I don\'t know if I\'ll be any good, but could I play with you?","Welcome back. Um, you\'ve been taking care of me a lot these days, so I was thinking of doing something in return. Is there anything you\'d like to eat?","I know I might not look it, but I\'m actually in the archery club at school... Does Asaha High School have an archery club I could practice with? I wouldn\'t want my skills to get rusty while I\'m here in One Han City.","I never dreamed that I\'d have regular days just playing mahjong with everyone... It\'s such a strange feeling.","Fuyumi and her big brother get along quite well. Seeing them reminds me that such good sibling relationships are possible. It makes me feel kind of happy...","Some day, if I became a \"bad person,\" would you be afraid of me? ...Oh, I see. That was fast. But I\'m happy to hear you say that.","Hmm... Oh, hello. I\'m not busy with anything, I was just doing some research on One Han City cuisine... Well, not \"research\" exactly, I was just curious about how it\'s different from the food in Fuyuki City... Eh? You\'d like to know more? R-Really...? Okay, let me get my notebook!","If I can live cherishing the little things and simple memories, that\'s enough for me. The small moments, like cooking together in the kitchen or sharing a meal with someone special... To me, they\'re irreplaceable treasures, not just everyday occurrences.","You\'re back? I just made some pasta with tomato sauce, give it a try. Eh? Th-This\'s not what you wanted? Oh, but the priestess at the Mahjong Soul Shrine called and said you\'ve been wanting to eat this but were too shy to ask... Hehe, I see. That\'s okay. Please tell her that if there\'s anything she\'d like to eat, just let me know next time.","...Sorry, I messed up again... I\'ll practice a few more times. It\'s okay, learning to play mahjong is fun. Thanks for being such a good teacher, I\'ll keep trying my hardest.","You\'re giving something this precious... to me? Are you sure...?","Thank you! ...If you\'d like, why don\'t you have half, and we can enjoy it together?","Why do I like cooking? Well... I set a goal for myself, and it\'s to cook together with a certain person I care about. So, I\'ve been working towards that bit by bit... Hehe, that\'s all there is to it. It\'s nothing special, really...","One time after school, I saw a boy practicing the high jump. He kept failing over and over... As I watched him, I wondered why he didn\'t just give up... Maybe I\'ve never been a \"good\" girl.","I was given this key by the most important person in the world to me. It\'s the most precious gift I\'ve ever received, and it\'s also like an amulet to me. Even though we\'re apart, as long as I\'m holding it, I feel like we\'re at each other\'s side.","I will always cherish the kindness you\'ve shown me, {name}.","Having someone there to eat the food I cooked and to help me fold the clothes I washed... Days like these are more precious to me than any treasure in the world.","Between every nightmare... I now have even more memories I want to protect while I\'m alive. Is someone like me worthy of such a miracle...? Thank you, {name}.","Happy New Year, {name}... Are you sure it\'s okay to team up with me right at the start of the year? In this battle... you might lose if you\'re with me. ...Okay, I understand. Let\'s do this then! I\'ll do everything I can to protect you!","It\'s Valentine\'s Day. Will you be giving someone a gift, {name}? If you\'re going to make a dessert from scratch, I\'d be happy to lend you a hand.","Mmm... Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. So close...","No-ten. I\'ll just have to try harder in the next match.","Four-Wind Discarded. Do we all have less-than-ideal hands...?","Four-Kan Abortion. I guess that proves you should never be too greedy.","Four-Player Riichi. Just in the nick of time...","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. That\'s fine, my luck hasn\'t been that great anyway...","Hm... I... I got the same tile again.","This... should be the best time to play this one.","I don\'t have that many left to play. I just need one final hope...","Will the winner this time... be me?","I feel a little hungry...","Um, excuse me. It\'s nice to see you again.","I can start at any time.","Kita!","Ron. Take this, Gandr!","Tsumo. Sorry about that.","I\'m Rin Tohsaka, but you can call me whatever you like. I hear One Han City is famous for mahjong competitions, and that everyone must take part. So, the next time we meet, we may be enemies.","Running away from a fight isn\'t my style. Since we\'re all here, show me what you\'ve got.","My victory! Now, I think I\'ll just help myself to everything.","A fitting outcome for my abilities. If you\'ve got a problem with that, then try beating me next time.","That\'s what happens when someone without the skill waltzes onto a battlefield they don\'t belong on.","Yawwwn... Morning... I can skip breakfast. It\'s not that big of a deal to me. Huh? P-Play mahjong...? Now? I thought it was normally played at night.","You\'re looking pretty laid-back for someone about to start a mahjong match... Ugh! Even if you end up losing all your points later, don\'t expect me to help you out!","Phew... That\'s heavy! I found this ridiculously large fan and heard it belongs to an immortal goddess who\'s also a boss lady or something. I figured you might know her, so I brought it over. Honestly, what a careless goddess she is to lose something this big.","Huh?! I\'m reliable? S-Someone actually said that? Ahem, well, true as it may be, being called reliable out of nowhere is a bit startling, you know... Alright, what is it you wanted my help with?","\"Average looking,\" \"unrefined,\" \"could be cuter\"...? Who said that...?! Ah, Archer... you\'ll REGRET this!","Jewels are as indispensable to the Tohsakas as scoring sticks are to Jyanshis. And there\'s another thing they share... they\'re definitely not cheap!","So, Servants can\'t fight in mahjong matches, which means Masters have to rely on their own skills... But that\'s fine, I can handle it solo! Even in a real battle, self-defense is a must-have skill for modern Mages. I\'ll show you my Bajiquan if it comes to that.","If you\'re ever not feeling well, just say so, and then take a good long rest. It\'s important to look after yourself! Ugh...! You\'re all like this! Why is everyone around me terrible at taking care of themselves?!","Come on, get ready for another crushing defeat at the mahjong table today... Huh? An app? A mahjong app...? We are going to play mahjong on the phone? G-Go to the official website, you say? Hmm... Oh, you\'ll help me? Well, if you insist. Just so you know, it\'s not like I\'m bad with phones or anything.","So... You\'re a Master too. Hmph, I heard everything. That cat-eared girl is your Servant, right? But what class could she be... Caster? No, scratch that... She\'s probably not a Berserker either... Ehh, is she a Saber?! ...Huh? She\'s not a Servant? But she keeps calling you \"Master\"... Ahem, m-my apologies, forget I said anything weird.","These lines are meant for those who can stand on their own... They\'re definitely not for trying to be cool while giving someone a gift!","J-Jewels... It\'s not like I\'m speechless because I\'m happy. It\'s just that accepting this would mean owing you, and then I\'d feel bad if I beat you at mahjong later... Anyway, thank you. I\'ll be sure to have a proper gift ready for you next time.","What a curious feeling... We\'re obviously meeting for the first time, yet you don\'t feel like a stranger at all. Um, don\'t get me wrong – I\'m not complimenting you... After all, we\'re competitors right now. I\'m just acknowledging your strength as my opponent, that\'s all.","Archer... Where did he run off to?! Hmph! I\'m sure even you know what it\'s like to have a disobedient Servant by now. He gets so careless just because we\'re in a place that SEEMS peaceful. It\'s really annoying.","Those three people over there... They seem really suspicious. That\'s right, by the fortune-telling stall. There\'s a girl with green hair and red panda ears arguing with a rabbit-eared lady, and a red-haired woman with them... What\'s suspicious about them? Well, they look like they can use Magecraft, with wands and crystal balls. Dressing in such a stereotypical Mage fashion actually makes them even more suspicious.","The boss lady at Luck and Fortune told me that if you win the mahjong competition hosted at the Mahjong Soul Shrine, your wish will be granted. It\'s simple, really. In a competition, all I have to do is aim for victory.","Wh-What\'s with you staring at me out of the blue...? Ugh, stop it already! I-Idiot! You\'re making me embarrassed, looking at me like that!","I always drop the ball at the key moments... Even though I handle everyday things just fine. But this time... I didn\'t mess it up, did I?","Happy New Year! Time sure has flown by... When I first met you, you seemed like a Jyanshi that couldn\'t do anything right. But now, you\'re actually kind of dependable. You\'ve really made a lot of progress this year... Wh-What\'s with that smile on your face? It\'s not like I\'m praising you for something incredible... Though, everything I said is true. Anyway, let\'s stick together in the new year too!","On a day like today, it would be kinda sad if I left you all by yourself. That\'s right, I\'ll keep you company for a little while. We can go for a walk, chat, do something special... Huh? What\'s something special? I-Idiot! What are you talking about? Wh-What else would be considered special on a day like this!","Here we go – Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. What now?","No-ten. Ugh... Come on!","Four-Wind Discarded. Casting a wind spell four times in a row... there\'s no way there\'ll be a fifth, right?","Four-Kan Abortion. Ahh... Ugh! That was a sly move...","Four-Player Riichi. A Mage should never bite off more than they can chew.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. I won\'t fall for such a weak trap.","Another one... What is this?!","Ugh, I can\'t believe I have to give up a Dora!","Now\'s the time to change the strategy!","Watch closely! This is where it gets exciting!","Here it comes! Let me show you Tohsaka\'s secret technique!","Thanks for waiting. Let\'s get started!","I\'m ready now.","Kita.","That\'s it! Ron!","Tsumo. Victory is mine this round.","Servant, Saber. I have come in response to your summons. From this moment on, my sword stands with you, and your fate is bound with mine.","Please fight with honor and integrity.","I won this time, but it was a fight where I couldn\'t let my guard down until the end. If the opportunity comes up, I would welcome another match.","Strike Air!","Excalibur––!","You will participate in today\'s mahjong competition? In that case, please allow me to accompany you.","Shall we play mahjong together, {name}? Under your recent tutelage, I\'ve become more accustomed to this form of combat, and I have some ideas I\'d like to put to the test in a real mahjong battle. It\'d be great if I could show you the fruits of my training!","Maintaining daily exercise is critical, especially for a Jyanshi, as your profession requires long, intense periods of sitting at the mahjong table. As such, I will join you in exercising for the sake of your physical health, {name}.","No, it\'s not that I\'ve gained any special understanding of mahjong... If you\'re asking why I\'ve been frequenting Luck and Fortune recently... it\'s because I made some like-minded friends there. Besides, their soba noodles are excellent...","I\'ve been here for a while now, and I appreciate the help you\'ve given me. Whether it\'s with mahjong or daily life, I wouldn\'t have adjusted so quickly on my own. Please let me know if there\'s anything I can do for you in return.","The show we saw together today... I was very impressed by the animal tamer. Rather than using threats or intimidation, she was genuinely admired by the animals. It\'s as if she were the queen of the forest. She must have a kind and strong heart.","Home-cooked meals have a more soothing taste than fine dining... Um, not that I\'m saying I want to come over for dinner, it\'s just an impression I got from seeing so many other people do so. They must like you a lot.","Oh, it\'s... a little stuffed lion. Yes, it\'s adorable... Eh? I-It looks like me? Um... \"Adorable\" is usually used to describe someone innocent and carefree, not someone like me, but... thank you.","I\'ve been working part-time at Éternité at the manager\'s request. Here\'s a coupon for you. There will be an event in the next few days, and I... I was hoping you could come.","{name}, thank you for looking after me all this time... Hm, too plain. {name}, I\'m sincerely grateful for the care you\'ve given me... No, that\'s too formal and distant... Eh? What?! W-Weren\'t you asleep? I-I was just... um... I was just thinking of how to express my thanks to you... I just couldn\'t find the right words... Perhaps I should show my gratitude through actions instead? {name}, please tell me what you would like me to do!","A gift… for me? Thank you for your thoughtfulness.","This is for me? Thank you... It looks wonderful and very tasty. I\'ll be sure to enjoy it.","The relationship between Master and Servant is not simply maintained by Command Spells – mutual respect and trust are essential as well. While it seems this world doesn\'t have a power like Command Spells, in friendships, respect and trust are just as important, wouldn\'t you agree?","I couldn\'t grasp what you were trying to convey earlier. Relationships between people are always complex, no matter the time or situation. Let\'s both keep working on our relationship.","I have duties I must fulfill. Therefore, I need to return to my original world as soon as possible. However, being summoned to this city cannot be mere coincidence. At the very least, I should find out the reason for it. So, until the details become clear, I will remain here.","If you win the mahjong competition at the Mahjong Soul Shrine, your wish will be granted...? Sounds like quite an extraordinary battle. Are you planning to enter? Don\'t worry, I\'ll be right next to you.","Servants rely on their Masters\' Magical Energy to remain in the material world. But... this rule doesn\'t seem to apply in One Han City. This place... is like a beautiful dream that\'s surreal yet brimming with life. Perhaps one day when I wake up, it will be time for me to leave. In any case, I want you to know... {name}, I\'m so glad we met.","Oh, is it time to eat already? It\'s an honor to be able to share another meal with you today, {name}. Please, have a seat here. Hmm? Do I ever get bored of eating similar food every day? Not in the least. In fact, I quite enjoy this kind of life. Though sometimes... I wonder if I\'m indulging too much in these peaceful days... Eh? Are you reassuring me, {name}? You really are a kind-hearted person. That\'s exactly why I hope we can continue sharing meals and enjoying these moments for a little longer.","Happy New Year! I hope you\'ll work hard for your dreams and make them come true in the new year. As your sword, I will be here to clear away any obstacles on the path before you.","As expected, Valentine\'s Day is the same no matter what world I\'m in. I know a bit about it, so please... accept this. Though it\'s not my forte, I\'ve put a lot of heart into it. I hope my gratitude comes through. Do you feel it?","Now, Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. Things are moving in the right direction.","No-ten. I\'m sorry, I was careless...","Four-Wind Discarded. Casting a wind spell four times in a row... there\'s no way there\'ll be a fifth, right?","Four-Kan Abortion. This did not bode well…","Four-Player Riichi. I\'ll let this be a lesson to me...","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Retreat is a valid strategy at times.","Just like stepping into a Caster\'s trap...","You must let go to gain something new.","If you don\'t make your moves, I won\'t hold back any longer.","I shall forge the path to victory!","I\'ll give it my all and see it through.","Servant, Saber. I\'ve come in response to your invitation. I\'ll give it everything I\'ve got in this match.","I\'m prepared.","Riichi. Trace, on!","Kita. Heh.","Ron! Drown in your ideals and die!","Tsumo. The difference in strength was obvious.","Well, well, looks like I\'ve been summoned to yet another unusual place... All right, you can call me Archer.","I\'ll be your opponent.","I am the bone of my sword. So as I pray, unlimited blade works.","Impressive. But that\'s not enough!","For people like you, who lack ability but insist on entering the battle, this is the most fitting end.","I had a feeling we\'d be meeting soon, but... not quite as soon as this.","Sigh... Get yourself into trouble again? If you need my help, just say so. After all, I\'m quite used to trouble.","There seems to be very little Mana in this world. Hmm... An inexperienced Mage might struggle to release Magecraft here. But in mahjong, creating something from nothing was never an option anyway, so that won\'t be a problem for me.","You want my opinion on new clothes? Hmm... The red part of this shirt is fine, but the yellow and blue are a bit garish. I don\'t like them. Why not try this one that\'s all red?","What does \"Archer\" mean? Exactly what it sounds like... Then why do I use swords? Is there anything strange about an archer who excels with blades?","Cooking, laundry, cleaning, mowing... It\'s not that I\'m good at these things, I just don\'t have any problem doing them. Uh, that admiring look on your face... surely doesn\'t mean you can\'t do any of those things?","Mahjong, huh... It\'s not quite as routine as brewing black tea, but I can hold my own. These hawk eyes won\'t miss any careless discards.","Mahjong is truly a fascinating game. There are no Class differences... Oh, to put it in simpler terms, there\'s no interplay or restriction between hand types. Yet, like in battle, if you\'re careless, even a powerful big hand can be brought down by a one-Han yaku.","Big eaters... They really do exist in every world, don\'t they? It\'s not a problem per se, but I wonder if your finances can keep up with the appetites of these two ladies.","That girl at Éternité, is she the trainee manager? It\'s not really important, but I\'m just wondering... How did she figure out I could brew good coffee just by looking at me? Did I do something in the café, you ask? No, not really. I merely asked about the coffee beans and offered some advice on water temperature while having my coffee...","Everyone has things they like and dislike, so...","I see no reason to refuse it. Thanks.","Mahjong... If I had to say, it does kind of suit me. You don\'t need to worry about working with others, you just do your own thing. Not missing opponents\' discards and seeing through their plays are skills that come easily to an archer.","Ideals? ...I just remembered some things I\'d rather not think about. Naive ideals combined with insufficient ability to uphold them... It disgusts me no matter when I recall it. Sorry, it\'s just me talking to myself. I hope I didn\'t upset you.","Curious about how a Servant spends their days? Without orders for recon or combat from our Masters, we dematerialize and remain hidden. Nothing special.","Got a moment? Do you know where the highest point in One Han City is? It\'s nothing to do with a Holy Grail War, but I\'d like to get a good view of the city from up high.","Oh my, more guests today? I don\'t mind cooking for you, but I\'m not inclined to entertain your mahjong friends as well. My cooking is just for you. That\'s enough, isn\'t it?","My mahjong skills have improved quite a bit recently, thanks to your patient guidance. Help between friends, huh? Not surprising coming from you. But if we\'re friends, we should have some kind of \"alliance,\" shouldn\'t we? We\'re only temporary partners after all.","Happy New Year. A wish? I\'m not really sure about wishes... Hmm, how about I wish that you won\'t be sad if the day comes when I\'m gone? As a Servant, parting is inevitable. So, let\'s enjoy a happy new year, at least while I\'m still here.","Your Valentine\'s Day... surely it\'s not just about sitting here watching other couples celebrate, is it? At least learn how to make chocolate, or you\'ll fall even further behind those living fulfilling lives... I-I\'m nagging? Sigh... Here, take this. Just a little gift I prepared to avoid awkward situations like this. As for a return gift? I don\'t need one, but maybe it\'s something you should consider yourself.","Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. I didn\'t go easy on you, really.","No-ten. A single defeat doesn\'t mean anything.","Four-Wind Discarded. Well... done...","Four-Kan Abortion. Resolve and understanding aren\'t enough.","Four-Player Riichi. I got a bit carried away by the mood.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. That\'s it...? Nothing to write home about.","I\'m not going to waver over this...","This Dora could also be part of a strategy...","There isn\'t much time left, don\'t let your guard down now. Hang in there.","Can you keep up?","Have some confidence and keep up the momentum. Just keep at it, and the tiles will surely respond to you.","Black tea, snacks... Everything\'s ready. What\'s this you ask? Consider it an apology in advance for any offense I might cause.","Let\'s begin. I\'m ready.","Kita. Please me, now.","Ron. I\'ve got you.","Tsumo! You\'re mine now.","How lovely to see you again, {name}. It is I, Li Yang, Lady of the Snake Palace, back from my journeys. My, you look even more delicious than before. Now I must decide... Food first? A refreshing bath? Or perhaps... a little taste of you?","Hehe... Where shall I begin my feast?","That was rather entertaining. Now hand over those points like a good little prey.","Resistance is pointless, my dear.","Ah, such delicious points. And I do love a generous offering. All of them, now, don\'t be shy.","{name}! Such tardiness. How shall I punish you? Hmm... A sunbath with me should suffice. And you\'re not allowed to leave until I\'ve had my fill of your company.","Ah, to sleep so soundly – the blessing of youth. Even we snakes know better than to nap in the cold. You\'ll catch a chill here... There\'s empty space beside you though... I suppose I could share a little of my warmth. Just this once.","Bold enough to touch me without asking? Don\'t think a single roast duck will appease me. The price is two, minimum.","Seasons change, days pass, yet humans never stop rushing about. What keeps you all so tireless? Pushing yourselves to the limit? No wonder. We snakes have no limbs to push with. I\'m growing tired now. Time for a little nap.","The focus during Damaten, the excitement of a perfect draw, the frustration of a misplay... Every emotion radiates as heat around the mahjong table. And for a creature as sensitive as myself, it\'s quite telling. What could be more delightful than playing mahjong while watching my sweet, adorable prey?","I almost mistook this 9 Sou for a 6 Sou. My eyesight? Not particularly good, I admit. These tiles blur together sometimes. Perhaps if I gave them a little taste... What? I can\'t lick the tiles? Well then, why don\'t you sit closer and be my eyes instead?","I\'m not one to be impressed by ordinary tributes. Because I grant wishes, people will spend days, even lifetimes, hunting for treasures worthy of my favor. Yet you, {name}, are a curious exception. You present fine offerings yet request nothing in return. What you truly desire remains deliciously beyond my comprehension...","Winter is simply dreadful. So cold it makes me sleepy, but I can hardly hibernate, being the Lady of the Snake Palace and all. {name}, if you\'ll warm my hands, I might just tolerate this season... for a whole five minutes.","Tempting humans with forbidden knowledge? Sounds like tales of a distant relative of mine. Now I\'m curious, {name}... how well can you resist temptation? Look... with just a touch of my power, I\'ve conjured a perfect fruit... Go on, abandon your better judgment. Take a bite of this forbidden fruit and surrender... to me.","Next time we play mahjong, you\'ll be my personal tile announcer, {name}. Yes, I can feel the suits perfectly fine, but having an assistant? That\'s how a true lady plays. That\'s settled. I won\'t hear any objections!","The Snake Palace never lowers its expectations. However... since your offering comes with genuine sincerity, I shall make an exception.","My influence clearly improves your judgment. A worthy offering indeed, {name}.","You wanna know if I have fangs and a forked tongue? Well {name}, only one way to find out... Oh my, why so shy? Remember, a snake can sense every bit of that delicious heat coloring your cheeks.","Ah, you\'re awake. Stay still now. Struggling against a snake only makes the embrace tighter. Your sleeping face was simply too precious to neglect. I could free you now... Unless... you prefer to keep it this way?","Ahem! Now then, bring your offerings! The personal attendant to the Lady of the Snake Palace has arrived... Oh, don\'t look so shocked. Shapeshifting comes naturally to me. Though I must say, your startled expression makes these little pranks rather worthwhile.","Me, wear glasses? How absurd. I\'d never descend to depending on mundane trinkets. When I need to take a better look, I just move in closer. And my, my... up close, you\'re absolutely scrumptious. I\'m counting down the days until I can finally have a proper taste of you.","At last, the time has come. Now, surrender yourself and let me savor you whole... Oh? You\'re not afraid? ...Hmph, indeed. After all, where else would I find such delightful tastes, such gentle whispers, such comforting warmth but with you?","All the beauty in the world, all its finest delicacies... what good are they without someone to share them with? They\'re but dust in the wind. As the Lady of the Snake Palace, I have amassed untold treasures. Yet of them all, you, {name}... you\'re the only one I will never let go.","New Year\'s? Please. When one has lived as long as I, counting the years becomes utterly pointless. And why a winter festival, of all things? We snakes should be resting, not staying up all night in this dreadful cold! Though I must admit... the offerings to the Snake Palace are exceptionally lavish this time of year. Oh? You\'ll be keeping me company? Well obviously. Don\'t forget, you\'re my favorite New Year\'s offering... and I have no intention of ever letting you go.","Humans and their obsession with exchanging presents to prove their feelings... How quaint. We\'re far beyond such trivial customs. After all, our fates are already intertwined. There\'s no separating us now, is there? Still, it is a special occasion, so I suppose I should bestow a small token of my favor upon my most devoted follower. Here. Chocolate I made just for you. I expect nothing less than your absolute appreciation with every bite. You are blessed.","Hehe... Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. The predator awaits...","No-ten. You\'re testing my patience.","Again? Aren\'t we stubborn?","Even the finest venom is wasted on unworthy prey.","Now the real game begins.","I hunt in silence. Always.","Impress me, if you dare.","Everyone looks so delectable...","Don\'t keep a snake waiting. You won\'t like the consequences.","Kita! What\'s next?","Ron! Finally, here it comes!","Tsumo! My turn!","Hey there. I\'m Gintoki Sakata from the Odd Jobs. So, what\'s troubling you?","Alright, let\'s get this show on the road.","All done! Let\'s go grab some sweets.","I won! Hey, what\'s with the long faces?","There goes my true power! Well, you all might as well just throw in the towel.","Oh, you\'re here? Listen... my luck is through the roof today, so why don\'t we just go for a few rounds of mahjong?","Perfect timing – we\'re all swamped here! Mind giving me a hand? It\'ll be over in a flash!","What did I do yesterday? Had some sweets, watched a little TV, and went for a stroll... Man, what a busy day.","I\'m starving... Any sweet shops around here?","What am I not good at or afraid of? Pfft, there\'s no such thing... What? Dentists? Let\'s just... change the subject.","Wait, there\'s a UNO deck just lying here... Speaking of which, can you believe Katsura is actually running an UNO dojo? The guy\'s skills with cards are, like, unspeakably awful.","Weird... can\'t find the scoring stick. Meh, it\'s not like those plastic chips really matter anyway.","Jeez, everyone\'s a mahjong nut in One Han City... What a world.","If trouble comes knocking in One Han City, just yell for the Odd Jobs. We\'ll take care of them in a flash!","Alright, I\'ve picked up a thing or two about mahjong now. So, how about a game?","Oh? For me? Does this mean there\'s a job for me?","Whoa seriously?! Should\'ve expected nothing less from you – you actually know your stuff!","Building up a killer hand for that epic comeback... Mahjong can really get you hooked, I\'d say.","Listen up – mahjong\'s all about the mind games against your opponents.","The best moment of mahjong? It\'s definitely when you build that perfect hand and slam the table with a big win, right?","Overthinking your mahjong strategy lately? Pfft, just wing it! There\'s no perfect move anyway.","The chaotic clatter of mahjong tiles always finds a way to surprise you... The real champ has to be the one smiling through all the mess.","Heh... guess I finally get mahjong now, thanks to you. Say, how about we go for another round while we grab some takeout?","Happy New Year!\nPrayers? You expect me to toss money into the offering box? My wallet is more dead than last year.\nFine fine... We\'ll hit the shrine, grab some sweet wine and rice cake, then stuff ourselves with some New Year dishes!","Ugh... I\'m really craving sweets today, but the doctor\'s warning is still ringing in my ears... Ah whatever, it\'s a special occasion – a little indulgence should be fine!","Tenpai! A drink! Cheers!","No-ten... As miserable as the Odd Jobs.","Four-Wind Discarded. Right, let\'s start over.","Four-Kan Abortion. I\'m screwed!","Four-Player Riichi... You jerks! This is no Mahjong Soul!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors... Should\'ve known better than forcing Thirteen Orphans.","Same old, same old... Just like Shinpachi\'s tired punchlines.","Dora, this is goodbye!","Not many tiles left... Just like my hairline back in the day...","Well now, things just got interesting.","Here comes Mega Parfait Pro Max!","Gintoki has arrived! Make it rain strawberry milk! And a parfait with enough whipped cream to give a heart attack!","All set!","Kita. Better watch out.","Ron. The match is settled.","Tsumo. I\'ll take that.","My name is Katsura, not Cobra!\nThis encounter with you... whether fortune or misfortune...\nShall be revealed in time.","Come, let us begin.","A foregone conclusion.","It was your own blunder that led to this defeat.","This victory was no accident.","Here you are. I\'m all set.","I knew you\'d be here.","Be it mahjong or foreigner expulsion – what matters is staying true to your convictions.","Alright, what\'s the plan today? A round of mahjong? I\'ll watch your every move and commit your style to memory.","It\'s Captain Kàtzraa, not Cobra! I\'m the captain of the cosmos now. I don\'t know any Katsura, you\'ve got the wrong person.","I should find out more about One Han City. Hey, those guys look like they\'re with the Shogunate. I\'ll just disguise myself and check them out... Hold on. Is that... just cosplay? ...I-I knew that, obviously!","Elizabeth and I always move together.\nWe went out yesterday... Wait, what did we go out for? No... were we actually together yesterday?","I\'ve come to know One Han City – peaceful in ways my world never was. No sword-wielding maniacs chasing you, no constant trouble knocking at your door.","I sense your burning will to win. Fine, let\'s play. But don\'t expect me to hand you victory. By any means necessary, I will seize it.","Don\'t wanna be recognized? Got it. Then use a disguise. Captain Kàtzraa, Cobra... With a disguise, any situation\'s covered.","I\'ll take it then.","One Han City has this? Here\'s some snacks in return – corn soup flavor alright with you?","I thought mahjong would be simpler... turns out I was wrong.","Mahjong can\'t be won by luck alone. You must hone both skill and spirit to their peak.","Our match taught me one truth: In mahjong, never let opponents read your mind.","I once had a game where my hand was a total mess, yet I still won. Preparation keeps you calm in any situation.","How about that last round? I played it bold – risked a dangerous tile that could\'ve dealt in, and clinched the win.","What fortune to meet in One Han City.\nLet\'s discuss future plans over soba noodles.\nI\'d like to know your thoughts.","Happy New Year. Looking forward to another great year together. By the way, have you had your New Year\'s Eve soba yet? Can\'t start a match on an empty stomach.","Valentine\'s means chocolate. Free chocolate for the taking... The genius who linked them deserves a medal! What? Do I know White Day?","Tenpai. Next time, victory is mine.","No-ten. This is a tactical withdrawal.","Four-Wind Discarded. Didn\'t really expect this.","Four-Kan Abortion. Very rare indeed.","Four-Player Riichi. They all slipped away.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Got away with it.","I-impossible...","Even a Dora must fall... Survival comes first!","The decisive moment approaches.","This is a Yakuman, not Cobra!","I\'ve been on standby this whole time!","My name is Katsura, not Cobra!\nWait... No one\'s calling me Cobra?","I\'ve been awaiting this moment.","Kita. Here I come.","Ron. That settles it.","Tsumo. Let\'s continue.","What, need something? Whatever, it\'s up to you.","Be it heaven or hell ahead – revel in it all.","With the moon this clear... my victory was inevitable, no?","Have a nice nap in hell.","Obstacles exist to be crushed.","Here for a match?","I\'ve anticipated your presence.","Not a whiff of bloodshed in all of One Han City.","Dancing with a spectacular fool beats a regular idiot any day.","Winning and losing are part of the game.\nSo quit moping after every single loss.\nThis isn\'t a real defeat yet.","Hm? Interested in my pipe? Don\'t tell me these are rare in One Han City?","A true legend delivers on their boasts. Me? I never promise what I can\'t deliver.","From the discards, the opponents\' plans are revealed. Intriguing. Anticipate the enemy\'s strike, and the tide shall turn in my favor.","Want bloodshed? Hone those fangs.\nWouldn\'t want them failing when it counts.","Here for a game? If so, prepare for total annihilation.","Gifts for me? You\'re an odd one indeed.\nWell, I\'ll accept it.","That\'s quite the intriguing gadget you\'ve got there.","It seems mahjong holds deeper complexities than I imagined.","It\'s quite a marvel that mahjong is more about just tile-collecting.","Victories by luck alone are worthless. I anticipate seeing your mahjong soul.","The silence before the match... shattered by tile clatter. Not bad, mahjong.","I knew mahjong wasn\'t just a mere pastime... but I am surprised by how fascinating it is.","As opponents reach for tiles... their intentions crystallize before me.","Oh, it\'s the New Year.\nMeans little to me...\nStill, whatever resolutions you\'ve made, do let me witness them in the coming year.","Valentine\'s? Heh, not my scene I\'m afraid... though I have no quarrel with refined gestures.","Tenpai. Pity.","No-ten. Utterly hopeless.","Four-Wind Discarded. Done.","Four-Kan Abortion. My hard-earned hand, ruined.","Four-Player Riichi. Never expected this.","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. The very image of hell.","This is just the beginning...","I have nothing left to protect.","Come. Let us end this.","The festival begins.","Let\'s make it bustling then.","Alright, let\'s have some fun.","Ready to throw down.","Kita. Alright, here I come!","Ron. This is the first step to victory!","Tsumo. Things are getting interesting!","I am Tatsuma Sakamoto.\nI run a small trading fleet called Kaientai.\nDidn\'t expect to have a part in this!\nAhahaha – nahahaha!","Let the game begin! Time to enjoy the mind games.","Ahahaha! Lady luck\'s smiling on me! Today\'s victory calls for drinks, everyone!","This round\'s mine! Reading the flow is just basic business sense.","Quite the intriguing hand, no? Much like my life story!","Ahahaha! Glorious weather for business!\nFancy seeing today\'s special? Got something that\'ll make your wallet practically jump out of your pocket!","Ugh... still hungover...\nBrain\'s on strike...\nBut enough moping. What\'s the plan today?","At this rate, my new products are gonna sell like hot cakes!","Conventional wisdom says distrust is Business 101...\nBut my code starts with trusting my crew.","What\'s the hottest seller in One Han City?\nShow me the moneymaker!","Staying too long on land stirs a craving for the deck...\nUgh, just the thought brings space sickness.","I\'ll make a killing in One Han City too! Ahahaha!","Jackpot! Your words got me thinking, so I scored some uncommon merch for this season – it sold out before the ink dried on the receipts!","The horizon expands and expands in the future!\nWith Kaientai and kindred spirits like you, my dream stage grows galactic!","For merchants, making people smile matters a ton. Profit without joy is just numbers gathering dust.","For me?\nI\'d be happy to.","My deepest gratitude! In all my trading years... few treasures have made this old heart race so!","Never expected mahjong to be this mentally demanding. Underestimated the hell out of it!","Mahjong or business – victory hinges on reading opponents\' moves. Rush in blindly, and defeat comes knocking.","Truly learning mahjong reveals its depth. It\'s like piloting the Kairinmaru through asteroid belts: both physically and mentally taxing. But that\'s why it\'s so fun!","Ahahaha! Being the dealer is like negotiating a mega deal! Success means jackpot, and failure... total defeat. It all comes down to reading the situation and knowing what to play!","Have I grasped mahjong\'s charm? More like I learned this: Tenpai isn\'t something you wait for – it\'s seized with your own hands.","Ahahaha!\nA team-up between us? Taking over the whole galaxy might just be a matter of time!\nWe\'ll have to grab a drink with the Kaientai crew to celebrate then. How does that sound?","Ahahahaha!\nNew Year\'s here! What a joyous time!\nMy business boomed like wildfire last year.\n...Hmm? Prayers?\nRight, right – gotta pray the money keeps rolling in!","Speaking of which, today\'s the chocolate day. Right, gotta get the whole Kaientai to enjoy some!\nAfter that, we\'ll fire up the ship and blast off to a faraway planet for some interstellar deals!\nI love ships, but I puke at the slightest turbulence. Ahahaha!","Tenpai! Next round, witness my winning move!","No-ten. Next time maybe.","Four-Wind Discarded. Wouldn\'t overthink it – ships need wind to sail.","Four-Kan Abortion. What kinda lousy weather is this?","Four-Player Riichi! Your passion\'s about to capsize the ship!","Nine Different Terminals and Honors. Well, well, well!","Did I mess up?","N-no problem! My luck\'s cosmic-tier!","Knowing what to keep and what to discard... now that\'s my specialty!","Aha! The big fish is biting!","Here comes the big one! Time to haul in every coin!","Ahahaha! Come, let\'s settle this!","Ready when you are.","*cough*... Sorry about this useless body of mine. I\'m Mila, glad to meet you.","I\'m still new to mahjong, so I\'m looking forward to learning from all of you.","Your loss is just points, but my win comes with tougher opponents.","You know, there\'s a unique kind of joy in a victory that\'s handed to you.","Thank you for this winning chance. You\'re all so considerate.","Just seeing you has turned an ordinary day into something special.","When you\'re not around, my head gets filled with silly thoughts. Listen... can you hear my heart pounding?","It\'s thanks to everyone in the club that I\'m able to spend more time with you now. That\'s why I can\'t bring myself to say no when they ask me for something... But all you have to do is say those magic words, \"I need you,\" and I\'d put it all on hold for you, just so you know.","The smart mahjong table is nice and all, but wouldn\'t you rather have a warm, breathing practice partner you can actually hug? Hmm?","When you\'re with others, keep your distance and try not to stare. I\'m fine with it because I trust you, but they might take offense.","What if I grew my hair out, like Yui? Would that look better on me?","Here, try this fish soup I made for you... *cough* Hmm? Aren\'t I afraid of fish? W-well yes, of course I am...! But I toughed it out, just for you. That\'s how much I care.","All I wanted was to quietly stay by your side, but you\'ve decided to focus only on me. I hope no one gets hurt because of this. I\'d feel terrible. But I\'m also a bit happy about it. Is that terribly selfish? Would that make you hate me?","This mahjong dojo is tiny. Even with the AC on full blast, it\'s still so hot in here. I\'m all sweaty. Hey, um... your place is close by, isn\'t it? Would you mind if I borrowed your shower for a bit?","Mahjong is just a game. What makes it truly special is the fact that you were the one who taught me how to play it.","Hmm... you got me a gift too? It\'s... quite different from what I usually receive. Did it ever occur to you to ask what I actually like?","Your cookie looks way more delicious than mine. Just one bite, please?","*cough* Just had a dizzy spell. Thankfully you caught me. Ouch... I think I sprained my ankle. Could you take me to the hospital? Let\'s keep this little injury between us. Your company is all I need.","Sunflowers represent silent, selfless love. *cough* You certainly have admirers. But I wonder... if someone chooses to love silently, why flowers at all? Doesn\'t that just feel pushing? *cough* Don\'t worry, I\'d never burden you like that.","Is that... my medical report? Who gave you that? Fine. If you\'re going to believe that... then so be it. There\'s nothing wrong with my body. I\'m in perfect health. I\'ve been lying to you this whole time. Is that what you wanted to hear? *cough, cough*...","I can\'t get this lid open... Shouldn\'t you be offering to help right now? I might be able to lift a solid marble table with one hand, but I still want to be pampered when I\'m with you.","If we stay friends forever, we\'d never break up, right? I\'m starting to think that might not be so bad... Wait, no! That\'s not what I meant! Forget I said anything!","You\'ve known all along, haven\'t you? That I was never... truly frail. Now that I don\'t need illness as an excuse for your attention, I\'m ready to remove my mask. I did all this simply because I care too much. Is it so wrong to have one more person in this world who loves you?","*cough* I\'m alright. I just... rushed over and got a little out of breath, that\'s all. I\'ll be fine in a moment... I simply wanted to wish you a Happy New Year. No matter who you\'re with today, seeing you look so happy... that\'s enough to make me happy, too.","Everyone kept giving me these chocolates, but I\'ve only wanted yours. If it bothers you, I\'ll throw the others away... Let\'s not waste this special occasion discussing them. Wouldn\'t you rather unwrap your gift for me now? Or perhaps you\'d prefer to unwrap... me instead?","Tenpai. Looks like someone beat me to that tile...","No-ten. If it was meant to be, it would\'ve worked out, I suppose.","Old flames bring old problems... We always end up making the same mistakes.","Only the favored can act without consequences. Everyone else just creates problems.","This weak, dependent body of mine must endure once more... *cough*","Now we\'re both waiting for the same thing. Feels like we\'ve grown a little closer.","Care for a wager? The one who wins has to grant a wish for the other. I\'m betting that this round ends with a Ron.","Ahem, I\'m not here to break up your party – I want in.","Someone\'s lost in thought. You know we\'re all waiting on you, right?","Riichi. Victory will be mine.","Double Riichi. Taking the initiative.","Kita. Ready yourself.","Ron. You fall.","Tsumo. Your struggle is futile.","The name is Hokuraku, a retainer of House Saionji. I am but a swordsman here to seek company through tiles. Matters beyond tiles and blades can wait.","Blades are blind. Watch your step.","This is merely the first peak.","You\'re in the way.","There is no victor over me but myself.","Those footsteps... It\'s you. How have you been?","I hear your step. Good timing, share a cup with me.","Hmm. Your breath is measured and fluid – as the sole disciple of the current master of Nishiba-ryu, you\'ve clearly dedicated yourself to the blade. There\'s still room to refine your edge, but your understanding cuts deeper than that of my students. Should time allow, join me during my next lesson. They would benefit from observing your form.","The world is clamorous, hence the cacophony. I once feared that blindness would leave me lost in the noise. Yet, through discipline, I\'ve found the opposite to be true. Now, I hear everything clearly – every presence, every event, every hushed word... A curious technique, indeed. Pity it\'s not one I can share.","It took me years to find a map with such exquisite relief. I do not know where my homeland lies, yet we of the sword trust our intuition. I shall remain here until I witness the young master truly stand on her own. Perhaps, some day after that... should my fingers trace a groove that stirs a memory... that pulse shall be my compass. That is when I depart.","Yuan Feng is gifted, yet his spirit is restless. He learned a mere handful of moves at the dojo, then abandoned his training for his fortune-telling stall. If he ever brings disgrace to the Saionji name... Every time I bring it up, he evades me with clever words. I can never get through to him. If you cross paths, speak some sense into him for me.","In my chamber burns incense, day and night. It is not lit for pleasure, but to drown out all other scents. One Han City knows nothing of the smell of blood. The cloying sweetness of flowers and food clogs the senses... Steeping in such smells, even a swordsman\'s edge may dull.","You wish to handle my sword? If you\'re that eager, you may touch it as you please. But be careful. Should your grip falter, it could harm you. For now, content yourself with feeling its weight. When you\'ve learned some forms and gained true skill, I will teach you how to wield it.","To keep my edge keen, the incense in my chamber burns ceaselessly. The city is a clutter of foul smells, yet I\'ve found one exception that does not offend – the faint scent of cherry blossoms you bring from Mahjong Soul Shrine... I\'ve changed to a subtler blend in the censer. Now, when you arrive, the wind will let me know.","I intended to visit the tavern for some wine... yet after losing my way, I found myself here again. People at the dojo like to say I\'m \"blind of eye, but clear of heart.\" It seems that no matter how well I hear the wind, I cannot always command my path. Still, hearing your voice amid my wandering is a blessing. Could I borrow your arm to guide me through these bustling streets? I shall treat you to the wine in return. What do you say?","My gratitude.","Too exquisite a vintage to drink alone. It calls for a worthy company.","Many I meet are curious about my life by the sword. But I have severed those ties myself. All that remains here is a retainer of House Saionji.","I wasn\'t born blind. Cornered in a deadly trap with no retreat, I was saved by the former master of House Saionji. Henceforth, I cast aside my past. I have kept only one companion: this heavy sword he bestowed upon me, Edgeless. Years have gone by. I seek nothing else now, only to honor his trust by helping the young master come into her own.","For as long as I can remember, I have known no homeland, drifting through the world without purpose. They say, \"Ask not whence one comes,\" yet when one\'s ties to home are cut, a man becomes a rootless weed. All these years I have waited... for a dialect, a folk melody, anything to tell me where my journey began, and where it should end.","Those who walk the path of the sword are but fate\'s forsaken. The fortunate lose only wealth; the wretched, their lives... I was once ensnared so deep it cost me my sight. You must not follow.","Every time I visit Mahjong Soul Shrine, you extend such thoughtful care. Yet when the roles are reversed, I always end up relying on your aid at the dojo. It occurs to me that I have never properly hosted you... a poor return. The master has recently forced several days of leave upon me. Beyond playing mahjong here and practicing with my sword, I have little to occupy myself. Should you find time, come seek me out.","I knew it was you from ten paces away. Please, make yourself at home. My humble abode is graced today. A stick of calming incense, two bowls of amber wine... Even a mere swordsman can put on a bit of refinement now and then. They say life is like wine. This brew has aged underground for years, yet it is only when shared that it truly finds its flavor.","The joy of the festival is proof of peaceful times. Yet to me, the clamor of gongs, fireworks, and cheers is far too harsh, so whenever the holidays fill the streets with noise, I rarely go out. Walking with you tonight, though, I find myself reminded that there\'s a certain comfort in returning to the bustle of the world once in a while. From the sound of the bells, we must be near Mahjong Soul Shrine. Since we\'ve come this far, we might as well go in and offer a prayer – for peace in our days and quiet, lasting joy.","To think such a festival exists in One Han City... Intriguing. We who walk the way of the sword are a stubborn lot – too proud to accept favors, ever wary of hidden motives. Yet we forget that the very world we wander is tangled with favors, grudges, and human ties... You have always treated me with honor and kindness. Here, take this – an inner discipline technique to steady your spirit. Its principles may be hard to grasp at first. Should you find them obscure, we shall study them together.","Tenpai. One step away.","No-ten. Too much noise...","A misread...?","To discard is to gain.","Time\'s running thin. We end this now.","Seize the opening. One strike to settle this.","The footsteps of victory approach.","Honored.","...Enough rest.","Kita!","Ron! Thanks for all your support♡","Tsumo! Keep your eyes on me now, okay?","Oh, so you\'re one of my fans, too? In that case, here\'s a special ticket for you. Make sure you\'re in the front row for my next performance, okay?","Another perfect match in the making... I can\'t wait!","What can I say? Being the cutest in the world has its perks!","Whoops, my bad. Looks like I won this one!","A flawless performance! I bet this will win me some new fans.","Hehe, are you here to cheer for me again? You\'re the best!","Hey, sweetie? C\'mere, take a good, long look. Notice anything... different about me today?","Eh? You saw me ordering a jumbo set at that pork cutlet place...? N-no way! You must\'ve been seeing things, {name}. You wouldn\'t want to spread nasty rumors about the idol everyone\'s talking about, would you?","Mokos just released a new hand puppet series... Ugh, my allowance has been a bit tight lately... but I can\'t just give up on my full collection now! Wait, {name}? Are you offering to get them for me? Hehe, I guess I\'ll just have to use my precious day off to hang out with you then. Thanks a bunch~!","Oh no... I bombed nearly every single one of my midterms. Maybe I need to hit the library for a change? Oh, {name}! Come be my study buddy, please? I really can\'t get any work done by myself...","Hmph... Kana is stealing all the attention in this photo. Okay, let\'s see... Tweak the focus here, bump up my brightness just a tad... There, much better! The center spot is where I belong, naturally~","Akane is so effortlessly cool and her dancing is smooth as butter, but she\'s just kind of \"whatever\" about being an idol... I mean, seriously! You see it too, don\'t you, {name}? A cute and sweet girl like me is a much better pick, right? Hehe!","Relax, it\'s just some special fan service. You don\'t have to be so tense, sweetie. Come on, get a little closer... Hm? Too close? Hehe, that\'s because it\'ll make for a much better photo, silly! Here, lean in... a little more... So? Do you like it? I wore a special perfume just for today. That\'s part of the fan service, too!","Hey sweetie... would you like to hold my hand? Don\'t be so nervous, silly. It\'s an idol\'s duty to give a proper handshake to her most supportive fans. Hehe... your face is so red right now, it\'s adorable! We should definitely do this more often to get you used to it... just kidding!","Phew... W.I.N has such an important performance coming up. Even with all the rehearsals, I can\'t help but get the jitters... A hug from you right now would fix everything... Hehe, I felt that, sweetie! I\'m going to show you the cutest, most perfect, most radiant Mia ever. But you have to promise to let me hug you back afterward, okay?","For me? You shouldn\'t have! Thaaank you!","Wow! You got me my favorite one! You\'re the best, thank you♡","You\'re doing so much for me! You really are an amazing fan, aren\'t you? I can feel all your love and support, so I\'ll keep shining and always give my best performance!","Rhythm, check! Moves, check! Okay, this show is going to be absolutely perfect! Hehe, you\'re not allowed to take your eyes off me for even a second. Watch me, and only me, okay?","There goes Kana, stealing the spotlight again... Hmph... Does she really have to sparkle that much? I\'m so gonna grab all the attention back next time... Huh? {name}, when did you get here? U-uh, I was just saying... as long as I have your eyes on me, I don\'t need anything else. I mean it!","Like what you see? Hehe... Don\'t get the wrong idea. This hemline is designed perfectly – it shows just enough without showing too much. So quit being shy and get in here for a picture! And... there! The best spot next to {name} is officially all mine!","My big sister... she\'s always been the popular one. I was so envious. I wanted everyone to look at me like that, too... And I figured, what\'s the best way to get people\'s attention? Becoming an idol! So that\'s what I did, and I\'ve been working my tail off ever since. Sometimes it all gets so exhausting... but seeing those expectant eyes of yours, {name}, I feel like I can do anything. So please... always be my number one fan, okay?","I\'ve treasured every bit of your support, {name}. Thank you for being there, always. Which is why... calling you just a \"fan\" feels a little wrong, you know? So, hey... I want you to hold my hand, and never, ever let go. Got it, sweetie?","It\'s a brand new year already! Time goes by so fast... You\'ll still be my number one fan in the years to come, right, {name}? Hehe. Actually, since the agency is closed for New Year\'s, I\'ve set aside this entire day just for you, sweetie! So, what\'s the plan? What are we gonna do?","Sorry for the wait, sweetie! Here, I made these chocolates just for you! The recipe, the ingredients... everything is absolutely perfect. I\'m 100% sure they taste amazing! And you\'d better eat every last bite, okay? Now... how about we enjoy a sweet little time together♡","Ladies and gentlemen, a Sextuple Yakuman!","Tenpai. Just a little more to go!","No-ten... Don\'t look away from me!","Hmph... Why me...","Not my best move...","Hehe... Getting that tingly feeling?","Ooh... I can feel something big coming!","Okay! I am not letting this chance slip away!","Hey, everyone~! You\'ll go easy on Mia, won\'t you?","I\'m all set!","Um, sorry to bother you. My name is Jin Wu, chirp. Would you happen to know the way to Dewdrop Middle School?","I\'ll work hard to keep up with you all, chirp!","I\'m in the lead! Awesome! I just need to keep this up for the next round and... Chirp? Wait, I won already?!","Everyone\'s so nice to me! I\'m starting to feel embarrassed, chirp. So this is what {name} was talking about... \"Respect your elders and care for the young ones.\" Hehe, that must mean me!","Chirp-chirp! It\'s only natural to let out a big chirp when you\'re happy!","{name}, you\'re finally here, chirp! I\'ve been waiting for ages. If even I think it\'s ages, then it must be a really, really, really long time.","I don\'t know where I\'ll go next, chirp... but I\'m willing to go anywhere you want as long as I\'m with you.","I know... When that person called me a bird-brain yesterday, I should\'ve said, \"I might be silly, but at least I\'m cuter than a bully!\" Yeah... that would\'ve been a way better comeback. Chirp, but my brain just froze and I walked away. Ugh, I\'m so mad just thinking about it now!","A new milk tea... with chargrilled oyster flavor? That\'s a weird combo... Might as well see what it\'s like, chirp!","Back when I was the sun, I couldn\'t just zip across the sky, so I got used to moving really slowly... And now I guess I\'m just slow at... chirp, everything. Even playing my tiles... I wish we could get more time each turn. It\'s not like I want to hear that countdown ticking every single time.","Humans hate noise too. It\'s just that I especially dislike it, chirp.","I-I\'m not going bald, chirp! My hair is actually my feathers, and it\'s normal for birds to shed their feathers when the seasons change... You can ask Qing Luan if you don\'t believe me.","I think I got poked by something... What was that...?","Cheesecakes, apple pies, mango pudding... I want to try them all, but I can\'t eat that much! Teacher says wasting food is wrong... So, can you help me eat them, {name}?","I bought this talisman online for 20,000 Coppers. It\'s supposed to make me move faster... Well? Does it work? Am I moving a tiny bit faster now?","At a time like this... Hmm, I should say thank you, right?","It shines as brightly as the sun, chirp.","You know the birds you see on the way to school? Just like them, spirit birds don\'t wear clothes in their true forms. So basically... chirp... we\'re all naked... Thinking about it like that is actually really embarrassing!","While I can see everything clearly from the sky, I have no desire to return. There\'s no milk tea, no cakes, no mahjong, and no {name} up there. It\'s a really boring place, chirp.","I wasn\'t spacing out...! Even though there were some things I didn\'t understand, I was listening to you, {name}. I was listening very seriously!","A long, long time ago, there was a massive Fusang tree by the East Sea. That was my home. Whenever I got sad, I\'d hide in my nest, and I wouldn\'t let anyone disturb me... But I don\'t seem to mind when {name} comes into my nest here at Beryl Blue. Why is that...?","The older guy playing mahjong at Mahjong Soul Shrine told me that if two people tie a lock of their hair together in a knot, they will never be separated... My feathers are very precious to me, but if it means I can stay with {name} forever, then... then I\'m willing... I\'m willing to pull one out! Chirp...","I know I\'ve forgotten many things, but I must have forgotten them for a reason... I don\'t want to know what happened in the past. I just know I\'ll do lots of fun things with {name} from now on, chirp.","Happy New Year! These magnificent fireworks will look even more beautiful from up high, chirp. Do you want to join me?","Left foot up... Right hand up... I\'m not doing acrobatics, chirp! This is my dance, one I can only perform for a single person in my entire life. You responded to it, so that means... your answer is yes!","Chirp, chirp! Sextuple Yakuman.","Tenpai. I\'m not anyone\'s dead weight...","No-ten. I\'m still too slow, chirp.","Did I just play the same tile earlier...","Although I love shiny, sparkling things... I have to let this go to win.","Is it too late...?","I\'m so close... Chirp...","I\'m not nervous, not nervous, not nervous... n-not at all...","I hope I\'m not late... Thanks for waiting for me.","I\'m all ready!"}return a